NK027(sha)001:1: // mdo dbang rtsa ba'i dal don bzhi pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:4: bcu gcig gi gsang sngags bla na med pa'i theg pa rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:10: dang po la phyi nang gi bshags pa bya ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:12: de la phyi'i bshags pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:13: spang skong sogs sngar byas pa la bsdus kyang 'gal ba med do //
NK027(sha)001:15: na rag bskang bshags kyi cho ga ci tsam 'grub par bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:16: gnyis pa dal gyi cho ga la don lnga ste /
NK027(sha)001:23: steg byi dor byas la ba byung lngas byugs /
NK027(sha)001:24: de nas yan lag rab gnas ni /
NK027(sha)001:25: steg bu gra gcig tu man+dala pad+ma 'dab brgyad mdzes
NK027(sha)001:26: tshon du byas pa'i mtha' rdo rje ra bas bskor
NK027(sha)001:27: ba / de'i dbus su rin po che'i bum pa sna tshogs rdo rjes mtshan pa'i nang du /
NK027(sha)001:28: chu gtsang mar snying po nyi shu rtsa lnga tshang ba blug /
NK027(sha)001:29: kha rgyan mgul ching gzungs thag dang bcas pa bsham /
NK027(sha)001:30: shar du dam tshig thig dang gtor ma /
NK027(sha)001:34: pho brang gi dbus su rin po che'i snod du tshon lnga /
NK027(sha)001:36: dam rdzas bdud rtsi rnam gsum bzhag /
NK027(sha)001:37: rdo rje slob dpon gyi mdun du rigs kyi bum pa la so so'i thugs phyag mtshan ni /
NK027(sha)001:38: phyi nang gi mchod pa lnga tshangs par bsham /
NK027(sha)001:39: de nas slob dpon chas gos dkar po gon la /
NK027(sha)001:43: badz+ra kro ta sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK027(sha)001:45: ma sur+ya ma d+ha la h'u /
NK027(sha)001:46: badz+ra kro ta h'u ka ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:48: badz+ra kro ta bi dza ya h'u /
NK027(sha)001:49: ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:50: badz+ra kro ta ni la tan+t+ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:51: da ha da ha h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:52: badz+ra kro ta ya man+ta ka h'u /
NK027(sha)001:53: pa tsa pa tsa h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:54: badz+ra kro ta ar+ya a tsa la h'u /
NK027(sha)001:56: badz+ra kro ta h+ya g+h+ri wa h'u /
NK027(sha)001:57: hu lu hu lu h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:58: badz+ra kro ta a pa ra tsi ta h'u /
NK027(sha)001:60: badz+ra kro ta a mri ta kun+d+ha li h'u /
NK027(sha)001:62: badz+ra kro ta kre lok+sha h'u /
NK027(sha)001:64: badz+ra kro ta ma h+aa pa la h'u /
NK027(sha)001:65: s+pho ta s+pho ta h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:66: ces pas rol mo sgra dang bcas pas mtshams bcad do //
NK027(sha)001:68: ye nas mnyam nyid chos sku dag pa las //
NK027(sha)001:69: ma rig dbang gi sgro dang bskur btab ste //
NK027(sha)001:70: bde dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs so sor smin //
NK027(sha)001:71: de bzlog don phyir rgyal ba'i dam mnos te //
NK027(sha)001:72: bdag cag ma rig lus dang ngag sems kyi //
NK027(sha)001:73: bag med tshul gyi dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK027(sha)001:74: rgyal ba 'khor bcas thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK027(sha)001:75: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK027(sha)001:76: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:77: byang chub mchog tu bdag gi sems bskyed de //
NK027(sha)001:78: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med byang chub sems //
NK027(sha)001:79: deng nas tshul bzhin yongs su bzung bar bgyi //
NK027(sha)001:80: dus gsum sangs rgyas 'khor dang bcas //
NK027(sha)001:81: rang bzhin gnas nas sku bskyod de //
NK027(sha)001:82: mkhyen pas gnas mchog 'dir gshegs nas //
NK027(sha)001:83: brtse bas byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK027(sha)001:85: dam bca' byin dbab byas la /
NK027(sha)001:86: yang dag zhi khro thung ba'i bstod pa yan chad bya /
NK027(sha)001:89: gu gul gyi dud bas bdug cing /
NK027(sha)001:90: las thams cad pa'i bum pa ram yam kham gis sbyangs /
NK027(sha)001:91: shu dz+ny+aa nas stong par bsam la /
NK027(sha)001:92: phyi dur khrod nang gzhal yas khang du bsam /
NK027(sha)001:93: ma sur+ya man+dala nyi ma'i steng du /
NK027(sha)001:95: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ljang ku g.yas rdo rje rgya gram /
NK027(sha)001:96: g.yon dril bu thogs pa gcig bsgom /
NK027(sha)001:99: karma he ru kas dbu brgyan par bsam la /
NK027(sha)001:100: big+nana ta kri ta a mri ta kun+d+ha li ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:103: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK027(sha)001:104: rgyal ba rgyal mtsho ye shes kyi //
NK027(sha)001:105: srid pa rgya mtsho mtha' yas kyi //
NK027(sha)001:106: spyod pa rgya mtsho rmad 'byung kun //
NK027(sha)001:107: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK027(sha)001:108: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo bi shwa mu she b+h+ya /
NK027(sha)001:109: sarba tad khang ud ga te s+pha ra na hi mam ga g+ha na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:110: sh+r+ai badz+ra ra ga a lo ke h+r+aih sh+r+ai badz+ra ra ga g+hen+d+he g+han /
NK027(sha)001:112: ma h+aa sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hih ma h+aa rak+ta la kh+aa hi dang //
NK027(sha)001:113: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:114: ye shes dkyil 'khor thig le che //
NK027(sha)001:115: bsod nams dkyil 'khor sku yi tshogs //
NK027(sha)001:116: snang stong thig le kun rdzogs hoh /
NK027(sha)001:117: mi dmigs sgyu 'phrul mnyam pa'i dbyings //
NK027(sha)001:118: mtha' yas kun bzang sna tshogs 'phro //
NK027(sha)001:119: mtha' yas kun nas lhun gyis thim //
NK027(sha)001:120: sna tshogs sku gsung thugs chen po hoh /
NK027(sha)001:121: phyogs bcu 'jig rten rdul snyed du //
NK027(sha)001:122: rgyal ba'i don rnams rdul phran snyed //
NK027(sha)001:123: sprul pa rdul phran bsam yas kyi //
NK027(sha)001:124: skad gcig yun la lhun gyis grub ho /
NK027(sha)001:125: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK027(sha)001:126: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid che //
NK027(sha)001:127: sku gsung thugs kyi kun tu khyab //
NK027(sha)001:128: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che ho dang /
NK027(sha)001:129: hoh rgyal ba rgyal mtsho dgongs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:130: mchod pa rgya mtsho bzhes su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:131: nyams chag rgya mtsho bskang du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:132: dngos grub rgya mtsho stsal du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:133: phrin las rgya mtsho bsgrub tu gsol //
NK027(sha)001:135: de nas mdzub rtse gnyis bum pa la gtugs la /
NK027(sha)001:138: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa 'od du zhu nas bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor bsam /
NK027(sha)001:139: sarba b+hi shud+d+he d+harma tha sid+d+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)001:140: zhes pas bum pa'i chus kun la gtor bas nyes
NK027(sha)001:141: skyon thams cad chos nyid stong pa nyid du bsam
NK027(sha)001:142: / de nas dal la dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i bsam gyis chag chag gdab ste //
NK027(sha)001:143: bdud rtsi dri chen ye shes lnga ldan pa //
NK027(sha)001:144: de bzhin gsang mchog dngos grub dam pa'i mchog /
NK027(sha)001:145: bka' gsang bsgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
NK027(sha)001:146: dam rdzas bdud rtsi dri chen chag chag 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:147: ma h+aa ba su man+dala h'u /
NK027(sha)001:149: dam rdzas dam pa'i bdud rtsi dri chu 'di //
NK027(sha)001:150: ye shes rang byung bdud rtsi bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:151: skye med byang chub sems su rtogs pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:152: gsang ba'i bdud rtsi chen po'i chag chag 'debs /
NK027(sha)001:153: ma h+aa sa man+ta ku gus man+dala h'u /
NK027(sha)001:156: bka' gsang rmad byung dkyil 'khor chen po 'dir //
NK027(sha)001:157: 'khor ba rgyun gcod byang chub sems kyi ngang //
NK027(sha)001:158: mkha' dbyings rnam dag yum gyi gzhal yas su //
NK027(sha)001:159: rak+ta gsang ba mchog gi chag chag 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:161: de nas thig gdab pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:163: stong pa'i ngang las sur+ya tsan+t+ra rat+na pad+ma /
NK027(sha)001:165: de nas bdag gi thugs ka nas /
NK027(sha)001:166: h+aum swa am hah dam tshig thig le nyi zla pad+ma dang /
NK027(sha)001:170: badz+ra sa ma ye dzah e h+ya hi lan gsum brjod pas /
NK027(sha)001:171: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs /
NK027(sha)001:172: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK027(sha)001:173: gzugs sku 'ja' tshon lta bu 'gro don mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:174: thabs dang shes rab mchog la mnga' brnyes pa //
NK027(sha)001:175: rigs lnga bde bar gshegs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)001:176: dmigs med chos kyi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)001:177: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)001:178: cir yang sprul pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)001:179: khams gsum zhing du sbyor la mdzes pa'i sku mchog sems can bsgral la mkhas //
NK027(sha)001:180: ngo mtshar pho brang de bzhin gshegs pa'i yum //
NK027(sha)001:181: shes rab thabs kyi gtso bo la mnyes ma //
NK027(sha)001:182: rigs kyis yum gyur rnams la thabs mkhas thugs rje sprul pa'i ngang //
NK027(sha)001:183: rang rgyud rnam par dag pas grub pa brnyes //
NK027(sha)001:184: thugs rje chen pos 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:185: sems dpa' sems ma rnams la byams dang snying rje dga' ba btang snyoms kyi //
NK027(sha)001:186: nyon mongs log par lta ba'i dgra rnams 'joms //
NK027(sha)001:187: gshin rje gshed po la sogs khro rgyal bzhi //
NK027(sha)001:188: sgo ba yab yum rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)001:189: chos rnams ye nas gnyis med lhun grub pa //
NK027(sha)001:190: rtog par bya ba'i yul dang chos bzang mo //
NK027(sha)001:191: de nyid don rig byed pa rdo rje yin //
NK027(sha)001:192: gnyis med dkyil 'khor gtso la rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK027(sha)001:193: rtog pa rgyu drug so sor 'khor ba la //
NK027(sha)001:194: thabs mkhas thugs rjes ci 'dul der ston pas //
NK027(sha)001:195: thub pa chen po drug la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)001:196: a ti pu hoh pra ti dza hoh zhes phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)001:198: mi gnas pa'i ye shes chen po'i bdag nyid /
NK027(sha)001:199: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol lo //
NK027(sha)001:200: bdag rdo rje slob dpon gyi slob ma rnams kyi
NK027(sha)001:201: don du 'dus pa chen po'i dal sku gsung thugs
NK027(sha)001:202: yon tan mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo gsang
NK027(sha)001:203: ba las kyang cher gsang ba thugs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK027(sha)001:204: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dal du thig 'debs pas de
NK027(sha)001:205: bzhin gshegs pa thams cad bdag la mthu bstan du
NK027(sha)001:206: gsol / byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK027(sha)001:208: rdo rje ye shes kyi thig gsal tu gsol //
NK027(sha)001:209: badz+ra tish+tha tish+tha g+hu h+ya sa ma ya dz+ny+aa na
NK027(sha)001:210: am gu sha dza dzah zhes lan gsum brjod pas
NK027(sha)001:211: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sbyor ba byang chub sems
NK027(sha)001:212: kyi chu rgyun ye shes kha dog gi rang bzhin
NK027(sha)001:213: du byung / thig skud lnga la thim /
NK027(sha)001:214: sku gsung thugs nas 'od zer dkar dmar mthing gsum
NK027(sha)001:215: 'phros nas dam tshig gi thig la thim pas sku
NK027(sha)001:217: de nas slob dpon shar du blta /
NK027(sha)001:218: slob ma nub tu blta la thig sna gtad de /
NK027(sha)001:220: yi ge h'u zhes bya ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:221: rdo rje rigs kyi de bzhin te //
NK027(sha)001:222: me long ye shes rang bzhin gyi //
NK027(sha)001:223: zhe sdang dngos po sbyong ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:224: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:225: ma h+aa shu dz+ny+aa na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa
NK027(sha)001:226: wa ad+ma ko&ahamh zhes pas stong nyid ye shes sngo
NK027(sha)001:229: yi ge zhes bya ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:230: de bzhin rigs kyis de bzhin te //
NK027(sha)001:231: me long ye shes rang bzhin gyi //
NK027(sha)001:232: gti mug dngos po sbyong ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:233: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:234: ma h+aa shudz+ny+aa na shudz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK027(sha)001:235: zhes pas stong nyid ye shes sngo breng nge byung bar bsam /
NK027(sha)001:237: yi ge zhes bya ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:238: de bzhin rigs kyi de bzhin de //
NK027(sha)001:239: me long ye shes rang bzhin gyi //
NK027(sha)001:240: gti mug dngos po sbyong ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:241: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:242: a da re sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha wa
NK027(sha)001:243: ad+ma ko&ahamh me long lta bu'i ye shes dkar breng
NK027(sha)001:245: yi ge swa zhes bya ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:246: rin chen rigs kyi de bzhin te //
NK027(sha)001:247: mnyam nyid ye shes nga rgyal dngos po sbyong ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:248: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:249: ma h+aa sa man ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra /
NK027(sha)001:250: mnyam nyid ye shes ser breng nge byung bar bsam //
NK027(sha)001:251: yi ge zhes bya ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:252: pad+ma rigs kyi de bzhin te //
NK027(sha)001:253: sor rtogs ye shes rang bzhin gyi //
NK027(sha)001:254: 'dod chags dngos po sbyong ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:255: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:256: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes dmar bring nge byung bar bsam /
NK027(sha)001:257: yi ge ha zhes bya ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:258: las kyi rigs kyi de bzhin de //
NK027(sha)001:259: bya ba grub phrag dog dngos po sbyong ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:260: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:261: ma h+aa kri t+ya dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha wa
NK027(sha)001:262: ad+ma ko&a hamh bya ba grub pa'i ye shes ljang
NK027(sha)001:263: breng nge byung bar bsam mo //
NK027(sha)001:264: de nas thig skud rnams gcig tu bsdom la /
NK027(sha)001:266: 'dus pa chen po mdo yi dkyil 'khor du //
NK027(sha)001:267: gnyis med byang chub sems kyi 'phro 'du las //
NK027(sha)001:268: rdo rje ye shes thig chen 'di btab pas //
NK027(sha)001:269: pho brang dal la yid bzhin lhun gyis grub //
NK027(sha)001:271: zhes bzlas shing thig skud sbrel nas sku gsung thugs
NK027(sha)001:272: yon tan phrin las nyi shu rtsa lnga'i ngo bor
NK027(sha)001:273: bsam / de nas las thig las /
NK027(sha)001:274: yi ge zhes bya ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:275: bde gshegs sku yi rang bzhin te //
NK027(sha)001:276: lus kyi dngos po sbyong ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:277: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:278: ka ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa yi ge h'u zhes bya ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:279: bde gshegs gsung gi rang bzhin te //
NK027(sha)001:280: ngag gi dngos po sbyong ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:281: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:282: wa ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa yi ge h'u zhes bya ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:283: bde gshegs thugs kyi rang bzhin te //
NK027(sha)001:284: yid kyi dngos po sbyong ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:285: byin rlabs tsit+ta badz+ra de nas thig rnams gcig tu bsdom la /
NK027(sha)001:287: mi mtha' g.yo 'gul med pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:288: rnal 'byor mnyam nyid thod brgal du //
NK027(sha)001:289: khro gtum rngams pa'i las mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:290: gnas 'dir gzhal yas bri bar bya //
NK027(sha)001:291: +aahmh'u badz+ra dz+ny+aa na ma ti pra ma h'u /
NK027(sha)001:292: zhes brjod pas re re'ang dgu phrugs su ldan par bsam mo //
NK027(sha)001:293: de nas rdo rje dril bu rab gnas ni /
NK027(sha)001:295: stong pa'i ngang las che mchog lte bar yar gyi ra lngar h+aum las rigs lnga /
NK027(sha)001:296: mar gyi ra lngar mum lam mam pam tam /
NK027(sha)001:298: rtse dgu pa la mtshams kyi ra bzhir lung gi
NK027(sha)001:299: he ru ka yar pad 'dab brgyad las sems dpa'
NK027(sha)001:300: brgyad / mar pad 'dab la sgo ba bzhi /
NK027(sha)001:303: ril po la dal gyi lha thams cad rdzogs par bsam /
NK027(sha)001:304: dril bu'i lte bar khro mo gnam zhal ma /
NK027(sha)001:305: zhal la yum sher phyin ma /
NK027(sha)001:307: 'og gi pad+ma'i dbus dang phyogs mtshams su yum lnga gsang yum bzhi /
NK027(sha)001:308: gong ras la khro mo brgyad /
NK027(sha)001:309: rdo ra la khro mo nyi shu /
NK027(sha)001:310: lce las khro mo gar bsgyur ma /
NK027(sha)001:311: rtse dgu pa la mtshams bzhi'i ra la las bzhi'i snying po bskyed do //
NK027(sha)001:313: sku gsung thugs byin gyis rlobs /
NK027(sha)001:314: kun bzang mchod sprin nas bstod pa'i bar bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:315: de nas h'u zhes brjod pas lha rnams 'od du zhu /
NK027(sha)001:316: rdor dril la thim pas ye shes kyi ngo bor bsam zhing /
NK027(sha)001:317: badz+ra d+ha ka dza la ha na da ha badz+ra pany+tsa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:318: g+han d+ha pa sha d+harma d+ha ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:320: rdo rje las 'bras bu'i chos thams cad rdzogs te 'gro don mdzad par bsam /
NK027(sha)001:321: dril bu stong pa nyid kyi ngang las chos sgrogs par bsam zhing /
NK027(sha)001:324: rdo rje dril bu rig pa 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:325: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pas //
NK027(sha)001:327: chos la de bzhin dbang bsgyur shog /
NK027(sha)001:328: ces brjod cing rdo rje gsor bas khams gsum zil gyi gnon /
NK027(sha)001:329: dril bu bsil bas srid gsum dbang du bsdus par bsam mo //
NK027(sha)001:330: de nas b+han+d+ha'i rab gnas ni /
NK027(sha)001:332: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las 'dus pa chen po rtsa ba'i dal bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:341: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK027(sha)001:343: gtum chen glu drug gi bstod cing /
NK027(sha)001:344: bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha dz+ny+aa na d+hartu +aah ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK027(sha)001:345: zhes ci rigs bzlas pas lha rnams 'od du zhu /
NK027(sha)001:346: ye shes kyi bdud rtsis gang bar bsam mo //
NK027(sha)001:347: de nas tshon byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:348: tshon rigs mthun du bkod la dpa' bo 'bru lnga bkod /
NK027(sha)001:351: stong pa'i ngang las gdan lnga brtseg tu cho ga gsum gyis lhar bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:353: dbab drangs bstim brtan pa la /
NK027(sha)001:354: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK027(sha)001:356: bstod pa'i bar byas la gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:357: kun mkhyen ye shes dag pa la //
NK027(sha)001:358: dug lnga sgrib pa ma mthong bas //
NK027(sha)001:359: mtshon cing dag par bya ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:360: byin brlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:364: ye shes re re'ang lnga lnga dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK027(sha)001:365: spung zhing snum pa ltar byos gsungs /
NK027(sha)001:366: de ltar yan lag rab gnas zin nas rdo rje
NK027(sha)001:367: slob dpon chas gos lngas brgyan te h'u zhes rdo
NK027(sha)001:369: dal gyi dbus su phyin la shar du bltas te rnam rgyal gyi nga rgyal gyi 'dug la /
NK027(sha)001:370: 'dus pa chen po'i lha tshogs mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs te phyi nang gsang ba'am /
NK027(sha)001:371: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod la /
NK027(sha)001:372: yum bzhi po rig bzhir byin gyis brlab la /
NK027(sha)001:374: dbab drangs bstim brtan la gsang yum bzhi'i phyogs bzhi nas gsol ba btab bo //
NK027(sha)001:376: sangs rgyas kun 'dus grong bar nyid //
NK027(sha)001:377: de ring bshad par mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:378: thams cad bdag nyid dgongs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:380: zhi ba'i ye shes rang snang ba //
NK027(sha)001:381: rgyan rnams kun gyi rab mdzes pa //
NK027(sha)001:382: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku yi mchog /
NK027(sha)001:383: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:385: yon tan rin chen rgyas pa'i gtso //
NK027(sha)001:386: ma lus kun gyi re ba bskangs //
NK027(sha)001:388: sangs rgyas kun gyi yon tan mchog /
NK027(sha)001:389: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:391: rang bzhin dag pas gos pa med //
NK027(sha)001:392: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung gi mchog /
NK027(sha)001:393: 'dod chags pha rol phyin pa brnyes //
NK027(sha)001:394: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:396: bsam pa thams cad yongs rdzogs pa //
NK027(sha)001:397: thams cad sgrol ba'i ded dpon mchog /
NK027(sha)001:398: sangs rgyas kun gyi phrin las bdag /
NK027(sha)001:399: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:401: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rdzogs pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:402: rang rig mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK027(sha)001:403: ye shes pho brang 'khor lo'i tshul //
NK027(sha)001:404: dkyil 'khor snying po bshad du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:407: phyogs bcu ma lus thams cad kyi //
NK027(sha)001:408: rgyal ba sras bcas gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:409: bdag cag rdo rje rgyal po yi //
NK027(sha)001:410: slob bu rnams kyis don phyir du //
NK027(sha)001:411: dkyil 'khor chen po bdag bgyis pas //
NK027(sha)001:412: bdag cag rjes su bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:413: sa 'di shes par byin rlabs par //
NK027(sha)001:414: bde bar gshegs pas mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:415: zhes brjod la thugs ka'i 'od zer gyi nam mkhar
NK027(sha)001:416: bzhugs pa'i lha tshogs rnams h'u bzhis bsdus te thugs
NK027(sha)001:418: slob ma rnams yi dam gang yin bsgom pa'i dbang
NK027(sha)001:419: po sgo lnga nas 'od zer sna tshogs 'phro bar
NK027(sha)001:420: bsam mo // de nas byang shar mtshams nas rdo rje 'gros kyis bskor zhing sum b+ha ni dang /
NK027(sha)001:421: khro bo bcu'i sngags kyis bgegs bskrad la /
NK027(sha)001:422: gral du 'khod pa la sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlab cing go bago'o //
NK027(sha)001:423: de nas ci tsam 'os pa'i dal zur thig nas 'debs pa'i bar cha lnga bgos pa'am /
NK027(sha)001:426: de'i dbus su shong na zhi ba'i dal me ri yan chad bris pa yin /
NK027(sha)001:427: ma shong na sla nga'am ka to ra sas bkang
NK027(sha)001:428: la zhi ba'i dal bri man dzu'i khar rtsib brgyad
NK027(sha)001:429: kyi dbus su bzhag pa phyag len no //
NK027(sha)001:431: de'i phyi ma'ang cha lnga lngar bgos pa bar khyams bcu /
NK027(sha)001:432: de'i phyi ma la gzhal yas chen po'i sna tshogs rta bab rnams so //
NK027(sha)001:433: de'i phyi ma la pad rdor me ri dug gsum gyi mtshan ma'o //
NK027(sha)001:434: rdo rje 'chang gi dal 'dir gru bzhi byas na'ang
NK027(sha)001:435: gab pa'i dbang drug nas khyam zla gam kha sprod
NK027(sha)001:436: du bshad bas gru khyog zlum por rigs so //
NK027(sha)001:437: kham por dung chos su phud la a mri ta
NK027(sha)001:438: tsan dan dkar dmar dza ti ga pur a kar
NK027(sha)001:441: 'degs lha gnas dri'i thig le byas te /
NK027(sha)001:442: sur+ya tsan tra ma ta las gdan bsam /
NK027(sha)001:443: h'u h'u h'u badz+ra tsi ta he /
NK027(sha)001:444: a a a badz+ra sa ma ya ah a kro ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK027(sha)001:445: ka ta ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:446: ru lu hu lu h'u b+h+yo h+aum /
NK027(sha)001:447: che mchog lha yi ngo bor bsam /
NK027(sha)001:448: de'i mdun du sur+ya tsan tra ma d+ha la /
NK027(sha)001:449: h'u badz+ra d+h+rig mum da du shwa ri /
NK027(sha)001:451: sogs sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su dgod do //
NK027(sha)001:453: de'i dbus kyi 'khor lo rtsib brgyad kyi lte bar badz+ra he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:454: shar du b+hud+d+ha he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:456: nub tu pad+ma he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:457: byang du karma he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:458: shar lhor rak+sha he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:459: lho nub tu sa nu he nub byang du gu
NK027(sha)001:460: h+ya he byang shar du yag sha he ru ka
NK027(sha)001:461: bskyed / grwa bzhir glo 'bur du sur+ya dang ko'u ri brgyad kyi sngags /
NK027(sha)001:462: khyams dang po'i phyogs mtshams sur+ya dang sing+ha ha ma brgyad kyi sngags /
NK027(sha)001:463: sgo bzhir sur+ya dang sgo ba bzhi'i sngags /
NK027(sha)001:464: khyams gnyis pa'i phyogs mtshams bzhir sur+ya dang a rag mo h'u /
NK027(sha)001:467: sgo bzhir sh+r+ai badz+ra mud ka ra sha ra ya na mo /
NK027(sha)001:468: sh+r+ai badz+ra g+han+ta tra dza la na mo /
NK027(sha)001:469: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga ma sha ya ya na mo /
NK027(sha)001:470: badz+ra kha tam kha pra dza la ya ya na mo /
NK027(sha)001:471: khyams gsum pa'i phyogs bzhir drug drug sgo bzhir re
NK027(sha)001:472: re dbang phyug ma nyer brgyad kyi sngags dang khyams
NK027(sha)001:475: mkha' 'gro ma so gnyis khyams lnga la shar lho nub byang bzhi ru gnyis gnyis ma mo bdun /
NK027(sha)001:479: khyams drug pa la shar nub tu bzhi bzhi /
NK027(sha)001:485: khyams bdun ba la nub tu /
NK027(sha)001:486: kro ta kro ti h'u zhes /
NK027(sha)001:490: lho byang gi sgor bzhir bzhi /
NK027(sha)001:491: khro bo khro mo drug bcu /
NK027(sha)001:493: khyams brgyad pa la shar sur+ya dang /
NK027(sha)001:494: b+ha na b+ha na am gu sha dzah drug cu /
NK027(sha)001:496: ha la ha la pa sha h'u /
NK027(sha)001:498: nub tu sur+ya gardza gardza s+pho ta bam gi drug cu /
NK027(sha)001:500: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+d+he ho drug cu'o //
NK027(sha)001:501: khyams dgu pa la phyogs bzhir bco lnga pho nya brgyad /
NK027(sha)001:503: ma ma sha ri ma mo las byed drug cu /
NK027(sha)001:505: khyams bcu pa sur+ya tsan+t+ra pad+ma ma d+ha las /
NK027(sha)001:506: bka' brgyad theg pa'i lha tshogs tshang ba /
NK027(sha)001:507: rta bab kyi khyams la sur+ya tsan+t+ra pad+ma man+dala ma h+aa gu ru sha ri rum /
NK027(sha)001:508: zhes pas rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang bka' brgyud bla ma rnams tshang ba'i tshom bu bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:509: de dag dal dang rig 'dzin brgyud pa la sogs /
NK027(sha)001:511: de nas gnyis pa lha sta gon la gnas pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:513: nang du rtsa ba yan lag gi mchod pa bsham mo //
NK027(sha)001:516: ye nas mnyam nyid kyi bshams /
NK027(sha)001:519: mchod pa rnams byin gyis brlabs /
NK027(sha)001:520: rang nyid kun bzang du gsal ba'i thugs ka'i h'u las /
NK027(sha)001:521: 'byung ba rim brtsegs dang bcas pa'i zhi ba'i dal bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:523: bdag he ru kar gnas pa'i thugs kar 'byung ba
NK027(sha)001:524: rim brtsegs dang bcas pa'i dal la khrag 'thung yab
NK027(sha)001:534: steng gi khro bo khro mo drug cu /
NK027(sha)001:535: shar du dung gi pho nya drug cu /
NK027(sha)001:536: lho lcags sam gser gyi pho nya drug cu /
NK027(sha)001:537: nub tu bswe'i pho nya drug cu /
NK027(sha)001:538: byang du g.yu'i pho nya drug cu /
NK027(sha)001:539: 'og tu ma mo las byed drug cu /
NK027(sha)001:540: rig 'dzin la sogs pa thams cad sngags kyi rdzogs tshul du bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:541: zhi khro gnyis ka la dus gcig tu ye shes lngas dbang bskur /
NK027(sha)001:542: sku gsung thugs byin gyis barlobasa /
NK027(sha)001:543: sa man dzas snyan gsan dbab /
NK027(sha)001:545: dzahmh'u bam hos gnyis su med par bstim /
NK027(sha)001:546: kun tu bzang po dang phyag dang zhabs bsil dang /
NK027(sha)001:547: lha mo bzhi bsnol gyi mchod /
NK027(sha)001:548: zhi ba'i lha tshogs rnams la su ra tas gtor ma 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:549: khro bo la dzahmh'u bam hos 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:551: ar+g+ham la badz+ra a mri ta ha ra na pra ti dza b+ha ga wan /
NK027(sha)001:552: dzahmh'u bam hoh pa na bem /
NK027(sha)001:554: sarba ma h+aa su ka sid+d+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)001:555: zhi ba la gsang nan gyi mchod /
NK027(sha)001:556: dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra a dan d+hush+pe pu be d+hi ba g+han+d+he /
NK027(sha)001:557: b+ha lin pra ti dza hoh sh+r+ai pa na kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK027(sha)001:558: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam par sbyar bar 'di //
NK027(sha)001:559: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK027(sha)001:560: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i rab brgyan te //
NK027(sha)001:561: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:562: khro bo la rak+ta tshar gsum 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:565: de nas dril bu bsil zhing spos bdug la /
NK027(sha)001:566: yang na sa ma ya h'u ho bstim /
NK027(sha)001:567: tshom bu'i lha rnams sbyor ba mdzad nas 'od du zhu ste sa gzhi la thim pas /
NK027(sha)001:568: sa gzhi ye shes lnga rang snang du byin brlab gsungs so //
NK027(sha)001:569: mgon po thugs rje che ldan pa //
NK027(sha)001:570: thams cad kun nas dgongs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:571: deng gi gnas mchog dam pa 'dir //
NK027(sha)001:572: slob ma rnams kyis don phyir du //
NK027(sha)001:573: sang gi nang par bdug bdal nas //
NK027(sha)001:574: dkyil 'khor chen po bzhengs gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:575: sta gon la ni bzhugs nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:576: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:577: zhes pas lha sta gon no //
NK027(sha)001:578: de nas gsum pa bum pa sta gon ni /
NK027(sha)001:579: bum pa lnga dkar rtsis byug pa la /
NK027(sha)001:580: rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan bris pa bla ma'i mdun du ras gtsang ma'i khar bzhag go //
NK027(sha)001:581: de nas bden pa brdar ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:583: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa thams
NK027(sha)001:584: cad kyi sku gsung thugs spyan drangs nas bkod pa
NK027(sha)001:585: mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bka' bden pa
NK027(sha)001:586: dang / bden pa yang dag pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:587: bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs dang /
NK027(sha)001:588: zhi khro gsang ba mchog gi bka' bden pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:589: bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)001:590: rnal 'byor ba bdag gi slob ma 'di rnams kyis
NK027(sha)001:591: don du bum pa lha'i dal du bzhengs par 'tshal
NK027(sha)001:593: bgegs dang 'byung po thams cad 'dir ma gnas par gzhan du deng shig /
NK027(sha)001:595: b+hi shwa badz+ra kro ta tshang ba /
NK027(sha)001:596: brjod cing rdo rje thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:597: gtor bas bgegs thams cad bskrad par bsam mo //
NK027(sha)001:598: de'i rjes su'ang bgegs kyi mi tshugs pa'i phyir gu gul gyi bdug /
NK027(sha)001:599: bkra shis pa'i phyir spos kyi bdug /
NK027(sha)001:600: yang ram yam kham gi bum pa bsangs sbyangs /
NK027(sha)001:601: stong pa'i ngang las rdo rje mtshon pa'i dbus kyis
NK027(sha)001:602: bum par b+h+r+aum gyi 'phro 'du dang b+h+r+aum b+hi sha
NK027(sha)001:604: gdan dang bcas pa bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:605: nang du yungs dkar blug la kun bzang yab yum
NK027(sha)001:606: dang mi bskyod pa yab yum gyis gtso byas pa'o
NK027(sha)001:607: // shar du rnam snang gi gtso byas pa'i lha bzhi bcu /
NK027(sha)001:611: bum rdzas nyer lnga tshang ba'i kha rgyan gzungs thag rigs mthun bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:612: khro bo gsang ba'i bum pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:613: b+han+d+ha dkar po lcang lo can /
NK027(sha)001:614: gra dar mthing dmar gyi khung du bzhag la de'i
NK027(sha)001:615: nang du rdo rje slob dpon gyi gtso byas pa'i
NK027(sha)001:616: mched lcam rdo rje spun du yod kyi grangs sman
NK027(sha)001:617: ril bu byas la bzhag go //
NK027(sha)001:619: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las 'dus pa chen po
NK027(sha)001:620: gzhal yas gdan dang bcas pa bskyed la gtso bo
NK027(sha)001:621: nas ma bdun sring bzhi yan chad bum pa'i nang
NK027(sha)001:622: du yungs kar blug cing sngags kyi rdzogs par bskyed
NK027(sha)001:623: / lnga tshan nyer lnga'i rdzas dang 'bru bcud tshang bar blug pa'i khar rdo rje bzhag la /
NK027(sha)001:625: thod pa gcig gi kha bcad /
NK027(sha)001:626: dar sna lngas bkab la bzhag go //
NK027(sha)001:627: yang na zhi ba'i bum pa lnga po rigs lnga dang /
NK027(sha)001:628: khro bo'i bum pa b+han+d+ha mtshan ldan la rigs lnga
NK027(sha)001:629: so so'i thugs phyag mtshan bris la dbus su che
NK027(sha)001:630: mchog gi gtso bo byas pa'i lha lnga brgya brgyad
NK027(sha)001:632: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang thams cad tshang bar bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:633: rigs bzhi'i bum pa la rigs rang rang gi gtso
NK027(sha)001:634: byas pa'i lha lnga bcu rtsa brgyad po bskyed cing
NK027(sha)001:636: phyogs bzhi dbus su dgod cing /
NK027(sha)001:637: many+dzu khar ka pa la lngar bdud rtsi blug /
NK027(sha)001:638: lha la ye shes lngas dbang bskur /
NK027(sha)001:640: kun bzang gi mchod pa lnga 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:641: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri tas sman mchod 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:642: ma h+aa b+ha ling+tasa gtor ma 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:643: ma h+aa rak+ta kh+aa hih khrag 'bul //
NK027(sha)001:644: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni /
NK027(sha)001:646: dal kun rgyas par 'bul gyi bar dang /
NK027(sha)001:647: gsal ldan ma'i byin rlabs rim chos dbyings mchod pa'i a la la ste mchod pa 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:648: a la la ste bzhes su gsol /
NK027(sha)001:650: ri rab chen po'i gling bzhi nas //
NK027(sha)001:651: gnas pa'i sems can thams cad kun //
NK027(sha)001:652: ye shes me chen sgom byas te //
NK027(sha)001:653: thams cad ma lus bsregs par byed //
NK027(sha)001:655: srid gsum bsregs pa'i me chen te //
NK027(sha)001:656: yid kyi ye shes me ru 'bar //
NK027(sha)001:658: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:659: pad+ma la ni rdo rje zhugs //
NK027(sha)001:660: 'khril ba'i chos can mnyam sbyor bas //
NK027(sha)001:661: bdag nyid mnyes pas mnyes par bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:662: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)001:664: dzahmh'u bam hoh h'u h'u h'u /
NK027(sha)001:666: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa puts+tsha badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK027(sha)001:667: zhes pas lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang sbyor sgrol gyi mchod pa 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:670: de nas khro bo'i gsang bum gyi gzungs thag g.yon pas bzung /
NK027(sha)001:671: g.yas phreng ba bsgrang zhing gu h+ya dz+ny+aan ru lu brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas zhing /
NK027(sha)001:672: bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK027(sha)001:675: bum pa nang gi lha la thim /
NK027(sha)001:677: glad pa dung khang du song /
NK027(sha)001:679: rdo rje nas yum gyi mkhar bab /
NK027(sha)001:683: srog dag pa'i lam nas byung /
NK027(sha)001:684: sgal tshig nas brgyud de rdo rje nas yum gyi mkhar bab /
NK027(sha)001:685: sbyor mtshams nas bdud rtsi'i rgyun bab pas bum pa gang bar bsam zhing /
NK027(sha)001:686: ta pa la te ma ma ha te pa ta la h'u /
NK027(sha)001:687: zhes brjod pas lha tshogs bdud rtsir zhu /
NK027(sha)001:688: bum pa gang bas kyang dus gsum sangs rgyas thams
NK027(sha)001:689: cad kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i
NK027(sha)001:690: ngo bor rdzogs par bsam la /
NK027(sha)001:692: gsal ldan mas byin gyis brlab la /
NK027(sha)001:694: dbyings mnyes nas bdag nyid sangs rgyas srid gsum dga'
NK027(sha)001:695: ba sgyu 'phrul phyogs bcu sangs rgyas da la ma
NK027(sha)001:696: lus dang / khams gsum 'gro rnams mngon du gyur //
NK027(sha)001:698: zhi ba'i bum pa dbus dang phyogs bzhir bzhag /
NK027(sha)001:699: dbus kyi bum pa'i nang du thod pa dum bu gcig pa'i nang 'bru bcud kyi phud blug la /
NK027(sha)001:700: bdud rtsi btab khar rdo rje bzhag la zhi ba'i dal bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:701: bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od 'phros nas b+han+d+ha bdud
NK027(sha)001:702: rtsis gang ba'i bar gong bzhin byas la dbus shar
NK027(sha)001:704: bsang sbyangs bskyed pa sogs byas la bla mas khro
NK027(sha)001:705: bo'i gsang bum bzung zhing zhi ba'i bum pa rgyal
NK027(sha)001:706: thabs sogs kyi bzung la dal gyi mtha' bskor te
NK027(sha)001:709: bum pa ma lags rgyal po lags //
NK027(sha)001:710: rgyal po'i sngags kyi btab nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:711: rgyal po chen po mnga' gsol gyi //
NK027(sha)001:712: rgyal po'i tshul du bzhugs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:713: zhes brjod la bum pa rang gi mdun nam phyogs bzhi dbus lngar dgod /
NK027(sha)001:714: las bum du bdud rtsi 'khyil bar bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:715: byin gyis brlabs te rgyal theb kyi mdun du dgod do //
NK027(sha)001:717: de nas yo byad byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:718: yo byad kyi phud bsags la ram yam kham gi bsang sbyangs la /
NK027(sha)001:720: sam ha ra na h'u gi 'phros 'dus /
NK027(sha)001:721: tram rat+na tre lok+sha man+dala h'u /
NK027(sha)001:722: zhes pas yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che
NK027(sha)001:723: mi bzad pa'i gter gyi phung po'i rtser +aahmh'u gi
NK027(sha)001:724: 'od las phyi nang gsang ba'i longs spyod bsam gyi
NK027(sha)001:725: mi khyab pa 'byung bar bsam mo //
NK027(sha)001:726: bye brag tu byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:727: yo byad tsho gsum du bcad la /
NK027(sha)001:728: tsho gcig bam ser po'i 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:729: dpa' bo 'bru lngar bskyed la tshogs dang mchod pa bya /
NK027(sha)001:730: tsho gcig a dang ma'i 'phro 'du las 'dod yon du byin gyis brlabs la /
NK027(sha)001:731: bsgrub pa po rnams kyis rol /
NK027(sha)001:732: tsho gcig nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags kyi mang po rgya cher spel la mchod mgron la 'gyed /
NK027(sha)001:733: der tshogs thams cad lha dang lha mor bsam /
NK027(sha)001:735: lnga pa slob ma sta gon ni nyer gnyis dal
NK027(sha)001:736: gyi lha tshogs pad+ma 'dab brgyad so shing sogs dang
NK027(sha)001:737: spyi dang khyad par gyi mchod pa bshams /
NK027(sha)001:738: mtshams nas 'dzab bstod kyi bar bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:739: de nas slob ma rnams khrus bya /
NK027(sha)001:741: hoh mi gnas pa'i ye shes chen po'i bdag nyid
NK027(sha)001:742: 'dus pa chen po'i dal gyi lha tshogs 'khor rgyal
NK027(sha)001:743: ba rgya mtsho zhing gi rdul rnyed dang bcas pa
NK027(sha)001:744: rnams gsan cing dgongs su gsol lo //
NK027(sha)001:745: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'khor ba la nges
NK027(sha)001:746: par 'byung nas 'gro ba sems can rnams kyi don
NK027(sha)001:747: gyi slad du byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas
NK027(sha)001:748: mthar phyin par 'tshal bas de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK027(sha)001:749: cad kyi zhal ston zhing byin gyis brlab pa dang
NK027(sha)001:752: de nas kun rdzob sems bskyed ni /
NK027(sha)001:753: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK027(sha)001:754: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK027(sha)001:755: rtogs pa'i dbang gi 'khor ba la //
NK027(sha)001:756: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK027(sha)001:758: e ma ngo mtshar rmad gyi chos //
NK027(sha)001:759: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK027(sha)001:760: skye ba med la thams cad skye //
NK027(sha)001:761: skyes pa nyid na'ang skye ba med //
NK027(sha)001:762: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK027(sha)001:763: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK027(sha)001:766: e ma ngo mtshar rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK027(sha)001:767: gnas pa med la thams cad gnas //
NK027(sha)001:768: gnas pa nyid na'ang gnas pa med //
NK027(sha)001:769: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK027(sha)001:770: rdzogs pa'i dmigs pa med la thams cad dmigs //
NK027(sha)001:771: dmigs pa nyid na'ang e ma ngo mtshar rmad rdzogs
NK027(sha)001:772: pa'i sangs rgyas 'gro 'ong med la 'gro dang 'ong
NK027(sha)001:775: de nas bla ma badz+ra he ru kar sgom la /
NK027(sha)001:778: theg chen gsang sngags snying po'i mchog /
NK027(sha)001:779: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK027(sha)001:780: khyod la rab tu brtan par bya //
NK027(sha)001:784: ting 'dzin lhag byang chub sems dang tshogs mchog bstan /
NK027(sha)001:786: de nas gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:787: bcom ldan kun bzang he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:788: da la gtso bo khyed la 'dud //
NK027(sha)001:789: thar pa chen po bdag 'dod de //
NK027(sha)001:790: de'i dbang dang dam tshig dang //
NK027(sha)001:791: mgon po dpa' bo skyabs song zhing //
NK027(sha)001:792: theg chen khang par gzhug pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:793: mkhyen rab ye shes bdag la gsol //
NK027(sha)001:796: bu 'dir shog cig ci bder ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:797: las spyod rim par 'gro ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:798: sku gsung thugs kyis rdo rje zungs //
NK027(sha)001:799: 'dus pa chen po'i dbang rdzogs sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:801: slob ma rnams kyis glad pa dung khang du ma
NK027(sha)001:802: las nyi ma'i 'phro 'du 'od kyi lus gang mgo
NK027(sha)001:803: bzhugs / a yu h'u dzah zhes pa'i tshe'i rang
NK027(sha)001:804: bzhin mu tig ltar dkar po dri ma med par
NK027(sha)001:805: bzhugs / bsam / yang dung kham du b+h+r+aum gyi
NK027(sha)001:806: 'phro 'du las zla gam dmar po sgo gcig pa'i
NK027(sha)001:807: nang du badz+ra kro ta h'u /
NK027(sha)001:808: ka ra h'u gi h'u ka ra bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:809: badz+ra kro ta ar+ya a tsa h'u gi mi g.yo bas sgo bsrung bar bsam /
NK027(sha)001:810: rang dpal chen du gsal ba'i sor mo bcur nyi
NK027(sha)001:811: ma'i gdan 'bru lnga la rigs lnga yab yum gyi
NK027(sha)001:812: 'phro 'dus slob ma rnams kyi sdig sgrib ral bar
NK027(sha)001:814: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs kyi /
NK027(sha)001:815: gang dag 'di rnams kyis rgyud la gnas pa'i las dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:816: lta ba dman zhing shes rab zhen pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:817: khyad par gsang sngags kyis sgor zhugs nas gsang ba
NK027(sha)001:818: zab mo'i dbang nod pa la sgrib pa gong gi
NK027(sha)001:819: rim pa bzhin gnas pa thams cad skad cig gcig
NK027(sha)001:820: la byang zhing dag par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:823: sgrib pa ma lus pa dag nas sems shel sgong ltar gyur par bsam /
NK027(sha)001:824: badz+ra a we sha ya a +aah zhes pas /
NK027(sha)001:826: lus bkrag mdangs dang ldan par bsam la /
NK027(sha)001:827: rang nyid yi dam du bsgom /
NK027(sha)001:830: de nas slob ma rnams kyis phyag 'tshal /
NK027(sha)001:832: dpa' bo rdo rje 'dzin pa khyod //
NK027(sha)001:834: sdug bsngal chu bo rgyun bzlog pa //
NK027(sha)001:835: don gnyis bdag gi bstan byin phyir //
NK027(sha)001:836: thabs kyi las mtha' gang lags pa //
NK027(sha)001:837: rim pa yan lag bsten byin phyir //
NK027(sha)001:838: thugs rjes nye bar bstan mdzad de //
NK027(sha)001:839: de ring gnas par mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:841: bla mas bdud rtsi thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:842: dpal ldan rdo rje sku gsung thugs 'chang ba //
NK027(sha)001:843: rdo rje mi phyed sku gsung thugs dang ldan //
NK027(sha)001:844: deng nas bdag la byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK027(sha)001:845: rdo rje sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:851: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ka ya waka tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK027(sha)001:852: zhes lan gsum rdo rjes reg go //
NK027(sha)001:853: de nas bla mas rdo rje phyed la 'dzin du bcug la /
NK027(sha)001:854: bdag ni lha mchog skal bar ldan //
NK027(sha)001:855: deng ni theg pa chen po la //
NK027(sha)001:856: brtan par bya phyir bdag la ni //
NK027(sha)001:857: ye shes bsrung pa mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:860: +aahbig+nana ta krita a mri ta kun+d+ha li h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:862: kha bshal khang du yang bstan /
NK027(sha)001:865: badz+ra dzi ha sam b+ha ra pra ti ni h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:866: kyis sor shing sbom pas bzhar /
NK027(sha)001:867: phra mos so brus la man+dala du mkha' dbyings ma'i phyag rgyas dor ro //
NK027(sha)001:868: phyogs bzhir rtse mo bstan na rigs bzhi 'grub /
NK027(sha)001:869: byang shar du byung na bskyar ro //
NK027(sha)001:872: ces pas bsrung skud pho'i g.yon du bcing /
NK027(sha)001:874: badz+ra tish+tha tish+tha h'u s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:875: rtsa ku sha che chung sngas stan du byin /
NK027(sha)001:876: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK027(sha)001:877: phur bas sras mchog tu byin rlabs la sbyin /
NK027(sha)001:878: de nas bla ma la phyag byas te /
NK027(sha)001:880: de nas bla mas byang shar nas reg mdzub gang drangs te /
NK027(sha)001:881: zangs gzhong ting phur gyi bkab pa rdo rjes mnan la bzhag go //
NK027(sha)001:882: skabs 'dir dbang gi sngon 'gro la gling bzhi dang 'gag brgyad bshad do //
NK027(sha)001:883: nub mod phrin las gzhung bsrang /
NK027(sha)001:885: grub na gling bzhi srid pa'i spyi mdos bya /
NK027(sha)001:886: de nas ku shas sngas stan byas te /
NK027(sha)001:888: mo'i g.yon 'og tu bcug la rmi lam thun gsum du bcad de /
NK027(sha)001:889: tho rangs rmi lam bzang ngan brtag go //
NK027(sha)001:890: de'ang gang byung drang por smros shig bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:891: de yang gsang ba spyi rgyud las /
NK027(sha)001:892: rmi lam sangs rgyas mthong ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:893: yon tan rgya mtsho mngon sum bzhin //
NK027(sha)001:894: mchod rten dang ni sku gzugs mthong //
NK027(sha)001:895: de nas mchod pa la sogs dang //
NK027(sha)001:896: dge slong dag la chos nyan dang //
NK027(sha)001:897: yang na ma nyan na'ang rung //
NK027(sha)001:898: chos kyi rnam par spyod pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:899: de bzhin mdo sde klag pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:900: rmi lam dge 'dun mthong ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:901: yang na dge slong gcig pu mthong //
NK027(sha)001:902: de dang 'grogs shing gtam zer dang //
NK027(sha)001:903: yang na dge slong dngos por gyur //
NK027(sha)001:904: gtsug lag khang dag mthong ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:905: de bzhin dge slong ma dag mthong //
NK027(sha)001:906: rgyal po'i sras dag mthong ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:907: de bzhin pha ma bla ma dang //
NK027(sha)001:908: mdza' bo rnam pa sna tshogs dang //
NK027(sha)001:909: rmi lam du ni mthong na shes //
NK027(sha)001:910: rig 'dzin sngags dang dngos grub kun //
NK027(sha)001:911: rgyal por bkur dang slob ma 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:912: kun dga' rnam pa sna tshogs dang //
NK027(sha)001:913: 'bab chu rnams dang rgya mtsho dang //
NK027(sha)001:914: ri dang glang po che dag dang //
NK027(sha)001:915: mthong na yang ni bzang bar grags //
NK027(sha)001:916: gzhon pa bzang po zhon pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:917: nor bu 'bru dang zas mchog shes //
NK027(sha)001:919: rgya kag ri la 'dzeg pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:920: ka ra bi ri'i me tog thu //
NK027(sha)001:921: mchod sdong bye ma thal phung la //
NK027(sha)001:922: 'dzeg dang bong bu la zhon dang //
NK027(sha)001:923: longs spyod song nas ma log dang //
NK027(sha)001:924: de bzhin spre'u zhon pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:926: bud med nag mo khros ma ni //
NK027(sha)001:927: de la 'dod chags spyad pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:928: g.yang ma shing la lhung ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:929: ljon shing 'bras med skam po dang //
NK027(sha)001:930: khyi dang khra dang srin po dang //
NK027(sha)001:931: de las zhon pas zos pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:932: phag dang rnga mong ma he dang //
NK027(sha)001:933: zhon nas dbyug pa thogs pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:934: mi nag po'i sdig pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:935: til mar byug pa phreng ba thogs //
NK027(sha)001:936: skra breg phreng ba dmar po bcing //
NK027(sha)001:937: de rnams ngan pa'i rmi bltas yin //
NK027(sha)001:940: ngan na slob ma bdud rtsi 'khyil bar bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:943: de nas zangs gzhung bsal te /
NK027(sha)001:944: reg 'dres na nyams pa yod pas bshags pa bya /
NK027(sha)001:946: de nas chas gos ser po mdzub mo smin mtshams su bsnol la /
NK027(sha)001:947: ha ha hi hi zhes pas tshom bu'i lha tshogs
NK027(sha)001:948: dang thig nam mkhar bteg la dbus kyis lte ba
NK027(sha)001:950: de nas slob ma la bris zhes gnang ba byin la brir gzhug go //
NK027(sha)001:951: bri zin nas nam mkhar bteg pa'i lha tshogs dal la bstim mo //
NK027(sha)001:952: de nas dgong mo cha gsum btang ste /
NK027(sha)001:953: bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu la /
NK027(sha)001:954: gtor ma btang la phyi'i mtshams bcad /
NK027(sha)001:955: phyi'i bar mtshams rgyal chen bzhi la tho'i phrin las bcol ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:956: cha gsum gyi gtor ma dang po de las che ba bzhi /
NK027(sha)001:957: gzhan bcu byas la bar pa tha ma bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:958: sha khrag gi brgyan pa'i gtor ma dang /
NK027(sha)001:960: mchod pa rnam pa lnga yon chab dang bcas pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:961: bsgrub khang gi phyi'i sa bde bar phyogs mtshams su
NK027(sha)001:962: man+dala pad+ma 'dab brgyad kyi lte ba phyogs mdog bya
NK027(sha)001:963: / tho yang shar nas bzung ste dkar ser dmar ljang brtsig /
NK027(sha)001:964: de la 'bras bu dang bcas pa'i shing dang rgyal
NK027(sha)001:965: chen bzhi'i gzugs bris ba cod pan dang bcas pa
NK027(sha)001:966: gzugs go // de nas rnal 'byor pas lcags kyu'i
NK027(sha)001:967: phyag rgyas tri badz+ra am ku sha dza lan gsum
NK027(sha)001:968: gyi bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer lcags kyu'i
NK027(sha)001:969: gzugs go // rnam par 'phros / bgegs rnams mdun
NK027(sha)001:970: du bkug la sngags drug phyag drug gtor ma byin
NK027(sha)001:971: gzugs go // rnam par 'phros / la / bdag
NK027(sha)001:972: gi bsod nams dang la sogs kyi bsngosa la btang
NK027(sha)001:973: gzugs go // rnam par 'phros / la / ngo
NK027(sha)001:974: // thams cad kyi bsngo zhing chang phud rgyas par
NK027(sha)001:975: gzugs go // rnam par 'phros / la / ngo // gtor la / na mo /
NK027(sha)001:976: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs su mchi'o //
NK027(sha)001:977: dkon mchog gsum gyis bden pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:978: bden pa yang dag pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:979: bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs kyi /
NK027(sha)001:980: gsang sngags tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dal gsang ba bas
NK027(sha)001:981: kyang ches gsang ba yang gsang rmad du byung ba'i
NK027(sha)001:982: dal chen po'i bdag rnal 'byor pa tshogs shing 'dus
NK027(sha)001:983: pa rnams la bar du gcod pa'i gdon bgegs 'byung
NK027(sha)001:984: po'i rigs su gtogs pa gnas 'dir ma gnas par
NK027(sha)001:985: dpag tshad rgyang grags su ma nye bar phyir deng
NK027(sha)001:986: shig / ces mtshams gcod kyi sngags kyi rang gi
NK027(sha)001:987: thugs ka nas rdo rje gnod sbyin dpag tu med
NK027(sha)001:988: shig / pa 'phros pas / thams cad gling gzhan du bskrad par bsam mo //
NK027(sha)001:989: de nas byang gi tho'i rtsar phyin la rang karma
NK027(sha)001:990: he ru kar bskyed pa'i thugs ka nas b+h+r+aum 'phro
NK027(sha)001:991: 'du las / tho gzhal yas khang du gyur pa'i nang du nyi zla las /
NK027(sha)001:992: b+he sha ra ma ne ye yag k+sha a ti pa ta ye h'u dzah zhes pas /
NK027(sha)001:993: rnam thos sras g.yas rin po ches mtshan pa'i rgyal mtshan g.yon ne'u le'i rkyal pa /
NK027(sha)001:994: bswe khrab bswe rmog can don grub kyi dbu brgyan par bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:995: sku gsung thugs byin gyis rlab bo //
NK027(sha)001:996: de nas rang rta mgrin du bskyed nas /
NK027(sha)001:997: pad+ma ta krita badz+ra kro ta h+ya g+r+ai wa h'u /
NK027(sha)001:1000: ri rab lhun po'i byang phyogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:1001: lcang lo can gyi pho brang nas //
NK027(sha)001:1002: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gi //
NK027(sha)001:1003: tshur gshegs tshur byon rnam thos sras //
NK027(sha)001:1004: btsun mo sras dang blon por bcas //
NK027(sha)001:1005: g.yog 'khor bye ba stong ldan rnams //
NK027(sha)001:1006: 'dir byon mchod pa dam pa bzhes //
NK027(sha)001:1007: phrin las bsgrub phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:1008: b+he sha ra ma na ye yak+sha a ti pa ta ye /
NK027(sha)001:1009: dzah h'u bam hos dgug bstims /
NK027(sha)001:1010: ka ya wak+ka tsit+ta badz+ra tish+thasa brtan pa bzhugs su gsol /
NK027(sha)001:1012: nags tshal bcud ni yid dgar 'ong //
NK027(sha)001:1013: dri zhim rgyas pa lha yi rdzas //
NK027(sha)001:1014: lha rdzas dam pa'i bdug spos 'di //
NK027(sha)001:1015: rgyal chen 'khor dang bcas rnams la //
NK027(sha)001:1016: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags kyis //
NK027(sha)001:1017: thugs rjes dgongs la bzhes su gsol /
NK027(sha)001:1019: gtsang zhing gtsang mar skyes pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:1020: lha rdzas dam pa'i me tog 'di //
NK027(sha)001:1021: rgyal chen 'khor bdag cag thugs rjes dgongs la badz+ra puspe h'u /
NK027(sha)001:1022: sdug bsngal 'jom shing bkra shis pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:1023: dgyes shing mun sel mar me 'di //
NK027(sha)001:1024: rgyal chen 'khor dang bcas rnams la //
NK027(sha)001:1025: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags na //
NK027(sha)001:1026: thugs rjes dgongs la bzhes su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:1027: badz+ra a lo ke puts+tsha me h'u /
NK027(sha)001:1028: gtsang zhing gtsang mar skyes pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:1029: lha rdzas dam pa'i dri chab 'di //
NK027(sha)001:1030: rgyal chen 'khor dang bdag cag thugs rjes dgongs badz+ra gan+d+he sman rnams bcud ni yid dgar 'ong //
NK027(sha)001:1031: sngags kyi zhal zas bcud 'di la //
NK027(sha)001:1032: rgyal chen 'khor dang bcas rnams la //
NK027(sha)001:1033: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags na //
NK027(sha)001:1034: thugs rjes badz+ra nee wi t+ya pu tsa me ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri tas sman 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:1035: ma h+aa b+ha ling+tasa gtor ma 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:1037: ri rgyal lhun po'i byang phyogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:1038: pho brang chen po lcang lo can //
NK027(sha)001:1039: zab cing rgyal chen gzigs pa po //
NK027(sha)001:1040: chos skyong rgyal po rnam thos sras //
NK027(sha)001:1041: btsun mo sras dang blon por bcas //
NK027(sha)001:1042: g.yog 'khor bye ba stong ldan rnams //
NK027(sha)001:1044: sngon gyi thugs dam rjes dgongs la //
NK027(sha)001:1045: gnas 'dir brtse zhing gshegs nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:1046: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK027(sha)001:1047: bdag cag dpon slob 'khor bcas kyi //
NK027(sha)001:1048: bar chad thams cad zhi ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:1049: bsam pa chos bzhin 'grub par mdzod //
NK027(sha)001:1050: b+he shar ma na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:1051: phyag rgya khu tshur gnyis bcing mthil gnyis gdengs la phrin las bcol ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:1052: hoh byang phyogs skyong ba'i rgyal po chen po phyi rnam thos sras /
NK027(sha)001:1054: gsang ba don yod grub pa khyod kyi ston pa'i
NK027(sha)001:1055: spyan sngar bstan pa skyong bar dam bcas te mgon
NK027(sha)001:1056: po mi 'gyur ba'i gdan la bzhugs nas khas blangs
NK027(sha)001:1057: pa bzhin du rnal 'byor pa dang bdag cag bsgrub
NK027(sha)001:1058: pa la zhugs pa rnams la byang phyogs gnod sbyin
NK027(sha)001:1059: gyi bar chad zhi ba dang bsgrub pa ma thon
NK027(sha)001:1060: gyi bar du phyi'i dgra bgegs nang du ma btang
NK027(sha)001:1061: / nang gi dngos grub phyir ma btang /
NK027(sha)001:1065: bar chad zhi ba'i phrin las mdzad du gsol /
NK027(sha)001:1067: de nas shar du phyin la /
NK027(sha)001:1068: rang b+hud+d+ha he ru kar bsgoms /
NK027(sha)001:1069: b+h+r+aum gyi 'phro 'du las tho gzhal yas khang gi nang du zla ba las /
NK027(sha)001:1070: ti sta ra sta ye g+han d+ha a ti pa ta ye h'u dza las /
NK027(sha)001:1071: yul 'khor srung dkar po g.yas pi wam g.yon ne'u le dung khrab dung rmog can /
NK027(sha)001:1072: rnam snang gi dbu brgyan par bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:1073: sku gsung thugs byin rlabs kyi /
NK027(sha)001:1075: ri rgyal lhun po'i shar phyogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:1076: spos ngad ldan pa'i pho brang nas //
NK027(sha)001:1077: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK027(sha)001:1078: tshur byon rgyal chen yul 'khor bsrungs //
NK027(sha)001:1079: btsun mo sras dang blon por bcas //
NK027(sha)001:1080: g.yog 'khor bye ba stong sde rnams //
NK027(sha)001:1081: 'dir byon mchod pa dam pa bzhes //
NK027(sha)001:1082: phrin las bsgrub phyir gshegs su gsol /
NK027(sha)001:1083: tish+tha ra sta ye g+han d+ha a ti pa ta ye dzahmh'u bam hoh gzhan gong bzhin /
NK027(sha)001:1085: ri rgyal lhun po'i shar phyogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:1086: pho brang chen po spos ngad ldan //
NK027(sha)001:1087: zab cing rgyal chen gzigs pa po //
NK027(sha)001:1088: chos skyongs rgyal po yul 'khor bsrungs //
NK027(sha)001:1089: btsun mo sras dang blon 'khor bcas //
NK027(sha)001:1090: g.yog 'khor bye ba stong sde rnams //
NK027(sha)001:1092: sngon gyi thugs dam rjes dgongs la //
NK027(sha)001:1093: gnas 'dir brtse zhing gshegs nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:1094: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK027(sha)001:1095: bdag cag dpon slob 'khor bcas kyi //
NK027(sha)001:1096: bar chad thams cad zhi ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:1097: bsam pa chos bzhin 'grub par mdzod //
NK027(sha)001:1098: ti sta ra sta ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:1099: phyag rgya khu tshur gnyis bcang /
NK027(sha)001:1103: shar phyogs skyong ba'i rgyal po phyi yul 'khor bsrungs /
NK027(sha)001:1105: gsang ba rnam par snang mdzad khyod kyi ston pa'i spyan sngar /
NK027(sha)001:1106: bstan pa skyong bar dam bcas te shar dri za'i bar chad zhi ba sogs 'gres so //
NK027(sha)001:1108: rang rat+na he ru kar bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:1109: b+h+r+aum gyi 'phro 'du las gzhal yas khang du zla ba la /
NK027(sha)001:1110: b+he ru ta ka kur b+han g+han d+ha a ti
NK027(sha)001:1111: pa ta ye h'u dzahls 'phags skyes po sngon po
NK027(sha)001:1112: g.yas ral gri / lcags khrab lcags rmog can /
NK027(sha)001:1113: rin 'byung gi dbu rgyan can bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:1117: ri rgyal lhun po'i lho phyogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:1119: dad pa dang ni tshur byon rgyal chen 'phags skyes po //
NK027(sha)001:1120: btsun mo sras dang blon por bcas //
NK027(sha)001:1121: g.yog 'khor bye ba stong sde rnams //
NK027(sha)001:1122: 'dir byon mchod pa dam pa bzhes /
NK027(sha)001:1123: bla med bee ru ta ka ye kur ban d+ha /
NK027(sha)001:1124: a ti pa ta ye h'u dzah dzahmh'u bam hoh h'u /
NK027(sha)001:1125: ri rgyal lhun po'i lho phyogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:1127: zab cing rgya che gzigs pa po //
NK027(sha)001:1128: phyogs skyong rgyal po 'phags skyes po //
NK027(sha)001:1129: btsun mor sras dang blon por bcas //
NK027(sha)001:1130: g.yog 'khor bye ba stong bla med mchod pa 'di 'bul gyi //
NK027(sha)001:1131: sngon gyi thugs dam rjes dgongs la //
NK027(sha)001:1132: gnas 'dir brtse zhing gshegs nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:1133: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK027(sha)001:1134: bdag cag dpon slob 'khor bcas kyi //
NK027(sha)001:1135: bar chad thams cad zhi ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:1136: bsam pa chos bzhin 'grub par mdzod //
NK027(sha)001:1137: b+he ru ta ka ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:1139: lho phyogs rgyal po chen po phyi 'phags skyes po /
NK027(sha)001:1141: gsang ba rin 'byung khyod kyi sogs dang /
NK027(sha)001:1142: grul bum bar chad zhi ba 'gres so //
NK027(sha)001:1143: de nas nub tu phyin te /
NK027(sha)001:1145: b+h+r+aum gyi 'phro 'du las tho gzhal yas khang gi nang du zla ba las /
NK027(sha)001:1146: b+he ru bag sha ye na ga a ti ga
NK027(sha)001:1147: pa ta ye h'u dzahls spyan mi bzang dmar po
NK027(sha)001:1148: g.yas sbrul zhags g.yon pu ri zangs khrab zangs rmog
NK027(sha)001:1149: can 'od dpag med kyi dbu brgyan par bskyed la
NK027(sha)001:1152: ri rgyal lhun po'i nub phyogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:1153: rgya mtsho chu yi pho brang nas //
NK027(sha)001:1154: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gi //
NK027(sha)001:1155: tshur byon rgyal po spyan mi bzang //
NK027(sha)001:1156: btsun mo sras dang blon por bcas //
NK027(sha)001:1157: g.yog 'khor bye ba stong sde rnams //
NK027(sha)001:1158: 'dir byon mchod pa dam pa bzhes //
NK027(sha)001:1159: b+he ru bag sha ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:1160: a ti pa ta ye h'u dzah dzahmh'u bam hoh 'gres /
NK027(sha)001:1162: ri rgyal lhun po'i nub phyogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:1163: rgya mtsho chu yi pho brang nas //
NK027(sha)001:1164: zab cing rgya che gzigs pa po //
NK027(sha)001:1165: phyogs skyong rgyal po spyan mi bzang //
NK027(sha)001:1166: btsun mo g.yog 'khor bla med mchod pa 'di 'bul gyi //
NK027(sha)001:1167: sngon gyi thugs dam rjes dgongs la //
NK027(sha)001:1168: gnas 'dir brtse zhing gshegs nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:1169: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK027(sha)001:1170: bdag cag dpon slob 'khor bcas kyis //
NK027(sha)001:1171: bar chad thams cad zhi ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:1172: bsam pa chos bzhin 'grub par mdzod //
NK027(sha)001:1173: b+he ru bag sha ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:1174: phyag rgya khu tshur bcing mthil gnyis 'dengs la /
NK027(sha)001:1177: nub phyogs skyong ba'i rgyal po chen po phyi spyan mi bzang /
NK027(sha)001:1179: gsang ba snang ba mtha' yas khyod kyi klu'i bar chad zhi ba sogs 'gres so //
NK027(sha)001:1180: de nas phyogs skyong bcu la'ang spro na tho brtsegs /
NK027(sha)001:1181: mchod pa gtor ma sogs kyi 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:1182: so so'i bstod pa dbang po rdo rje 'chang ba la sogs pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:1183: de nas nang du 'dus pa la gral phyag tshul phyag bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:1184: thun mong bsrungs ba'i 'khor los mtshams bcad /
NK027(sha)001:1185: phyi'i nang mtshams dam sri mnan /
NK027(sha)001:1186: bar chad bgegs dang ye shes lha gnyis las /
NK027(sha)001:1187: dang po rang ye shes pa ya man ta kar bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:1189: rang bzhin dag pa'i ngo bo las //
NK027(sha)001:1190: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis med pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:1191: ma rtog pa dang log par rtog /
NK027(sha)001:1192: sor rtog yang dog nyid ma rtog /
NK027(sha)001:1193: sgrib pas sems spangs dma' ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:1194: sems kyi rtog pas bcings pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:1195: gzhi stong ci la bar chad byed //
NK027(sha)001:1196: rang gi dam tshig rang ma 'da' //
NK027(sha)001:1197: 'dzam bu gling gi lho phyogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:1198: 'di nas dpag tshad brgyad khri nas //
NK027(sha)001:1199: gshin rje'i rgyal po chos ston gyi //
NK027(sha)001:1200: khyod kyi chos skal de ru nyon //
NK027(sha)001:1201: ma 'da' rang rang gnas su dengs //
NK027(sha)001:1202: sa ma ya ka pa tsam rak+sha rak+sha h'u /
NK027(sha)001:1204: ling+ga'i ske nas thag pa nag po btags la 'gug 'dren byas la mgo mthur du bsten la mnan /
NK027(sha)001:1205: de'i steng du khro bo'i gzugs lug gsog la bris /
NK027(sha)001:1208: sh+r+ai ya man ta ka h'u /
NK027(sha)001:1209: sa man dzas snyan gsan dbab /
NK027(sha)001:1211: rgyal po gshin rje gshed po khyod //
NK027(sha)001:1212: dam tshig gnas mchog dam pa 'dir //
NK027(sha)001:1213: dam sri ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:1214: thugs rjes dbang gi gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:1217: bde bar gshegs so nas lha mo bzhi bsnol gyi mchod la /
NK027(sha)001:1219: sum cu rtsa gsum lha yi gnas mchog nas //
NK027(sha)001:1220: bcom ldan chos rje 'od kyi bka' rtsal pa //
NK027(sha)001:1221: lha srin sde brgyad 'byung po'i dpon rnams kun //
NK027(sha)001:1222: bsgrub pa mchog la deng 'dir bdag 'jug gi //
NK027(sha)001:1223: bla med byang chub 'bras bu ma thob par //
NK027(sha)001:1224: sgo 'dir bskrad la su yang ma 'da' cig /
NK027(sha)001:1225: khro bo'i rgyal po gshin rje gshed la phrin las gsol ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:1226: bdag la dngos grub kyi sdong grogs dang /
NK027(sha)001:1227: phyi mtshams bsrung zhing nang mtshams skyong ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:1228: khyad par bsgrub pa ma tshang gyi bar du phyi'i dgra bgegs nang du ma btang /
NK027(sha)001:1229: nang gi dngos grub phyir ma btang /
NK027(sha)001:1230: ya ma dam sri la sogs pa'i bar chad thams cad bsrung du gsol /
NK027(sha)001:1231: kro ti a mri kun+da li /
NK027(sha)001:1233: de nas gsang mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:1234: kun lang la rdo rje thugs kar bzung la /
NK027(sha)001:1235: mi rtogs pa'i ngang las thugs kar h'u bsam la
NK027(sha)001:1236: 'phro 'du las rdo rje rtse lnga pa yang 'phro
NK027(sha)001:1237: 'dus las / badz+ra kro ta a mri ta kun+d+ha li h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:1238: ces pas bdag nyid bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ljang ku rdo rje rtse gsum thogs pa bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:1241: gsang ba'i dam can so so nas //
NK027(sha)001:1242: 'du ba lha ni ma gtog pa //
NK027(sha)001:1243: thugs dam thugs rjes bskang zin gyi //
NK027(sha)001:1244: da lta nyid du so so dengs //
NK027(sha)001:1245: ci ste bka' las 'das gyur na //
NK027(sha)001:1246: rdo rje 'dzin rgyal khros nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:1247: rdo rje mtshon cha 'bar ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:1248: de ma thag tu bkas nas gshegs //
NK027(sha)001:1249: bdun rgyud rigs kyang brlag par bya //
NK027(sha)001:1251: na mo rat+na tra ya ya /
NK027(sha)001:1253: ma h+aa yak+sha sen pa ta ye /
NK027(sha)001:1256: zhes pa nas a mri ta h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:1258: h'u zhes pas khro bo'i gur du gyur na bskal pa'i rlung mi thar bar bsam mo //
NK027(sha)001:1259: de nas gzugs brnyan gyi dal rdzas dgod pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:1260: zhi ba'i gzhal yas khang du bdag nyid kun tu
NK027(sha)001:1261: bzang po yab yum du bskyed la mkha' gsang byin
NK027(sha)001:1262: gyis rlobs / sbyor ba mdzad pa'i byang chub sems
NK027(sha)001:1263: kyi 'od zer las kun bzang yab yum bton na
NK027(sha)001:1264: tsakli la bstim zhing snying po mi bskyod pa yab
NK027(sha)001:1265: yum bton la h'u badz+ra d+h+rika kyi kun bzang gi
NK027(sha)001:1267: de bzhin du thub drug yan chad rang rang gi gnas su so so'i sngags brjod cing dgod do //
NK027(sha)001:1268: de nas dbang chen khro bo dbus su badz+ra he ru ka phyung la sngags kyi dgod /
NK027(sha)001:1269: phyogs kyi rtsibs bzhi la rigs bzhi he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:1270: mtshams bzhir lung gi he ru ka'i rtsa sngags kyi dgod /
NK027(sha)001:1271: grwa bzhir glo 'bur la ko'u ri brgyad /
NK027(sha)001:1273: khyams dang po ser po la he brgyad kyi seng ha brgyad /
NK027(sha)001:1274: sgo bzhir phata bzhi sgo ma bzhi /
NK027(sha)001:1275: khyams gnyis dkar po la a brgyad las spros par ma brgyad /
NK027(sha)001:1276: yak+sha rag mo ham gi dgod /
NK027(sha)001:1278: dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai badz+ra mud ka ra ya na
NK027(sha)001:1279: ma sh+r+ai badz+ra g+han+d+he pra dza la na mah sh+r+ai
NK027(sha)001:1280: badz+ra ra ga sa ma ya na mah sh+r+ai badz+ra
NK027(sha)001:1281: la tam ga ya na ma sa dgod /
NK027(sha)001:1282: khyams gsum pa dmar po b+h+yo nyer brgyad la dbang mo nyer brgyad /
NK027(sha)001:1283: khyams bzhi pa ser po la e bam las mkha'
NK027(sha)001:1284: 'gro so gnyis e a ra li h'u gi dgod
NK027(sha)001:1287: bzhi la sgo ma sring bzhi /
NK027(sha)001:1290: khyams drug pa dkar po la h'u bco brgyad la ging bco brgyad /
NK027(sha)001:1291: ging ka ra ha ha ru lu ru lu b+h+yo /
NK027(sha)001:1292: khyams bdun pa nag po la /
NK027(sha)001:1293: h'u drug cu la khro bo drug cu kro ta kro ti h'u gi dgod /
NK027(sha)001:1294: khyams brgyad pa phyogs mdog la shar du dza drug cu la /
NK027(sha)001:1295: b+ha na b+ha na am ku sha dzas dung gi pho nya drug cu dgod /
NK027(sha)001:1297: ha la ha la pa sham h'u /
NK027(sha)001:1298: nub phyogs su gardza gardza s+pho ta bam /
NK027(sha)001:1300: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+d+he hos dgod /
NK027(sha)001:1301: khyams dgu pa ljang ku la ma drug cu la
NK027(sha)001:1302: 'og gi ma mo drug cu ma ma sha h'u
NK027(sha)001:1303: gi dgod / khyams bcu sna tshogs mdog la theg dgu'i lha tshogs tshangs ba dgod /
NK027(sha)001:1304: rta bab kyi khyams rdo rje 'chang gi dal la
NK027(sha)001:1305: shar stod nas ma h+aa gu ru sha ri ram
NK027(sha)001:1306: gyi rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang rnams rim pa bzhin du
NK027(sha)001:1307: dgod par bya'o // de nas khro bo gsang ba'i bum pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:1308: rtags gsum bla ma'i drung du dgod /
NK027(sha)001:1309: zhi ba'i bum pa phyogs bzhir dbus sam dal gyi mthar dgod /
NK027(sha)001:1310: las bum las mkhan gyi mdun du'o //
NK027(sha)001:1311: gzhan yang mda' brgyad dar sna dang bcas pa /
NK027(sha)001:1312: gri brgyad me long dang bcas pa /
NK027(sha)001:1313: phur pa brgyad bru khung dang bcas pa /
NK027(sha)001:1314: 'phan brgyad bla re dang yol bas brgyan par bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:1315: de nas byin dbab pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:1316: thams cad gos bzang po gon /
NK027(sha)001:1317: spos dud dang rol mo bya /
NK027(sha)001:1319: mo rnams kyis phreng bas g.yab cing /
NK027(sha)001:1321: nam mkha' mtha' dang mnyam pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)001:1322: rnam 'byor dbang phyug rigs kyis yum dang bcas //
NK027(sha)001:1323: rgyal ba'i bsrung mar gyur pa'i dam tshig can //
NK027(sha)001:1324: mchod do bla ma rnams la skyabs su mchi //
NK027(sha)001:1326: mi gnas ye shes thugs kyis dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)001:1327: bcom ldan che mchog khro rgyal 'khor dang bcas //
NK027(sha)001:1328: sngags kyi bshug pa'i brda'i spyan 'dren gyi //
NK027(sha)001:1329: phyag rgya gar gyi brda' yi g.yab dor na //
NK027(sha)001:1330: dpal chen yab yum thugs dam rjes dgongs la //
NK027(sha)001:1331: thams cad brda' la dgongs te gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:1333: chos nyid bde ba chen po'i sku byung ba //
NK027(sha)001:1334: bcom ldan che mchog yab yum gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:1335: dur khrod reg pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:1336: rgyud lung khro rgyal yab yum gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:1337: ye shes 'bar ma brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)001:1338: ko ri khro mo brgyad po gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:1339: chos nyid mkha' ltar dag pa'i seng ha phra men brgyad po gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:1340: 'bar ba'i bar khyams dur khrod nang shed nas //
NK027(sha)001:1341: spor ma gsang yum tshogs rnams tshad med bzhi rdzogs gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)001:1342: rta gdong sgo ma 'khor bcas dam tshig lhun gyis grub pa'i pho brang nas //
NK027(sha)001:1343: dbang phyug ming sring 'khor bcas zhe sdang 'bar ba thugs kyi pho brang nas //
NK027(sha)001:1344: khro rgyal srin po dur khrod 'bar ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)001:1345: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis sgrol byed 'bar ba
NK027(sha)001:1346: las kyi dkyil rdo rje ging chen 'khor bcas gang
NK027(sha)001:1347: gi bka' nyan las byed dkyil pho nya sder mo
NK027(sha)001:1348: 'khor las rnams yongs su grub pa'i ye shes ma
NK027(sha)001:1349: mo'i tshogs rnams sdom pa gsum la gnas pa'i dkyil
NK027(sha)001:1350: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang 'khor bcas deng gi gnas mchog
NK027(sha)001:1352: b+han+d+ha gsar rnying tshogs ni rdzas ltar lhags //
NK027(sha)001:1353: keng rus gsar rnying tshogs ni ri ltar spungs //
NK027(sha)001:1354: rak+ta gsar rnying tshogs ni mtsho ltar bskyil //
NK027(sha)001:1355: mang sa gsar rnying tshogs ni thar mar bdal //
NK027(sha)001:1356: zhing chen gsar rnying tshogs ni bye ltar bkram //
NK027(sha)001:1357: tsit+ta gsar rnying tshogs ni rlung ltar spungs //
NK027(sha)001:1358: byang chub sems kyi tshogs ni gangs ltar chags //
NK027(sha)001:1359: rgyan cha gsar rnying tshogs ni sprin ltar gtib //
NK027(sha)001:1360: ta na g+ha na'i tshogs ni dbyings nas rol //
NK027(sha)001:1361: rdo rje mched lcam lha dang lha mor rol //
NK027(sha)001:1362: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs ni mkha' ltar gtib //
NK027(sha)001:1363: rnal 'byor longs spyod che la spyan 'dren na //
NK027(sha)001:1364: thugs dam brda' la dgongs te gshegs nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:1365: dkyil 'khor chen po 'di la byin phob la //
NK027(sha)001:1366: bsgrub pa'i rtags dang mtshan ma bstan nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:1367: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol /
NK027(sha)001:1368: badz+ra sa ma ya sid+d+hi phob phob /
NK027(sha)001:1370: ma ya dzah yo gi ni /
NK027(sha)001:1371: sa ma ya dzah badz+ra a we sha ya a +aah zhes brjod pas lha tshogs byon byon /
NK027(sha)001:1373: a we sha yas gnyis su med par bstim pas /
NK027(sha)001:1374: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams gzi brjid dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK027(sha)001:1375: de nas bar mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:1379: bdag nyid rnam par snang mdzad dkar po zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK027(sha)001:1380: zhal dbus dkar g.yas sngo g.yon dmar ba /
NK027(sha)001:1381: phyag dang po gnyis 'khor lo dang pad+ma /
NK027(sha)001:1382: bar ma gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK027(sha)001:1383: mtha' ma gnyis rin chen ral gri bsnams pa /
NK027(sha)001:1384: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs par bsam /
NK027(sha)001:1385: de'i thugs ka nas badz+ra kro ta ar+ya a tsa la badz+ra ma h+aa kro ta h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:1387: mi g.yo ba sngo skya g.yas dkar g.yon dmar ba /
NK027(sha)001:1388: g.yas rdo rje ral gri mda' /
NK027(sha)001:1389: g.yon dgra s+t+wa zhags pa gzhu bsnams pa gcig byung nas mdun du bka' non du bsam /
NK027(sha)001:1391: phata na mahs man ta'i sngags brjod cing ral gri
NK027(sha)001:1392: phyag rgya g.yas nas glad la bskor bas bgegs bskrad
NK027(sha)001:1393: / g.yon nas bskor bas ral gri'i gur du bsam /
NK027(sha)001:1394: de nas bsnyen par gnang ba'i dbang bzhi bskur ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:1396: ye shes kyi rdo rje dril bur bsam te /
NK027(sha)001:1398: thabs dang shes rab dbang chen te //
NK027(sha)001:1399: rdo rje dril bu rig pa 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:1401: chos la 'dod cing dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:1403: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK027(sha)001:1404: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi zhing
NK027(sha)001:1405: khams dag pa zad mi shes pa rgyan gyi 'khor
NK027(sha)001:1407: bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs kyi /
NK027(sha)001:1408: rigs kyi bu skal ldan rgyal ba'i sras rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:1409: rdo rje dril bus dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:1410: gsang ba'i dal chen por bzhugs te /
NK027(sha)001:1411: bsnyen sgrub rnams pa bzhi'i sgo nas phrin las rnam pa bzhi la longs spyod pa la /
NK027(sha)001:1412: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa 'brel ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:1413: badz+ra g+han+d+he tish+tha a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)001:1415: dril bu bsil zhing snying khar gtug /
NK027(sha)001:1418: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:1420: sku gsung thugs kyi byin gyis rlobs /
NK027(sha)001:1422: mi g.yo chos sku yon tan mchog mnga' ba //
NK027(sha)001:1423: sdug bsngal log par 'khyam pa'i sems can rnams //
NK027(sha)001:1424: thugs rje gnyis med dbyings su sgrol mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:1425: khro rgyal 'bar ba'i dbang 'di khyod la sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:1427: smon lam gong bzhin byas te /
NK027(sha)001:1429: bar du gcod pa'i bgegs dang log 'dren ya ma
NK027(sha)001:1430: dam sri thams cad 'dul ba'i dbang dam pa badz+ra
NK027(sha)001:1431: k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+nana bam h'u phata
NK027(sha)001:1433: zhes pas phur pa snying khar gtug /
NK027(sha)001:1436: a tsan+t+ra las zla ba la tram bcu'i 'phro 'du
NK027(sha)001:1437: las phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi byin rlabs phreng ba
NK027(sha)001:1440: ru tra bsgral ba bzhad pa che //
NK027(sha)001:1441: khur ba dbugs kyi rlung 'byin pa //
NK027(sha)001:1442: 'brug gi sgra ltar zab pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:1443: ru lu ru lu sgra sgrogs bzhad //
NK027(sha)001:1444: phyag rgya 'di yi dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:1446: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK027(sha)001:1447: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi zhing
NK027(sha)001:1448: khams dag pa mdzad pa mi shes pa rgyan gyi
NK027(sha)001:1450: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlab kyis /
NK027(sha)001:1451: rigs kyi bu skal ldan rgyal ba'i sras rnams la phreng bas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:1452: ru lu 'bru brgyad kyi 'dzab kyi dbang dang /
NK027(sha)001:1453: sangs rgyas gsung gi dngos grub kyi sgra dbyangs kyis
NK027(sha)001:1454: mi 'dzad pa dbang dam pa ru lu ru lu
NK027(sha)001:1455: h'u b+h+yo h'u / a b+hi gi phreng ba snying khar gtug cing 'dzab kyi rigs bgrang ngo //
NK027(sha)001:1456: de nas rnga nyi ma'i steng du /
NK027(sha)001:1457: h'u gi 'phro 'du las badz+ra tsa ma ra dza
NK027(sha)001:1458: ma ra ya h'u gi ye shes kyi lhar bsam
NK027(sha)001:1460: chos sku mchog mnga' ye shes tshul khrims ldan //
NK027(sha)001:1461: dpal gyi phyag rgya ye shes tsa ma ra //
NK027(sha)001:1462: rigs kyi bu mchog khyod la dbang bskur ba //
NK027(sha)001:1463: ma mo mkha' 'gro thams cad dbang bsdud cing //
NK027(sha)001:1464: thugs dam gnas nas 'khol nas bran bzhin du //
NK027(sha)001:1465: khol ba'i dbang mchog dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:1466: badz+ra tsa ma ra ya a b+hi zhes pas snying khar gtug la brdung ngo //
NK027(sha)001:1467: de nas brda' sgo dbye ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:1469: ye nas mnyam nyid mi 'ad'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:1470: gzung 'dzin bsnol ba'i sgo bcad de //
NK027(sha)001:1471: bdag med mi gnas ye shes kyi //
NK027(sha)001:1472: yul las 'das pa'i sgo phyes shig /
NK027(sha)001:1473: man+dala tsak+shu pra we sha ya phata /
NK027(sha)001:1476: shar lho nub byang sgo bzhi nas //
NK027(sha)001:1477: ye shes bzhi yi sgo phyes te //
NK027(sha)001:1478: zhi khro gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor lo //
NK027(sha)001:1479: rnal 'byor bdag gi las bgyid do //
NK027(sha)001:1480: phyag 'tshal bas lha dang dbyer med tu bsam /
NK027(sha)001:1481: de yan chad bsnyen pa'i cho ga'o //
NK027(sha)001:1482: spyi don gnyis pa nye ba'i bsnyen pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:1485: ma tam mnan pa ni byang shar du phyin te /
NK027(sha)001:1486: badz+ra he ru ka h'u gi rang he ru kar bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:1487: lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas ma tam kha ru am gu sha dzah zhes lan gsum bdun du bkug la /
NK027(sha)001:1488: badz+ra gu h+ya tri sha sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)001:1489: zhes thod pa'i phyag rgya lan gsum bstan la /
NK027(sha)001:1490: sngon gyi dam bca' las ma 'das bar bsam la kha tam gi phyag rgya bcas te /
NK027(sha)001:1492: ma tam bya ba'i sdig can khyod //
NK027(sha)001:1493: sngon yang dpal chen he ru kas //
NK027(sha)001:1494: bsgral nas dur khrod gnas su byas //
NK027(sha)001:1495: shes pa bla med gnas su spar //
NK027(sha)001:1496: da yang rnal 'byor dbang phyug gis //
NK027(sha)001:1497: bsgral nas bsgrub pa'i gnas su bya //
NK027(sha)001:1498: phung po khams sogs gnas sbyangs nas //
NK027(sha)001:1499: rang byung mchod rten brgyad byas te //
NK027(sha)001:1500: ma mo brgyad kyi bsrung bar byed //
NK027(sha)001:1501: thugs dam chen po ci bzhin du //
NK027(sha)001:1502: byin chen rnams kyi byin phob la //
NK027(sha)001:1503: dngos grub chen po sdong grogs mdzod //
NK027(sha)001:1504: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa sa ma ya
NK027(sha)001:1505: mu ta ma tam pra ban tsakra ha na ha
NK027(sha)001:1506: na h'u phata / ces kha trang gi phyag rgya bstun bas mgo lho nub /
NK027(sha)001:1507: rkang pa byang shar du bstan nas bskyil /
NK027(sha)001:1508: bdag gi zhabs g.yas kyi the'unga dza las lcags kyur bsam la /
NK027(sha)001:1509: gnas kyi sgo 'di su yi bcad //
NK027(sha)001:1510: sems kyi bdag pos bcad dam bcing //
NK027(sha)001:1511: gzung 'dzin rkang pa bsnol ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:1512: yul las 'das pa sgo phyes shig /
NK027(sha)001:1513: h'u h'u phata phata ma tang ka ru h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:1514: sarba phye tam tsa bya phye tang tsa bya /
NK027(sha)001:1516: ral gri'i phyag rgyas kha tram kha pra we sha ya phata kyi khog pa dral /
NK027(sha)001:1518: h'u dkar po bdag gi thugs kar thim pas thugs ye shes dbyer med du bsam /
NK027(sha)001:1519: b+h+r+aum bi shwa b+hi shud+d+he b+han+d+ha dz+ny+aa na ram /
NK027(sha)001:1520: zhes pas khog pa zla gam smug nag gcig tu bsam /
NK027(sha)001:1521: b+h+rum kham pra we sha ya phata /
NK027(sha)001:1522: kyi sgo phyes pa'i nang du h'u h'u gi phyin /
NK027(sha)001:1523: ha ha h'u s+pha ra na phata /
NK027(sha)001:1524: sam ha ra na h'u gi sgo bcad la /
NK027(sha)001:1526: steng yang rdo rje'i bla re la //
NK027(sha)001:1527: 'og kyang rdo rje'i sa gzhi la //
NK027(sha)001:1528: phyogs mtshams rdo rje'i gtam pa la //
NK027(sha)001:1529: rdo rje'i mtshams las ma 'das shig /
NK027(sha)001:1530: badz+ra yak+sha kro ta h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:1532: ram yam kham zhes pas rdo rje'i gur du gyur nas bskal pa'i rlung gi mi thar bar /
NK027(sha)001:1533: khro bo bcu'i stang stabs bya /
NK027(sha)001:1535: skra mtshams su zhag gi zo ris /
NK027(sha)001:1536: dpral bar thal chen gyi tshom bu /
NK027(sha)001:1537: smin mtshams na khrag gi thig le bya /
NK027(sha)001:1538: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi mchod pa byin gyis rlobs /
NK027(sha)001:1539: zhi khro'i gzhal yas khang du gsung ngo //
NK027(sha)001:1540: de nas 'dzab zhi khro rig 'dzin gsum las /
NK027(sha)001:1541: dang po zhi ba'i 'dzab khang dbye ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:1542: rdo rje dbyings kyi dal gsal gdab la spyir 'byung
NK027(sha)001:1543: ba rim brtsegs kyi steng du b+h+r+aum gyi 'phro 'du
NK027(sha)001:1544: las / b+h+r+aum bi shwa b+hi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na
NK027(sha)001:1545: tsakra rat+na pad+ma karma g+ha na d+ha sur+ya tsan+t+ra pad+ma
NK027(sha)001:1546: las / man+dala zhes pas / lha'i gzhal yas khang
NK027(sha)001:1547: lte ba zlum po mu khyud glo 'bur gru chad
NK027(sha)001:1548: las / man+dala zhes pas / dang / lha rnams
NK027(sha)001:1549: sgo khyud rta bab 'dod snams pha gu d+r+wa phyed
NK027(sha)001:1550: pad+ma rdo ra me ri dang bcas pa'i dbus su
NK027(sha)001:1551: las / man+dala zhes pas / dang / h'u h'u
NK027(sha)001:1552: h'u / badz+ra tsit+ta h'u a a +aah badz+ra b+ha
NK027(sha)001:1553: tra sa man ta a kun bzang bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:1554: de nas mi bskyod pa la sogs zhi ba'i lha tshogs thams cad bskyed nas dbang bskur /
NK027(sha)001:1557: stim brtan par bzhugs su gsol nas lhag pa'i /
NK027(sha)001:1560: mi bskyod ye shes mchog dang ldan pa'i ral snal du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:1561: a la la hoh sems dpa' bde mchog de nyid 'gog pa rnams la slong ba'i phyir /
NK027(sha)001:1562: chags pa med pa'i bde mchog kun tu myong mdzad shes bzhin du snam du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:1563: mchog tu gsang ba'i bde la rol zhing dam bcas 'jig rten sgrol /
NK027(sha)001:1564: byang chub skye gnas bde mchog dbyings las mi nyams dga' ba'i gar mdzod cig /
NK027(sha)001:1566: zhen pa'i mtha' dang nyon mongs sngo skam gzir ba'i
NK027(sha)001:1567: rmong byed bde mchog rgyan dang ldan pas thabs kyis
NK027(sha)001:1569: 'gro kun mtshungs par spyod pas byang chub sgo mor
NK027(sha)001:1570: lam ston cing bde mchog bdud rtsi khyad par med
NK027(sha)001:1572: a la la hoh zhes brjod de /
NK027(sha)001:1574: gnyis pa 'dzab dngos la lha bskul ba /
NK027(sha)001:1575: rtog pa gnas gsal gdab cing 'dzab bya ba /
NK027(sha)001:1578: kun bzang gong ltar bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:1579: rang gi thugs ka nas 'od gtso bo'i thugs kar
NK027(sha)001:1580: 'phros pas mnyes te gtso bo'i thugs ka nas 'od
NK027(sha)001:1582: rang gi bag chags dri ma dag /
NK027(sha)001:1583: gtso bo mnyes pa'i zhal 'dzum dang bcas pas rang la thim /
NK027(sha)001:1584: mchog thun mong gi dngos grub ster bar bsam la /
NK027(sha)001:1586: rig pa gsung gi byin rlabs kyi //
NK027(sha)001:1587: ljags kyi rtse la bkram nas ni //
NK027(sha)001:1588: du ma nyid du so sor go //
NK027(sha)001:1590: seng chen bsnol ba'i khri steng nas //
NK027(sha)001:1591: rin chen nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan //
NK027(sha)001:1592: e ma kun bzang rdo rje nyid //
NK027(sha)001:1593: rig pa'i tshul snang sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:1594: sangs rgyas thams cad bskyed pa'i yab //
NK027(sha)001:1596: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK027(sha)001:1597: dang po byang chub mchog gi rgya //
NK027(sha)001:1598: bar pa rdo rje dril bu 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:1599: tha ma mnyam bzhag ye shes 'phro //
NK027(sha)001:1600: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK027(sha)001:1601: phyi yi yul la sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:1602: snang srid thams cad chos kyi dbyings //
NK027(sha)001:1603: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i yum //
NK027(sha)001:1604: bya ba mo dang gnyis su med //
NK027(sha)001:1605: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyi //
NK027(sha)001:1606: thams cad lha la mchod par 'bul //
NK027(sha)001:1607: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol /
NK027(sha)001:1609: ye shes rang rig ma skyes sems //
NK027(sha)001:1610: kun bzang yab kyi rang bzhin la //
NK027(sha)001:1611: ting 'dzin byed par dbang bskur nas //
