NK027(sha)001:1612: ma lus kun gyi byed por shog /
NK027(sha)001:1613: chos kyi skye mched ma skyes sems //
NK027(sha)001:1614: kun bzang yum gyi rang bzhin la //
NK027(sha)001:1615: ting 'dzin bya bar dbang bskur nas //
NK027(sha)001:1616: chos rnams kun gyi bya bar shog /
NK027(sha)001:1617: h'u h'u h'u badz+ra tsit+ta h'u /
NK027(sha)001:1618: a a +aa badz+ra sa man ta +aa /
NK027(sha)001:1620: byang chub sems mchog ye shes rdo rje'i thugs //
NK027(sha)001:1621: srid gsum dbang sdud thams cad mkhyen pa'i dpal //
NK027(sha)001:1622: bsnyel ba mi mnga' 'gro ba'i skyabs mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:1623: kun bzang rdo rje yid la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:1625: gdod nas ma byung ma skyes chos kyis dbyings //
NK027(sha)001:1626: ma skyes mi 'gag dngos por 'dzin dang bral //
NK027(sha)001:1627: 'byung byed thams cad bskyed pa yum gyi tshul //
NK027(sha)001:1628: bzang mo bya ba ma lus phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:1631: mum d+ha du shwa ri mi bskyod pa yab yum bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:1633: rig pa gsung gi byin gyis rlobs //
NK027(sha)001:1634: ljags kyi rtse la bkram nas ni //
NK027(sha)001:1635: du ma nyid du so sor go //
NK027(sha)001:1637: seng chen bsnol ba'i khri stengs su /
NK027(sha)001:1638: rin chen nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan //
NK027(sha)001:1639: ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' gtso //
NK027(sha)001:1642: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK027(sha)001:1643: rdo rje 'khor lo rin chen g.yas //
NK027(sha)001:1644: dril bu pad+ma ral gri g.yon //
NK027(sha)001:1645: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK027(sha)001:1646: kun tu bzang dang gnyis su med //
NK027(sha)001:1647: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyi //
NK027(sha)001:1648: yi dam lha la mchod par 'bul //
NK027(sha)001:1649: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK027(sha)001:1651: rnam shes nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK027(sha)001:1652: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pas //
NK027(sha)001:1654: mi bskyod yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK027(sha)001:1655: ting 'dzin thugs kyis dbang bskur nas //
NK027(sha)001:1656: dngos grub las rnams mngon byed shog /
NK027(sha)001:1659: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK027(sha)001:1660: gzugs sku stong pa nyid kyi tshul 'dzin cing //
NK027(sha)001:1661: yon tan ye shes lnga don thugs chud pa //
NK027(sha)001:1662: rgyal mchog mi bskyod pa la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:1663: don dam gnyis med dbyings su gsal //
NK027(sha)001:1664: dbang phyug yum mchog tshul 'dzin cing //
NK027(sha)001:1665: yon tan rnam rtog mi mnga' ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:1666: rgyal yum kun tu bzang mo la'o //
NK027(sha)001:1667: shar du 'khor lo'i rtsibs la rnam snang bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:1669: shar phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs nas //
NK027(sha)001:1670: glang chen bsnol ba'i khri steng nas //
NK027(sha)001:1671: rin chen nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan //
NK027(sha)001:1672: bcom ldan rnam par snang mdzad gtso //
NK027(sha)001:1675: g.yas sngo g.yon dmar dbus dkar zhal //
NK027(sha)001:1676: 'khor lo rdo rje rin chen g.yas //
NK027(sha)001:1677: dril bu pad+ma rgya gram g.yon //
NK027(sha)001:1678: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK027(sha)001:1679: sangs rgyas spyan dang gnyis su med //
NK027(sha)001:1680: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyi //
NK027(sha)001:1681: yi dam lha la mchod pa 'bul //
NK027(sha)001:1682: bla med gzugs phung sa yi ngo bo nyid //
NK027(sha)001:1683: sems phyir rnam snang yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK027(sha)001:1684: ting 'dzin sku ru dbang bskur nas //
NK027(sha)001:1685: dngos grub las rnams mngon byed shog /
NK027(sha)001:1686: dzi na dzig lam te sha ra ti //
NK027(sha)001:1687: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK027(sha)001:1688: gzugs sku me long ye shes tshul 'dzin cing //
NK027(sha)001:1689: yon tan chos kyis 'khor lo mdzad pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:1690: rgyal mchog rnam snang mdzad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:1691: don dam gnyis med dbyings su gsal //
NK027(sha)001:1692: de dbyings dbyings phyug tshul 'dzin cing //
NK027(sha)001:1693: yon tan 'bras bu yod de stong pa'i mchog /
NK027(sha)001:1694: sangs rgyas spyan la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:1697: lho phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng nas //
NK027(sha)001:1698: rta mchog bsnol ba'i khri steng nas //
NK027(sha)001:1699: rin chen pad+ma nyi zla'i gdan //
NK027(sha)001:1700: bcom ldan rin chen 'byung ldan gyi //
NK027(sha)001:1702: g.yas sngo g.yon dmar dbus ser zhal //
NK027(sha)001:1703: rin chen rdo rje 'khor lo g.yas //
NK027(sha)001:1704: dril bu pad+ma rgya gram g.yon //
NK027(sha)001:1705: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK027(sha)001:1706: ma ma ki dang gnyis su med //
NK027(sha)001:1707: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyi //
NK027(sha)001:1708: yi dam lha la mchod pa 'bul //
NK027(sha)001:1709: bla med tshor ba chu yi ngo bo nyid //
NK027(sha)001:1710: sems phyir rin 'byung yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK027(sha)001:1711: ting 'dzin yon tan dbang bskur nas //
NK027(sha)001:1712: dngos grub las rnams mngon byed shog /
NK027(sha)001:1714: mam mo ha ra ti s+t+wam //
NK027(sha)001:1715: chos sku gzugs sku mnyam pa nyid kyi tshul 'dzin cing //
NK027(sha)001:1716: yon tan yid bzhin re ba bkang mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:1717: rgyal mchog rin chen 'byung la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:1718: don dam rin chen dbyings phyug tshul 'dzin cing //
NK027(sha)001:1719: yon tan re 'dod ma m+aa ki la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:1720: nub tu snang ba mtha' yas bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:1722: nub phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs su //
NK027(sha)001:1723: rma bya bsnol ba'i gdan steng nas //
NK027(sha)001:1724: rin chen pad+ma nyi zla'i gdan //
NK027(sha)001:1725: bcom ldan snang ba mtha' yas che //
NK027(sha)001:1728: g.yas ser g.yon ljang dbus dmar zhal //
NK027(sha)001:1730: dril bu rin chen ral gri g.yon //
NK027(sha)001:1731: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK027(sha)001:1732: na bza' dkar dang gnyis su med //
NK027(sha)001:1733: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyi //
NK027(sha)001:1734: 'du shes me yi ngo bo nyid //
NK027(sha)001:1735: sems phyir snang mtha' yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK027(sha)001:1736: ting 'dzin gsung gi dbang bskur nas //
NK027(sha)001:1737: dngos grub las rnams mngon byed shog /
NK027(sha)001:1740: chos sku nam mkha' gzugs sku so sor rtogs pa'i mtha' gnyis skyon rnams dag mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:1741: rgyal mchog snang ba mtha' yas la //
NK027(sha)001:1742: don dam gnyis med dbyings su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:1744: spyi dang rang gi cha 'dzin ma //
NK027(sha)001:1745: na bza' dkar la byang du don yod grub pa yab yum bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:1747: byang phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs su //
NK027(sha)001:1748: shang shang bsnol ba'i gdan steng nas //
NK027(sha)001:1749: rin chen pad+ma nyi zla'i gdan //
NK027(sha)001:1750: bcom ldan don yod grub pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:1753: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus ljang zhal //
NK027(sha)001:1754: ral gri rdo rje 'khor lo g.yas //
NK027(sha)001:1755: dril bu rin chen pad+ma g.yon //
NK027(sha)001:1756: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK027(sha)001:1757: dam tshig sgrol dang gnyis su med //
NK027(sha)001:1758: bdag gi bla med 'du byed rlung gi ngo bo nyid //
NK027(sha)001:1759: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa //
NK027(sha)001:1760: don grub yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK027(sha)001:1761: ting 'dzin phrin las dbang bskur nas //
NK027(sha)001:1762: dngos grub las rnams mngon byed shog /
NK027(sha)001:1765: chos sku gzugs sku bya ba grub pa'i tshul 'dzin cing //
NK027(sha)001:1766: phrin las sna tshogs don mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:1767: rgyal mchog don yod grub la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:1768: don dam gnyis med dbyings su gsal //
NK027(sha)001:1769: las kyi dbyings phyug tshul 'dzin cing //
NK027(sha)001:1770: bdag gzhan don grub cha 'dzin ma //
NK027(sha)001:1771: dam tshig sgrol la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:1773: shar lho'i gong ras la sa snying yab yum bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:1774: shar lho 'khor lo'i gong ras la //
NK027(sha)001:1775: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan steng na //
NK027(sha)001:1776: byang sems sa yi snying po dang //
NK027(sha)001:1777: yum chen lha mo l+aa se ma //
NK027(sha)001:1778: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs las //
NK027(sha)001:1779: las nyon bag chags sbyang du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:1780: mig gzugs sems su ma skyes pa //
NK027(sha)001:1781: sa snying yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK027(sha)001:1782: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang bskur nas //
NK027(sha)001:1783: spyod yul yongs su dag byed shog /
NK027(sha)001:1785: h'u l+aa s+ye sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)001:1787: me long ye shes khyad par las //
NK027(sha)001:1788: mtshan dpe sems dpa'i sku ston cing //
NK027(sha)001:1789: che ba'i yon tan bskyed mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:1790: sa yi snying po phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:1791: gnyis med chos dbyings khyad par las //
NK027(sha)001:1792: mtshan dpe lha mo'i skur ston cing //
NK027(sha)001:1793: rnam dag zil gyi gnon mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:1794: l+aa s+ye ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:1795: lho nub kyi gong ras la nam snying yab yum bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:1797: lho nub 'khor lo'i gong ras la //
NK027(sha)001:1798: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan steng nas //
NK027(sha)001:1799: byang sems nam mkha'i snying po dang //
NK027(sha)001:1800: yum chen lha mo ma le gnyis //
NK027(sha)001:1801: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs las //
NK027(sha)001:1802: las nyon bag chags sbyangs du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:1803: sna dri sems phyir ma skyes pa //
NK027(sha)001:1804: nam snying yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK027(sha)001:1805: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang bskur nas //
NK027(sha)001:1806: spyod yul yongs su dag byed shog /
NK027(sha)001:1808: tram ma le ma ya s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)001:1810: mnyam nyid ye shes khyad par las //
NK027(sha)001:1811: mtshan dpe sems dpa'i skur ston cing //
NK027(sha)001:1812: rnam rtog d+r+wa ba gcod mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:1813: nam mkha'i snying po phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:1814: gnyis med chos dbyings khyad par las //
NK027(sha)001:1815: mtshan dpe lha mo'i skur ston cing //
NK027(sha)001:1816: 'khor ba zil gyi gnon mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:1817: ma le ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:1818: nub byang gi gong ras la spyan gzigs yab yum bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:1820: nub byang 'khor lo'i gong ras la //
NK027(sha)001:1821: nyi zla pad+ma'i byang sems spyan ras gzigs dbang dang //
NK027(sha)001:1822: yum chen lha mo girti gnyis //
NK027(sha)001:1823: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs las //
NK027(sha)001:1824: las nyon bag chags sbyangs du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:1825: lce ro sems phyir ma skyes pa //
NK027(sha)001:1826: spyan gzigs yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK027(sha)001:1827: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang bskur nas //
NK027(sha)001:1828: spyod yul yongs su dag byed shog /
NK027(sha)001:1829: h+r+aihha h'u pad+ma b+ha d+ha ma /
NK027(sha)001:1830: h+r+aih g+hirti ra ga ya hoh h'u /
NK027(sha)001:1831: sor rtogs ye shes khyad par las //
NK027(sha)001:1832: mtshan dpe sems dpa'i skur ston cing //
NK027(sha)001:1833: mtha' 'am dri mas ma gos pa //
NK027(sha)001:1834: spyan ras gzigs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:1835: mtshan dpe lha mo'i skur ston cing //
NK027(sha)001:1836: gnyis med don gyi tshim mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:1838: byang shar gyi gong ras la phyag rdor yab yum bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:1840: byang shar 'khor lo'i gong ras la //
NK027(sha)001:1841: nyi zla byang sems phyag na rdo rje dang //
NK027(sha)001:1842: yum chen lha mo nirti gnyis //
NK027(sha)001:1843: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs las //
NK027(sha)001:1844: las nyon bag chags sbyang du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:1845: lus rigs sems phyir ma skyes pa //
NK027(sha)001:1846: phyag rdor yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK027(sha)001:1847: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang bskur nas //
NK027(sha)001:1848: spyod yul yongs su dag byed shog /
NK027(sha)001:1849: dzim ku ru pa ni h+r+aih a nirti ra ga ya mi /
NK027(sha)001:1851: bya grub ye shes khyad par las //
NK027(sha)001:1852: mtshan dpe sems dpa' skur ston cing //
NK027(sha)001:1853: rnam rtog ma lus 'joms mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:1854: phyag na rdo rje phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:1855: gnyis med chos dbyings khyad par las //
NK027(sha)001:1856: mtshan dpe lha mo'i skur ston cing //
NK027(sha)001:1857: phrin las sna tshogs rdzogs mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:1858: nirti ma la phyi'i sems dpa'i 'dzab ni /
NK027(sha)001:1859: shar lhor byams pa yab yum bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:1861: dkyil 'khor shar lho'i gru chad la //
NK027(sha)001:1862: nyi zla byang chub sems dpa' byams pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:1863: yum chen lha mo d+hush+pe ma //
NK027(sha)001:1864: gnyis med rol pa las nyon bag chags mi dbang 'dus dus ma skyes pa //
NK027(sha)001:1865: byams pa yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK027(sha)001:1866: ting 'dzin sems dpas dbang bskur nas //
NK027(sha)001:1867: spyod yul yongs su me tri da ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:1868: dza d+hush+pe pra we sha ya phata dzah h'u /
NK027(sha)001:1869: rig pa thugs kyi khyad par las //
NK027(sha)001:1870: mtshan dpe sems dpa'i sku ston cing //
NK027(sha)001:1871: rgyal ba'i yon tan rgyas mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:1872: byams pa de la skye ma chos kyi byin rlabs las //
NK027(sha)001:1873: mtshan dpe lha mo'i skye med don dam ston mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:1874: d+hush+pe m+aa la lho nub kyi grar sgrib sel yab yum bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:1876: dkyil 'khor lho nub gru chad la //
NK027(sha)001:1877: nyi zla'i pad+ma'i byang sems sgrib pa rnam sel dang //
NK027(sha)001:1878: yum chen lha mo push+pe gnyis //
NK027(sha)001:1879: gnyis med rol las nyon rna dbang da lta ma skyes sems //
NK027(sha)001:1880: sgrib sel yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK027(sha)001:1881: ting 'dzin sems dpa'i dbang bskur nas //
NK027(sha)001:1882: spyod yul thi tam ni sa ram ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:1883: h'u push+pe a we sha ya phata dzah h'u /
NK027(sha)001:1884: ye shes rig pa'i khyad par las //
NK027(sha)001:1885: mtshan dpe sems dpa'i skye med chos sku ston mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:1886: sgrib pa rnam sel phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:1888: skye med chos dbyings khyad par las //
NK027(sha)001:1889: mtshan dpe lha mo'i skur rig pa nyid las char mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:1890: me tog ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:1891: nub byang du kun bzang yab yum bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:1893: dkyil 'khor nub kyi gru chad la //
NK027(sha)001:1894: nyi zla byang sems kun tu bzang po dang //
NK027(sha)001:1895: yum chen lha mo a lo ke /
NK027(sha)001:1896: gnyis med las nyon rna dbang ma 'ongs ma skyes sems //
NK027(sha)001:1897: kun bzang yab yum rang bzhin las /
NK027(sha)001:1898: ting 'dzin spyod yul h'u swa ra tsa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:1899: bam d+hi pa su ki ni /
NK027(sha)001:1901: ye shes rol pa'i khyad par las //
NK027(sha)001:1902: mtshan dpe 'bras bu'i chos rnams rdzogs mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:1903: kun tu bzang po phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:1905: skye med chos dbyings byin rlabs las //
NK027(sha)001:1906: mtshan dpe rig pa nyid la gsal mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:1907: a lo ke la byang shar grar 'jam dpal yab yum bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:1909: dkyil 'khor byang shar gru chad la //
NK027(sha)001:1910: nyi zla byang chub sems dpa' 'jam dpal dang //
NK027(sha)001:1911: yum chen lha mo g+han+d+he ma //
NK027(sha)001:1912: gnyis med las nyon lce dbang ma 'ongs ma skyes sems //
NK027(sha)001:1913: 'jam dpal yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK027(sha)001:1914: ting 'dzin spyod yul yongs su mum sh+r+ai a ram ga ya ho /
NK027(sha)001:1916: ye shes rig pa'i khyad par las //
NK027(sha)001:1917: mtshan dpe sems dpa'i 'khor ba'i mtshan nyid rtogs mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:1919: skye med chos dbyings byin mtshan dpe lha mo'i mtha' yi skyon rnams dag mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:1920: g+han+d+he ma la de nas lha rnams la thub pa bskyed de /

NK027(sha)001:1925: sku mdog dkar po lha rnams 'dren //
NK027(sha)001:1926: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyi //
NK027(sha)001:1928: nyon mongs dreg pa ma skyes sems //
NK027(sha)001:1929: lha yi thub pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK027(sha)001:1930: rang bzhin thub par dbang bsgyur nas //
NK027(sha)001:1931: gdul bya ma lus 'dren byed shog /

NK027(sha)001:2076: sor rtogs ye shes byin rlabs kyi //
NK027(sha)001:2077: klu chen khro bor skur ston cing //
NK027(sha)001:2078: thabs kyis nyon mongs bdud rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:2079: khro rgyal rta mchog dpal la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2081: gnyis med chos kyi dbyings kyi byin rlabs las //
NK027(sha)001:2082: 'gro ba 'dul phyir lcags sgrog ma ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2083: thabs kyi nyon mongs gnas nas 'dren mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:2084: nyi zla lcags sgrog ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2085: byang sgo bdud rtsi 'khyil pa yab yum bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:2087: gzhal yas khang gi byang sgo ru //
NK027(sha)001:2088: rdo rje brag gi khri stengs su //
NK027(sha)001:2089: nyi ma gsal ba'i gdan 'joms pa'i khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK027(sha)001:2090: 'bebs pa'i lha mo dril bu ma //
NK027(sha)001:2091: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs kyi //
NK027(sha)001:2092: gnod sbyin gdon rnams bsal du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:2093: rigs 'dus mtshan ma ma skyes sems //
NK027(sha)001:2094: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK027(sha)001:2095: ting 'dzin bdud rtsi gdul bya ma lus h'u prad dz+ny+aa ta krita phata /
NK027(sha)001:2096: karma da ra kro ti sha ri dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:2098: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes byin brlabs las //
NK027(sha)001:2099: gnod sbyin 'dul phyir khro bor skur ston pa //
NK027(sha)001:2100: thabs kyi nyon mongs bdud rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:2101: khro rgyal bdud rtsi 'khyil la phyag h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2102: gnyis med chos kyi dbyings kyi byin rlabs las //
NK027(sha)001:2103: 'gro ba 'dul phyir thal byed ma ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2104: thabs kyis 'gro ba ma lus 'dren mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:2105: rdo rje dril bu ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2107: b+ho d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha dz+ny+aa na d+ha tu +aah bzlas /
NK027(sha)001:2109: ye nas mnyam nyid kyi bshags //
NK027(sha)001:2110: ye shes rgyal po'i sku gsung thugs //
NK027(sha)001:2111: yon tan da lta phyag rgya badz+ra sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)001:2112: badz+ra sa ma ya hoh dzahmh'u bam hos /
NK027(sha)001:2114: de nas tshogs 'bul zhing rol mo bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:2115: de nas khro bo'i 'dzab khang dbye ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:2118: b+h+r+aum b+hi sha b+hi shud+d+he b+han+d+ha dz+ny+aa na tsakra sur+ya tsan tra pad+ma e man+dala /
NK027(sha)001:2121: ru tra kro ti sti ra bam /
NK027(sha)001:2122: a kro ma h+aa kro ta sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:2123: ka ta ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2124: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:2125: ka ta ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2126: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:2127: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:2128: sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2147: steng gi khro bo khro mo drug cu /
NK027(sha)001:2150: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang rnams rim pas rtsa sngags kyi bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:2153: ka ya waka tsi tas brtan par bzhugs su gsol /
NK027(sha)001:2155: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
NK027(sha)001:2156: bsgrub dang gdug pa 'dul ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:2157: 'bar ba khro bo'i lha tshogs la //
NK027(sha)001:2158: sgo gsum gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)001:2165: glu ye shes rnams dbyangs dang bcas 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:2166: rgya mtsho lnga'i smon lam gdab pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:2168: a kra ma ma h+aa kro ta sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2169: ka ta ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2170: phata dzah ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2172: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK027(sha)001:2173: 'khor lo 'bar ba dbus kyi lte ba la //
NK027(sha)001:2174: bcom ldan che mchog dpal chen he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:2175: ston pa kun tu bzang po gnas gyur ba //
NK027(sha)001:2176: rgyal ba khro rgyal kun gyi rje btsun yab //
NK027(sha)001:2177: che ba'i nang nas che mchog 'dran zla med //
NK027(sha)001:2178: che btsan 'dran zla bral ba kun gyi mchog /
NK027(sha)001:2179: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2180: 'bar ba'i dbu ni nyi shu rtsa gcig gi //
NK027(sha)001:2181: sa ni nyi shu rtsa gcig rim pas mnan //
NK027(sha)001:2182: g.yas g.yon phyag ni bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis na //
NK027(sha)001:2183: rgyal ba sangs rgyas bzhi cu rtsa gnyis bzhugs //
NK027(sha)001:2184: zhabs brgyad bsgrad pas khro bo'i dbu rgyan bardzisa //
NK027(sha)001:2185: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer sku la brjid //
NK027(sha)001:2186: dpal gyi chas rgyad dur khrod rgyan rnams rdzogs //
NK027(sha)001:2187: che mchog he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2188: kun tu bzang mo'i chos nyid gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:2189: dpal 'bar khro mo kun gyi rje btsun yum //
NK027(sha)001:2190: shes rab dbyings nas sku bskyed thugs rje ldan //
NK027(sha)001:2191: khro mo gnam zhal ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2192: a kra ka ta ru lu zhes bzlas so //
NK027(sha)001:2193: bcom ldan dbang mchog he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:2195: dbu gsum dang por byung ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:2196: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK027(sha)001:2197: sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa'i dbu //
NK027(sha)001:2198: khams gsum mya ngan 'das pa'i zhal //
NK027(sha)001:2199: dbu gsum rab tu rngam pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:2200: g.yas sngo g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK027(sha)001:2201: thabs dang shes rab sems kyi dbu //
NK027(sha)001:2202: srid gsum dbyings su rdzogs pa'i zhal //
NK027(sha)001:2203: dbu gsum thog mar rngam pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:2204: g.yas g.yon dbu gsum mthing ba'i zhal //
NK027(sha)001:2205: lung dang man ngag sems kyi dbu //
NK027(sha)001:2206: khams gsum re ba bskang ba'i zhal //
NK027(sha)001:2207: bco brgyad phyag rgya rol ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:2208: stong pa bco brgyad dbyings su thim //
NK027(sha)001:2209: rdo rje glo snying zhing chung g.yas //
NK027(sha)001:2210: b+han+d+ha zhing chung sti ra g.yon //
NK027(sha)001:2211: zhing zhags nyi ma khyung chen g.yas //
NK027(sha)001:2212: zhing chen zla ba 'ug pa g.yon //
NK027(sha)001:2213: me dang rgya mtsho lbu ba g.yas //
NK027(sha)001:2214: klu dang rin chen ri rab g.yon //
NK027(sha)001:2215: yon tan bac+wo brgyad dbyings su rdzogs //
NK027(sha)001:2216: khro rgyal rgyan rnams sku la brjod //
NK027(sha)001:2217: klu rgyal che mchog he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:2218: dbang mchog sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2219: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:2222: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK027(sha)001:2224: dreg pa bsnol ba'i khri stengs su //
NK027(sha)001:2225: rdo rje mi bskyod gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:2227: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku bskyod pa //
NK027(sha)001:2228: mchod cing byin rlabs bsgrub pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:2229: badz+ra he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2230: nam mkha' kun bzang gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:2231: khro mo dbyings phyug skur gsal ba //
NK027(sha)001:2232: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med //
NK027(sha)001:2233: kro ti shwa ri'i sku la bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2234: badz+ra sh+r+ai badz+ra kro ti ru lu ru lu h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2235: dbang gi da la chen po yi //
NK027(sha)001:2236: shar phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK027(sha)001:2237: dri za bsnol ba'i khri stengs su //
NK027(sha)001:2238: rnam par snang mdzad gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:2241: mchod cing bsgrub ste byin rlabs las //
NK027(sha)001:2242: b+hud+d+ha he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2243: sangs rgyas spyan ma gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:2244: khro mo dbang phyug skur gsal ba //
NK027(sha)001:2245: thabs dang shes rab byang chub sems //
NK027(sha)001:2246: spyan 'dren mchod cing bsgrub pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:2247: b+hud+d+ha kro ti shwa ri'i sku la bud+d+ha sh+r+ai bud+d+ha kro ti ru lu ru lu h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2248: dbang gi dkyil 'khor lho phyogs gshin rje bsnol rin chen 'byung ldan gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:2250: 'jigs byed ser nag skur bskyed pa //
NK027(sha)001:2251: spyan 'dren mchod cing bsgrub pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:2252: rat+na he ru ka la bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2254: ma ma ki ni gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:2255: 'jigs byed khro mo'i skur gsal ba //
NK027(sha)001:2256: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK027(sha)001:2257: spyan 'dren rat+na kro ti shwa ri'i sku la rat+na sh+r+ai rat+na kro ta h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2258: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po'i nub phyogs 'khor lo'i
NK027(sha)001:2259: klu dbang bsnol ba'i snang ba mtha' yas gnas gyur
NK027(sha)001:2261: 'jigs byed dmar nag ral pa can //
NK027(sha)001:2262: sgom zhing mchod do bsgrub pa'i lha //
NK027(sha)001:2263: pad+ma he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2264: na bza' dkar mo gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:2265: 'jigs byed khro mo'i skur gsal ba //
NK027(sha)001:2266: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK027(sha)001:2267: gnyis med byang chub sems bsgrub pa /
NK027(sha)001:2268: pad+ma kro ti'i sku la bstod /
NK027(sha)001:2269: pad+ma ru lu ru lu h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2270: dbang gi dkyil 'khor byang phyogs 'khor lo'i gnod sbyin bsnol don yod grub pa gnas gyur ba //
NK027(sha)001:2273: gsal bar bskyed cing mchod bsgrub pa //
NK027(sha)001:2274: karma he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2275: dam tshig sgrol ma gnas gyur ba //
NK027(sha)001:2276: 'jigs byed khro mo'i skur gsal ba //
NK027(sha)001:2277: lhag pa'i byang chub sems 'phros pa //
NK027(sha)001:2278: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK027(sha)001:2279: karma kro ti shwa ri sku la bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2280: karma sh+r+ai karma kro ta ru lu ru lu h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2281: dbang gi dkyil 'khor shar lho'i 'khor lo'i mthu stobs mnga' bdag gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:2282: sgrol byed chen po'i bdud rnams 'joms //
NK027(sha)001:2283: bdud dang srin po'i sgrol la brtson //
NK027(sha)001:2284: mthing nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK027(sha)001:2285: rak+sha he ru ka la lha mo ral gcig gnas gyur ba //
NK027(sha)001:2286: khro mo yab kyi cha lugs can //
NK027(sha)001:2287: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK027(sha)001:2288: rak+sha kro ti'i sku la bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2289: rak+sha rak+sha kro ti ru lu h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2290: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK027(sha)001:2291: lho nub dam tshig chen po gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:2292: dpal chen dam tshig mnga' mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:2293: ser nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK027(sha)001:2294: bskal pa brgyar yang dam tshig lhag /
NK027(sha)001:2295: sa nu he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2296: yum chen dam tshig gnas gyur ba //
NK027(sha)001:2297: khro mo dbyings phyug bya ra mkhan //
NK027(sha)001:2298: sangs rgyas sems can 'das mi byed //
NK027(sha)001:2299: dam tshig dbyings su bskul byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:2300: sa nu kro ti sku la sa nu sh+r+ai sa nu kro ti ru lu h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2301: dbang gi nub byang 'khor lo'i mkhyen rab mnga' bdag gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:2302: sgrol byed chen po'i dreg pa 'dul //
NK027(sha)001:2303: ljang nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK027(sha)001:2304: dus rnams rtag tu gsang ba'i lha //
NK027(sha)001:2305: zhe sdang 'khor ba sgrol la brtson //
NK027(sha)001:2306: g+hu h+ye ru ka la bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2307: bardzusa skyes 'joms ma gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:2308: khro mo yab kyi cha lugs can //
NK027(sha)001:2309: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK027(sha)001:2310: g+hu h+ya kro ti'i g+hu h+ye sh+r+ai g+hu h+ye kro ti ru lu h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2311: dbang gi dkyil 'khor byang shar 'khor lo'i thugs rjes mnga' bdag gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:2314: gang bsgrub mthu dang dbang bstsol ba //
NK027(sha)001:2315: yak+sha he ru ka la 'jig rten ma mo gnas khro rgyal dbang phyug kun gyi rje //
NK027(sha)001:2316: sprul pa kun gyi yang sprul pa //
NK027(sha)001:2317: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med pa //
NK027(sha)001:2319: yak+sha kro ti ru lu ru lu h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2320: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dbang gi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)001:2321: 'bar ba'i glo 'bur gru chad bzhi po las //
NK027(sha)001:2322: ko'u ri la sogs khro mo brgyad rnams ni /
NK027(sha)001:2323: gdugs pa thabs kyi 'dul ba'i drag shul can //
NK027(sha)001:2324: sku mdog phyag mtshan sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK027(sha)001:2325: ye shes ma mo brgyad la phyag badz+ra ko'u ri ha /
NK027(sha)001:2327: ru lu ru lu zhes khro mo brgyad kyi sngags dang /
NK027(sha)001:2330: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i bar khyams gser mdog na //
NK027(sha)001:2331: seng ha la sogs phra men brgyad rnams ni //
NK027(sha)001:2332: ye shes las la 'gyed pa'i phra men ma //
NK027(sha)001:2333: rnam 'phrul las kyi 'gro ba'i don mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:2334: seng ha phra men brgyad badz+ra seng ha mu kha mu kha he brgyad dang /
NK027(sha)001:2337: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i bar khyams shar lho nub byang sgo bzhi ru //
NK027(sha)001:2338: tshad med bzhi yi 'gro ba'i don mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:2339: rta gdong phag gdong seng gdong spyang gdong bzhi //
NK027(sha)001:2340: zhi rgyas dbang drag las la thogs med brtson //
NK027(sha)001:2341: rtag chad bdag 'dzin mtshan mar lta las grol //
NK027(sha)001:2342: ye shes sgo ma bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2343: badz+ra ar+ya te tsa ting dza sogs /
NK027(sha)001:2345: tshogs chen 'dus pa 'bar ba'i bar khyams gnyis pa dkar po na //
NK027(sha)001:2346: chos nyid rnam dag ngang las rang snang ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:2347: sna tshogs cir yang 'gyur ba'i sku mnga' ba //
NK027(sha)001:2348: srid gsum zhing du sbyor ba'i g.yang gzhi gsol //
NK027(sha)001:2349: spor ma chen mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2350: badz+ra a pra ti ha a r+ya ni tsa tur ta ra phata /
NK027(sha)001:2353: tshogs chen bar khyams shar lho nub byang sgo bzhi ru //
NK027(sha)001:2354: dgyes pa bskyed pa gsang ba'i yum chen bzhi //
NK027(sha)001:2355: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs sna tshogs 'phro //
NK027(sha)001:2356: shes rab yum chen bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2357: sh+r+ai badz+ra mud kha ra mu kha /
NK027(sha)001:2359: ru badz+ra sh+r+ai kha tram badz+ra g+han+d+he ru lu h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2361: 'bar ba'i bar khyams dmar po gsum pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:2362: ma sring la sogs dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad //
NK027(sha)001:2363: dregs pa lha chen rnams kyi chung ma ste //
NK027(sha)001:2364: dbang drag las la thogs pa med par spyod //
NK027(sha)001:2365: dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad la ma nu rak+sha si b+h+yo /
NK027(sha)001:2366: zhes pa la sogs ba dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad kyi sngags dang ru lu spel ma bzla /
NK027(sha)001:2368: tshogs chen 'bar ba'i bar khyams bzhi pa gser mdog na //
NK027(sha)001:2369: nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //
NK027(sha)001:2370: 'dod dgu bsgyur ba'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK027(sha)001:2371: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyi grogs mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:2372: mkha' 'gro sum cu gnyis la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2375: tshogs chen 'bar ba'i bar khyams lnga pa dmar po na /
NK027(sha)001:2376: 'jig rten dreg pa 'dul ba ma mo'i tshogs //
NK027(sha)001:2377: phyi 'khor 'dus zhing nang 'khor skyong mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:2378: dur khrod ma bdun las kyi sring mo bzhi //
NK027(sha)001:2379: bgegs bsrung ma mo rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2381: zhes pa bdun dang ru lu spel /
NK027(sha)001:2383: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dbang gi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)001:2384: 'bar ba'i bar khyams drug pa dkar po ni //
NK027(sha)001:2385: khams gsum sgrol ba'i ging chen bco brgyad ni //
NK027(sha)001:2386: srid gsum las la thogs med sgrol la brtson //
NK027(sha)001:2387: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu gtan nas brlag par byed //
NK027(sha)001:2388: ging chen bco brgyad rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2389: ka ra ha ha ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2391: tshogs chen 'bar ba'i bar khyams bdun pa nag po na //
NK027(sha)001:2392: bcom ldan h'u mdzad sa gsum brjid kyi gnon //
NK027(sha)001:2393: khams gsum 'dul mdzad ye shes lha yi lha //
NK027(sha)001:2394: 'jigs byed 'bar bas gdugs pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms //
NK027(sha)001:2395: khro bo khro mo rnams la kro ta kro ti h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2397: tshogs chen 'bar ba'i bar khyams brgyad kyi phyogs mdog na //
NK027(sha)001:2398: ye shes thugs rjes phyogs bcur khyab pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:2399: gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i las la thogs med pa //
NK027(sha)001:2400: ci bgyi bka' nyan las rnams myur mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:2401: phyogs bzhi pho nya'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2402: b+ha na b+ha na am gu sha dzah ru lu ha la ha la pa sha h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2403: ru lu gardza gardza pho ta bam /
NK027(sha)001:2404: ru lu pa tsa pa tsa g+han+d+he hoh ru lu h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2405: tshogs chen 'bar ba'i bar khyams dgu pa ljang ku na //
NK027(sha)001:2406: stong khams yongs su las la dbang byed pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:2407: ma chen rgyal mo srid pa gsum gyis bdag /
NK027(sha)001:2408: yum chen las la dbang ba'i dbang mo che //
NK027(sha)001:2409: ma mo drug cu'i tshogs la ma ma sha ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2411: tshogs chen 'dus 'bar ba'i bar khyams bcu pa mdzes tshon nas //
NK027(sha)001:2412: theg dgu'i lha tshogs rgyal ba zhi khro rnams //
NK027(sha)001:2413: dbyings nas ye shes dbyer med gdul bya la //
NK027(sha)001:2414: chu dang chu zla bzhin du ston mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:2415: 'gro ba'i don rnams bsgrub la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:2416: b+ho d+hi tsit+ta dang ru lu h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2417: gzhal yas khang chen rta babs khyams zer sgo bzhi na //
NK027(sha)001:2418: rig 'dzin bla ma byin rlabs mthu rtsal can //
NK027(sha)001:2419: lhun grub phyag chen tshe dbang rnam smin bzhi //
NK027(sha)001:2420: rgya bod mkhas grub rtsa rgyud bla ma rnams //
NK027(sha)001:2421: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyis dngos grub 'dir stsol la //
NK027(sha)001:2422: don gnyis grub par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK027(sha)001:2423: ma h+aa gu ru sha ri ram gi li h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2424: ru lu ru lu spel zhing bzlas /
NK027(sha)001:2425: de nas nam lang ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:2426: rab tu gnas pa bya ba la don brgyad do //
NK027(sha)001:2427: sngon du 'gro ba'i cho ga dang /
NK027(sha)001:2428: ting nge 'dzin gyi dal bskyed pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:2429: rang bzhin spyan drangs shing bstim pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:2430: dbang po skyon bsal gyi chos bdun bya bas /
NK027(sha)001:2431: me long phul te chu bdun gyi khrus gsol ba /
NK027(sha)001:2432: phyi ma dang che ba'i yon tan rgyan chas rnams kyis dbang bskur zhing mnga' gsol ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:2433: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa 'bul ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:2434: brtan par bzhugs su gsol zhing smon lam gdab pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:2435: dang po sngon du bya ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:2436: dal gyi shar du man+dala 'dab brgyad mdzes tshon bya /
NK027(sha)001:2437: dbus su man+dzu khar rin po che'i snod du /
NK027(sha)001:2438: bzed zhal gyi me long bzhag /
NK027(sha)001:2439: shar du dbang po'i skyon bsal gyi thur ma la sogs pa bshams /
NK027(sha)001:2440: lhor rgyas pa'i sbyin bsreg bya /
NK027(sha)001:2441: nub tu cha gsum gtor ma btang /
NK027(sha)001:2444: mkhar ba'i snod du rnam lnga sogs sbyar ba'i chus /
NK027(sha)001:2445: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ka ya b+hi sho d+ha ni h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2446: zhes pas me long la sku gzugs 'char ba la
NK027(sha)001:2447: khrus gsol bas dngos 'dzin gyi dri ma thams cad
NK027(sha)001:2448: dag par bsam / til mar la a h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK027(sha)001:2449: zhes byug pas thugs byang chub kyi gzungs dang ldan par bsam /
NK027(sha)001:2450: shing shun lnga'i phyi ma dang /
NK027(sha)001:2452: gong gi sngags kyi khrus gsol sa khams lnga'i rtog
NK027(sha)001:2453: pa dag nas che ba'i yon tan phun sum tshogs
NK027(sha)001:2454: par bsam / ras kha tshar gyi phyis te /
NK027(sha)001:2455: rat+na pra b+han dza tsa ra s+w+aa h+aas ltas ngan dang shes sgrib dag par bsam /
NK027(sha)001:2456: de nas spos dri bzang po phul bas sangs rgyas
NK027(sha)001:2457: kyi mdzad pa'i phrin las yongs su rdzogs par bsam
NK027(sha)001:2458: / de nas nang gi zhi khro bya ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:2459: rang lus kyi phyogs mtshams steng 'og phyogs skyong bcu'i gdan la khro bcu bsam la /
NK027(sha)001:2462: gdod nas ma skyes rnam dag chos kyi sku //
NK027(sha)001:2463: chos nyid byang chub sems su dbyer med kyang //
NK027(sha)001:2464: srid pa srog gi bsdus pa'i sems can rnams //
NK027(sha)001:2465: log rtog dngos por gol ba'i dbang gi na //
NK027(sha)001:2466: sdug bsngal brgyad khri bzhi stong rang las byung //
NK027(sha)001:2467: sdug bsngal brgyad dang gsum gyis 'gro ba rnams //
NK027(sha)001:2468: rgyu 'bras theg pa gzhan gyi mi 'dul te //
NK027(sha)001:2469: gsang sngags gsang chen nges pa'i dus la babs /
NK027(sha)001:2471: srid gsum phyi nang snod bcud thams cad na //
NK027(sha)001:2472: snyigs ma lnga dang skye 'gro ma lus kun //
NK027(sha)001:2473: thams cad sangs rgyas nyid kyi rang bzhin las //
NK027(sha)001:2474: thabs la mkhas pa 'di ltar btags shing sgom //
NK027(sha)001:2477: steng 'og phyogs mtshams dngos por cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2478: khro bcu yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2479: phyogs bcur gnas pa'i bgegs rnams kun bsal nas //
NK027(sha)001:2480: bar chad med cing dngos grub thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2482: ye shes sku mchog ma bya /
NK027(sha)001:2483: sgrib pa rnam gnyis dngos por cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2484: yid kyi mngon du bshags pa'i byin rlabs kyi //
NK027(sha)001:2485: sgrib pa ye nas dag pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:2486: sems nyid rang bzhin med pa'i don rtogs shog /
NK027(sha)001:2489: mthu dang bral ba'i sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2490: bder gshegs byin rlabs gsal bar rdzogs pa'i mthus //
NK027(sha)001:2491: rgyas ba'i sku ru lhun gyis grub nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:2492: thams cad byin rlabs mthu nyid lhun grub shog /
NK027(sha)001:2495: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2496: bdud rtsi sman mchog bsgrub cing mchod pa'i mthus //
NK027(sha)001:2497: yun du glag lta'i gnod pa kun bsal nas //
NK027(sha)001:2498: skye shi med pa lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2500: brgyad khri bzhi stong gdon rnams cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2501: tshogs dang gtor mas mchod pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2502: 'phral du skabs tshul gnod pa kun bsal nas /
NK027(sha)001:2503: 'pho 'gyur med pa lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2505: thun mong rdzas kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2506: mchod pa byin gyis rlobs pa'i nus mthu yi //
NK027(sha)001:2507: 'dod pa'i yon tan mngon du rdzogs gyur nas /
NK027(sha)001:2508: dus gsum bder gshegs ma lus mchod par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2510: bla mas rgyud lung zhi ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:2511: slob ma gcig gi rgyud lung khro bo bya /
NK027(sha)001:2512: zhi ba'i sems bskyed ting 'dzin gsum bya /
NK027(sha)001:2514: gnam sa so so'i ri brag cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2515: de bzhin nyid kyi ting 'dzin bsgom pa'i mthus //
NK027(sha)001:2516: chos nyid rtog pa nyid du rtogs pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:2517: spros pa med pa lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2519: ma rtogs sems can sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2520: kun tu snang ba'i ting 'dzin bsgom pa'i mthus //
NK027(sha)001:2521: chos nyid skye ba med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:2522: gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2524: ma rig sems kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2525: rgyu yi ting 'dzin rtse gcig bsgom pa'i mthus //
NK027(sha)001:2526: chos nyid byang chub sems kyi don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:2527: rang byung ye shes lhun na mo h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2528: snod kyi 'jig rten 'byung ba cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2529: gzhal yas khang chen bsgom pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2530: chos nyid mtha' dbus med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:2531: 'og min gnas su lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2533: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2534: rigs lnga yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2535: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:2536: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2538: dpa' bo'i yul du rnam shes cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2539: sems dpa' sems ma bsgom pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2540: thams cad lha dang lha mo'i don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:2541: rgyal ba'i sras su lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2543: yan lag bzhi'i dngos por cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2544: sgo ba yab yum bsgom pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2545: yab yum 'du 'bral med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:2546: phrin las rnam bzhi na mo h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2547: yid dang chos kyi dngos por cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2548: kun bzang yab yum bsgom pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2549: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:2550: chos sku 'gyur med lhun na mo h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2551: 'gro ba rigs drug dngos por cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2552: thub pa drug tu bsgom pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2553: rol pa cir yang snang ba'i don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:2554: sangs rgyas mdzad pa na mo h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2555: lus ngag yid gsum dngos po rig pa'i dbang bskur byin gyis rlobs pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:2556: las dang nyon mongs ma lus kun byang nas /
NK027(sha)001:2557: sku dang ye shes na mo h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2558: sangs rgyas sems can bde gshegs spyan drangs bstim pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2559: ye nas gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:2560: gnyis su med par na mo h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2561: bdag dang gzhan du ye nas 'dres pa chen po'i byin rlabs kyi //
NK027(sha)001:2562: gnyis su med par lhun na mo h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2563: 'gro drug sems can sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2564: dam bca' rnam gsum byas pa'i byin sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i mngon rdzogs sogs /
NK027(sha)001:2566: bsam pa mtha' ru phyin pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:2567: bdag gzhan bde bar gshegs pa khyed ci 'dra /
NK027(sha)001:2568: gnyis kyi don ni mthar phyin shog /
NK027(sha)001:2570: gzung 'dzin rnam rtog dngos po phyag rgya'i mchod pa phul ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2571: phyag rgya rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:2572: thams cad phyag rgya chen po lhun grub shog /
NK027(sha)001:2574: phyi nang gsang ba'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2575: kun tu bde bar gshegs pa bcom ldan 'das /
NK027(sha)001:2577: bzang po'i mchod pa phul ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:2578: dngos po thams cad mchod par gyur nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:2579: spyod yul thams cad yongs su dag par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2581: bdag gzhan dngos por khyad par cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2582: mchod pa rnams lnga phul ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:2583: thams cad 'gag pa med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:2584: 'khor gsum ma lus yongs su dag par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2586: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams dngos po cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2587: bdud rtsi sman mchod 'bul ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2588: 'phral du skabs tshul dngos po kun bsal nas //
NK027(sha)001:2589: skye shi med par lhun gyis na mo h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2590: stong phrag lang pur tos pa ka ma yam zhes sogs 'gres /
NK027(sha)001:2591: brgyad cu'i bgegs rnams dngos por cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2592: dam rdzas gtor mas mchod yun du glag lta gnod pa kun bsal nas //
NK027(sha)001:2593: 'pho 'gyur med par lhun na mo h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2594: sems kyi mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni /
NK027(sha)001:2595: rtog pa'i dngos por dngos po yo byad lnga ru grub nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:2596: rig pa cir yang snang ba lhun grub shog /
NK027(sha)001:2598: ri rab chen po'i gling bzhi sogs /
NK027(sha)001:2599: chags snang rnam gnyis dngos por cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2600: sta na g+ha na rnam gnyis mchod pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2601: spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:2602: bdag gzhan don gnyis lhun gyis grub na mo h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2603: yul dang dbang po'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2604: 'dod yon lnga yi mchod pa 'bul ba'i mthus //
NK027(sha)001:2605: yul sems gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs na //
NK027(sha)001:2606: spyod yul ma lus yongs su dag par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2608: dbang po'i spyod yul ces sogs /
NK027(sha)001:2609: nyon mongs sdug bsngal dngos por cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2610: glu dang rol mo'i sgra snyan 'bul ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:2611: thams cad theg pa chen po'i sgrar gyur nas //
NK027(sha)001:2612: gsang sngags don gnyis kun gyi rtogs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2615: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi /
NK027(sha)001:2616: bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa'
NK027(sha)001:2617: la sogs pa rigs lnga rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i 'khor
NK027(sha)001:2618: bsam gyi mi khyab pa dang bcas pa thams cad
NK027(sha)001:2620: bdag cag rnal 'byor gyi mchod pa dam pa rig
NK027(sha)001:2621: pa'i khyad par phyi nang gsang gsum sbyar te phul
NK027(sha)001:2622: bas / sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud mnyes pa chen por gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:2623: de'i byin gyis rlobs kyis mtha' yas pa'i sems can
NK027(sha)001:2624: thams cad rdo rje 'chang gi gral thob par gyur
NK027(sha)001:2625: cig / bdag gi nyams pa bskangs te dngos grub kyi snod dam par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:2626: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sar mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:2627: a la la hoh dam tshig gang 'dod zhu /
NK027(sha)001:2628: yid la bsam pa'i dngos grub cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2629: smon lam sngon du btab pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2630: gang la ci bsam lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2631: 'gro don rtsol ba'i sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2632: bsnyen bsgrub rnam bzhi'i 'dzab bsnyen byas pa'i mthus //
NK027(sha)001:2633: thams mdor na zhi ba'i las byang /
NK027(sha)001:2634: cad kun tu bzang mo'i don rtogs sngon 'gro zhi ba dang mthun /
NK027(sha)001:2636: dngos grub rnam gnyis lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2637: ces khams gsum lha'i dal du byas la b+ho d+hi tsit+ta'i 'dzab bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:2638: sems bskyed ting nge 'dzin rnam gsum mthun /
NK027(sha)001:2641: dur khrod rdzas kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2642: 'bar ba'i gzhal yas bsgom pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2643: rdzas su lta ba'i rtog pa kun bsal nas //
NK027(sha)001:2644: gnas mchog rab 'byams lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2646: 'dod pa'i yon tan tshogs kyis mchod par sbyar //
NK027(sha)001:2647: mtha' la zhen pa'i gdung ba kun bral nas //
NK027(sha)001:2648: bde ba chen po lhun gyis na mo h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2649: ru tra rnams gsum dngos por cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2650: he ru dgu ru bsgom pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2651: bdud dang srin po'i bar chad kun bral nas //
NK027(sha)001:2652: ye shes dgu ru lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2654: khams gsum sa dgu'i dngos po yum chen dgu ru sgom pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2655: ma bdun sring bzhi'i bar chad kun bral nas //
NK027(sha)001:2656: thig le dgu ru lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2657: bskal pa'i me dpung na bzhugs pa yan chad /
NK027(sha)001:2659: rnam shes brgyad kyi dngos po ko'u ri brgyad du sgom pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2660: h'u de dbab la dur khrod chas brgyad yul la mngon par rtog pa kun bcom nas //
NK027(sha)001:2661: rnam par rtog pa'i 'du shes med par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2663: dur khrod brgyad kyi dngos phra men brgyad du sgom pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2664: mtshan mar snang ba'i dngos po lha rnams dang po phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du sngags brjod /
NK027(sha)001:2665: sngags brjod pa gong rim bzhin gru chad bzhi /
NK027(sha)001:2667: rnam par dag pa'i bag chags med par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2670: bzhi po'i dngos po sgo ma bzhi ru sgom pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2671: tshad med bzhi ru rdzogs pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:2672: phrin las rnam bzhi 'du 'bral med par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2674: phyogs mtshams brgyad kyi dngos po ci spor ma brgyad
NK027(sha)001:2675: du sgom pa'i snang srid sde brgyad bar chad kun
NK027(sha)001:2676: bral nas // 'jig rten bar chad gang yang med par lha rnams gnyis /
NK027(sha)001:2679: 'byung ba bzhi'i dngos gsang ba'i yum bzhi sgom chos nyid snying rje med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:2680: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2683: sgal tshig rnams kyi dbang phyug nyer brgyad sgom rnam par dag pa'i bar chad kun bsal nas //
NK027(sha)001:2684: bar chad rkyen gyi sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2686: rus g+ho'i tshig gi dngos po ci snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2687: khro bo khro mo sgom pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2688: khams gsum gdug pa ma lus kun bsgral nas //
NK027(sha)001:2689: sangs rgyas phrin las lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2691: so dang rus pa'i dngos po mkha' 'gro so gnyis bsgom pa'i lha rnams bzhi par /
NK027(sha)001:2692: bar du gcod pa thams cad kun bsal nas //
NK027(sha)001:2693: bsgrub pa'i bar du gcod pa med par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2696: lhu tshig bac+wo brgyad dngos po ging chen bco brgyad bsgral ba'i zhing bcu ma lus kun bsgral nas //
NK027(sha)001:2697: sangs rgyas zhing khams ma lus dag par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2699: rtsa bran mang po'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2700: pho nya sum brgya drug cu bsgom pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:2701: dam tshig nyams dang dgra bgegs kun bsgral nas //
NK027(sha)001:2702: gnod pa'i bar chad ci yang med par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2704: sha khrag rtsa yi dngos po ma bdun sring bzhi tshe srog gnod pa'i bar chad kun bsal nas //
NK027(sha)001:2705: nyin mtshan rtag tu thams cad skyobs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2707: skra dang ba spu'i dngos po rig 'dzin khro tshogs yang sprul khros pa'i mthus //
NK027(sha)001:2708: skra rtse ba spu thig les khyab gyur te //
NK027(sha)001:2709: sprul pa 'phro zhing rtog pa gar skyes pa //
NK027(sha)001:2710: der yud rang byung dkyil 'khor thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2711: sku gsung thugs kyi byin gyis rlobs /
NK027(sha)001:2716: lus ngag yid gsum dngos po cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2717: bde gshegs lha la phyag 'tshal byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2718: ye nas 'dres pa chen po'i don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:2719: gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2721: srin mo'i cha lugs shin tu 'jigs par ston //
NK027(sha)001:2722: phyogs mtshams 'dzin pa'i spor ma brgyad rnams la //
NK027(sha)001:2723: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas dngos mchod 'bul //
NK027(sha)001:2724: dpal chen sku la 'du 'bral med pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:2725: ye shes thugs kyis dgyes sde rnam bzhi la //
NK027(sha)001:2726: rnam dag 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor chen po'i mthar bsrung ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:2727: dam can dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad la //
NK027(sha)001:2728: rnam dag khams gsum gdug pa ma lus 'dul mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:2729: khro bo khro mo rol ba'i tshogs rnams la //
NK027(sha)001:2730: rnam phrin las ma lus myur du 'grub byed pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:2731: rdo rje mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis la //
NK027(sha)001:2732: rnam dag zhing bcu ma lus gnas 'dren byed pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:2733: rdo rje 'da' kar ging chen bco brgyad la //
NK027(sha)001:2734: rnam dag ye shes rol ba'i phyag rgya cir snang ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:2735: mgyogs ma pho nya sum brgya drug cu la //
NK027(sha)001:2736: rnam dag phyi 'khor bsrung zhing nang 'khor skyong mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:2737: dam can rgya mtsho ma mo'i tshogs rnams la //
NK027(sha)001:2738: rnam dag rdo rje gral 'chang rim par gnon mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:2739: rnal 'byor dbang phyug rig 'dzin tshogs rnams la //
NK027(sha)001:2740: rnam dag thugs rjes brtse dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK027(sha)001:2741: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2742: bdud rtsi sman gyi mchod pa'i byin rlabs kyi //
NK027(sha)001:2743: 'phral du skabs tshol gnod pa kun bral nas //
NK027(sha)001:2744: skye shi med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2746: stong phrag brgyad cu'i bgegs rnams cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2747: dam rdzas gtor ma 'bul ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2748: yun du glag lta'i gnod pa kun zhi nas //
NK027(sha)001:2749: 'pho 'gyur med pa lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2750: bdag gi thugs ka nas h+r+aihls 'od zer 'phros /
NK027(sha)001:2751: zhes mchod pa yan chad brjod /
NK027(sha)001:2753: chags sdang rnam gsum dngos po cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2754: khams gsum khrag gi rgya mtsho phul ba'i mthus //
NK027(sha)001:2755: nyon mongs sems su gsal ba'i don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:2756: sems nyid dbye ba med pa'i don rtogs shog /
NK027(sha)001:2757: phyi snod b+han+d+ha zhes pa nas /
NK027(sha)001:2760: zhen cing chags pa'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2761: khams gsum khrag gi rgya mtshor phul ba'i mthus //
NK027(sha)001:2762: dug lnga ma lus rtsad nas dag gyur nas //
NK027(sha)001:2763: gnyis med mchod pa lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2765: phyogs bcu dus bzhi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK027(sha)001:2766: kyi bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das dpal che mchog he
NK027(sha)001:2768: he ru ka dgu klong 'bar ba'i 'khor khro bo
NK027(sha)001:2769: khro mo bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams cad gsan
NK027(sha)001:2770: cing bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK027(sha)001:2771: bdag cag rnal 'byor mchod pa dam pa rig pa'i
NK027(sha)001:2772: khyad par phyi nang gsang ba gsum du phul bas
NK027(sha)001:2773: / sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud mnyes pa chen po'i khyab par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:2774: de'i byin rlabs kyi mtha' yas sems can thams cad rdo rje 'chang gi gral thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:2775: bdag gi dam tshig nyams pa thams cad bskangs nas
NK027(sha)001:2776: dngos grub kyi snod du gyur te yi ge 'khor
NK027(sha)001:2777: lo tshogs chen gyis sar mngon par rdzogs par sangs
NK027(sha)001:2778: rgyas nas 'khor ba ka nas dag par gyur cig
NK027(sha)001:2780: dam tshig tu khams gsum lha'i dal du bsam 'dzab bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:2781: khro bo la lha mang nyung nges pa med /
NK027(sha)001:2783: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na b+ho d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su ka h'u h'u h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2786: rgyu 'bras rtsol ba'i sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2787: bsnyen bsgrub rnam bzhi 'dzab bsnyen byas pa'i mthus //
NK027(sha)001:2788: thams cad kun tu bzang mo'i don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:2789: dngos grub rnam gsum lhun gyis grub na mo h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2790: 'dod yon lnga yi dngos po cir tshogs kyi mchod pa byas pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2791: mtha' la zhen pa'i gdung ba kun bral nas //
NK027(sha)001:2792: bde ba chen po longs spyod rdzogs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2794: lo zur zla skeg gnod pa'i dngos po mkha' 'gro dbang zhi khro gnyis kyi lhag ma bya /
NK027(sha)001:2795: phyug lhag ma'i phud kyi mchod pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:2796: mo ngan rmi lam ngan pa kun bsal nas //
NK027(sha)001:2797: bar chad rkyen gyi sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2799: 'jig rten srin mo 'gro drug cir snang yang //
NK027(sha)001:2800: gtor ma dbril bkol med par bsngosa pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:2802: 'jig rten srin mo 'gro drug kun tshim nas //
NK027(sha)001:2803: zhing bcu sgrol zhing 'gro don rdzogs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2805: gzung 'dzin gnyis su dngos po cir lha dang gzhal yas khang du bsdus pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:2806: rtag chad gnyis su 'dzin pa'i mtha' bral nas //
NK027(sha)001:2807: snang srid chos kyi sku ru rtogs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2809: rnam zhi khro gnyis kyi rjes mchod byas /
NK027(sha)001:2811: dag chos kyi lus bsrung go bsgo bya /
NK027(sha)001:2812: spyod lam rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:2813: bdag nyid yi dam lha ru gyur nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:2814: 'gro don ma lus rdzogs par byed par shog /
NK027(sha)001:2816: de nas lhag ma bsdus te /
NK027(sha)001:2818: mar me btsug la dal nas gom pa bdun 'phags
NK027(sha)001:2819: pa'i sar phrin las rnam bzhi gang byed pa'i man+dala
NK027(sha)001:2820: bya / bla mas rtsa ba'i dal dang /
NK027(sha)001:2821: las mkhan sgo ma bzhi yan chad gsal gdab /
NK027(sha)001:2823: badz+ra sa man dzas lhag ma'i snyan gsan dbab /
NK027(sha)001:2824: sems dpa'i phyag rgya bcas la lha dang kha chus dam tshig la thims pa rnams /
NK027(sha)001:2825: sngon gyi thugs dam la ma 'da' bar bsgrub pa po bdag gi sdong grogs mdzod la gshegs shig /
NK027(sha)001:2826: e a ra li hring hring /
NK027(sha)001:2827: zhes thal mo lan gsum gdab /
NK027(sha)001:2828: d+aak+ki ni'i phyag rgyas spyan drangs /
NK027(sha)001:2829: dal phyi rol du khyung gshog gi phyag rgyas zil gyi nan /
NK027(sha)001:2830: rta gdong gi phyag rgyas dbang du bsdu /
NK027(sha)001:2835: dpal chen rak+sha he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:2836: ko'u ri'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:2837: byang chub sems dpa' brgyad rnams kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2838: ko'u ri khro mo brgyad du sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2839: srin mo chen mo brgyad rnams btul //
NK027(sha)001:2840: lhag ma byin rlabs dam la btag /
NK027(sha)001:2841: byang sems sa yi snying po yin //
NK027(sha)001:2842: khro mo chen mo ko'u rir sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2843: srin mo chen mo ging thod btul //
NK027(sha)001:2844: lhag ma byin rlabs dam la rdo rje'i dam la bro bskyal te //
NK027(sha)001:2845: gtan gyi bran du mchis kyi 'tshal //
NK027(sha)001:2846: sngon gyi khas blangs dam bcas bzhin //
NK027(sha)001:2847: rdo rje'i dam las ma 'da' bar //
NK027(sha)001:2848: las kyi lhag ma 'di long la //
NK027(sha)001:2849: khas blang dam bcas ci bzhin du //
NK027(sha)001:2850: bcol ba'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK027(sha)001:2851: phyi yi dkyil 'khor mtha' bsrungs shig /
NK027(sha)001:2852: byang sems nam mkha'i snying po yi //
NK027(sha)001:2853: khro mo chen mo tsi'u rig sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2854: srin mo chen mo mda' 'phen btul //
NK027(sha)001:2855: lhag ma byin rlabs dam la btags //
NK027(sha)001:2856: rdo rje'i dam la bro bskyal te //
NK027(sha)001:2857: gtan gyi bran du mchis kyi 'tshal //
NK027(sha)001:2858: sngon gyi khas blangs dam bca' bzhin //
NK027(sha)001:2859: rdo rje'i dam las ma 'da' bar //
NK027(sha)001:2860: las kyi lhag ma khas blang bcol ba'i phrin las
NK027(sha)001:2861: phyi yi dkyil 'khor byang sems spyan ras gzigs dbang
NK027(sha)001:2862: ni // khro mo chen mo sra mor sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2863: srin mo chen mo 'dzin byed sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2864: lhag ma rdo rje'i dam la gtan gyi sngon gyi
NK027(sha)001:2865: khas blang rdo rje'i dam las las kyi bcol ba'i
NK027(sha)001:2866: phyi yi byang sems phyag na rdo rje yi //
NK027(sha)001:2867: khro mo chen mo be ltar sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2868: srin mo chen mo za byed btul //
NK027(sha)001:2869: lhag ma rdo rje'i gtan gyi sngon gyi khas blang
NK027(sha)001:2870: rdo rje'i dam las las kyis khas blang bcol ba'i
NK027(sha)001:2871: phrin las phyi yi byang chub sems dpa' khro mo
NK027(sha)001:2873: srin mo nang grol dreg ma btul //
NK027(sha)001:2874: lhag ma rdo rje'i gtan gyi sngon gyi khas blang
NK027(sha)001:2875: rdo rje'i dam las las kyis lhag ma khas blang
NK027(sha)001:2876: dam bca' bcol ba'i phyi yi byang sems sgrib pa
NK027(sha)001:2877: rnam sel gyi // khro mo chen mo kas mar sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2878: srin mo chen mo rab 'dzin btul //
NK027(sha)001:2879: lhag ma rdo rje'i gtan gyi sngon gyi khas blang
NK027(sha)001:2880: rdo rje'i dam la las kyis lhag khas blangs dam
NK027(sha)001:2881: bcol ba'i phyi yi byang sems kun tu bzang mo
NK027(sha)001:2882: yi // khro mo chen mo rme shar sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2883: srin mo chen mo srog gcod btul //
NK027(sha)001:2884: lhag ma byin rlabs rdo rje'i dam la gtan gyi
NK027(sha)001:2885: sngon gyi khas rdo rje'i dam las ma 'da' bar
NK027(sha)001:2886: // las kyi lhag khas blang bcol ba'i phyi yi dkyil 'khor byang chub sems dpa' 'jam dpal gyi //
NK027(sha)001:2887: khro mo chen mo tsan d+har sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2888: srin mo chen mo bsnyen ma btul //
NK027(sha)001:2889: lhag ma rdo rje'i dam las gtan gyi sngon gyi khas blang /
NK027(sha)001:2890: rdo rje'i dam las ma las kyi lhag ma bcol ba'i phrin las phyi yi dkyil 'khor h'u /
NK027(sha)001:2891: dpal chen rak+sha he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:2892: phra men tshogs kyi bskor ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:2893: dpal chen he ru zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:2894: mchod pa'i lha mo brgyad rnams kyi //
NK027(sha)001:2895: sid+ha phra men brgyad du sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2896: srin mo chen mo brgyad rnams btul //
NK027(sha)001:2897: lhag ma byin rdo rje'i dam la gtan gyi bran
NK027(sha)001:2898: du sngon gyi khas blangs rdo rje'i dam las las
NK027(sha)001:2899: kyi lhag ma khas blang dam bcas bcol phyi yi
NK027(sha)001:2900: dkyil 'khor shar lho'i lha mo l+aa s+ye ma //
NK027(sha)001:2901: phra men chen mo seng ha sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2902: srin mo 'jigs byed seng mgo btul //
NK027(sha)001:2903: lhag ma byin rlabs rdo rje'i gtan gyi bran te
NK027(sha)001:2904: sngon gyi khas blang rdo rje'i dam las las kyi
NK027(sha)001:2905: lhag ma khas blang dam bcas bcol ba'i phrin las
NK027(sha)001:2906: grub phyi yi dkyil 'khor lho phyogs lha mo l+aa
NK027(sha)001:2907: s+ye mas // phra men chen mo stag mgor sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2908: srin mo bya byed stag mgo btul //
NK027(sha)001:2909: lhag ma byin rlabs rdo rje'i dam la gtan gyi bran du mchis kyi 'tshal //
NK027(sha)001:2911: nub phyogs lha mo g+hirti mas //
NK027(sha)001:2912: phra men chen mo wa mgor sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2913: srin mo legs byed wa mgo btul //
NK027(sha)001:2915: byang phyogs lha mo nirti mas //
NK027(sha)001:2916: khro mo chen mo ra mgor sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2917: srin mo ra ro khyi mgo btul //
NK027(sha)001:2918: lhag ma byin rlabs rdo rje'i dam la gtan gyi
NK027(sha)001:2919: bran du sngon gyi khas blang rdo rje'i dam la
NK027(sha)001:2920: las kyi lhag ma khas blang dam bcol ba'i phyi
NK027(sha)001:2921: yi dkyil 'khor shar lho lha mo d+hush+pe mas //
NK027(sha)001:2922: phra men chen mo rgod mgor sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2923: srin mo bya rgod mgo can btul //
NK027(sha)001:2924: lhag ma lho nub lha mo me tog mas //
NK027(sha)001:2925: phra me na kang ka'i mgo ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2926: srin mo kang ka'i mgo can btul //
NK027(sha)001:2927: lhag ma nub byang lha mo mar me mas //
NK027(sha)001:2928: phra men bya rog mgo ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2929: srin mo 'jigs byed bya rog btul //
NK027(sha)001:2930: lhag ma byang shar lha mo dri chab mas //
NK027(sha)001:2931: phra men hu lu mu khar sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2932: srin mo bskul byed 'ug mgo btul //
NK027(sha)001:2934: dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK027(sha)001:2935: sgo ma'i tshogs kyi bskor ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:2936: tshad med sgo ma bzhi rnams kyis //
NK027(sha)001:2937: rta gdong sgo ma bzhi ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2938: shar gyi byams pa lcags kyu mas //
NK027(sha)001:2939: sgo ma rta gdong lcags kyu mas //
NK027(sha)001:2940: srin mo rta yi mgo can btul //
NK027(sha)001:2941: lhag ma lho yi snying rje zhags pa ma //
NK027(sha)001:2942: sgo ma phag gdong zhags pa sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2943: srin mo phag gi mgo can btul //
NK027(sha)001:2944: lhag ma byin nub kyi dga' ba lcags sgrog mas //
NK027(sha)001:2945: sgo ma dred mgo lcags sgrogs sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2946: srin mo dred kyi mgo can lhag ma byin rlabs
NK027(sha)001:2947: rdo rje'i dam la bro gtan gyi bran te sngon
NK027(sha)001:2948: gyi khas blangs rdo rje dam la las kyi lhag
NK027(sha)001:2949: ma khas blangs dam bcas bcol ba'i phyi yi dkyil
NK027(sha)001:2950: 'khor byang gi btang snyoms dril bu mas //
NK027(sha)001:2951: sgo ma chen mo spyang mgor sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2952: srin mo chen mo spyang mgor btul //
NK027(sha)001:2955: dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK027(sha)001:2956: spor ma'i tshogs kyi bskor nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:2957: dpal chen thugs kyis sbyor ba las //
NK027(sha)001:2958: thub drug yid ches brgyad po yi //
NK027(sha)001:2959: spor ma chen mo brgyad du sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2960: phyogs skyong brgyad kyi bu mo btul //
NK027(sha)001:2962: kun tu bzang mo gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:2963: 'bar ma nyi zer zhags par sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2964: spor ma nyi zer zhags pa btul //
NK027(sha)001:2966: yi dwags thub pa gnas gyur ba //
NK027(sha)001:2968: spor ma chen mo glog phreng btul //
NK027(sha)001:2970: mi yi thub pa gnas gyur ba //
NK027(sha)001:2971: spor ma mdung thung 'phen du sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2972: spor ma gtum mo gdung thung btul //
NK027(sha)001:2974: dmyal ba'i thub pa gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:2975: spor ma gshin rje ral grir sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2976: spor ma chen mo ral gri btul //
NK027(sha)001:2978: kun tu bzang mo gnas gyur ba //
NK027(sha)001:2979: spor ma dril 'khrol ma ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2980: spor ma rdo rje dril 'khrol btul //
NK027(sha)001:2982: lha min thub pa gnas gyur ba //
NK027(sha)001:2983: spor ma skar mda' gdeng du sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2984: spor ma thog 'beb skur mda' btul /
NK027(sha)001:2985: lhag ma byin rlabs rdo rje'i dam la gtan gyi
NK027(sha)001:2986: bran te sngon gyi khas blang las kyi lhag ma
NK027(sha)001:2987: khas blangs dam bcol ba'i phyi yi byol song thub
NK027(sha)001:2989: spor ma glog sha 'debs su sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2990: spor ma ban glang sna tshogs btul //
NK027(sha)001:2992: lha yi thub pa gnas gyur ba //
NK027(sha)001:2993: spor ma khyung thog ma ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:2994: spor ma gnod sbyin khyung thog btul //
NK027(sha)001:2997: dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK027(sha)001:2998: gsang ba'i yum bzhi bskor ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:2999: dpal chen thugs kyis sbyor ba las //
NK027(sha)001:3000: yi ge h'u bzhis sprul byas nas //
NK027(sha)001:3001: de las gsang ba'i yum bzhir sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3002: de bzhin srin mo bzhi btul te //
NK027(sha)001:3003: shar gyi bde ba za byed mas //
NK027(sha)001:3004: srin mo bya byed khrag 'thung btul /
NK027(sha)001:3006: lho'i bde ba rmong byed mas //
NK027(sha)001:3007: srin mo chen mo rus 'chang btul /
NK027(sha)001:3009: nub kyi bde ba rgyas 'debs mas //
NK027(sha)001:3010: srin mo dur khrod ro kun btul //
NK027(sha)001:3012: byang gi bde ba tshe 'phel mas //
NK027(sha)001:3013: srin mo dur khrod bdag mo btul /
NK027(sha)001:3016: dpal chen dbang phyug tshogs kyi bskor ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:3017: dpal chen thugs kyis sbyor ba las //
NK027(sha)001:3018: tshangs ma la sogs ye shes kyi //
NK027(sha)001:3019: dbang mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi //
NK027(sha)001:3020: las kyi dbang mo mgo brnyan tshogs //
NK027(sha)001:3021: 'jig rten rnams kyis sring mo ste //
NK027(sha)001:3022: lag na glo snying nang rol thogs //
NK027(sha)001:3023: nyi shu rtsa brgyad tshogs su sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3024: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad la //
NK027(sha)001:3025: 'gal byed gnod pa'i tshogs rnams btul //
NK027(sha)001:3026: lhag ma byin rlabs dam la btags //
NK027(sha)001:3027: rdo rje'i dam las gtan gyi bran du sngon gyi
NK027(sha)001:3028: khas blang las kyi lhag ma khas blangs dam bcas
NK027(sha)001:3029: bcol ba'i phyi'ii dkyil 'khor mtha' srung cig /
NK027(sha)001:3031: dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK027(sha)001:3032: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs kyis dpal chen sku yi 'od zer las //
NK027(sha)001:3033: sems dpa' sum cu rtsa gnyis kyi //
NK027(sha)001:3034: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3035: srin mo sum cu rtsa gnyis btul //
NK027(sha)001:3037: sems dpa' rdo rje sems dpa' yi //
NK027(sha)001:3038: mkha' 'gro dga' byed ma ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3039: srin mo chen mo dga' byed btul //
NK027(sha)001:3041: rdo rje sems dpa' rdo rje rgyal po yi //
NK027(sha)001:3043: srin mo chen mo spor ma btul //
NK027(sha)001:3045: sems dpa' rdo rje legs pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:3046: mkha' 'gro gsod byed ma ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3047: srin mo chen mo gsod byed btul //
NK027(sha)001:3049: sems dpa' rdo rje rin chen gyi //
NK027(sha)001:3051: srin mo chen mo 'bar ma btul //
NK027(sha)001:3053: sems dpa' rdo rje nyi ma yi //
NK027(sha)001:3054: mkha' 'gro gzi brjid ma ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3055: srin mo chen mo gzi brjid btul //
NK027(sha)001:3057: sems dpa' rdo rje rgyal mtshan gyi //
NK027(sha)001:3058: mkha' 'gro bdud rtsi rgyal byed sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3059: srin mo rgyal byed dbang ldan btul //
NK027(sha)001:3061: sems dpa' rdo rje bzhed pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:3063: srin mo chen mo 'joms byed btul //
NK027(sha)001:3064: lhag ma byin rlabs rdo rje'i dam la gtan gyi
NK027(sha)001:3065: sngon gyi las kyis khas blangs dam bcas ji bcol
NK027(sha)001:3066: ba'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor sems dpa' rdo rje chos rab
NK027(sha)001:3067: kyi // mkha' 'gro chags byed ma ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3068: srin mo chen mo chag ma btul //
NK027(sha)001:3069: lhag ma sems dpa' rdo rje rnon po yi //
NK027(sha)001:3070: mkha' 'gro chags bral ma ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3071: srin mo chen mo chags bral btul //
NK027(sha)001:3072: lhag ma sems dpa' rdo rje 'khor lo yi //
NK027(sha)001:3074: srin mo chen mo 'khor lo btul //
NK027(sha)001:3076: sems dpa' rdo rje smra ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:3078: srin mo chen mo rgyas ma btul //
NK027(sha)001:3080: sems dpa' rdo rje sna tshogs kyi //
NK027(sha)001:3081: mkha' 'gro sna tshogs gzugs su sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3082: srin mo chen mo sna tshogs btul //
NK027(sha)001:3084: sems dpa' rdo rje go cha yi //
NK027(sha)001:3085: mkha' 'gro chen mo srin mor sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3086: srin mo chen mo ma srin btul //
NK027(sha)001:3088: sems dpa' rdo rje mche ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:3089: mkha' 'gro gnod sbyin ma ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3090: srin mo chen mo gnod sbyin btul /
NK027(sha)001:3092: sems dpa' rdo rje khu tshur gyi //
NK027(sha)001:3094: srin mo chen mo phrog ma btul //
NK027(sha)001:3097: mkha' 'gro bya rog gdong du sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3098: srin mo chen mo mig 'byed btul //
NK027(sha)001:3100: sems dpa' kun tu bzang mo yi //
NK027(sha)001:3102: srin mo chen mo 'jigs byed btul //
NK027(sha)001:3103: lhag ma byin rlabs rdo rje'i dam la gtan gyi bran du mchis kyi 'tshal //
NK027(sha)001:3104: sngon gyi khas blang las kyi lhag ma khas blangs
NK027(sha)001:3105: dam bcas bcol ba'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' bsrung zhing
NK027(sha)001:3106: // sems dpa' zla 'od gzhon nu yi //
NK027(sha)001:3108: srin mo chen mo mon thang btul //
NK027(sha)001:3110: byang chub sems dpa' bzang skyong gi //
NK027(sha)001:3111: mkha' 'gro bzang skyong ma ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3112: srin mo bzhad kyi mgo can lhag ma sogs /
NK027(sha)001:3113: sems dpa' tra ba'i 'od can gyis //
NK027(sha)001:3114: mkha' 'gro khyi mgo ma ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3115: srin mo khyi'i mgo can btul //
NK027(sha)001:3117: sems dpa' rdo rje snying po yi //
NK027(sha)001:3118: mkha' 'gro phag gdong ma ru sprul /
NK027(sha)001:3119: srin mo phag gi mgo can btul //
NK027(sha)001:3121: sems dpa' nam mkha'i mdzod kyi ni //
NK027(sha)001:3122: mkha' 'gro rnga mong mgo ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3123: srin mo rnga mong mgo can btul //
NK027(sha)001:3125: sems dpa' 'od dpag med kyi ni //
NK027(sha)001:3126: mkha' 'gro bong bu'i mgo can sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3127: srin mo bong bu'i mgo can btul //
NK027(sha)001:3129: sems dpa' ngan song kun 'byung gi //
NK027(sha)001:3130: mkha' 'gro ra mgo ma ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3131: srin mo ra'i mgo can btul //
NK027(sha)001:3133: sems dpa' rgyal ba'i ye shes kyi //
NK027(sha)001:3134: mkha' 'gro byi ba'i mgo ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3135: srin mo byi ba'i mgo can btul //
NK027(sha)001:3137: sems dpa' blo gros mi bzad pas //
NK027(sha)001:3138: mkha' 'gro keng rus ma ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3139: srin mo keng rus 'dzin ma btul //
NK027(sha)001:3140: lhag ma byin rlabs rdo rje'i dam la bro bskyal te //
NK027(sha)001:3141: gtan gyi bran du mchis kyi 'tshal //
NK027(sha)001:3142: sngon gyi khas blangs dam las kyi lhag ma 'di long la //
NK027(sha)001:3143: khas blang dam bca' ci bzhin du //
NK027(sha)001:3144: bcol ba'i phyi'i dkyil sems ma spobs pa brtsegs pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:3145: mkha' 'gro rus phreng can du sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3146: srin mo rus pa'i phreng can btul //
NK027(sha)001:3148: byang chub sems dpa' byams pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:3150: srin mo pur+na'i chung ma btul //
NK027(sha)001:3152: sems dpa' ngan song kun 'dren gyi //
NK027(sha)001:3154: gshin rje rnam 'joms chung ma btul //
NK027(sha)001:3156: sems dpa' spos kyi glang po yi //
NK027(sha)001:3157: mkha' 'gro d+ha sha g+h+ram bar sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3158: d+ha sha g+h+ri ba'i chung ma btul //
NK027(sha)001:3160: byang sems don yod grub pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:3162: gnod sbyin 'bod srog chung ma btul //
NK027(sha)001:3165: dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK027(sha)001:3166: pho nya'i tshogs kyi bskor ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:3167: 'od zer sum brgya drug cu las //
NK027(sha)001:3168: pho nya sum brgya drug cu sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3169: shar du 'od zer dkar po las //
NK027(sha)001:3170: dung gi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3171: dri za'i gdon tshogs drug cur btul //
NK027(sha)001:3172: lhag ma lho ru 'od zer sngon po la //
NK027(sha)001:3173: lcag gi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3174: gshin rje'i gdon tshogs drug cur btul /
NK027(sha)001:3175: lhag ma byin rlabs rdo rje'i gtan gyi bran du mchis kyi 'tshal //
NK027(sha)001:3176: sngon gyi khas blang las kyi lhag ma khas blang
NK027(sha)001:3177: dam bcas bcol ba'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig
NK027(sha)001:3179: nub tu 'od zer dmar po las //
NK027(sha)001:3180: zang gi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3181: klu yi gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK027(sha)001:3183: byang tu 'od zer ljang ku las //
NK027(sha)001:3184: g.yu yi mi mo drug cu sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3185: gnod sbyin gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK027(sha)001:3187: steng du 'od zer sngon po las //
NK027(sha)001:3188: gser gyi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3189: ya bdud gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK027(sha)001:3192: bse'i mi mo drug cu sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3193: ma mo'i gdon tshogs drug lhag ma sogs h'u /
NK027(sha)001:3194: dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK027(sha)001:3195: ging chen tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:3196: dpal chen he ru ka bzhad pas //
NK027(sha)001:3197: rdo rje ging chen bco brgyad sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3198: gdon gyi rgyal po bco brgyad btul //
NK027(sha)001:3201: dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK027(sha)001:3202: ma bdun tshogs kyi bskor ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:3203: dpal chen thugs kyis sbyor ba las //
NK027(sha)001:3204: yi ge h'u bdun spros pa las //
NK027(sha)001:3205: gsang ba'i ma mo bdun du sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3206: srin mo chen mo bdun po btul //
NK027(sha)001:3209: dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK027(sha)001:3210: sring mo bzhi yi bskor ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:3211: gling bzhi dbang bsgyur chen mo yi //
NK027(sha)001:3212: sring mo chen mo bzhi ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3213: bgegs kyi rgyal po bzhi po btul //
NK027(sha)001:3214: lhag ma byin rlabs dam la btags //
NK027(sha)001:3215: rdo rje'i dam la bro bskyal te //
NK027(sha)001:3216: gtan gyi bran du mchis kyi 'tshal //
NK027(sha)001:3217: sngon gyi khas blang las kyis lhag ma khas blang dam bcas ci bzhin du //
NK027(sha)001:3218: bcol ba'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig /
NK027(sha)001:3220: bcom ldan rdo rje mi bskyod pas //
NK027(sha)001:3221: dpal chen badz+ra he ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3222: dbus kyi yi dwags dreg pa btul //
NK027(sha)001:3224: bcom ldan rnam par snang mdzad kyi //
NK027(sha)001:3225: dpal chen b+hud+d+ha he ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3226: shar gyi dri za srin mo btul //
NK027(sha)001:3228: bcom ldan rin chen 'byung ldan gyi //
NK027(sha)001:3229: dpal chen rat+na he ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3230: lho'i gshin rje srin po btul //
NK027(sha)001:3232: bcom ldan snang ba mtha' yas kyi //
NK027(sha)001:3233: dpal chen pad+ma he ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3234: nub kyi klu'i gdon lhag ma sogs /
NK027(sha)001:3235: bcom ldan don yod grub pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:3236: dpal chen karma he ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3237: byang gi gnod sbyin srin po btul //
NK027(sha)001:3239: rigs kyis yum chen lnga rnams kyi //
NK027(sha)001:3240: khro mo chen mo lnga ru sprul //
NK027(sha)001:3241: srin mo chen mo lnga rnams btul //
NK027(sha)001:3242: lhag ma byin rlabs dam la btags //
NK027(sha)001:3243: sngon gyi dam la ma g.yel bar //
NK027(sha)001:3244: bka' yi gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK027(sha)001:3245: thugs dam chen po ci bzhin du //
NK027(sha)001:3246: rnal 'byor bcol ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NK027(sha)001:3250: ye nas mnyam nyid kyi bshags /
NK027(sha)001:3253: mchod pa byin gyis rlobs so //
NK027(sha)001:3254: de nas bum pa bskyed pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:3255: shu nye ta dz+ny+aa na d+harma d+hartu swa b+h+aa wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK027(sha)001:3261: bam a mri ta man+dala la /
NK027(sha)001:3263: su pa pa ta man+dala lam rat+na b+ha wa man+dala /
NK027(sha)001:3267: b+h+r+aum bi shud+d+he a kar shud+d+he du ti rat+na sur+ya tsan tra pad+ma man+dala h'u tram h+r+aih+aah spro bsdu /
NK027(sha)001:3272: mum d+ha du shwa ri nas /
NK027(sha)001:3274: b+ho d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha dz+ny+aa na d+hartu +aah h'u swa am ha /
NK027(sha)001:3275: ma h+aa shu nya ta dz+ny+aa na ta na a
NK027(sha)001:3276: da ri sha sa man ta pra we sha kri
NK027(sha)001:3277: sta a nu sta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha wa
NK027(sha)001:3280: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ka ya waka tsit+ta a nu ra ga /
NK027(sha)001:3281: puts+tsha badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK027(sha)001:3284: kha rgyan mgul ching gzungs thag can du dbang bskur /
NK027(sha)001:3289: a ti pu hoh pra ti dza hos phyag bya /
NK027(sha)001:3291: sman mchod sngags kyi sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:3292: b+ha lid+tasa gtor ma lhag pa ting 'dzin dang /
NK027(sha)001:3294: ye shes dang rgyal ba rgya mtsho lnga'i smon lam btab la /
NK027(sha)001:3296: de nas chu bdun tshan gnyis pa brtag pa gsum gyis byin brlab byas la /
NK027(sha)001:3298: de nas rgyal theb kyi rtsa ba las kyi zhi khro'i gzhung bsrang /
NK027(sha)001:3301: rang bzhin gyi dal spyan drangs /
NK027(sha)001:3302: 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab pa yan chad bya /
NK027(sha)001:3306: gnyis pa ting 'dzin gyi dal bskyed pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:3307: rang rdo rje gzhon nur bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:3308: ma sur+ya man+dala zhes pas phyogs bcur nyi ma'i /
NK027(sha)001:3309: sum b+ha ni lha bcu phyogs bcu'i gdan la khro bo bcu bsgom /
NK027(sha)001:3312: dbang mchog bsgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK027(sha)001:3313: nga ni dkyil 'khor las byed kyi //
NK027(sha)001:3314: phyogs skyong bcu po'i mnan pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:3315: 'khor gyi gdon tshogs ma lus kun //
NK027(sha)001:3316: dus gsum sangs rgyas bka' byung gi //
NK027(sha)001:3318: badz+ra kro ta sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK027(sha)001:3320: rang badz+ra he ru kar bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:3321: badz+ra kro ta h'u ka ra h'u gardza gardza h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:3323: phur pa phyogs bcur gdab bo //
NK027(sha)001:3324: de nas gsang ba'i dri sbyangs bdag nyid kun bzang
NK027(sha)001:3325: yab yum sbyor ba'i mkha' nas rdo rje sems dpa'
NK027(sha)001:3327: rdo rje sems dpa' thugs ka'i h'u la ramyam kham
NK027(sha)001:3328: gi dkyil 'khor gyi dngos mtshan sbyangs la smon lam
NK027(sha)001:3330: mi gnas pa'i ye shes chen po'i bdag nyid phyag
NK027(sha)001:3331: rgya'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams cad bdag la
NK027(sha)001:3333: da lta yang bdag cag gi mtha' yas pa'i sems
NK027(sha)001:3334: can thams cad 'khor ba las bsgral ba'i lha tshogs
NK027(sha)001:3335: rnams la rab tu gnas pa'i phrin las bgyi bar
NK027(sha)001:3336: 'tshal bas / de bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi /
NK027(sha)001:3337: bdag la mthu bstan du gsol /
NK027(sha)001:3340: rab gnas ye shes kyi snang ba thob par mdzad du gsol /
NK027(sha)001:3341: ces pas phreng ba dal du dor /
NK027(sha)001:3342: rat+na ma le a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)001:3343: dam tshig gi phyag rgyas blang ste ma gor bcing /
NK027(sha)001:3344: thal mo khog stong du bsgyur /
NK027(sha)001:3345: shudz+ny+aa na bdun brjod pas gzugs brnyan gyi dal chos
NK027(sha)001:3346: nyid rnam par dag pa'i klong stong pa nyid kyi
NK027(sha)001:3347: sems su bsgoms / yang rdor sems kyi thugs ka
NK027(sha)001:3348: nas 'byung ba rim brtsegs la b+h+r+aum smug nag las
NK027(sha)001:3350: yang thugs ka nas h'u bco brgyad phyung la he ru ka dgu /
NK027(sha)001:3351: ha brgyad las ko'u ri brgyad /
NK027(sha)001:3352: he brgyad las seng ha brgyad /
NK027(sha)001:3353: phata bzhi la sgo ma bzhi /
NK027(sha)001:3354: ma brgyad las spor ma brgyad /
NK027(sha)001:3357: b+h+yo nyer brgyad las dbang phyug ma ste khrag 'thung rtsa ba'i dal bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:3358: e so gnyis las phrin las myur mgyog gi dal bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:3359: h'u drug cu las khro bo rol pa'i /
NK027(sha)001:3361: las myur mgyog 'gro yid kyi dal bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:3362: ma drug cu las dam tshig rgya mtsho'i dal /
NK027(sha)001:3363: dza brgyad las sgrol ging gi dkyil 'khor /
