NK027(sha)001:3364: b+h+yo bcu gcig las ma bdun sring bzhi dam tshig gi dal bskyed do //
NK027(sha)001:3365: de'i steng du yang rdor sems kyi thugs ka nas zhi ba'i dal bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:3366: zhi khro gnyis ka dus gcig tu dbang bskur la //
NK027(sha)001:3367: rin chen bum pas dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:3368: dbang chen rdo rje'i sku bsgom ste //
NK027(sha)001:3369: ye shes lnga yi rang bzhin gyi //
NK027(sha)001:3370: dbang bskur chos dbyings gsal bar shog /
NK027(sha)001:3371: ma h+aa shu dz+ny+aa na a d+ha ri sha /
NK027(sha)001:3372: sa man+ta pra ta pra we sha ya tri ta /
NK027(sha)001:3373: a nu ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&aham /
NK027(sha)001:3375: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK027(sha)001:3376: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las zhing khams
NK027(sha)001:3377: dag pa mi bzad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bka'
NK027(sha)001:3378: bden pa dang / bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs kyi /
NK027(sha)001:3379: 'dus pa chen po'i lha rnams la ye shes lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:3380: rnam par shes pa brgyad ye shes lnga lhun gyis grub nas /
NK027(sha)001:3381: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen po rnams dang /
NK027(sha)001:3382: yon tan gyi bdag po rang srid pa gsum gyi sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3383: ces pa yan chad ting nge 'dzin gyi dal bskyed pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:3384: de nas gsum pa ye shes kyi dal spyan drangs pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:3385: spos chen gyi dud pa btang /
NK027(sha)001:3387: chos kun rig pa rang snang ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:3388: rdo rje dbyings kyi lha tshogs dang //
NK027(sha)001:3389: khams gsum ma lus bdal ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:3391: rdo rje 'chang gral rim bgrod pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:3393: smon lam dam tshig lung bzhin du //
NK027(sha)001:3394: gnas 'dir ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:3397: sprin dpung bzhin du gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:3398: chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang nas //
NK027(sha)001:3399: gzhal yas chen po'i gnas mchog nas //
NK027(sha)001:3400: rgyal ba 'khor bcas ma lus kun //
NK027(sha)001:3401: thugs rjes dbang gi gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:3402: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten thams cad na //
NK027(sha)001:3403: rgyal ba gang bzhugs 'khor dang bcas //
NK027(sha)001:3404: rdo rje dam can ci snyed pa //
NK027(sha)001:3405: thams cad kun nas dgongs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:3406: rgyal ba'i thugs dam bskang ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:3407: 'khor ba yongs su sbyor ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:3409: thugs dam dbang gi gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:3410: badz+ra sa ma ya h'u dzah zhes snyan gsan dbab /
NK027(sha)001:3411: thugs rje'i lcags kyus thugs rjes rgyud bskul zhing /
NK027(sha)001:3412: byams pa'i zhags pas gnas nas spyan yang 'dren /
NK027(sha)001:3413: lcags sgrog bka' yi pho nya'i gnas bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:3414: bder gshegs bzhugs shing rnam grol dgyes pa bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:3418: ka ya wa gi bar bzhugs su gsol nas /
NK027(sha)001:3420: zhes pas rdo rje sems dpa' rang la bstim pas
NK027(sha)001:3421: dal mnga' gsol ba'i gzi brjid dang ldan par bsam
NK027(sha)001:3422: mo // de nas me long 'bul ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:3424: me long dag la gzugs brnyan snang ba ltar //
NK027(sha)001:3425: chos rnams rang bzhin gdod nas dag pa la //
NK027(sha)001:3426: che ba'i yon tan mang po 'byung gyur zhing //
NK027(sha)001:3427: rnam par byang ba'i chos nyid gsal bar shog /
NK027(sha)001:3428: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la me long phul bas /
NK027(sha)001:3429: kun gzhi'i bag chags kyi g.ya' dang bral nas chos
NK027(sha)001:3430: sku brjod du med pa'i don mtha' yas pa'i sems
NK027(sha)001:3431: can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3432: ces brjod la gong bzhin du khrus bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:3433: de nas dbang po'i skyon bsal ba'i chos bdun bya ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:3434: gser gyi thur ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:3436: khyad par rgyu las byung ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:3437: rin po che yi thur ma yi //
NK027(sha)001:3438: spyan gyi dbang po'i skyon bsal nas //
NK027(sha)001:3439: spyan lnga yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3440: bde bar gshegs pa sku la gser gyi thur mas spyan mas spyan phyes pas /
NK027(sha)001:3441: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi spyan dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3444: rin po che yi thur ma yi //
NK027(sha)001:3445: dbang po snyan gyi skyon bsal bas //
NK027(sha)001:3446: snyan lnga yongs su rdzogs thob ste //
NK027(sha)001:3447: ma 'gags snyan pa thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3448: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la rin po che'i snyan bsal bas /
NK027(sha)001:3449: sangs rgyas kyi snyan yongs su gsan pa ma 'gag
NK027(sha)001:3450: pa bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad
NK027(sha)001:3453: rin po chen po'i rmong gzer gyi //
NK027(sha)001:3454: shang gi dbang po'i skyon bsal bas //
NK027(sha)001:3455: sems kyi rnam grangs shes par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3456: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la rin po che rmong gzer gyi zhal shang gi spu btog pas /
NK027(sha)001:3457: gzhan sems kyi rnam grangs shes pa'i don bdag dang
NK027(sha)001:3458: mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par
NK027(sha)001:3459: gyur cig / ljag bzhar thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:3460: rin po che yi ljag bzhar gyi //
NK027(sha)001:3461: ljags kyi dbang po'i skyon bsal bas //
NK027(sha)001:3462: gsung rab ma lus 'chad par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3463: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la rin po che'i ljag bzhar gyi dri ma bsal bas /
NK027(sha)001:3464: gsung rab ma lus pa 'chad pa'i don bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sogs /
NK027(sha)001:3466: rin po che yi tshems shing gi //
NK027(sha)001:3467: tshems kyi dri ma rab gsal bas //
NK027(sha)001:3468: mnyam par bzhag pa thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3469: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku rin po che'i tshems shing gi dri ma bsal bas /
NK027(sha)001:3470: bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3472: rin chen dung gi so mang gi //
NK027(sha)001:3473: dbu skra dri ma'i skyon bsal bas //
NK027(sha)001:3474: tshogs brgyad ma 'dres mkhyen par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3475: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la dung gi so mang
NK027(sha)001:3476: gi dbu skra bshad pas dug gsum rtsad nas bcad
NK027(sha)001:3477: de / nyon mongs pa'i zung ngu dang bral ba bdag dang mtha' yas sogs /
NK027(sha)001:3479: khyad par rgyu las byung ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:3480: rin po che yi spu gri yi //
NK027(sha)001:3481: dbu skra'i skyon rnams bsal byed pas //
NK027(sha)001:3482: nyon mongs rtsad nas gcod par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3483: spu gris sprul sku dbu skra bzhar bas /
NK027(sha)001:3484: dug gsum rtsad nas gcod de /
NK027(sha)001:3485: nyon mongs pa'i zug rngu dang bral te /
NK027(sha)001:3486: bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3487: don lnga pa dngos po skyon sbyang gi chos la /
NK027(sha)001:3491: rgyal ba'i sku la nyon mongs mi mnga' yang //
NK027(sha)001:3492: sems can nyon mongs bag chags sbyang slad du //
NK027(sha)001:3493: rgyal ba'i sku la chu gtsang khrus gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3494: las dang nyon mongs bag chags dag par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3495: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la chu gtsang gi sku khrus gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3496: bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi /
NK027(sha)001:3497: las dang nyon mongs pa'i dri ma dag par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3498: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ka ya b+hi shwo d+ha ni ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:3501: rgyal ba'i sku la rab rib mi mnga' yang //
NK027(sha)001:3502: sems can ma rig mun pa bsal slad du //
NK027(sha)001:3503: rgyal ba'i sku la sprul chab khrus gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3504: rmong pa'i rab rib ma lus dag par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3505: bde bar gshegs pa la sprul chab khrus gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3506: bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad shes bya'i dri ma dag par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3507: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ka ya sogs /
NK027(sha)001:3510: rgyal ba'i sku la dri ma mi mnga' yang //
NK027(sha)001:3511: sems can sdug bsngal ma lus bsal slad du //
NK027(sha)001:3512: rgyal ba'i sku la 'dag chal khrus gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3513: tshul khrims rnam dag byang chub sku thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:3514: bde gshegs sku la 'dag chab kyi khrus gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3515: tshul khrims kyi phung po mngon par byang chub pa'i
NK027(sha)001:3516: sku bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad
NK027(sha)001:3517: kyi las dang nyon mongs pa'i dri ma dag par
NK027(sha)001:3518: gyur cig / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ka ya b+hi sho d+ha ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:3522: rgyal ba'i sku la bsnyel ba mi mnga' yang //
NK027(sha)001:3523: sems can mu ge'i sdug bsngal bsal ba'i slad du rgyal ba'i sku la 'bru chab khrus gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3524: ting 'dzin phung po chos sku thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3525: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la 'bru chab kyi khrus gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3526: ting nge 'dzin gyi phung po dang /
NK027(sha)001:3532: phrin las lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas sku gzugs la //
NK027(sha)001:3533: spos chen dri yi sku khrus 'di gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3534: dri mchog stong gsum kun du 'byung ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:3535: shes rab phung po sprul sku thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3536: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la spos chab kyi khrus gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3537: shes rab kyi phung po sprul pa'i sku bdag dang sarba ta th+aa sman lnga'i chu /
NK027(sha)001:3539: rdo rje'i sku mchog nam mkha'i rang bzhin la //
NK027(sha)001:3540: dri med sman chab sku khrus 'di gsol gyi //
NK027(sha)001:3541: nyon mongs sdug bsngal nad 'joms rgyal po 'di //
NK027(sha)001:3542: rnam grol phung po'i rdo rje'i sku thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:3543: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la /
NK027(sha)001:3545: bram ze'i sku rnam par grol ba'i phung po dang /
NK027(sha)001:3546: rdo rje'i sku bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i 'gres so //
NK027(sha)001:3547: sarba ta th+aa rin po che'i chab la /
NK027(sha)001:3549: chos rnams yongs su rdzogs pa'i sku mchog la //
NK027(sha)001:3550: rin chen chab kyi sku khrus 'di gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3551: yid bzhin nor ltar ma lus re bskang bas //
NK027(sha)001:3552: ye shes phung po longs spyod rdzogs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3553: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la /
NK027(sha)001:3554: rin po che'i chab kyi sku khrus gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3555: rnam par grol ba'i ye shes mthong ba'i phung po
NK027(sha)001:3556: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i
NK027(sha)001:3558: las dang nyon mongs pa'i dri ma dag par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3559: de dag ni chu bdun gyi sku khrus gsol ba'o //
NK027(sha)001:3562: thugs rje lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas sku gzugs la //
NK027(sha)001:3563: srid zhu gus phyir ras kyi sku phyis pas //
NK027(sha)001:3564: las dang nyon mongs bag chags kun byang nas //
NK027(sha)001:3565: longs spyod rnam par dag pa'i sku thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:3566: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la /
NK027(sha)001:3567: ras kha tshar ma nyams par sku phyis pas //
NK027(sha)001:3568: gzugs brnyan las byung ba'i dri ma thams cad dang bral nas /
NK027(sha)001:3569: longs spyod rnam par dag pa'i sgo bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sogs /
NK027(sha)001:3570: sarba ta th+aa de nas khro bo'i dbang po'i skyon bsal gyi chos bdun te /
NK027(sha)001:3573: khrag 'thung spyan ma sgrib pa mi mnga' yang //
NK027(sha)001:3574: rnal 'byor 'gro drug bag chags bsal bya'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:3575: gser gyi thur mas spyan gyi skyon bsal te //
NK027(sha)001:3576: srid gsum ye shes spyan du gsal gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3577: badz+ra tsak+shu sa man ta b+hi ta ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:3579: lha tshogs kyi spyan gyi nyes pa bsal nas /
NK027(sha)001:3580: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi /
NK027(sha)001:3581: spyan bdag dang mtha' yas 'gres snyan brud la /
NK027(sha)001:3583: khrag 'thung snyan la 'gags pa mi mnga' yang //
NK027(sha)001:3584: rnal 'byor 'gro drug bag chags bsal ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:3585: dngul gyi thur mas snyan gyi skyon bsal te //
NK027(sha)001:3586: khams gsum sgra rnams dus gcig gsal gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3587: srog srung pra we sha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:3588: snyan gyi nyes pa bsal nas srid gsum sems can thams cad chos sgra chen po thos nas /
NK027(sha)001:3589: shes rgyud grol ba bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3591: khrag 'thung shang la nyes skyon mi mnga' yang //
NK027(sha)001:3592: rnal 'byor 'gro drug bag chags bsal ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:3593: lcags kyi smad gzer shang gi skyon bsal bas //
NK027(sha)001:3594: khams gsum dri rnams dus gcig gsal gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3596: smad gzer gyi shing gi spu btog pas dug lnga ye shes su grol nas /
NK027(sha)001:3600: khrag 'thung ljags la nyes skyon mi mnga' yang //
NK027(sha)001:3601: rnal 'byor 'gro drug bag chags bsal ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:3602: gser gyi ljags bzhar ljags kyi skyon bsal bas /
NK027(sha)001:3603: khams gsum sems can chos kyi ro tshor shog /
NK027(sha)001:3604: ljags kyi nyes skyon bsal bas chos nyid kyi ro tshor te rang sar grol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3605: bdag dang mtha' pa'i rus pa'i tshems shing la /
NK027(sha)001:3606: khrag 'thung tshems la nyon mongs mi mnga' yang //
NK027(sha)001:3607: rnal 'byor 'gro drug bag chags bsal ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:3608: rus pa'i thur mas tshems kyi nyes bsal bas //
NK027(sha)001:3609: 'khor ba'i dug gsum rtsad nas chod gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3611: tshems kyi nyes skyon bsal bas dug gsum rtsad nas
NK027(sha)001:3612: chod pa bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams
NK027(sha)001:3613: cad kyi thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3615: khrag 'thung sku la nyes skyon mi mnga' yang //
NK027(sha)001:3616: rnal 'byor 'gro drug bag chags bsal ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:3617: dung gi so mang gi dbu bshad pas /
NK027(sha)001:3618: srid gsum longs spyod rdzogs sku thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3621: thabs shes ma 'dres pas 'gro ba'i don byed pa bdag dang mtha' yas sogs /
NK027(sha)001:3623: khrag 'thung sku la rnal 'byor 'gro drug gser gyi chan pas zhal gyi spu breg pas //
NK027(sha)001:3624: sprul pa sku yi dbang po thob gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3625: nir ma ka ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:3626: zhal gyi spu breg pas bag chags rtsad nas chod de /
NK027(sha)001:3627: rang byung ye shes bdag dang sogs /
NK027(sha)001:3628: de dag gi dbang po skyon bsal lo //
NK027(sha)001:3629: dngos po'i skyon sbyangs ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:3631: dang po zhun chen gyi chu la /
NK027(sha)001:3632: don dam bcud kyi thig le chen po 'di //
NK027(sha)001:3633: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3634: lhan gcig skyes pa'i dri ma kun dag nas //
NK027(sha)001:3635: byang chub sems kyi rlan dang ldan par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3636: b+ho d+hi tsit+ta dz+ny+aa na b+hi shud+d+he h'u /
NK027(sha)001:3637: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la zhun chen gyi khrus gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3638: lhan gcig skyes pa'i dri ma dag nas /
NK027(sha)001:3639: bde chen byang chub kyi sems bdag dang mtha' yas
NK027(sha)001:3640: pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig
NK027(sha)001:3643: lhag pa'i thal ba phrin las rdzogs pa'i chus //
NK027(sha)001:3644: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3645: bdag gzhan gnyis 'dzin dri ma kun spang nas //
NK027(sha)001:3646: gnyis su med pa'i don dang ldan par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3647: badz+ra bi sa smri ti dz+ny+aa na b+hi shud+d+he h'u /
NK027(sha)001:3648: thal chen chus khrus gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3649: kun brtags kyi dri ma bsal nas /
NK027(sha)001:3650: gnyis med kyi dri ma bsal nas gnyis med kyi don bdag byang chub sems kyi chu la /
NK027(sha)001:3652: skye med byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin 'di //
NK027(sha)001:3653: dkar la dag pa gnyis med ye shes che //
NK027(sha)001:3654: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3655: rdo rje rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3656: badz+ra b+ho d+hi tsit+ta dz+ny+aa na b+hi shud+d+he ham /
NK027(sha)001:3657: byang chub sems kyi khrus gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3658: rdo rje rigs kyis dngos grub dang me long lta
NK027(sha)001:3659: bu'i ye shes bdag dang mtha' yas dri chen gyi
NK027(sha)001:3661: dri chen gsang ba'i rdzas chen dam rdzas mchog /
NK027(sha)001:3662: skye 'chi med pa rdo rje'i chu //
NK027(sha)001:3663: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3664: de bzhin rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3665: badz+ra a yu dz+ny+aa na b+hi shud+d+he h'u /
NK027(sha)001:3666: dri chen chus khrus gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3667: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dngos grub dang yod med las
NK027(sha)001:3668: 'das pa stong pa nyid kyi ye shes bdag dang
NK027(sha)001:3669: mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par
NK027(sha)001:3670: gyur cig / mang sa'i chu la /
NK027(sha)001:3672: khams gsum rgyu drug 'khor ba'i sems can rnams //
NK027(sha)001:3673: dug gsum bsgral ba chen po bcud kyi chu //
NK027(sha)001:3674: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3675: rin chen rigs kyis dngos grub thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3676: badz+ra ma h+aa mam sa b+hi shud+d+he h'u /
NK027(sha)001:3677: sha chen gyis khrus gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3678: rin chen rigs kyi dngos grub dang mnyam pa nyid
NK027(sha)001:3679: ye shes bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams
NK027(sha)001:3681: pad+ma rak+ta gsang ba'i dbang gi rdzas //
NK027(sha)001:3682: chags par byed pa dmar la dwangs pa'i chus //
NK027(sha)001:3683: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3684: pad+ma rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3685: pad+ma rak+sha ti la ka b+hi shud+d+he h'u /
NK027(sha)001:3687: pad+ma rigs kyis dngos grub dang //
NK027(sha)001:3688: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes bdag dang mtha' yas dri chu la /
NK027(sha)001:3690: dri chu kun gyi sems byed las kyi rigs //
NK027(sha)001:3691: thams cad dag byed bdud rtsi chen po'i chus //
NK027(sha)001:3692: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3693: las kyi rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3694: ma h+aa ma ma ku ku dz+ny+aa na b+hi shud+d+he h'u /
NK027(sha)001:3696: las kyi rigs kyis dngos grub dang bya ba grub
NK027(sha)001:3697: pa'i ye shes bdag ro ras kyi sku phyi ba
NK027(sha)001:3699: thugs rje lhun rdzogs khrag 'thung dkyil 'khor la //
NK027(sha)001:3700: dur khrod chen po'i ras kyi sku phyes bas /
NK027(sha)001:3701: shes bya'i las dang nyon mongs sgrib byang nas //
NK027(sha)001:3702: spyod lam rnam par dag pa'i sku thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:3703: badz+ra ta th+aa ga ta dz+ny+aa na b+hi shud+d+he ham /
NK027(sha)001:3704: ro ras kyi sku phyi bas /
NK027(sha)001:3705: shes bya'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK027(sha)001:3706: spyod lam rnam par dag pa //
NK027(sha)001:3707: bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3708: de ni dngos po skyon sbyong ngo //
NK027(sha)001:3709: don drug pa che ba'i yon tan dang rgyan chas kyi mnga' gsol ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:3710: bdun pa phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyis mchod pa 'bul ba dril ba la don bzhi ste /
NK027(sha)001:3711: gzugs bye brag tu mnga' gsol ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:3712: mdzes pa rgyan du mnga' gsol ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:3713: che ba'i yon tan phun sum tshogs par mnga' gsol ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:3714: mnyes mchod bzhes par mnga' gsol ba'o //
NK027(sha)001:3715: dang po gzugs bye brag tu mnga' gsol ba /
NK027(sha)001:3728: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po ni //
NK027(sha)001:3729: bde gshegs sku la dbu yi mnga' gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3730: rnam par thar pa'i dbu gsum thob nas ni //
NK027(sha)001:3731: khams gsum yongs su dag par mdzad gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3732: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la /
NK027(sha)001:3733: dbu gsum gyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3734: khams gsum dbang du bsgyur zhing rnam par dag pa'i dbu gsum bdag dang phyag la /
NK027(sha)001:3737: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK027(sha)001:3738: bde gshegs sku la phyag gi mnga' gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3739: ye shes drug gi 'gro ba'i don mdzad nas //
NK027(sha)001:3740: khams gsum 'gro drug rtsad nas gcod par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3741: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la phyag gi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3742: ye shes drug gi don rtogs pa bdag dang mtha'
NK027(sha)001:3743: yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur
NK027(sha)001:3744: cig / zhabs la dza bzhi'i 'phro 'dus las /
NK027(sha)001:3746: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la zhabs kyi mnga' gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3747: rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhi'i 'gro don mthar phyin nas //
NK027(sha)001:3748: bdud bzhi ma lus zil gyi gnon gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3749: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la zhabs kyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3750: rdzu 'phrul rkang pa bzhi'i bdud bzhi zil gyi gnon
NK027(sha)001:3751: pa bdag dang dbu skra la dza'i 'phro 'du las
NK027(sha)001:3753: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK027(sha)001:3754: bde gshegs sku la skra'i mnga' gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3755: khyab pa thugs rje chen po'i phrin las kyi //
NK027(sha)001:3756: lta ba mthar mi ltung dang ldan par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3757: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la dbu skra spyang lo mthon mthing gi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3758: khyab byed chen po'i phrin las dang /
NK027(sha)001:3759: mtha' bral gyi lta ba bdag dang smin ma la ra'i 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:3761: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la smin mas mnga' gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3762: thabs chen g.yang bzhi mkhas pa'i byin rlabs kyi //
NK027(sha)001:3763: gdul bya'i 'gro ba chud mi gsan par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3764: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la smin ma'i mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3765: thabs mkhas che ba gdul bya 'dren pa bdag dang
NK027(sha)001:3766: mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par
NK027(sha)001:3767: gyur cig / spyan la a a h+r+aih'i 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:3769: lhag pa'i bde gshegs sku la spyan gyi mnga' gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3770: spyan lnga ma lus yongs su rdzogs nas ni //
NK027(sha)001:3771: rmongs pa'i rab rib thams cad dag par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3772: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la spyan gyi mnga' gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3773: thams cad gsal zhing rig pa ma 'gag par mthong ba bdag dang ljags la a'i 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:3775: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la ljag gi mnga' gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3776: sgra skad bsam gyis mi khyab bye brag gi //
NK027(sha)001:3777: gdul bya sems can thams cad smin grol shog /
NK027(sha)001:3778: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la khyab byed ljags kyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3779: sgra'i bye brag gi sna tshogs pas /
NK027(sha)001:3780: gdul bya thams cad dus gcig las smin par mdzad pas /
NK027(sha)001:3781: bdag dang mtha' yas tshems mche ba la kla'i 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:3783: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK027(sha)001:3784: bde gshegs sku la mche bas mnga' skye shi'i sdug bsngal rtsad nas gcod mdzad cing //
NK027(sha)001:3785: sgrib pa thams cad ma lus zad byed shog /
NK027(sha)001:3786: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la tshems mche bas mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3787: skye shi'i sdug bsngal rtsad nas gcod mdzad cing //
NK027(sha)001:3792: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la sku mdog rgyan gsal bas //
NK027(sha)001:3793: mi 'gyur chos nyid skyon gyi ma gos dang //
NK027(sha)001:3794: che ba'i yon tan spyod bzhin ma 'gag pa //
NK027(sha)001:3795: sna tshogs rol pa'i rgyan du shar nas ni //
NK027(sha)001:3796: phrin las lnga po yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3798: sku mdog gi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3799: mi 'gyur chos nyid skyon gyi ma gos par spyod cing /
NK027(sha)001:3800: sna tshogs rol pa'i phrin las lnga yongs su rdzogs
NK027(sha)001:3801: pa bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad
NK027(sha)001:3804: h'u h'u h'u h'u h'u h'u /
NK027(sha)001:3807: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la phyag mtshan drug phul bas //
NK027(sha)001:3808: ye shes drug gi 'gro don yongs rdzogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:3809: phrin las chen po'i 'gro don mthar phyin shog /
NK027(sha)001:3810: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la phyag mtshan drug gi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3811: ye shes drug rdzogs te phrin las mthar phyin pa /
NK027(sha)001:3812: bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can bcu pa gzugs gi bye brag go //
NK027(sha)001:3813: gnyis pa mdzes pa'i rgyan la /
NK027(sha)001:3814: dbu rgyan dang h'u s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:3818: lhag pa'i bde gshegs sku la dbu rgyan mnga' gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3819: sems rgyud rnam shes tshogs brgyad gnas dag nas //
NK027(sha)001:3820: ye shes lnga yi 'gro don mthar phyin shog /
NK027(sha)001:3821: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la rin po che'i dbu rgyan gyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3822: rnam shes tshogs brgyad gnas dag nas /
NK027(sha)001:3823: ye shes lnga bdag dang mtha' yas cod pan la h'u h+r+aih'i 'phro 'du la /
NK027(sha)001:3825: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la cod pan
NK027(sha)001:3826: mnga' khams gsum gdug pa ma lus kun 'dul zhing
NK027(sha)001:3827: // srid gsum chos kyi rgyal po byed par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3828: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la cod pan gyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3829: khams gsum gyi gdug pa ma lus pa 'dul zhing /
NK027(sha)001:3830: srid gsum chos kyi rgyal por bdag dang mtha' yas snyan cha dang mgul chu /
NK027(sha)001:3833: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la snyan cha dang //
NK027(sha)001:3834: mgul chu la sogs rgyan gyi mnga' gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3835: rdzu 'phrul snyan gyi mnga' gsol ldan par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3836: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la rin chen rgyan cha mgul chus mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3837: rdzu 'phrul gyi snyan gyi rang rig pa mnga' brnyes pa /
NK027(sha)001:3838: bdag dang do shal la a tram gi 'phro 'du la /
NK027(sha)001:3840: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la do shal
NK027(sha)001:3841: mnga' don rnams thams cad rig pas rtogs nas ni
NK027(sha)001:3842: // mi brjed gzungs dang rtag tu ldan par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3843: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la /
NK027(sha)001:3844: rin po che'i do shal gyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3845: don thams cad ma lus par rig cing mi brjed pa'i gzungs bdag dang /
NK027(sha)001:3846: se mo do la tram gyi 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:3847: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la se mo do yi ni //
NK027(sha)001:3849: mi brjed gzungs kyi sgo 'bum phrag rdzogs nas /
NK027(sha)001:3851: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la se mo do yi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3852: gzungs kyi sgo 'bum phrag rdzogs shing /
NK027(sha)001:3853: brgya phrag 'phrad pa bdag dpung rgyan la sa'i 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:3855: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dkyil bde gshegs sku la dpung rgyan mnga' gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3856: mi 'jigs pa bzhi ting nge 'dzin thob nas //
NK027(sha)001:3857: re dogs kun gyi mtha' dang bral gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3858: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la /
NK027(sha)001:3859: dpung rgyan gyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3860: mi 'jigs pa bzhi ting nge 'dzin gyi re dogs thams cad kyi mtha' dang bral ba /
NK027(sha)001:3861: bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i phyag zhabs kyi gdug gu'i 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:3863: lhag pa'i bde gshegs sku la gdu gus mnga' gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3864: tshul khrims rnam dag bcu lhun grub nas //
NK027(sha)001:3865: mtshan ma thams cad zil gyi gnon par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3866: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la rin po che'i gdu gu mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3867: tshul khrims rnam par dag pa'i stobs bcu'i lhun gyis grub nas /
NK027(sha)001:3868: mtshan ma thams cad zil gyi gnon pa /
NK027(sha)001:3869: bdag dang mtha' yas gdan khri las sems can chen po lnga'i gdan la sa'i 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:3871: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la sems can lnga yi ni /
NK027(sha)001:3872: gdan khri brjid bag ldan pas mnga' che ba'i yon tan lnga po lhun grub nas //
NK027(sha)001:3873: kun gyi bskur gnas sangs rgyas sar bkod shog /
NK027(sha)001:3874: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la /
NK027(sha)001:3875: sems can chen po lnga'i gdan khris mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3876: che ba'i yon tan lnga po lhun gyis grub nas /
NK027(sha)001:3877: sangs rgyas go 'phang bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i nyi
NK027(sha)001:3878: zla pad+ma'i gdan la a ma sa'i 'phro 'du las
NK027(sha)001:3880: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK027(sha)001:3881: bde gshegs sku la nyi zla'i gdan khri yi //
NK027(sha)001:3882: mnga' gsol mdzad pa de'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:3883: thugs rje chen pos kun la khyab par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3884: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan gyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3885: thugs rje chen po'i kun la khyab cing shes rab
NK027(sha)001:3886: chen po ltas ngan sel bas gang la yang spyod
NK027(sha)001:3888: bdag dang rin po che'i khri rkang la tram gi 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:3890: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la rin chen khri rkang gi /
NK027(sha)001:3891: gdan khri'i mnga' gsol byas pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:3892: 'gro ba'i re 'dod yid bzhin bskang gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3893: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la rin chen khri rkang gi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3894: 'gro ba ma lus pa'i re ba yid bzhin du bskangs pa /
NK027(sha)001:3895: bdag dang 'od zer las ra'i 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:3897: lhag pa'i gzugs bde gshegs sku la 'od zer mnga' byin rlabs 'od zer rang la gsal nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:3898: spros pa'i mtha' rnams yongs su bral gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:3899: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la 'od zer gyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3900: chos thams cad bsam gyis mi khyab cing /
NK027(sha)001:3901: ye shes rang gsal zhing spros pa'i mtha' thams cad
NK027(sha)001:3902: dang bral ba rtogs pas bdag dang mtha' yas stod
NK027(sha)001:3905: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la na bza' stod g.yog gi //
NK027(sha)001:3906: mnga' gsol byas pas gdul bya'i 'gro ba kun //
NK027(sha)001:3907: yongs su smin pas thams cad skyob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3908: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la /
NK027(sha)001:3909: na bza' stod g.yog gi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3910: gdul bya yongs su skyob pa bdag dang /
NK027(sha)001:3913: lhag pa'i bde gshegs sku la sham thabs mnga' gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3914: spyod lam rnam par dag pa'i sku rdzogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:3915: mdzad pa mthar mi 'gag pa thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3916: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la /
NK027(sha)001:3917: sham thabs kyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3918: gdul bya yongs su rdzogs pa bdag dang mtha' yas
NK027(sha)001:3919: pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig
NK027(sha)001:3922: lhag pa'i bde gshegs sku la gsang phod mnga' gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3923: gdul bya'i re ba yid bzhin bskang nas ni //
NK027(sha)001:3924: yon tan mdzad pa cir yang 'char bar shog /
NK027(sha)001:3925: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la /
NK027(sha)001:3926: gsang phod kyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3927: gdul bya ma lus pa'i re ba yid bzhin du bskang shing /
NK027(sha)001:3928: yon tan mdzad pa cir yang 'char ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:3929: bdag dang mtha' yas zi ldar la sa'i 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:3931: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la zi ldar mnga' gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3932: sangs rgyas dgongs pa ma lus thugs chud nas //
NK027(sha)001:3933: thugs kyis mdzad pa mthar mi 'gag par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3934: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la zi ldar sangs rgyas ma lus pa'i dgongs pa thugs su chud nas //
NK027(sha)001:3936: longs spyod pa bdag dang phyag rgya gar gyi phul du sa'i 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:3938: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK027(sha)001:3939: bde gshegs sku la phyag rgya gar phul bas //
NK027(sha)001:3940: sna tshogs lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las kyi //
NK027(sha)001:3941: phrin las thogs med kun la spyod par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3942: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la phyag rgya gar gyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3943: sna tshogs phrin las lhun gyis grub pa bdag dang mtha' de nas khro bo'i mnga' gsol ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:3944: dang po dbu la +aahmh'u gi 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:3945: dbu gsum gsal bar bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:3947: dbu gsum sku gsum rang chas ngo bo ste //
NK027(sha)001:3948: rnam par thar pa'i sgo gsum thob nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:3949: nyon mongs dug gsum ma lus rtsad bcad nas //
NK027(sha)001:3950: 'bras bu sku gsum lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3951: bde gshegs 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:3952: dbu gsum gyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3953: dug gsum rang sar grol te /
NK027(sha)001:3954: khams gsum zad par stong pa'i don bdag dang mtha'
NK027(sha)001:3955: yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur
NK027(sha)001:3960: phyag drug ye shes drug gi ngo bo ste //
NK027(sha)001:3961: pha rol phyin pa drug gi don nyid shar //
NK027(sha)001:3962: rgyu drug ye shes drug gi don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:3963: sangs rgyas sa la rab tu gnas par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3964: bde gshegs 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:3965: phyag rgya drug gi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3966: ye shes drug gi don rtogs te pha rol tu
NK027(sha)001:3967: phyin pa drug gi don khong du chud pa bdag
NK027(sha)001:3968: dang / phyag mtshan h'u drug las /
NK027(sha)001:3969: so sor gsal bar bsgom la /
NK027(sha)001:3971: dbyings dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pa'i ngang //
NK027(sha)001:3972: dug gsum sku gsung thugs su dbang bsdus te //
NK027(sha)001:3973: rig pa'i gsung dang thugs rjes 'gro ba 'dren //
NK027(sha)001:3974: 'khor ba ma spangs kun nas brda' sprod shog /
NK027(sha)001:3976: phyag mtshan gyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:3977: dbyings dang ye shes 'du 'bral med cing /
NK027(sha)001:3978: dug gsum dbang du bsdus shing /
NK027(sha)001:3980: 'khor ba ma spang spyod pa'i don zhabs bzhi dza bzhi gsal bar bsgom /
NK027(sha)001:3982: zhabs bzhi'i bdud bzhi ma lus zil gyi gnon //
NK027(sha)001:3983: sangs rgyas sa la bgrod par phyin nas ni //
NK027(sha)001:3984: rdzu 'phrul rkang pa'i zhabs bzhi lhun grub nas //
NK027(sha)001:3985: tshad med bzhi yi 'gro don byed par shog /
NK027(sha)001:3986: bde gshegs 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:3987: zhabs kyi mnga' gsol bas zhabs bzhis rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi lhun gyis grub nas /
NK027(sha)001:3988: bdud bzhi zil gyi mnan pa'i 'bras bu bdag dang
NK027(sha)001:3989: mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par
NK027(sha)001:3990: gyur cig / sku mdog la h'u lnga /
NK027(sha)001:3992: bde ba chen po'i chos nyid la //
NK027(sha)001:3993: sngo nag smug nag ser nag dang //
NK027(sha)001:3994: dmar nag ljang nag sna tshogs mdog cir yang 'gyur ba'i don rtogs shog /
NK027(sha)001:3995: bder gshegs 'jigs byed chen po sogs /
NK027(sha)001:3996: chos nyid sku mdog mnga' gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:3997: chos nyid gcig pur rang sar grol ba'i don bdag sma ra ka'i 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:3998: sma ra dmar ser me ltar 'phros pa las /
NK027(sha)001:3999: sma ra dmar ser ye shes rab tu 'phro //
NK027(sha)001:4000: khro bo khro mo'i sprul pa phra men 'gyed //
NK027(sha)001:4001: thugs rjes khyab par 'gro ba 'dren par mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:4002: rig pa'i ye shes chen po rtogs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4003: 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung ye shes kyi sma ras mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4004: khro bo khro mo'i sprul pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:4005: phra men mang pos don mdzad pa bdag smin sma ra'i 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:4008: smin ma ye shes 'phro ba'i rang bzhin las //
NK027(sha)001:4009: dug lnga thams cad ma spang rang sar grol //
NK027(sha)001:4010: gsang sngags spyod pa thabs chen mnga' ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:4011: thabs mkhas thugs rjes 'gro ba 'dren par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4012: 'jigs byed ye shes kyi smin mas mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4013: ye shes smin mas thabs mkhas pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:4017: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i gdul bya thams cad chud
NK027(sha)001:4018: mi gsan pa'i don bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems
NK027(sha)001:4019: can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:4023: spyan gsum ye shes me ltar 'bar ba'i 'od //
NK027(sha)001:4024: chos kyis spyan dang ye shes me gos spyan //
NK027(sha)001:4025: khyab pa thugs rje'i spyan gyi don mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:4026: bdag gzhan don gnyis lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4027: 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:4028: ye shes kyi spyan 'bar ba gsum kyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4029: chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa'i spyan khyab /
NK027(sha)001:4030: thugs rje'i spyan gyi skyon ma gos pa'i ye shes kyi spyan dang gsum gyis /
NK027(sha)001:4031: bdag gzhan gyi don thams cad lhun gyis grub pa'i don bdag /
NK027(sha)001:4035: ral pa kham nag srid pa'i rtse mor 'bar //
NK027(sha)001:4036: khyab pa'i thugs rjes 'gro drug 'dren par mdzod //
NK027(sha)001:4037: thugs kyis sprul pa phyogs bcur bkyes nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:4038: mtha' ru ma lhung don gnyis rtogs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4039: 'jigs byed chen po ye shes ral pas khyab pa'i thugs rje dang /
NK027(sha)001:4040: dbang drag mthar phyin pa'i phrin las /
NK027(sha)001:4041: mthar ma lhung ba lta ba rtogs pa'i don bdag dang snyan cha h+r+ai'i 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:4042: gser rag gdu gu kha dog steng /
NK027(sha)001:4044: sgra'i bye brag bsam mi khyab //
NK027(sha)001:4045: rang gi rig pa nyid las mi gzhan pa //
NK027(sha)001:4046: gsan cing thos pas gdul bya thams cad kyi //
NK027(sha)001:4047: gang yang ma 'gags spyod la dbang rdzogs shog /
NK027(sha)001:4048: 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:4049: rin po che'i snyan chas mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4050: sgra thams cad rig pa las mi gzhan par /
NK027(sha)001:4051: gang du yang ma 'gags par longs spyod pa'i don
NK027(sha)001:4052: bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi
NK027(sha)001:4055: chos nyid bde ba'i dri tshems pas /
NK027(sha)001:4056: h'u dri'i bye brag bsam mi khyab //
NK027(sha)001:4057: dbang po dwangs pas tshim byed chos kyi dri //
NK027(sha)001:4058: rdo rje h'u ring dri las byung ba las //
NK027(sha)001:4059: kun tu ma 'gags chags med don rtogs shog /
NK027(sha)001:4060: 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:4061: dri'i bye brag bsam gyis mi khyab pas mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4062: thams cad bzang ngan med pa mnyam pa nyid du longs spyod pa'i don rtogs te /
NK027(sha)001:4063: 'khor ba'i chos la longs spyod kyang /
NK027(sha)001:4064: nyes pa'i skyon gyi ma gos don bdag dang /
NK027(sha)001:4066: dmar la sras pa glog bzhin 'gyu /
NK027(sha)001:4068: khyab byed ljags sgra'i ngo bo ste //
NK027(sha)001:4069: chos kyi sgra chen bsam las sgrogs pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4070: 'gro drug sems can ma lus tshim mdzad nas //
NK027(sha)001:4071: rgyud rnams grol nas gdul bya smin par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4072: 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung khyab byed ljags kyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4073: sgra'i yan lag bsam mi khyab pa'i /
NK027(sha)001:4075: gdul bya thams cad dus gcig tu smin par mdzad pa'i don bdag 'gres so //
NK027(sha)001:4076: tshems kla'i 'phro 'du las mche ba dkar po rab tu rnam par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:4078: ye shes mche bas skye 'chi rtsad nas gcod //
NK027(sha)001:4079: 'gro drug sdug bsngal nad kyi gdung ba la //
NK027(sha)001:4080: ye shes mche bas sdug bsngal rab grol nas //
NK027(sha)001:4081: khams gsum 'khor ba thams cad stong par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4082: 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung rol ba'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:4083: ye shes kyi mche bas mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4084: sems can thams cad kyi skye 'chi rtsad nas gcod cing /
NK027(sha)001:4085: rang byung gi ye shes rtogs te /
NK027(sha)001:4086: 'khor ba thams cad stong pa'i don bdag dang mtha'
NK027(sha)001:4087: yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur
NK027(sha)001:4088: cig / de nas rol pa nyi shu las /
NK027(sha)001:4092: rol pa nyi shu dpal chen thugs kyis bdag /
NK027(sha)001:4093: chos kyi 'brug char rnga dang dung la sogs //
NK027(sha)001:4094: mchod gzungs rdzas dang ye shes ting 'dzin gyi //
NK027(sha)001:4095: sprul pa'i chos kyi ro dang ldan par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4097: rol pa nyi shus mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4098: rol pa chen po chos kyi 'brug sgra dang /
NK027(sha)001:4099: rol pa sna tshogs kyi char dang /
NK027(sha)001:4107: rgyan dang rngam pa tshem dang /
NK027(sha)001:4113: snang srid phyag rgyar gsal ba'i bden pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:4116: khro bo rol pa nyi shu'i don bdag yon tan gyi che ba gnyis las /
NK027(sha)001:4119: che ba nyi shu dpal chen nyid la ldan //
NK027(sha)001:4120: 'gran zla med pas che btsan nyid las byung //
NK027(sha)001:4121: mi nub go bas yon tan thams cad rdzogs //
NK027(sha)001:4122: kun du mdzad pas 'gro drug 'dren par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4123: 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:4124: che ba nyi shus mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4125: gnyen po med pa'i che ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:4126: 'gran zla med pa'i che ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:4127: khyad par 'phags pa'i che ba che btsan gcig pu'i che ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:4128: tshogs gnyis brlab kyi myur du byung ba'i tshe /
NK027(sha)001:4129: thams cad ma pham pa'i che ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:4130: mnga' dbang rdzogs pa'i che ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:4131: kun las rgyal ba'i yongs su mi nub pa'i thams
NK027(sha)001:4132: cad go ba'i ye shes gsal ba'i 'dod pa rdzogs
NK027(sha)001:4133: pa'i kun las rgyal ba'i yongs su mi nub pa'i
NK027(sha)001:4134: thams cad go ba'i ye shes gsal ba'i 'dod pa
NK027(sha)001:4135: rdzogs pa'i kun tu mdzad pa'i che ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:4136: thams cad sgrol ba'i myur du bsreg pa'i dbu'i mdzes
NK027(sha)001:4137: pa'i rgyan gyi brgyan pa'i sna tshogs 'dzin pa'i che
NK027(sha)001:4138: ba mnan pa'i che ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:4139: de ltar he ru ka'i che ba nyi shu'i don
NK027(sha)001:4140: bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi
NK027(sha)001:4142: brjid nyi shu la sa'i 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:4143: sku gzi brjid nyi shu ldan par bsam /
NK027(sha)001:4145: brjid chen nyi shu dpal chen nyid la ldan //
NK027(sha)001:4146: sku che brgyan ldan bkur 'os yid dang 'thad //
NK027(sha)001:4147: mdangs che kun la ston pa'i mtha' dang bral //
NK027(sha)001:4148: thugs rje thabs kyis 'gro ba 'dren par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4150: brjid nyi shus mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4151: sku che yan lag rag pa'i brjid dang /
NK027(sha)001:4152: grangs mang rgyan du 'tshe ba'i brjid dang /
NK027(sha)001:4153: bkur 'os gtso cher mthong ba'i brjid khyad du zhug yid 'thad pa'i brjid //
NK027(sha)001:4154: mdangs che stong gsum gang ba'i brjid //
NK027(sha)001:4155: tshig myur them chod pa'i bdag la nyer ston pa brjid dang //
NK027(sha)001:4156: khyad par yon tan mthong ba brjid //
NK027(sha)001:4157: yangs pa'i re dogs bral ba brjid //
NK027(sha)001:4158: mi bsnyil nyams chag rol pa'i brjid //
NK027(sha)001:4159: thugs rjes thugs dam rdzogs pa'i brjid //
NK027(sha)001:4160: ma rmongs thabs kyi 'dul ba'i kun la 'dod dgur
NK027(sha)001:4161: bsgyur ba'i gnod sbyor phan par mdzad pa'i thabs mkhas
NK027(sha)001:4163: gsal ba mtha' gnyis spangs pa'i 'khor ba mi snyil
NK027(sha)001:4164: bar gzigs pas mgon skyabs rgyun du mdzad pa'i 'dod
NK027(sha)001:4165: dgu lhun gyis grub pa'i brjid //
NK027(sha)001:4166: de ltar brjid nyi shu'i don bdag dang mtha' yas
NK027(sha)001:4167: pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig
NK027(sha)001:4168: / rngam pa nyi shu la sha nyi shu thim pas rngam nyi shu ldan par bsgom /
NK027(sha)001:4170: rngam chen nyi shu dpal chen nyid rdzogs pa //
NK027(sha)001:4171: sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa'i yon tan la //
NK027(sha)001:4172: zhal ljags tshems dang dbyings dang ting 'dzin dang //
NK027(sha)001:4173: 'phrin las la sogs thams cad 'grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4174: 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:4175: rngam pa nyi shu'i mnga' gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:4176: sku che yan lag rag pas rngam pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:4177: gsung che bstan pa rgya mtsho rngam //
NK027(sha)001:4178: thugs chos nyid nam mkha' 'dra ba'i mthu nam mkha' ltar rngam pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:4179: snang ba thams cad ri mo ltar //
NK027(sha)001:4180: cir yang 'gyur ba gang thab ltar //
NK027(sha)001:4181: zil gyi gnon par khyad du 'byung bar rngam pa
NK027(sha)001:4182: tshems rngam stabs su 'gying bar za bar rngo ba
NK027(sha)001:4184: cir yang 'gyur ba ljag gi skye shi gcod pa tshems kyi rngam pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:4185: go bar sgrog pa dbyangs kyi rngam pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:4186: ting 'dzin nam mkha'i skad tshogs ltar //
NK027(sha)001:4187: phrin las rgya mtsho'i rba rlabs ltar //
NK027(sha)001:4188: yon tan sa gzhi'i skye 'bru ltar //
NK027(sha)001:4189: thugs rje gar gyi phreng ba ltar gnas kyi 'phro 'du dur khrod ltar //
NK027(sha)001:4190: gnod pa dpa' bo bskum par rngam pa zhing gi
NK027(sha)001:4191: khyad par bla na med par spyod pa'i khyad par
NK027(sha)001:4192: la rngam thams cad mi 'gyur bar rngam pa dang
NK027(sha)001:4193: / de ltar rngam pa nyi shu'i don mdzad pa
NK027(sha)001:4194: bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi
NK027(sha)001:4196: cho 'phrul nyi shu e nyi shu rten gyi sku dang yan lag la zhugs pas /
NK027(sha)001:4197: cho 'phrul nyi shu dang ldan par bsam /
NK027(sha)001:4199: cho 'phrul nyi shu dpal chen nyid dang ldan //
NK027(sha)001:4200: chos nyid thugs rjes chos la kun snang ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:4201: kun tu spyod pa cir yang snang ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:4202: gang ltar 'tsho bas 'gro drug 'dren par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4203: 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:4204: cho 'phrul nyi shu'i mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4205: las kyis rdzu 'phrul skye ba'i cho 'phrul /
NK027(sha)001:4206: bsam gtan gyi cho 'phrul chos nyid kyi shes bya'i
NK027(sha)001:4207: rang bzhin gyi rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul chos snang
NK027(sha)001:4208: ba'i kun rdzob kyi rjes su bstan pa'i cir yang
NK027(sha)001:4209: snang ba'i rnam par bsgyur ba'i chos nyid kyi thugs
NK027(sha)001:4210: rjes sprul pa'i ye shes kyi gang ltar 'tsho ba
NK027(sha)001:4211: 'dul ba'i gang gis 'tsham pas 'dul ba'i bsgyur ba'i
NK027(sha)001:4212: 'dul ba'i gang theg pa la 'dul ba'i gang ltar
NK027(sha)001:4214: de ltar he ru ka'i cho 'phrul nyi shu'i don
NK027(sha)001:4215: bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi
NK027(sha)001:4217: dpal gyi chas brgyad la h'u brgyad las /
NK027(sha)001:4219: dpal chen sku yi chas brgyad kyi //
NK027(sha)001:4220: dreg pa zil gyi gnon pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:4221: thugs rjes byin rlabs cir yang 'char //
NK027(sha)001:4222: cis kyang mi tshugs dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:4223: 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:4224: dpal chen po chas brgyad kyi mnga' dreg pa can 'dul ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:4225: cis kyang mi tshugs pa'i don bdag dang nas /
NK027(sha)001:4226: glang chen ko rlon la h'u gi 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:4228: glang chen ko rlon theg chen don dang ldan //
NK027(sha)001:4229: gti mug ma spang rang sar grol nas ni //
NK027(sha)001:4230: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcu mnga' ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:4231: sdug bsngal thams cad zil gyi gnon par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4233: glang chen ko rlon gyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4234: gti mug ma spang rang sar grol nas ni /
NK027(sha)001:4235: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcus sdug bsngal thams cad zil gyi gnon /
NK027(sha)001:4236: dur khrod chas brgyad zhing gi g.yang gzhi thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:4239: thugs rjes kun la khyab pa'i don mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:4240: thabs la mkhas pas thugs rje cir yang snang //
NK027(sha)001:4241: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal thams cad bsal nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:4242: 'dod chags ma spang rang sar grol bar shog /
NK027(sha)001:4244: zhing gi g.yang gzhis mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4246: thabs la mkhas pa'i 'phrin las kyi 'gro ba ci
NK027(sha)001:4247: ltar 'dul ba'i don bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i stag
NK027(sha)001:4251: stag gi shes rab don dang ldan //
NK027(sha)001:4252: zhe sdang ma spang rang grol nas //
NK027(sha)001:4253: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal bsal nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:4254: bdud bzhi zil gyi gnon par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4255: 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:4256: stag gi sham thabs kyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4257: zhe sdang ma spang bdud bzhi zil gyi gnon pa'i don bdag dang zhag gi thig le /
NK027(sha)001:4260: chos rnams rang bzhin gnyis med cing //
NK027(sha)001:4261: byang chub sems su dag bya'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:4262: zhag gi thig les mtshan pa 'di //
NK027(sha)001:4263: ging chen kun dang gcig par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4265: zhag gi thig le'i mnga' zhe sdang ma spang rang sar dag nas /
NK027(sha)001:4266: longs spyod rdzogs skus 'gro ba'i don mdzad pas bdag dang sogs /
NK027(sha)001:4267: thal chen la h'u gi 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:4269: chos rnams rang bzhin gnyis med cing //
NK027(sha)001:4270: byang chub sems su dag bya'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:4271: thal ba'i tshom bu mtshan pa 'di //
NK027(sha)001:4272: mkha' 'gro kun dang gcig par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4274: thal chen gyi tshom bu'i mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4275: longs spyod rdzogs sku'i 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa bdag sogs /
NK027(sha)001:4276: rak+ta'i thig le h'u gi 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:4278: chos rnams byang chub sems su dag bya'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:4280: ging chen kun dang mthun par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4281: 'jigs byed chen po rak+ta'i thig les mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4282: 'dod chags sprul sku'i 'gro don mdzad pas /
NK027(sha)001:4283: bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i thod pa tshar gsum la /
NK027(sha)001:4286: thod pa tshar gsum dug gsum ngo bo ste //
NK027(sha)001:4287: lus ngag yid gsum rtog pa mi mnga' ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:4288: sangs rgyas sku gsum ngo bo grol bar shog /
NK027(sha)001:4289: 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung rol ba'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:4290: thod pa tshar gsum gyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4291: nyon mongs pa dug gsum ma spang bar sangs rgyas pa'i don bdag sprul chun la /
NK027(sha)001:4294: rigs bzhi sbrul gyi rgyan chas 'di //
NK027(sha)001:4295: zhe sdang ma spang gnas dag nas //
NK027(sha)001:4296: gdug pa thams cad thugs rjes 'dul //
NK027(sha)001:4297: ye shes brgyad kyi don rtogs shog /
NK027(sha)001:4299: sbrul chen rigs bzhi'i mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4301: zhe sdang ma spang rang sar grol ba'i de dag
NK027(sha)001:4302: gi khro bo mdzes pa'i rgyan cha drug gi chas
NK027(sha)001:4304: dbu ma man chad la mnga' gsol ba nyi shu rtsa gcig go //
NK027(sha)001:4305: de nas lha de dag che ba'i yon tan bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK027(sha)001:4310: ru tra dreg pa chen po btul ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:4311: zhing chen skam rlon phyi nang mkha' 'gro'i gdan //
NK027(sha)001:4312: thugs rjes kun la khyab par don mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:4313: nyon mongs gdug pa zil gyi gnon par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4314: 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:4316: zhing skam rlon gyi gdan gyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4317: khams gsum gyi dreg pa can thams cad btul ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:4318: nyon mongs pa thams cad zil gyi mnan pa'i mam gi 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:4321: seng ge glang chen ma he gzig stag dom //
NK027(sha)001:4322: sems can chen po lnga'i gdan khri 'di //
NK027(sha)001:4323: che ba'i yon tan lhun gyis grub nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:4324: sa rnams thams cad dus gcig gnon par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4325: 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung sems can chen po lnga'i gdan khri'i mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4326: che ba'i yon tan lhun gyis grub pa ste /
NK027(sha)001:4327: sa rnams mthar phyin pa'i don bdag dang ma las nyi ma'i gdan bsam /
NK027(sha)001:4329: sdug bsngal rgya mtsho gting skam nyi ma'i gdan //
NK027(sha)001:4330: ye shes thugs rje chen po bdal ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:4331: kun la khyab par 'gro don mdzad nas ni //
NK027(sha)001:4332: las dang nyon mongs thams cad bsregs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4333: 'jigs byed chen po shes rab nyi ma'i gdan gyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4334: ye shes kyi thugs rje chen pos las dang nyon mongs pa'i bag chags thams cad bsregs pa'i nas /
NK027(sha)001:4335: ram las ye shes kyi kha dog lnga 'phro bar bsgom /
NK027(sha)001:4337: sku'i rgyab yol me ri chen po las //
NK027(sha)001:4338: ye shes lnga'i 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK027(sha)001:4339: 'dod pa'i yon tan thams cad rdzogs gyur nas //
NK027(sha)001:4340: mtha' yi ltas ngan thams cad 'joms par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4341: 'jigs byed chen po rgyab yol me ri 'bar bas mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4342: shes rab ye shes kyi me chen pos /
NK027(sha)001:4343: mtha' ltas ngan thams cad bsreg kyi 'dod pa'i yon
NK027(sha)001:4344: tan thams cad lhun gyis grub pa'i don dang mtha'
NK027(sha)001:4345: yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur
NK027(sha)001:4346: cig / de nas zhi khro thun mong du gdugs la sogs pa 'dra /
NK027(sha)001:4347: gsum pa che ba'i longs spyod phun sum tshogs pas mnga' gsol la /
NK027(sha)001:4350: gzi brjid khyad par 'phags pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4351: bde gshegs sku la rin chen gdug phul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4352: log par lta ba tha dag yongs spangs nas //
NK027(sha)001:4353: 'bar ba'i rgyal po thub med grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4354: rgyal ba zhi khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dal
NK027(sha)001:4355: phyi'i lha tshogs la rin po che'i gdugs kyi mnga'
NK027(sha)001:4356: gsol bas / thugs rje chen pos gdul bya yongs su skyob cing /
NK027(sha)001:4357: tsha ba'i gdung ba sel ba bdag rgyal mtshan la h'u gi 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:4359: gzi brjid khyad par 'phags pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4360: bde gshegs sku la rgyal mtshan 'di phul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4361: log par lta ba tha dag yongs spang nas //
NK027(sha)001:4362: 'bar ba'i rgyal po thub med 'grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4363: rgyal mtshan gyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK027(sha)001:4364: phas kyi rgol ba thams cad tshar bcad cing mtshan mar lta ba zil gyi gnon pa bdag sogs /
NK027(sha)001:4367: gzi brjid khyad par 'phags pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4368: bder gshegs sku la bla re 'di phul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4369: log par lta ba tha dag yongs spang nas //
NK027(sha)001:4370: 'bar ba'i rgyal po thub med 'grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4372: chos nyid bdal ba chen po yol ba la h'u gi 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:4374: gzi brjid khyad par 'phags pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4375: bde gshegs sku la yol ba 'di phul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4376: log par lta ba tha dag yongs spang nas //
NK027(sha)001:4377: 'bar ba'i rgyal po thub med 'grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4378: rgyal ba zhi khro lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor phyi'i lha tshogs la /
NK027(sha)001:4380: sems kyi d+r+wa ba yongs su gsal ba skyon dang bral nas /
NK027(sha)001:4381: bdag nyid chen po skyob pa bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i 'phan la ham gyi 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:4383: gzi brjid khyad par 'phags pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4384: bde gshegs sku la 'phan 'di phul ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:4385: log par lta ba mtha' dag yongs spangs nas //
NK027(sha)001:4386: 'bar ba'i rgyal po thub med 'grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4388: thams cad bdag nyid chen po rtogs shing thogs pa
NK027(sha)001:4389: med pa'i shes rab bdag man+dala la sa'i 'phro 'du
NK027(sha)001:4391: 'bras bu mtha' yas kun la mnga' brnyes pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:4392: bde gshegs sku la man+dala 'di phul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4393: 'phags pa'i nor gyi dbul ba kun bral nas //
NK027(sha)001:4394: ting 'dzin 'bum phrag yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4395: gling bzhi'i man+dala rin chen spras pa phul bas /
NK027(sha)001:4397: ting 'dzin gyi sgo 'bum phrag la mnga' brnyes pa bdag sogs /
NK027(sha)001:4400: 'bras bu mtha' yas kun la mnga' brnyes pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:4401: bde gshegs sku yul mkhar 'di phul bas na //
NK027(sha)001:4402: 'phags pa'i zhing khams sna tshogs thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4403: rnal 'byor pa bdag gi rgyal ba zhi khro lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dal phyi'i lha tshogs la /
NK027(sha)001:4405: dbul ba sdug bsngal zhi nas /
NK027(sha)001:4406: gzhal yas chen po mnga' brnyes pa gsum dang bran pho mo hri'i 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:4408: gzi brjid khyad par 'phags pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4409: bde gshegs sku la pho mo'i bran phul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4410: log par lta ba tha dag yongs spang nas //
NK027(sha)001:4411: 'khor rnams yongs smin tshogs la dbang byed shog /
NK027(sha)001:4413: 'khor ba yongs su smin pa phun sum tshogs pa la /
NK027(sha)001:4414: dbang bsgyur ba bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i bu pho mo la hri'i 'phro 'du las /
NK027(sha)001:4416: gzi brjid khyad par 'phags pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4417: bde gshegs sku la lcam sring 'di phul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4418: log par lta ba mtha' dag sprul pas 'dul bya don la dbang byed shog /
NK027(sha)001:4419: bu dang bu mo phul bas /
NK027(sha)001:4420: thabs la mkhas pa'i sprul pa mang pos gdul bya
NK027(sha)001:4421: kha lo bsgyur ba dang gar mkhan la yam gi
NK027(sha)001:4423: gzigs brjid khyad par 'phags pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4424: bde gshegs rnams la gar mkhan 'di phul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4425: log par lta ba sgyu rtsal rnam rol ma 'gags spyod par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4426: rgyal ba zhi khro'i lha tshogs rnams /
NK027(sha)001:4427: gar stabs sna tshogs phul bas /
NK027(sha)001:4430: grol ba bdag gzhan thams cad byed par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:4433: gzi brjid khyad bde gshegs sku la gzungs ma 'di phul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4434: log par lta ba mtha' dag gsang spyod yongs su dag pa thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4436: gsang spyod yongs su dag pa snyoms par 'jug pa
NK027(sha)001:4437: bzhi pa mnyes mchod phul bar mnga' gsol ba la
NK027(sha)001:4438: gsum las / ma skyes rdo rje dang /
NK027(sha)001:4439: bdag dang phyogs bral gyi nang gi phyag 'tshal /
NK027(sha)001:4441: chos sku mu mtha' dpag med rigs //
NK027(sha)001:4442: thabs mkhas phyag rgya rgyu 'bras rdzogs //
NK027(sha)001:4443: rang byung rol pa rang snang ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:4444: rang bzhin sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)001:4446: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK027(sha)001:4447: bder gshegs sku la phyag gi mchod 'bul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4448: lha dang bdud rtsi gnyis su med pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4449: don la 'gyur ba'i 'bras bu thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4450: rnal 'byor bdag gi rgyal ba zhi khro yi //
NK027(sha)001:4451: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:4453: dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang gnyis med du mjal ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:4454: mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:4458: h'u h'u tram tram h'u a /
NK027(sha)001:4459: b+ho d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su ka dz+ny+aa na d+hartu +aa /
NK027(sha)001:4464: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK027(sha)001:4467: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
NK027(sha)001:4468: bder gshegs sku la phyag rgya gar 'bul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4469: mi 'da' dam tshig phrin las rol pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4470: phyag rgya bzhi don yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4471: phyag rgya'i mchod pa mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig sgo
NK027(sha)001:4472: nas bdag snang srid kun bzang nam mkha' mdzod sngags
NK027(sha)001:4474: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
NK027(sha)001:4475: snang srid mchod pa phul ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:4476: spyod yul yang dag lha dang dbyer med pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:4477: phyag rgya don rtogs kun nas kun bzang shog /
NK027(sha)001:4478: spyod yul yongs su dag pa snang srid kyi mchod pa phul bas /
NK027(sha)001:4479: dkyil 'khor kun dang dbyer med kun tu bzang po
NK027(sha)001:4480: bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi
NK027(sha)001:4481: ar+g+ham / yang dag don du dang /
NK027(sha)001:4483: rang bzhin spros bral chos sku rnam dag cing //
NK027(sha)001:4484: srid zhu gus pas ar+g+ham 'di phul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4485: phyi nang byang chub sems su rnam dag cing //
NK027(sha)001:4486: bsod nams mi 'dzad gter gyi phul gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:4488: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:4489: ar+g+ham gyi mchod pa phul bas /
NK027(sha)001:4490: spyod lam sgo yongs su dag nas /
NK027(sha)001:4491: bsod nams mi 'dzad pa'i gter bdag dang /
NK027(sha)001:4495: mchod pa rnam par dag pa'i rtags mnga' ba //
NK027(sha)001:4496: bde gshegs sku la bdug spos 'di phul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4497: dam tshig sdom pa'i nyes pa kun bral nas //
NK027(sha)001:4498: ye shes thugs rjes ma lus 'dzin par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4501: theg pa so so'i dam tshig sdom pa'i nyes ltung las grol te /
NK027(sha)001:4502: thugs rje'i ngang gi phyogs bcu'i 'gro ba 'dzin pa'i don bdag me tog sh+r+ai badz+ra push+pe tam /
NK027(sha)001:4503: yon tan lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas sku gzugs la //
NK027(sha)001:4504: rin chen mdzes pa'i me tog 'di phul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4505: log lta'i nyon mongs thal ba kun bral nas //
NK027(sha)001:4506: lta ba'i yi dam mchog gi sku thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:4507: rnal 'byor pa bdag gi rgyal ba zhi khro'i gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:4509: log lta nyon mongs kyi tha ba dang bral te /
NK027(sha)001:4510: bsod nams ye shes kyi sku bdag dang mtha' yas
NK027(sha)001:4511: badz+ra a lo ke h+r+aih thams cad mkhyen pa'i sku
NK027(sha)001:4513: mun pa sel byed mar me 'di 'bul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4514: ma rig 'thib pa'i mun pa kun bral nas //
NK027(sha)001:4515: spyan lnga yongs su dag pa thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4518: lhan gcig skyes pa'i ma rig pa'i mun pa rab tu bsal te /
NK027(sha)001:4519: sangs rgyas kyi spyan lnga bdag dang mtha' dri chab /
NK027(sha)001:4521: snyigs ma lnga dang 'bras bu yongs rdzogs pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:4522: bde gshegs sku la dri chab 'di phul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4523: nyon mongs gdung ba'i zug rngu kun bral nas //
NK027(sha)001:4524: 'od zer mtha' yas 'gyed pa'i sku thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:4526: phyogs bcu'i bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)001:4527: rnal 'byor pa bdag gi rgyal ba zhi khro'i gzugs
NK027(sha)001:4528: brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams la dri chab
NK027(sha)001:4529: phul bas / nyon mongs pa'i zug rngu zhi nas //
NK027(sha)001:4530: 'od zer mtha' yas 'gyed pa'i sku bdag dang sman phyi nang gi zhi khro'i sngags tshar ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:4531: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta dang /
NK027(sha)001:4532: ye shes sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4533: rgyal ba'i sku la bdud rtsi lnga phul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4534: sku lnga gdod nas ye shes lngar dag pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:4535: sku dang ye shes lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4536: bdud rtsi sman gyi mchod pa phul ba yis //
NK027(sha)001:4537: dug lnga ma spang ye shes lngar dag nas //
NK027(sha)001:4538: sku lnga bdag dang gtor ma /
NK027(sha)001:4542: chos rnams longs spyod yongs su dag pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4543: bder gshegs sku la gtor ma 'di phul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4544: rdzas dang spyod pa'i gdung ba kun bral nas //
NK027(sha)001:4545: gsang ba'i longs spyod yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4546: rnal 'byor pa bdag gi rgyal ba zhi khro'i gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:4548: dngos po rdzas kyi gdung ba ye shes su grol nas /
NK027(sha)001:4549: dam rdzas gsang ba'i longs spyod phun sum tshogs pa bdag dang /
NK027(sha)001:4552: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
NK027(sha)001:4553: bde gshegs sku la lhag pa'i ting 'dzin gyi //
NK027(sha)001:4554: mchod pa'i bye brag bsam yas phul ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:4555: phyi nang gsang don ma lus kun rdzogs te //
NK027(sha)001:4556: rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud brnyes nas //
NK027(sha)001:4557: 'bras bu mtha' yas kun la longs spyod shog /
NK027(sha)001:4558: lhag pa'i ting 'dzin gyi mchod pa phul bas /
NK027(sha)001:4559: rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs brnyes pa bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sgrol ba /
NK027(sha)001:4560: ye shes spyod yul yongs su dag pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4561: bde gshegs sku la sta na 'di phul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4562: khams gsum dug gsum rtsad nas dag gyur te //
NK027(sha)001:4563: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4565: sgrol ba'i mchod pa phul bas /
NK027(sha)001:4566: dug gsum rtsad nas gcod de /
NK027(sha)001:4567: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa bdag dang /
NK027(sha)001:4569: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4570: bde gshegs sku la g+ha na 'di phul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4571: snod bcud byang chub sems su rnam dag nas //
NK027(sha)001:4572: mtha' yas snyoms par 'jug pa thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4574: sbyor ba'i mchod pa phul bas /
NK027(sha)001:4576: snod bcud theg pa chen po'i dbyings su dag ste /
NK027(sha)001:4577: bsam yas lhun grub kyi ting 'dzin bdag dang mtha' yas 'dod lnga /
NK027(sha)001:4578: bdag dang mtha' yas 'bral ba med pa'i rgyal ba'i sku la 'dod yon phul ba yi /
NK027(sha)001:4579: mtha' la zhen pa'i gdung ba kun bral nas //
NK027(sha)001:4580: bde ba chen po don rnams rdzogs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4581: rnal 'byor pa bdag gi rgyal ba zhi khro'i gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:4583: mthar 'dzin gyi zhen pa bral nas /
NK027(sha)001:4586: 'khor ba'i rtsa ba 'dod chags zhe sdang dang //
NK027(sha)001:4587: gti mug ma spang rang sar grol ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:4588: khams gsum bag chags gting nas zang phyung ste //
NK027(sha)001:4589: sprul pa sku yi 'khor ba sgrol bar shog /
NK027(sha)001:4590: rak+ta tsha ra gsum phul la /
NK027(sha)001:4591: rgyal ba'i thugs rjes khams gsum gyi dug thams cad
NK027(sha)001:4592: ma spang bar rang sar grol ba bdag gar mchod
NK027(sha)001:4593: / rang bzhin rnam par dag pa rgyal ba'i sku gzugs phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa phul bas /
NK027(sha)001:4594: sku la spyod rol pa chen po'i phrin las kyi rdzu 'phrul thabs kyi 'gro ba'i don byed shog /
NK027(sha)001:4596: phyogs bcu'i gar ye shes kyi mchod pa phul bas /
NK027(sha)001:4597: thabs mkhas rdzu 'phrul gyi thams cad lhun gyis grub nas /
NK027(sha)001:4599: ye shes spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la rol mo 'di phul bas /
NK027(sha)001:4600: bdag dang 'gro ba sems can ma lus kun //
NK027(sha)001:4601: skye 'gags med pa'i don dang 'phrod par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4602: rol mo ye shes kyi mchod pa phul bas /
NK027(sha)001:4603: sgra'i bye brag sna tshogs don mthun du brda' 'phrod cing /
NK027(sha)001:4604: skye 'gags med par bdag dang zhi khro'i lha la tshogs mchod so sor 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:4605: yongs su smin pa phun sum tshogs pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4606: bde gshegs sku la tshogs mchod 'di phul bas //
NK027(sha)001:4607: rdzas su spyod pa'i gdung ba kun bral nas //
NK027(sha)001:4608: gsang ba'i longs spyod yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:4609: rnal 'byor pa bdag gi rgyal ba zhi khro'i gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:4610: longs spyod tshogs kyi mchod pa phul bas /
NK027(sha)001:4611: tshogs rnam pa gnyis yongs su rdzogs pa bdag dang mtha' dbyings kyi de nas bstod pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:4612: e ma hoh mi 'jigs khri la mthing ka rdo rje bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4613: zhe sdang rnam dag rgyal ba badz+ra d+h+rika /
NK027(sha)001:4614: stong nyid ye shes mthar phyin chos kyi sku //
NK027(sha)001:4615: mngon spyod thugs rje dpal la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:4616: stobs ldan khri la dung mdog 'khor lo bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4617: gti mug rnam dag rgyal ba dzi na dzig /
NK027(sha)001:4618: chos dbyings ye shes mthar phyin rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK027(sha)001:4619: thugs rje zhi ba'i dpal la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:4620: rdzu 'phrul khri la gser mdog nor bu bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4621: nga rgyal rnam dag rgyal ba rat+na d+h+rika /
NK027(sha)001:4622: mnyam nyid ye shes mthar phyin rdo rje'i sku //
NK027(sha)001:4623: yon tan rgyas pa'i dpal la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:4624: mdangs ldan khri la le brgan pad+ma bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4625: 'dod chags rnam dag rgyal ba a ro lig /
NK027(sha)001:4626: sor rtogs ye shes mthar phyin byang chub sku //
NK027(sha)001:4627: dbang bsgyur thugs rje dpal la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:4628: thogs med khri la ljang ku rgya gram bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4629: phrag dog rnam dag rgyal ba pra dz+ny+aa d+h+rika /
NK027(sha)001:4630: nan tan ye shes mthar phyin sprul pa'i sku //
NK027(sha)001:4631: las rab grub pa'i dpal la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:4632: ces bstod pa dang de dang kun gyi phyag tu me tog thogs te bskor ba byed cing /
NK027(sha)001:4633: dus kyi 'khrug pa zhi bar gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:4634: mtshon gyi bskal pa nyams par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:4635: mi nad phyug nad rgyun chad par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:4636: char chu dus su 'bab par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:4637: lo phyug rtag tu legs par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:4638: sems can thams cad bde skyid phun sum tshogs pa'i skal ba dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:4639: bla na med pa'i byang chub rin po che thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:4641: de dag ni rab gnas kyi cho ga bsnyen bsgrub
NK027(sha)001:4642: bzhi la nye bsnyen zhag drug yan chad kyi cho
NK027(sha)001:4644: spyi don gsum pa dkyil 'khor bsgrub cing cho ga la /
NK027(sha)001:4651: zhal zas la rol la rtsa ba dang yan lag gi mchod pa rnams so mar bshams /
NK027(sha)001:4655: srid pa phyi nang bcud ces pas bsrung ba'i khro bo'i mtshams bcad /
NK027(sha)001:4656: steng 'og phyogs mtshams kyi gsal gdab /
NK027(sha)001:4658: sgrib pa rnam gnyis kyi gsal gdab /
NK027(sha)001:4661: mthu dang bral zhes pas gsal gdab /
NK027(sha)001:4662: ma tram mnan zhing gsang mtshams bcad /
NK027(sha)001:4663: khro bo bcu'i stang stabs kyi dam sri brtul /
NK027(sha)001:4666: chos rnams ye nas gnyis su med pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4667: byang chub sems su gcig pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:4668: zhag gi zo ris mtshan pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:4669: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK027(sha)001:4670: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad dang //
NK027(sha)001:4671: sangs rgyas kun dang gcig pa 'di //
NK027(sha)001:4672: 'di yang sngon gyi dam tshig go //
NK027(sha)001:4674: ma h+aa mri ta man+dala h'u /
NK027(sha)001:4676: chos rnams ye nas gnyis su med pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4677: byang chub sems su gcig pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:4678: thal chen tshom bu mtshan pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:4679: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK027(sha)001:4680: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad dang //
NK027(sha)001:4681: ging chen kun dang gcig pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:4682: 'di yang sngon gyi dam tshig go //
NK027(sha)001:4684: ma h+aa king ni ri ti dz+wa la man+dala h'u /
NK027(sha)001:4686: chos rnams byang chub sems su rak+ta'i thig les mtshan pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:4687: he ru ka yi dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad dang //
NK027(sha)001:4688: mkha' 'gro kun dang gcig pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:4689: 'di yang sngon gyi dam tshig go //
NK027(sha)001:4691: ma h+aa rak+ta la ka la man+dala h'u /
NK027(sha)001:4692: de nas mchod pa byin gyis rlobs la /
NK027(sha)001:4693: thun mong rdzas zhes pas gsal gdab /
NK027(sha)001:4694: las mkhan gyi khro bo rgyud ltar bskyed la lung gi gsal gdab /
NK027(sha)001:4695: gzhung gi skabs su lha kun bzang yab yum gyi
NK027(sha)001:4696: gtso byas la 'dod don gsal gdab yan chad bya
NK027(sha)001:4700: rigs gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs kyi 'dzab bya /
NK027(sha)001:4701: chos sku nam mkha'i bstod pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:4704: sgo ba yan chad kyi bstod pa bya /
NK027(sha)001:4705: de nas che mchog gi zhal byang byas la /
NK027(sha)001:4707: rang byung khro bo chen po bcu //
NK027(sha)001:4708: bgegs rnams thams cad gzir ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:4709: phyogs mtshams phur pas btab nas ni //
NK027(sha)001:4710: bsrung dang mtshams kyi las mdzod cig /
NK027(sha)001:4720: s+pho ta s+pho ta h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:4721: sum b+ha nis gzir mnan bcad do //
NK027(sha)001:4723: dang po byang chub mchog dang /
NK027(sha)001:4724: dang po skye ba thog ma med pa nas //
NK027(sha)001:4725: rnal 'byor smin pa'i lus 'di yan chad du //
NK027(sha)001:4726: mi dge las kyi 'gro ba'i rgyu bsags pa //
NK027(sha)001:4727: byang zhing dag par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK027(sha)001:4733: bdud rtsi rang byung chen po 'dis //
NK027(sha)001:4734: ye shes lha la gtor byas pas //
NK027(sha)001:4735: bdag dang gnyis su med par 'grub //
NK027(sha)001:4736: dam ldan mched la gtor byas pas //
NK027(sha)001:4737: thugs dam gnyan po bskangs bar gyur //
NK027(sha)001:4738: rnal 'byor pa la gtor byas nas //
NK027(sha)001:4739: rtog sgrib bag chags byang bar gyur //
NK027(sha)001:4740: mi mthun phyogs la gtor byas pas //
NK027(sha)001:4741: drag po gtum po tshogs par 'gyur //
NK027(sha)001:4742: bdag gar ci bzhin bzhag pas na //
NK027(sha)001:4743: byang chub de nyid lhung gnas med //
NK027(sha)001:4744: byang chub sems ni kun tu grags //
NK027(sha)001:4745: thig le chos sku khyab pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:4746: ye nas dbyer med byar mi dgos //
NK027(sha)001:4747: dbyings su gyur na mnyam gnas pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:4749: de nyid byang chub sems su 'gyur //
NK027(sha)001:4751: byang chub sems dpa' rang bzhin bskyed //
NK027(sha)001:4753: kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' klong du //
NK027(sha)001:4754: dam tshig sgrol ma rlung gi rgya gram gtams //
NK027(sha)001:4755: ma ma ki ni rak+ta'i rgya mtsho 'khrugs //
NK027(sha)001:4756: sangs rgyas spyan ni keng rus ri rab bstim //
NK027(sha)001:4757: na bza' dkar mo kun tu drod 'bebs ma //
NK027(sha)001:4758: 'byung lnga yum lnga mtha' yas lhun gyis grub //
NK027(sha)001:4759: b+h+r+aum las bskyed pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK027(sha)001:4760: nam mkha'i dbyings dang mnyam pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4761: tshul bzhin byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK027(sha)001:4762: gzhal yas khang par gyur par bsam /
NK027(sha)001:4768: b+hud+d+ha kro ti shwa ri h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:4772: a kra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:4774: a kra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:4775: ma h+aa mu tra sh+r+ai sha pra ta b+hi shwa
NK027(sha)001:4776: kri ta a nu ta na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa
NK027(sha)001:4778: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa ka ya wak+ka tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK027(sha)001:4779: zhes pas byin gyis brlab bo //
NK027(sha)001:4780: e ma che mchog he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:4781: nyi shu rtsa gcig dbu ni rnam pa lhun gyis grub //
NK027(sha)001:4782: sgrib sbyangs ye shes dbu ni khro chen stobs po che //
NK027(sha)001:4783: dang po rab tu dga' ba'i sa gnon pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:4784: skyon med ye shes dbu ni khams gsum rgyal //
NK027(sha)001:4785: gnyis pa dri ma med pa'i sa ni mnan pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:4786: bdud 'joms ye shes dbu ni bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK027(sha)001:4787: gsum pa 'od 'phros sa ni gnon pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:4788: rtog 'joms ye shes dbu ni 'dod pa'i rgyal //
NK027(sha)001:4789: bzhi pa 'od byed sa ni gnon pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:4790: zil gnon ye shes dbu ni rta mchog dpal //
NK027(sha)001:4791: lnga pa sbyangs daka'i sa ni gnon pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:4792: rnam rtog ye shes dbu ni mi g.yo mgon //
NK027(sha)001:4793: drug pa mngon gyur sa ni gnon pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4794: thabs mkhas ye shes dbu ni gshin rje gshed //
NK027(sha)001:4795: bdun pa ring du song ba'i sa ni gnon pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:4796: stobs ldan ye shes dbu ni dbyug sngon can //
NK027(sha)001:4797: brgyad pa mi g.yo sa ni gnon pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:4798: mkhyen rab ye shes dbu ni rnam par rgyal //
NK027(sha)001:4799: dgu pa legs pa blo gros brjid gnon ye shes dbu ni h'u ka ra //
NK027(sha)001:4800: bcu pa chos kyis sprin gyis mngon song dbu ni yak+sha he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:4801: bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi kun mkhyen dbu ni gu h+ya he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:4802: bcu gnyis rdo rje 'dzin pa'i byams mgon dbu ni sa nu he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:4803: bcu gsum rdo rje 'chang ba'i rngam brjid dbu ni rak+sha he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:4804: bcu bzhi stug po bkod pa'i sa sprul pa'i dbu ni karma he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:4805: bac+wo lnga pad+ma spyan gyi chags med dbu ni pad+ma he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:4806: bcu drug 'khor lo tshogs chen sa yid bzhin dbu ni rat+na he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:4807: bcu bdun d+he wa ko sa 'bar 'phro dbu ni b+hud+d+ha he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:4808: bac+wo brgyad kun nas dbye ba med pa'i stobs ldan dbu ni badz+ra he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:4809: bcu dgu rdzogs pa bla ma'i khyab bdal dbu ni che mchog nyid kyi dbu //
NK027(sha)001:4810: nyi shu srid gsum ngang rdzogs sa gnon pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:4811: byang chub dbu ni rta skad nam mkhar sgrogs //
NK027(sha)001:4812: rtsa gcig ye shes bla ma'i sa gnon pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:4813: g.yas kyi dbu bdun zhal gdangs mche gtsigs pas //
NK027(sha)001:4814: 'khor ba skye 'chi rtsad nas gcod par mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:4815: g.yon gyi dbu bdun zhal gdangs mche gtsigs pas //
NK027(sha)001:4816: 'khor ba'i nyon mongs sdug bsngal zad par byed //
NK027(sha)001:4817: dbus kyi dbu bdun zhal gdangs mche gtsigs pas //
NK027(sha)001:4818: chos nyid klong du thams cad rub par byed //
NK027(sha)001:4819: g.yas kyi spyan bzlog nyi shu rtsa gcig gi //
NK027(sha)001:4820: bdud dang bgegs rigs thams cad thal bar rlog /
NK027(sha)001:4821: g.yon gyi spyan bzlog nyi shu rtsa gcig gi //
NK027(sha)001:4822: ngan song 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal phyag mas 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:4823: dbus kyi spyan bzlog nyi shu rtsa gcig gi //
NK027(sha)001:4824: mi 'gyur chos nyid dbyings su je re gzigs //
NK027(sha)001:4825: mche ba dkar po zangs yag gtsigs pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4826: 'khor ba'i bag chags skye 'chi rtsa ba gcod //
NK027(sha)001:4827: ral pa dmar ser gyen du bardzesa pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4828: chos dbyings ye shes mthar thug 'gran zla med //
NK027(sha)001:4829: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis phyag ni mngon sangs rgyas //
NK027(sha)001:4830: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyis dang po na //
NK027(sha)001:4831: kun tu bzang mo mnyam pa'i phyag rgya bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4832: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi dang po na //
NK027(sha)001:4833: kun tu bzang mo thal mo mnyam sbyar bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4834: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi gnyis pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4835: rnam par snang mdzad gser gyi 'khor lo bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4836: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi gnyis pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4837: sangs rgyas spyan ma gser gyi dril bu bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4838: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi gsum pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4839: rdo rje sems dpa' rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4840: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi gsum pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4841: rdo rje dbyings phyug shel gyi dril bu bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4842: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bzhi pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4843: rin chen 'byung ldan rin chen zur brgyad bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4844: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bzhi pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4845: ma m+aa ki ni g.yu yi dril bu bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4846: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi lnga pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4847: snang ba mtha' yas pad+ma 'dab brgyad bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4848: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi lnga pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4849: na bza' dkar mo byi ru'i dril bu bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4850: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi drug pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4851: don yod grub pa rdo rje rgya gram bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4852: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi drug pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4853: dam tshig sgrol ma mthing gi dril bu bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4854: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bdun pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4855: sa yi snying po rin chen myu gu bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4856: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bdun pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4857: l+aa s+ye dkar mo me long dril bu bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4858: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi brgyad pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4859: nam mkha'i snying po gcod byed ral gri bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4860: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi brgyad pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4861: ma le sngon mo rin chen phreng ba bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4862: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi dgu pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:4863: spyan ras gzigs dbang pad+ma dkar po bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4864: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi dgu pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:4865: g+hirti dmar mo lcags sgrog pi wam can //
NK027(sha)001:4866: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4867: phyag na rdo rje rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4868: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4869: nirti ljang ku dar gyi cod pan bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4870: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu bzhi na //
NK027(sha)001:4871: mgon po byams pa ku shing g+han+d+he bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4872: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu bzhi na //
NK027(sha)001:4873: lha mo d+hush+pe mas ni bdug spos bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4874: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu gnyis na //
NK027(sha)001:4875: sgrib pa rnams sel gsung rab po ti bsnams //
