NK027(sha)001:4876: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu gnyis na //
NK027(sha)001:4877: lha mo pu sh+pe mas ni me tog bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4878: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu gsum na //
NK027(sha)001:4879: kun tu bzang mo rin chen snye ma bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4880: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu gsum na //
NK027(sha)001:4881: lha mo a lo ke ni mar me bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4882: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu bzhi na //
NK027(sha)001:4883: 'jam dpal gzhon nu me tog ut+pala bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4884: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu bzhi na //
NK027(sha)001:4885: lha mo g+han+d+he mas ni dri chab bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4886: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bac+wo lnga na //
NK027(sha)001:4887: gshin rje gshed po thod dbyug dkar po gdengs //
NK027(sha)001:4888: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bac+wo lnga na //
NK027(sha)001:4889: 'gugs byed rta gdong ma ni lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:4890: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu drug na //
NK027(sha)001:4891: bgegs rnams mthar byed rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4892: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu drug na //
NK027(sha)001:4893: 'ching byed zhags pa mas ni zhags pa 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:4894: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu bdun na //
NK027(sha)001:4895: pad+ma mthar phyin thod pa sbrul gyi dkris //
NK027(sha)001:4896: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu bdun na //
NK027(sha)001:4897: bsdams byed nyi zla mas ni lcags sgrog bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4898: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bac+wo brgyad na //
NK027(sha)001:4899: shes rab mthar byed rdo rje rgya gram 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:4900: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bco brgyad na //
NK027(sha)001:4901: thal byed dril bu mas ni dril bu bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4902: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu dgu na //
NK027(sha)001:4903: lha dbang brgya byin sgra snyan dril bu bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4904: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu dgu na //
NK027(sha)001:4905: lha min thag zangs ris ni go cha bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4906: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi nyi shu na //
NK027(sha)001:4907: sh+aakya thub pa bsreg shing par bu bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4908: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi nyi shu na //
NK027(sha)001:4909: parna sha wa ri'i po ti bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4910: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi nyer gcig pas //
NK027(sha)001:4911: kha 'bar ma ni rin chen sgrom bu bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4912: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi tha ma na //
NK027(sha)001:4913: a wa glang mgo me chu grang dro bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4914: zhabs brgyad bsgrad pas khro bo'i dbu brgyad bardzisa //
NK027(sha)001:4915: zhabs brgyad g.yas kyi dang po bsgrad pas na //
NK027(sha)001:4916: thig le chen po'i ting 'dzin chen po dang //
NK027(sha)001:4917: spang ba med par chos kyi dbyings su sbyor //
NK027(sha)001:4918: zhabs brgyad g.yas kyi gnyis pa bsgrad pas ni //
NK027(sha)001:4919: bden pa chen po ting nge 'dzin la ni //
NK027(sha)001:4920: klong du gyur ba'i chos kyi dbyings su sbyor //
NK027(sha)001:4921: zhabs brgyad g.yas kyi gsum pa bsgrad pas ni //
NK027(sha)001:4922: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin la ni //
NK027(sha)001:4923: skye 'chi med pa chos kyi dbyings su sbyor //
NK027(sha)001:4924: zhabs brgyad g.yas kyi tha ma bsgrad pas ni //
NK027(sha)001:4925: thams cad 'byung gnas ting nge 'dzin la ni //
NK027(sha)001:4926: zag pa med pa chos kyi dbyings su sbyor //
NK027(sha)001:4927: zhabs brgyad g.yon gyi dang po bsgrad pas ni //
NK027(sha)001:4928: chags pa med pa ting nge 'dzin la ni //
NK027(sha)001:4929: ye nas dag pa chos kyi dbyings su sbyor //
NK027(sha)001:4930: zhabs brgyad g.yon gyi gnyis pa bsgrad pas ni //
NK027(sha)001:4931: 'da' bar dga' ba'i ting nge 'dzin la ni //
NK027(sha)001:4932: mthong ba med pa chos kyis dbyings su sbyor //
NK027(sha)001:4933: zhabs brgyad g.yon gyi gsum pa bsgrad pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4934: dmigs su med pa'i ting nge 'dzin la ni //
NK027(sha)001:4935: rang bzhin med pa chos kyi dbyings su sbyor //
NK027(sha)001:4936: zhabs brgyad g.yon gyi tha ma bsgrad pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:4937: skye 'chi med pa ting nge 'du 'bral med pa
NK027(sha)001:4938: chos dbu skra khams nag gyen du 'khyil ba ni
NK027(sha)001:4939: // srid pa gsum las rnam par rgyal ba'i rgyan //
NK027(sha)001:4940: rta mgo ljang nag rta skad sgrogs pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:4941: snang srid thams cad dbang du 'du ba'i rtags //
NK027(sha)001:4942: smin ma khro gnyer glog ltar 'gyu ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:4943: ma rig rmongs pa'i mun pa sel ba'i rtags //
NK027(sha)001:4944: tshangs pa'i g.yang gzhi'i na bza' gsol ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:4945: longs spyod rdzogs sku mngon du bstan pa'i rtags //
NK027(sha)001:4946: sku mdog mthing nag 'jigs par bstan pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:4947: chos kyi sku la 'jigs pa med pa'i rtags //
NK027(sha)001:4948: sku smad stag gi sham thabs mnab pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:4949: sprul pa'i sku yi cir yang ston mdzad rtags //
NK027(sha)001:4950: sku stod glang chen ko rlon gsol ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:4951: theg pa rim dgus 'gro don mdzad zhing chen g.yang gzhi sku la gsol ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:4952: thugs rje tshad med bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags //
NK027(sha)001:4953: thod pa skam pos dbu la brgyan pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:4954: dus gsum rgyal bas bsnyen bskur mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK027(sha)001:4955: sbrul nag stong gi gdeng kas brgyan pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:4956: klu rgyal rigs bzhi dbang du bsdu khrag dang zhag gi thig les brgyan pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:4957: ma mo mkha' 'gro dbang du bsdu ba'i rtags bskal pa'i me dpung klong na bzhugs pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:4958: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer 'phro ba'i rtags //
NK027(sha)001:4959: rdo rje'i gshog pa mkha' ltar lding ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:4960: stong gsum 'jig rten zil gyi gnon pa'i rtags //
NK027(sha)001:4961: 'bar ba chen po'i gar dgu'i 'gying bag ni //
NK027(sha)001:4962: che btsan dpe med kun las rgyal ba'i rtags //
NK027(sha)001:4963: khro rgyal che btsan 'bar ba'i zhabs 'og nas //
NK027(sha)001:4964: shin tu rngam pa'i khro mo gnam zhal ma //
NK027(sha)001:4965: sku mdog dud ka sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK027(sha)001:4966: dbu dgu phyag ni bco brgyad zhabs bzhi bsgrad //
NK027(sha)001:4967: rnam thar dbu brgyad gyen du 'byung ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:4968: gsang ba'i thugs rje thabs dang shes rab ldan //
NK027(sha)001:4969: byang chub sems ni bdud rtsi ga'ura bskyil //
NK027(sha)001:4970: 'jam dpal gzhon nus bdud rtsi'i pho brang bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4971: rta mgrin yab yum bdud rtsi'i pho brang bskyil //
NK027(sha)001:4972: stong pa bac+wo brgyad phyag ni mya ngan 'das //
NK027(sha)001:4973: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis //
NK027(sha)001:4974: b+han+d+ha rak+tasa bkang ba rdo rje bkrug /
NK027(sha)001:4975: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yas kyi gnyis pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:4976: ko'u ri b+han dmar zhing gi dbyug to phyar //
NK027(sha)001:4977: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yon gyi gnyis pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4978: seng ha kha ro seng mgo can //
NK027(sha)001:4979: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yas kyis gsum pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4980: tso'u ri ser mo mda' gzhu 'gegs pa bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4981: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yon gyi gsum pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4982: bya kri rna stag stag gi mgo can bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4983: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yas kyi bzhi pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4984: pra mo dmar mo chu srin rgyal mtshan phyar //
NK027(sha)001:4985: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yon gyi bzhi pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4986: sri la byi ldag wa yi mgo can bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4987: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yas kyi lnga pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4988: be ta byi za rdo rje rtse dgu phyar //
NK027(sha)001:4989: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yon gyi lnga pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4990: sho na 'drad lta spyang ki'i mgo can bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4991: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yas kyi drug pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4992: puska dmar ser byis ru 'dran pa bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4993: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yon gyi drug pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4994: kri ta mgrin dmar bya rgod mgo can bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:4995: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yas kyi bdun pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4996: karma dung dmar rdo rje dung khrag 'thung //
NK027(sha)001:4997: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yon gyi bdun pa na //
NK027(sha)001:4998: karma dung dmar rdo rje dung khrag 'thung //
NK027(sha)001:4999: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yon gyi bdun pa na //
NK027(sha)001:5000: kang ka kang phrag dur bya'i mgo can bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:5001: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yas kyi brgyad pa na //
NK027(sha)001:5002: sme sha mthing nag byi snying za ba bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:5003: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yon gyi brgyad pa na //
NK027(sha)001:5004: kha lta kha ro bya rog mgo can bco brgyad phyag gi g.yas kyi mtha' ma na //
NK027(sha)001:5005: tsan d+ha ser skya mgo lus phral ba bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:5006: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yon gyi mtha' ma na //
NK027(sha)001:5007: hu lu lcags kyu 'ug pa'i mgo can bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:5008: zhabs bzhi bsgrad pas rigs bzhi'i dbu na bardzisa //
NK027(sha)001:5009: zhabs bzhi g.yas kyi dang po bsgrad pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:5010: klong du gyur pa gsang ba'i ba ga dang //
NK027(sha)001:5011: bde ba chen po byang chub sems su sbyor //
NK027(sha)001:5012: zhabs bzhi g.yon gyi dang po bsgrad pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:5013: zad stong med pa gsang ba'i ba ga dang //
NK027(sha)001:5014: thams cad 'byung ba'i byang chub sems su sbyor //
NK027(sha)001:5015: zhabs bzhi g.yas kyi gnyis pa bsgrad pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:5016: 'du 'bral med par gsang ba'i ba ga dang //
NK027(sha)001:5017: skye shi med par byang chub sems su sbyor //
NK027(sha)001:5018: zhabs bzhi g.yon gyi gnyis pa bsgrad pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:5019: gdod nas dag pa gsang ba'i ba ga dang //
NK027(sha)001:5020: rdo rje'i lta bu'i byang chub sems su sbyor //
NK027(sha)001:5021: khro mo gnam zhal 'bar ma'i zhabs 'og na //
NK027(sha)001:5022: sku gdung 'bar ba'i dpal chen yab yum bcu //
NK027(sha)001:5023: sngo nag smug nag ser nag dmar nag ljang //
NK027(sha)001:5024: zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi rab tu bsgrad //
NK027(sha)001:5025: rdo rje 'khor yug dung chen gang ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:5026: ral gri thong gshol dgra s+t+wa sna tshogs bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:5027: sbrul dang thod rlon glang chen ko rlon dang //
NK027(sha)001:5028: zhing chen g.yang gzhi stag gi sham thabs dang //
NK027(sha)001:5029: khrag dang zhag dang rak+ta'i thig les brgyan //
NK027(sha)001:5030: bskal pa'i me ri 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs //
NK027(sha)001:5031: gnas yul khro mo bcu drug brjid pas bzhugs //
NK027(sha)001:5032: phyag rgya khro mo bzhis ni sgo bzhi bsrungs //
NK027(sha)001:5033: dbang phyug chen mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad ni //
NK027(sha)001:5034: rang rang rtag dang lag cha sna tshogs dang //
NK027(sha)001:5035: ci bgyi zhes gsol nas ni chas te gnas //
NK027(sha)001:5036: de ltar rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal bkod nas //
NK027(sha)001:5037: snang srid thams cad 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal //
NK027(sha)001:5038: phyogs bcu rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor spyan 'dren la //
NK027(sha)001:5039: 'jigs byed chen po'i dkyil 'khor bzhugs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5040: skad cig gcig la bder gshegs skur ston nas //
NK027(sha)001:5041: byin rlabs mchog dang ldan par mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5042: chos nyid mnyam pa'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK027(sha)001:5043: sku dang ye shes dkyil 'khor rang snang ba //
NK027(sha)001:5044: snang srid thams cad yum gyi sku la rdzogs //
NK027(sha)001:5045: che mchog yab yum rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)001:5046: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa'i sku //
NK027(sha)001:5047: khams gsum sems can thams cad 'dren pa'i dpal //
NK027(sha)001:5048: 'gro drug sems can kun gyi sgrib sbyangs pa //
NK027(sha)001:5049: bdud rtsi rgyal po khyed la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)001:5050: dus gsum 'bar bas skur lngar sbyor //
NK027(sha)001:5051: len pa med cing ston pa med //
NK027(sha)001:5052: rigs lnga dpal chen yab yum bcu //
NK027(sha)001:5054: chu zla lta bur snyog bral zhing //
NK027(sha)001:5055: thams cad rtogs pa yongs kyi spangs //
NK027(sha)001:5056: ko'u ri sing ha ma yi tshogs //
NK027(sha)001:5057: bdud rtsi sbyor la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)001:5058: bdag tu 'dzin med rnam par dag /
NK027(sha)001:5059: bdud dang ngan song gsum las thar //
NK027(sha)001:5060: dbang phyug ma dang ging gi tshogs //
NK027(sha)001:5061: bdud kyi bdud la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)001:5062: a ti p+au hoh ma h+aa pu ru hoh bde bar gshegs pas /
NK027(sha)001:5067: rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK027(sha)001:5068: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK027(sha)001:5069: gnyis med bde chen las byung ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:5070: zas mchog tshe yi dri chen po //
NK027(sha)001:5071: sha chen mchod pa rin po che //
NK027(sha)001:5072: pad+ma me tog yang dag ldan //
NK027(sha)001:5073: rdo rje chu ste bdud rtsi mchog /
NK027(sha)001:5074: ga pur shel gyi spos phor dri //
NK027(sha)001:5075: rin chen me ltar 'bar ba'i tshogs //
NK027(sha)001:5076: yon tan 'bum phrag yangs pa'i bcud //
NK027(sha)001:5077: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK027(sha)001:5078: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK027(sha)001:5079: rgyud lnga sems can kun grol ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:5080: dug lnga sel ba'i thabs mchog ste //
NK027(sha)001:5081: thams cad bdud rtsi'i rnal 'byor che //
NK027(sha)001:5082: ma lus 'dus pa'i thig le che //
NK027(sha)001:5083: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor ba //
NK027(sha)001:5084: gcig tu dpa' bo ro mchog dang //
NK027(sha)001:5085: gnyis su med par mnyam sbyor nas //
NK027(sha)001:5086: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK027(sha)001:5087: rgyal ba rgya mtsho thams cad la //
NK027(sha)001:5088: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam pas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK027(sha)001:5089: thugs rje brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK027(sha)001:5090: ye nas sangs rgyas che mchog he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:5091: sku dang ye shes nyid la dkyil 'khor rdzogs //
NK027(sha)001:5092: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam pas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK027(sha)001:5093: sgyu 'phrul dkyil 'khor ye shes rang snang ba //
NK027(sha)001:5094: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis sangs rgyas rang snang la //
NK027(sha)001:5095: rnam dag 'jam dpal gzhon nu rta mgrin yab yum dang //
NK027(sha)001:5096: srid 'dzin yab yum mnga' bdag lha tshogs la //
NK027(sha)001:5097: rnam dag khro mo gnam zhal ko'u seng bcu drug dang //
NK027(sha)001:5098: yum chen mkha' mnyam klong gi dkyil 'khor la //
NK027(sha)001:5099: rnam dag tshogs rje tshogs bdag dpal chen he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:5100: sku gdung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs la //
NK027(sha)001:5101: rnam dag sgo ma dbang phyug dam can ging gi tshogs //
NK027(sha)001:5102: dbang chen dkyil 'khor kun 'dus lha tshogs la //
NK027(sha)001:5103: rnam dag bsrung dang bskrad dang bsad kyi las mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:5104: rang byung bdud 'dul khro bo bcu rnams la //
NK027(sha)001:5105: rnam dag thugs kyi dngos grub dam pa 'di //
NK027(sha)001:5106: dngos grub med la dngos grub blangs //
NK027(sha)001:5107: byang chub sems kyi spyan 'dren la /
NK027(sha)001:5108: ji ltar dmigs pa bzhin du 'grub //
NK027(sha)001:5109: a ho su ka d+harma ka ya +aahmh'u /
NK027(sha)001:5110: sid+d+hi h+r+aih ma h+aa b+ha lid+ta kh+aa hih ye nas rgyud nyid dag pa la //
NK027(sha)001:5111: nga dang bdag tu rtogs pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:5112: khams gsum 'khor ba'i rgyu ru gyur //
NK027(sha)001:5113: khams gsum thams cad bsgral ba'i zhing //
NK027(sha)001:5114: a tsa ma sa m+aa ya d+har+m+aa d+hartu swa b+h+aa wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK027(sha)001:5115: lus kun yongs su 'khyud pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:5116: rdo rje pad+mara ldan byas nas //
NK027(sha)001:5117: rang byung rnams kyi bde mchog sems //
NK027(sha)001:5118: phul bas myur du 'dzin pa yin //
NK027(sha)001:5119: ra ga pu tsa hoh rgyu drug 'khor ba stong par bsgral slad du //
NK027(sha)001:5120: dug gsum rtsad bcad sha khrag rus pa'i tshogs //
NK027(sha)001:5121: gzung 'dzin rnam rtog kun dang bral ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:5122: mnyam pa chen po'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5123: ma h+aa mam sa la kh+aa hih rak+ta king ni
NK027(sha)001:5124: ri ti dz+wa la kh+aa hih lha mo rol mo
NK027(sha)001:5126: mdzes ldan sgyu ma'i gar dang tshangs pa'i dbyings //
NK027(sha)001:5127: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor rnams la 'bul lags na //
NK027(sha)001:5128: kun tu bzang mo'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5129: ma h+aa pu tsa hoh hoh spros pa med pa'i dbyings /
NK027(sha)001:5131: ye nas lhun gyis grub pa'i rang byung rang snang
NK027(sha)001:5132: gi dkyil 'khor chen po bcom ldan 'das khro bo
NK027(sha)001:5134: che mchog he ru ka dang /
NK027(sha)001:5135: khro mo gnam zhal ma dang /
NK027(sha)001:5136: sku gdung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor la sogs pa rnams mkhyen pa'i byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol /
NK027(sha)001:5137: yab yum thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa
NK027(sha)001:5138: las sprul pa'i sku phyag na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK027(sha)001:5139: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis dkyil 'khor gyi lha mo nyi
NK027(sha)001:5140: shu dang bcas pa mkhyen pas /
NK027(sha)001:5141: dbang mo ging dang bcas pa ye shes dang las
NK027(sha)001:5142: la grub pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa rnams mkhyen
NK027(sha)001:5143: pas hoh rnal 'byor gyi mchod pa longs spyod rdzogs
NK027(sha)001:5144: pa'i tshul du sbyor ba tshogs de la chos nyid
NK027(sha)001:5145: las byung 'phags pa kun tu bzang mo'i mchod pa'i
NK027(sha)001:5146: sprin bsam gyis mi khyab par sprul nas bdag nyid
NK027(sha)001:5147: chen po 'khor dang bcas pa la phud dang gtsang
NK027(sha)001:5149: ye shes la ye shes rol /
NK027(sha)001:5150: chos nyid la chos nyid rol ba'i tshul du bzhes shing longs spyod du gsol /
NK027(sha)001:5152: rdzogs pa'i ye shes rmad po che //
NK027(sha)001:5153: zla gam dkyil 'khor rin chen dbang //
NK027(sha)001:5154: shar gyi phyogs su kha bltas nas //
NK027(sha)001:5156: mchod khang yid bzhin rin po che //
NK027(sha)001:5158: phar 'phros pa ni thugs dam bskul //
NK027(sha)001:5159: slar 'dus pas ni dngos grub stsol //
NK027(sha)001:5160: 'di yang gnyan pa'i mchog yin te //
NK027(sha)001:5161: nam yang nyams pa'i dus mtha' med //
NK027(sha)001:5162: dug gsum dbyings su sbyor bar mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:5163: ces pas bstod pa dal gang byed kyi 'dzab bya /
NK027(sha)001:5164: de nas mchod pa byin rlabs dmigs med kyi spyan drangs la /
NK027(sha)001:5165: gzugs na lag gnyis me long bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:5166: gzugs mdzes kun nas phyogs bcur sprul //
NK027(sha)001:5168: reg ni lag nas g.yon 'khyud ma //
NK027(sha)001:5169: thugs ka ngag tu longs su sbyor //
NK027(sha)001:5170: kun tu sbyor ba bde ba che //
NK027(sha)001:5171: reg ni lha mo sku la 'khril gyi bar brjod /
NK027(sha)001:5172: de nas tshogs gsum du bcad de dang po machodapa 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:5173: rdo rje'i tshogs dang mo k+shi'i tshogs la sogs //
NK027(sha)001:5174: smin ma a 'bras rgun 'brum pa na pe //
NK027(sha)001:5175: na ri ge sar a ri ka la sogs //
NK027(sha)001:5176: de yi tshim byed sna tshogs rnams dang ni //
NK027(sha)001:5177: zla rdzogs yang dag ldan pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:5178: dam rdzas bdud rtsi mchog tu sbyar ba 'di //
NK027(sha)001:5179: bsnam zhing rol te dgongs pas dgongs nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:5180: dbang dang dngos grub bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5183: ma rig 'khrul pas gnod shing 'gyod pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:5184: snyoms las dbang gi yi dam lha spang zhing //
NK027(sha)001:5185: bslu byed rkyen gyi slob dpon snying nas smad //
NK027(sha)001:5186: nga rgyal dreg pas mched dang lcam dral 'khrugs //
NK027(sha)001:5187: lcam la phyar bas gsang tshig gzhan la spel //
NK027(sha)001:5188: ser snas bcangs pas mchod pa lo zlar 'gyang //
NK027(sha)001:5189: khrel 'dzem spangs pas che bas yon tan smad //
NK027(sha)001:5190: drag shul chung bas log 'dren tshar ma chod //
NK027(sha)001:5191: dad 'dun chung bas phrin las zab mo bsrang //
NK027(sha)001:5192: mtshan ngan dri mas gsang ba'i bu tsa tshag /
NK027(sha)001:5193: rngam pas thub thub phud dang lhag ma nyams //
NK027(sha)001:5194: mthong sems barngana chag blang dor gnyis su gyur //
NK027(sha)001:5195: bka' chad rnam grangs gyur pa ci mchis pa //
NK027(sha)001:5196: byang zhing dag par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5197: bdag cag mchod pa chags dang dam tshig nyams //
NK027(sha)001:5198: mchod pa chags pa longs spyod tshogs kyi bskangs //
NK027(sha)001:5199: rtsa ba yan lag nyams 'khrul ci mchis pa //
NK027(sha)001:5200: thams cad tshogs 'dis nyams chags bskangs gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:5202: rdo rje dam can ma lus dgongs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5203: rgyal ba zhi khro'i rjes 'brang mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK027(sha)001:5204: mchod sprin bla med nam mkha'i mtha' thug pa //
NK027(sha)001:5205: phul bas 'di bzhes bdag la skyab mdzod cig /
NK027(sha)001:5206: dus ngan tha mar skyes pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK027(sha)001:5207: rang rig mngon shes mthu dang mi ldan pas //
NK027(sha)001:5208: snod dang skal bar mi ldan slob ma btsud //
NK027(sha)001:5209: mi 'tsham pa la dbang bskur gsang ba bshad //
NK027(sha)001:5210: gsang sngags bcos kyi ngan pa'i rgyu bsags pa //
NK027(sha)001:5211: rjes su 'brang ba khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5212: khyed ni rang rig mthu dang ldan pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:5213: 'gro ba'i skyabs mgon ci bzhin bskul ba bzhin //
NK027(sha)001:5214: thugs rje byams mgon ldan pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK027(sha)001:5215: dad pas rang rig 'phags mchog khyed la mos //
NK027(sha)001:5216: rnal 'byor sku gsum ma thob bar du ni //
NK027(sha)001:5217: lus dang grib ma bzhin du 'grogs bya zhing //
NK027(sha)001:5218: rnal lnga'i mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK027(sha)001:5219: bdag gi bcol ba'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK027(sha)001:5221: de nas khro bo'i 'dzab khang phye la /
NK027(sha)001:5223: b+ho d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su ka h'u h'u h'u
NK027(sha)001:5224: dang rdo rje sems dpa' gnas gyur pa sogs kyi
NK027(sha)001:5226: de nas che mchog dbang gi cho ga'i 'dzab bya /
NK027(sha)001:5227: de nas lung gi he ru ka'i 'dzab bya /
NK027(sha)001:5235: lung gsal btab ste nub mdo'i cho ga bya /
NK027(sha)001:5236: nam langs ma thag lung gi lhag ma dang /
NK027(sha)001:5237: de nas snga dro cho ga 'bring po bya la /
NK027(sha)001:5250: yang na khams gsum ltar gsal gdab /
NK027(sha)001:5251: gsang ba thugs kyis snying po nus tshad bzla /
NK027(sha)001:5252: tha ma gzung thag bzung la gu h+ya dang ru lu bzla /
NK027(sha)001:5256: gung dang dgong mo khro bo bcu'i mtshams bcad /
NK027(sha)001:5257: ye nas mnyam nyid kyi bshags /
NK027(sha)001:5260: zhi khro'i lha sngags kyi gsal gdab /
NK027(sha)001:5261: kun bzang gi mchod pa lnga 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:5262: sngags mtshan bsdus pas zhi khro la /
NK027(sha)001:5267: khro bo la sngags kyi rak+ta 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:5271: b+ho d+hi tsit+ta dang ru lu'i 'dzab bya /
NK027(sha)001:5273: de dag dal zhag gi cho ga ste /
NK027(sha)001:5274: bsgrub pa zhag tu grangs su byed kyang de ltar bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:5275: bzhi pa bsgrub pa chen po ni /
NK027(sha)001:5276: zhag bcu bzhi dbang du byas na bcur 'gro ba'i dgong mo /
NK027(sha)001:5277: phrin las thung ba dang sbrel ma dbang gi sbyin bsreg bya /
NK027(sha)001:5278: tshar ba dang dkyil 'khor mtha' mar phyi'i rdo rje rgya gram bri /
NK027(sha)001:5279: dngos grub kyi zhal zas dang /
NK027(sha)001:5280: sha mar khur ba sogs mched lcam du yod kyi
NK027(sha)001:5281: grangs bas lnga 'gyur gyi lhag pa bya la mar
NK027(sha)001:5284: rdo rje tshe zla khams bkra shis kyi bya la sprod /
NK027(sha)001:5285: gsol sbyong bdud rtsi rlon sbyor /
NK027(sha)001:5287: khur bas bkab pa bsham mo //
NK027(sha)001:5288: de'i nub mo sngon 'gro bsgrub pa'i phrin las rgyas par bya /
NK027(sha)001:5289: mchod pa byin rlabs dus kyi dpal bshos la /
NK027(sha)001:5290: bdag gi thugs ka nas h'u dkar po'i 'phro 'du
NK027(sha)001:5291: 'od du zhu ba las dpal bshos byang chub kyi
NK027(sha)001:5292: sems dkar dmar gyi ngo bo longs spyod sna tshogs
NK027(sha)001:5295: tram rat+na tre lokya s+pha ra na phata /
NK027(sha)001:5296: sam ha ra na h'u gi rat+nasa mchod /
NK027(sha)001:5297: stong phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa thams cad 'byung bar bsam mo //
NK027(sha)001:5298: 'brang rgyas dang tshe lcam lung ltar byin gyis brlab bo //
NK027(sha)001:5299: gsol sbyangs las thugs ka'i h'u gi 'phro 'du las
NK027(sha)001:5300: b+h+r+aum bi shwa b+hi shud+d+he badz+ra na tsakra sur+ya tsan+t+ra
NK027(sha)001:5302: 'khor lo rtsib bzhi mu khyud can du dpal chen
NK027(sha)001:5303: po la ko'u ri brgyad kyi bskor bar bskyed la
NK027(sha)001:5304: / +aahmh'u las dal lha'i 'od zer thams cad la /
NK027(sha)001:5305: phog pas sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bo 'bru gsum du bsam /
NK027(sha)001:5306: de nas che mchog glang po'i dkyil 'khor gzhungs bsrangs /
NK027(sha)001:5309: rol nas slob ma phyir khrus bya /
NK027(sha)001:5311: slob dpon rang nyid dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa'i phyir /
NK027(sha)001:5316: ye shes rgyal po'i gsol ba btab la me tog dor /
NK027(sha)001:5317: badz+ra kro ta sa m+aa ya /
NK027(sha)001:5320: rang gi sgo gsum nas 'od zer dkar dmar mthing gsum 'phros /
NK027(sha)001:5321: lha'i sku gsung thugs la phog /
NK027(sha)001:5323: dkyil 'khor gyi steng na gang mos bla ma bzhugs
NK027(sha)001:5324: pa de lhag par mnyes par bsam nas thal mo
NK027(sha)001:5325: sbyar te / bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa steng rtsa ba'i dal gyi lha tshogs rnams dang /
NK027(sha)001:5326: mkha' 'gro rig pa 'dzin pa thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK027(sha)001:5327: bdag gi sems can thams cad kyi don bya ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:5328: slob ma 'di rnams 'khor ba las yongs su bsgral ba'i slad du /
NK027(sha)001:5329: 'dus pa chen po'i dbang bskur 'tshal gyi bdag ngag
NK027(sha)001:5330: nus pa dang ldan par byin gyis brlabs par mdzad
NK027(sha)001:5331: du gsol / zhes lan gsum byas pas /
NK027(sha)001:5332: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor lha tshogs kyi sku gsung
NK027(sha)001:5333: thugs las 'od zer dkar dmar mthing gsum byung nas
NK027(sha)001:5334: bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum la thim pas sgo
NK027(sha)001:5335: gsum gyi rtogs pa rang rgyud pa dag /
NK027(sha)001:5336: lha rnams dang rang bzhin gnyis su med par bsam /
NK027(sha)001:5338: zhal 'dzum pa dang bcas pas rigs kyi bu phrin las ci dga' bar spyod cing /
NK027(sha)001:5339: zhes gnang ba thob par bsam mo //
NK027(sha)001:5340: de nas lha la dbang rnams rang gi blang ste zhus pas /
NK027(sha)001:5341: rang sku gsung thugs ye shes kyi gzi brjid dang
NK027(sha)001:5342: ldan par bsam la dbang khri'i steng du 'dzeg go
NK027(sha)001:5343: // de nas slob dpon gyi bdag 'jug go /
NK027(sha)001:5344: de nas rgyal thabs kyi gu gul dang /
NK027(sha)001:5345: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i sngags ring gis bgegs bskrad /
NK027(sha)001:5346: slob ma rnams las mkhan gyi sna drangs la ru lu gar gyi bying dang bcas pas /
NK027(sha)001:5347: dkyil 'khor gyi bla ma lan gsum bskor ba byas te /
NK027(sha)001:5349: de nas slob ma dal du 'jug pa'i cho ga bya ste /
NK027(sha)001:5350: 'di la dang po bdag nyid 'jug pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:5351: gnyis pa slob ma khrus dang /
NK027(sha)001:5352: gsum pa mig dgab pa song nas /
NK027(sha)001:5353: bzhi pa slob ma dal du 'jug pa bzod par gsol ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:5354: bla mas thal mo sbyar te /
NK027(sha)001:5355: rdo rje ye shes thob byed pa //
NK027(sha)001:5356: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK027(sha)001:5358: bdag gi slob mar zhugs par bgyi //
NK027(sha)001:5359: bzod par mdzad de dgongs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5361: lha rnams dgyes pas chug cig /
NK027(sha)001:5362: ces pas bka' gnang bar bsam mo //
NK027(sha)001:5364: bu khyod dga' ba ci la dga' //
NK027(sha)001:5365: bu khyod dad pa ci la dad //
NK027(sha)001:5366: khyod kyi dgos pa ci lta bu //
NK027(sha)001:5367: da lta nyid du 'dir smros cig /
NK027(sha)001:5370: bdag ni skal ldan bde chen te //
NK027(sha)001:5372: byang chub sems la bdag dad de //
NK027(sha)001:5373: theg chen chos la bdag mos so //
NK027(sha)001:5374: zhes yan lag gsum pa byas la /
NK027(sha)001:5376: e ma bde chen snying po'i don //
NK027(sha)001:5377: ye nas lhun grub sangs rgyas chos //
NK027(sha)001:5378: khyed kyi rab tu bstan du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5379: ye shes rdo rjes byin rlabs kyi //
NK027(sha)001:5380: rdo rje'i lam nas drang nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:5382: byin rlabs dbang chog blangs bar gyis //
NK027(sha)001:5386: rang byung gdos pas bcing ba phung po 'di //
NK027(sha)001:5387: bdag med rgyal ba'i zhing du sbyor ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:5388: lus sogs rdzas kyi mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK027(sha)001:5389: bla med sman gyi mchod par 'bul lags na //
NK027(sha)001:5390: gnyis su med pa'i tshul gyi dgongs nas su //
NK027(sha)001:5391: blang dor med pa'i tshul gyi bzhes su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5395: slob ma'i glad pa rung khang nang du nyi ma'i 'od kyi lus thams cad khyab /
NK027(sha)001:5396: a yu h'u dzas tshe'i ngo bo mu tig dkar po lta bu /
NK027(sha)001:5397: b+h+r+aum las zla gam sgo bzhi gcig pa'i nang du /
NK027(sha)001:5398: badz+ra kro ta h'u gi h'u ka ra bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:5399: mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis rdo rje khur tshur can /
NK027(sha)001:5400: badz+ra kro ta ar+ya a tsa le mi g.yo bas sgo bsrungs bar bsam /
NK027(sha)001:5401: rang dpal gyi sor mo bcur nyi zla las yig
NK027(sha)001:5402: 'bru bcu las rigs lnga yab yum gyi 'phro 'du
NK027(sha)001:5404: phyogs bcu dus gsum kyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyi /
NK027(sha)001:5405: gang zag 'di dag gi rgyud la yod pa'i las dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:5407: shes rab zhan pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:5408: khyad par du gsang sngags zab mo'i dbang nod pa'i
NK027(sha)001:5409: sgrib pa gang yod pa thams cad skad cig nyid
NK027(sha)001:5410: la byang zhing dag par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:5412: sgrib pa ma lus pa sbyangs pas shes rgyud shel sgong ltar dag par bsam /
NK027(sha)001:5413: badz+ra a we sha ya a a as /
NK027(sha)001:5415: 'od du zhu nas lus bkrag mdangs ldan par bsam /
NK027(sha)001:5416: de nas rang gang mos kyi lhar bskyed la go bsgo /
NK027(sha)001:5418: brgyad pa skyabs su 'gro ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:5419: rdo rje rnal 'byor mchog gi lha //
NK027(sha)001:5421: rdo rje can la phyag 'tshal te //
NK027(sha)001:5422: byams mgon khyed la skyabs su mchi //
NK027(sha)001:5425: sangs rgyas bdag ni thams cad kyi //
NK027(sha)001:5426: gsang ba rdo rje gsum las byung //
NK027(sha)001:5427: khams gsum kun gyi phyag byas pas //
NK027(sha)001:5428: dbang bskur gnang ba chen po sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:5430: dgu pa dam tshig sbyin pa zhu ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:5433: a la la ste mchod pa 'bul //
NK027(sha)001:5434: gsang ba rdo rje gsum las byung //
NK027(sha)001:5435: a la la ste dgyes par mdzod //
NK027(sha)001:5436: a la la ste dam tshig bskangs //
NK027(sha)001:5437: a la la ste dngos grub stsol //
NK027(sha)001:5438: byang chub rdo rje sangs rgyas la //
NK027(sha)001:5439: mchod cing ci ltar mdzad pa ltar //
NK027(sha)001:5440: bdag kyang rab tu bsgral slad du //
NK027(sha)001:5441: nam mkha' rdo rje bdag la stsol //
NK027(sha)001:5444: badz+ra a mri ta ma ti tir man+dala /
NK027(sha)001:5447: rdo rje lce thog tu bzhag la /
NK027(sha)001:5448: dam tshig snod du ldan par bsam mo //
NK027(sha)001:5450: de nas dam tshig pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:5451: dpal ldan rdo rje sku gsung thugs 'chang ba /
NK027(sha)001:5452: rdo rje mi phyed sku gsung thugs dang ldan //
NK027(sha)001:5453: deng bdag sangs rgyas sku gsung thugs 'dzin pa //
NK027(sha)001:5454: rdo rje sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:5455: +aahmh'u sa ma ya dzah dam tshig sdom pa chen po ni //
NK027(sha)001:5456: sngon gyi rgyal ba rnams kyi thugs //
NK027(sha)001:5457: da lta nga yi snying la gnas //
NK027(sha)001:5458: da ni mched lcam rnams kyi srog /
NK027(sha)001:5461: rdo rje snying khar bzhag la /
NK027(sha)001:5462: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba 'di //
NK027(sha)001:5463: dam nyams ma 'dres gang la ni //
NK027(sha)001:5464: nam yang smra bar ma byed cig /
NK027(sha)001:5465: theg pa chen po ston byed pa //
NK027(sha)001:5466: nga la brnyas dang smad mi rung //
NK027(sha)001:5467: sku gsung thugs la rten gnas te //
NK027(sha)001:5468: ma lus sems can don gyis shig /
NK027(sha)001:5469: bcu gcig pa mna' chu ni /
NK027(sha)001:5470: tsan+dana dkar dmar sbyar ba'i chu rdo rje gnod sbyin du bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:5471: dam tshig ma bsrung ba'i nyes dmigs brjod pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:5472: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK027(sha)001:5473: dam tshig 'das nas bsreg par byed //
NK027(sha)001:5474: rdo rje khro bo chen por gyur //
NK027(sha)001:5475: rdo rje'i chu ni btung bar gyis //
NK027(sha)001:5476: badz+ra yak+sha h'u gi lan gsum dang /
NK027(sha)001:5478: de lta bas na bu khyod kyi //
NK027(sha)001:5479: dam tshig 'di dag bsrung bar gyis //
NK027(sha)001:5480: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub 'byung //
NK027(sha)001:5481: rdo rje bdud rtsi'i chu 'thung cig /
NK027(sha)001:5482: badz+ra u ta ka thas sbyin /
NK027(sha)001:5484: rgyal bas gsung pa'i ye shes gang //
NK027(sha)001:5485: de ring dngos grub mchog tu gsungs //
NK027(sha)001:5486: dam tshig che ba'i chen mo mchog /
NK027(sha)001:5487: bye brag med par khyed kyi spyod //
NK027(sha)001:5488: dge dang mi dge'i chos rnams la //
NK027(sha)001:5489: lhag par bsnyan par mi bya ste //
NK027(sha)001:5490: mnyam nyid rin chen klong bzhugs nas //
NK027(sha)001:5491: ci la'ang thog pa med par spyod /
NK027(sha)001:5493: kye ma rgyal ba'i rigs su gyur pa'i bu khyod rnams /
NK027(sha)001:5494: rdo rje slob dpon snying ltar khur //
NK027(sha)001:5495: rdo rje mched la mig bzhin gyis //
NK027(sha)001:5496: yi dam lha ni snying ltar khur //
NK027(sha)001:5497: gsang ba'i dam tshig rang mtshang ltar //
NK027(sha)001:5498: nam yang de bzhin sems par gyis //
NK027(sha)001:5499: sems can thams cad bu ltar zung //
NK027(sha)001:5500: rgyal ba'i bka' las ma 'da' zhig /
NK027(sha)001:5501: bcu gnyis mna' dgag pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:5502: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:5503: dam tshig sdom pa chen po ni //
NK027(sha)001:5504: lha rnams dang ni mi rnams dang //
NK027(sha)001:5505: bsgrub pa po dang rnal 'byor pa //
NK027(sha)001:5506: de dag nyams na khrag chen po //
NK027(sha)001:5507: nyams pa'i snying nas drag ste 'thung //
NK027(sha)001:5508: e dan te na ra kan /
NK027(sha)001:5509: bcu gsum pa rin po che'i me tog dor ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:5510: me tog la sogs rin chen phreng //
NK027(sha)001:5511: sngon tshe ye shes bsnyen pa'i lha //
NK027(sha)001:5512: thugs rjes bzung bar dgongs nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:5513: gang yin de la bab gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:5514: pra ti dza badz+ra hoh rigs gang la phog brtags /
NK027(sha)001:5515: bcu bzhi pa lha dbab ste /
NK027(sha)001:5516: lha gang la phog pa de dag gi phyag rgyas snying gi dkyil du bstim /
NK027(sha)001:5517: bco lnga pa lha yi spang ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:5519: dad med nyams na phung bar 'gyur /
NK027(sha)001:5521: gang zhig gi phyag rgya 'di spang na /
NK027(sha)001:5522: lha spang dge spyod don med 'gyur /
NK027(sha)001:5525: bdag nyid lha dang mnyam sbyor ni //
NK027(sha)001:5527: lha yi sku nyid gsal bsgom na //
NK027(sha)001:5529: de nyid chu zla'i tshul shes na //
NK027(sha)001:5530: ye shes tshogs chen rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK027(sha)001:5532: bcu drug pa mig dbye ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:5534: de ring dad pa'i shugs kyi ni //
NK027(sha)001:5536: sangs rgyas gsung gi rigs su 'khrungs //
NK027(sha)001:5537: sangs rgyas dngos grub thams cad ni //
NK027(sha)001:5538: rten nas thob par gyur ba yin //
NK027(sha)001:5539: badz+ra tsak+shu pra we sha ya phata /
NK027(sha)001:5541: ma rig pa'i mun pa bsal nas /
NK027(sha)001:5542: ye nas rang la gsal ba'i dkyil 'khor mthong ba bsam /
NK027(sha)001:5543: bcu bdun pa dkyil 'khor lha'i don rtags bshad pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:5544: chos kyi dbyings spros pa thams cad dang bral ba'i rtags su lte ba zlum po /
NK027(sha)001:5545: ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i rtags su 'khor lo rtsib bzhi lte ba dang lnga /
NK027(sha)001:5546: ye nas rgyu 'bras dbyer med pas rdo rje'i ra ba /
NK027(sha)001:5547: tshad med bzhi dang ldan pas gru chad bzhi /
NK027(sha)001:5548: lhag pa'i ye shes phrin las bzhi dang ldan pa'i glo 'bur bzhi /
NK027(sha)001:5549: che ba'i yon tan phyogs med du rgyas pas gru bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK027(sha)001:5550: ting nge 'dzin bzhi dang ldan pas sgo bzhi /
NK027(sha)001:5551: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i dur khrod kyi thod
NK027(sha)001:5552: pa skam rlon gnam lcags 'dzer chen gyi bsdam pa
NK027(sha)001:5553: / 'khor ba ma spangs gnas su dag pas zhing lpags kha sbyor gyi sgo /
NK027(sha)001:5559: gza' chen brgyad kyi gdung ma /
NK027(sha)001:5560: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi lcam /
NK027(sha)001:5562: de dag gi dur khrod 'bar ba'i rtags so //
NK027(sha)001:5563: ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i rtsig pa lnga rin po che'i ka ba /
NK027(sha)001:5564: rin chen gdung brgyad bsnol ma /
NK027(sha)001:5565: rin chen sna tshogs kyi dral phyam mo //
NK027(sha)001:5566: dmigs pa'i mun pa sel bas zla phyed rdo rje'i
NK027(sha)001:5567: gdung sgo gzhig par mi nus pa'i bcu gzhi rdo
NK027(sha)001:5568: rje'i bsdom pa / che ba'i yon tan yongs su ma 'gags pa'i mda' yab dkar po /
NK027(sha)001:5569: chos rnams lhun gyis grub cing /
NK027(sha)001:5570: theg pa brgyad nas bsgrod pa'i rta bab brgyad /
NK027(sha)001:5572: mtshan rtog dang bral ba'i 'khor lo /
NK027(sha)001:5576: dpag bsam gyi shing thams cad la dbang bsgyur ba'i me ri'i phreng ba'o //
NK027(sha)001:5577: lha'i de nyid ni me tog phog pa la sogs
NK027(sha)001:5578: pa lha'i snying po mtshan rigs sku mdog phyag mtshan
NK027(sha)001:5579: rnams bstan te nges par byas pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:5580: cho ga de dag tshar ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:5581: de nas 'bras bu dngos grub blangs pa'i rim pa nas /
NK027(sha)001:5582: thog mar 'byung po lta nyan tshar bcad pa'i phyir /
NK027(sha)001:5583: khro bcu'i mtshams drag tu bcad /
NK027(sha)001:5584: lha dang mkhon sbyang ba'i phyir bshags pa bya /
NK027(sha)001:5585: 'gro don mthar 'byung ba'i phyir dam bca' blangs /
NK027(sha)001:5586: rang nyid gzi brjid bskyed pa'i phyir 'di byin dbab /
NK027(sha)001:5587: rigs lnga'i dngos grub blangs pa'i phyir /
NK027(sha)001:5590: nga ni dpal ldan rdo rje 'chang //
NK027(sha)001:5593: nyid kyi bka' bzhin spyan 'dren na //
NK027(sha)001:5594: dam tshig tshul bzhin gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5595: dam tshig tshul bzhin ma gshegs cing //
NK027(sha)001:5596: bsgrub mchog dngos grub ma stsal na //
NK027(sha)001:5598: dam tshig mchog la dgongs nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:5599: thugs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5604: nyid kyi bka' bzhin spyan 'dren na //
NK027(sha)001:5605: dam tshig tshul bzhin gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5606: dam tshig tshul bzhin ma gshegs kyang //
NK027(sha)001:5607: bsgrub mchog dngos grub ma stsol na //
NK027(sha)001:5609: dam tshig mchog la dgongs nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:5610: sku yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5612: nga ni dpal ldan rin chen 'byung //
NK027(sha)001:5615: nyid kyi bka' bzhin spyan 'dren na //
NK027(sha)001:5616: dam tshig tshul bzhin gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5617: dam tshig tshul bzhin ma gshegs kyang //
NK027(sha)001:5618: bsgrub mchog dngos grub sku gsung thugs dang dam tshig mchog la dgongs nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:5619: yon tan dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5624: nyid kyi bka' bzhin spyan 'dren na //
NK027(sha)001:5625: dam tshig tshul bzhin gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5626: dam tshig tshul bzhin ma gshegs cing //
NK027(sha)001:5627: bsgrub mchog sku gsung thugs dang dam tshig mchog la dgongs su gsung gi dngos grub h'u /
NK027(sha)001:5628: nga ni dpal ldan karma phrin las dkyil 'khor karma
NK027(sha)001:5629: 'chang karma khrag 'thung nyid kyi bka' dam tshig tshul
NK027(sha)001:5631: dam tshig tshul bzhin bsgrub mchog dngos grub ma stsal na //
NK027(sha)001:5632: sku gsung thugs dang dam tshig mchog la dgongs nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:5633: las kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5635: dngos grub kyi snod du rung bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK027(sha)001:5636: nam mkha' mtha' klas chos kyi dbyings kyi khyab //
NK027(sha)001:5637: ma chags spyan mnga' ma bsgrub ye shes gsal //
NK027(sha)001:5638: kun nas kun tu dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5639: rdo rje'i zhags kyang tshangs lags so //
NK027(sha)001:5640: bzlas brjod grangs kyang tshangs lags so //
NK027(sha)001:5641: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus 'di lags //
NK027(sha)001:5642: 'gro ba mang po bdag gi bsgral //
NK027(sha)001:5643: bla med byang chub bdag gi bsgrub //
NK027(sha)001:5644: mthu chen mthu stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK027(sha)001:5645: dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK027(sha)001:5646: bdag gi las kyi 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK027(sha)001:5647: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK027(sha)001:5648: khro la khros pa zhi mdzad pa /
NK027(sha)001:5649: thugs rjes 'bar da ltar ru lu mnyam pa'i don la ma skyes gnyis med phyir //
NK027(sha)001:5650: dngos grub stsal dang rtsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK027(sha)001:5651: rig dang ma rig sgyu ma'i khyad par gyis //
NK027(sha)001:5652: sgyu ma'i spyod tshul mnyam par ma grub cing //
NK027(sha)001:5653: rgyal ba'i dgongs spyod klong du ma gyur bas //
NK027(sha)001:5654: log rtog srin po'i zhen pa ma bzlog na //
NK027(sha)001:5655: mkhyen rab ting 'dzin dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5656: chags pa'i nad kyi gdung ba'i sdug bsngal las //
NK027(sha)001:5657: bdud dang srin po zhe sdang glo bur gyi //
NK027(sha)001:5658: sgyu ma'i lus srog tshe la bar chod na //
NK027(sha)001:5659: khro rgyal mthu yi zil gyi mnan pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:5660: rdzu 'phrul lam mchog dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5661: gsung rab rgya mtsho bdud rtsi'i char phab na //
NK027(sha)001:5662: bag chags skyon gyi dri mas rmongs pa la //
NK027(sha)001:5663: shes shing rtogs pa'i shes rab mi ldan na //
NK027(sha)001:5664: shes bya thog med dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5665: 'bad pas brtsal ba'i dus gsum dge bshes te //
NK027(sha)001:5666: srid la phan 'dog ston pa'i dpal mgon lags //
NK027(sha)001:5667: drin la lan log gang lags ma 'tshal na //
NK027(sha)001:5668: sems kyi mngon shes dngos grub rnam rtog zhan pa'i bag chags 'thug po yi //
NK027(sha)001:5669: dus gsum chos rnams mun pa'i rdzas ltar sgrib //
NK027(sha)001:5670: dus gsum dge bshes drin la lan blan phyir //
NK027(sha)001:5671: dus la rmongs pas sems can don bskyid ni //
NK027(sha)001:5672: mngon shes drug gi rgyu drug rim gyi grangs med don slad du //
NK027(sha)001:5673: khams gsum ma lus khyab par 'gro ba'i tshe //
NK027(sha)001:5674: sems kyi gdos su bdag gi lus mchis na //
NK027(sha)001:5675: thogs med rkang mgyogs dngos grub log rtog mang pos shes rgyud g.yeng ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:5676: ston pa'i gsungs pa'i bka' brgyud ci snyed pa //
NK027(sha)001:5677: don dang yi ge brjod med ma bsam na //
NK027(sha)001:5678: mi brjed gzungs kyi dngos grub rang nyid rnam rtog las kyi dbang gyur cing //
NK027(sha)001:5679: sdug bsngal mang po'i bcing ba'i 'gro ba rnams //
NK027(sha)001:5680: 'dul thabs mang pos 'gro ba'i don bgyid kyi //
NK027(sha)001:5681: rnam bzhi las kyi dngos rang gi rnam rtog las kyi dbang gyur zhing //
NK027(sha)001:5682: blang dor med pa'i don la thugs brtse'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:5683: so so'i blo la ci ltar 'thad pa bzhin //
NK027(sha)001:5684: mthun 'jug thabs kyi 'gro ba 'dul byas kyi //
NK027(sha)001:5685: sa na yo ga pra'i dngos dus gsum zhan pa 'gro ba'i gcung snying nas //
NK027(sha)001:5686: 'tsho byed sman pa'i rgyal po bcos su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5687: sku gsung thugs kyis dngos grub dam pa ste //
NK027(sha)001:5688: dur khrod rdzas la brten nas bdag la stsol //
NK027(sha)001:5689: skya rengs dang po dngos grub dus la bab //
NK027(sha)001:5690: khrag 'thung 'khor bcas dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5691: khams gsum dreg pa ma lus 'tshal bar gyis //
NK027(sha)001:5692: bcom ldan dpal chen dngos grub ye shes thabs kyis 'gro don kun gyis kyi //
NK027(sha)001:5693: khro mo brgyad kyi dngos grub dur khrod rol pa'i khams gsum dbang bsdud kyi //
NK027(sha)001:5694: phra men brgyad kyi dngos phrin las rnam bzhis 'gro don sdud lags kyis //
NK027(sha)001:5695: khro bo bcu'i dngos grub sprul pa mang pos sems can kun 'dul phyir //
NK027(sha)001:5696: yang sprul snying sprul dngos grub ru lu bazla'o //
NK027(sha)001:5697: de nas rig 'dzin gyi dngos grub blang na ni /
NK027(sha)001:5699: chos nyid bde ba chen po'i sku byung ba //
NK027(sha)001:5700: bcom ldan che mchog yab yum dngos dur khrod dreg pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:5701: sgyu lus khro rgyal yab yum dngos ye shes 'bar ma brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)001:5702: ko'u ri khro mo brgyad kyi chos nyid mkha' ltar dag pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)001:5703: seng ha phra men brgyad kyi tshad med bzhi rtogs gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)001:5704: rta gdong sgo ma bzhi yi 'bar ba'i bar khyams dur khrod rol pa nas //
NK027(sha)001:5705: spor ma gsang yum tshogs bcas dam tshig lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)001:5706: dbang phyug ma sring tshogs kyis dur khrod 'bar ma chen mo'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)001:5707: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis dngos grub stsol //
NK027(sha)001:5708: phrin las myur mgyogs chen mo'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)001:5709: ma bdun sring bzhi'i sgrol byed rab tu 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)001:5710: sgrol byed ging chen bco brgyad zhe sdang 'bar ba thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)001:5711: khro rgyal srin po ci bgyis bka' nyan gyi //
NK027(sha)001:5712: pho nya sder mo'i tshogs kyi dngos las rnams yongs su grub pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)001:5713: ye shes ma mo'i tshogs kyis rdo rje bsdam pa'i sa la gnas pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:5714: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang tshogs kyi gnas mchog yan lag don gyi 'jig rten nas //
NK027(sha)001:5715: rgyal ba kun bzang dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5716: 'og min dbang phyug chen po'i gnas mchog nas //
NK027(sha)001:5717: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK027(sha)001:5718: rdo rje sems dpa' rigs lnga yab yum bcas //
NK027(sha)001:5719: longs spyod rdzogs pa sku yi dngos grub stsol //
NK027(sha)001:5720: lha klu gnod sbyin so so'i gnas mchog nas //
NK027(sha)001:5721: bcom ldan rigs gsum mgon po'i o rgyan d+ha na ko sha'i gling phug tu //
NK027(sha)001:5722: rdor sems sprul pa dga' rab rdo rje dang //
NK027(sha)001:5723: rgyal po'i bu mo rin chen gsal sgron la //
NK027(sha)001:5724: rdor sems gsang ba'i bdag po mngon byon nas //
NK027(sha)001:5725: dbang bzhi rdzogs bskur rtogs tshogs lha ngo 'phrod //
NK027(sha)001:5726: dbang rtags chags zhing me long rnams gnyis byon //
NK027(sha)001:5727: rig 'dzin khri phrag du ma sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:5728: de yi dngos grub deng 'dir stsal du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:5729: rgya bod gnyis kyi so mtshams su //
NK027(sha)001:5730: ma ga ta yi brag phug tu //
NK027(sha)001:5731: u rgyan rgyal po d+harma ka ya ni //
NK027(sha)001:5732: klu yi rgyal po'i bu mo yi //
NK027(sha)001:5733: dga' rab rdo rje spyan drangs nas //
NK027(sha)001:5734: tshom bu stong gi dkyil 'khor bsgrub //
NK027(sha)001:5735: khri phrag du ma sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:5736: de yi dngos grub deng 'dir rgya gar za hor yul gyi mtshams //
NK027(sha)001:5738: rgyal po in+d+ra bo d+hi dang //
NK027(sha)001:5739: sras mo ni lan d+ha ra gnyis //
NK027(sha)001:5740: tshom bu lnga yi dkyil 'khor bsgrub //
NK027(sha)001:5741: khri phrag du ma sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:5742: de yi dngos grub deng rgya gar sid+ha gnyis kyi mtshams //
NK027(sha)001:5743: g.yu mtsho gling dgu'i brag phug tu //
NK027(sha)001:5744: sing ha u pa ra tsa dang //
NK027(sha)001:5745: sras mo g+ho ma de wa gnyis //
NK027(sha)001:5746: tshom bu lnga bcu'i dkyil 'khor bsgrub //
NK027(sha)001:5747: brgya phrag du ma sangs rgyas pa /
NK027(sha)001:5748: de yi dngos grub deng rgya gar yul dbus ma ga ta //
NK027(sha)001:5749: bar na sa'i gnas rab tu //
NK027(sha)001:5750: dge slong mi phyed seng ge dang //
NK027(sha)001:5751: srin po'i bu mo na shi gnyis //
NK027(sha)001:5752: tshom bu gsum pa'i dkyil 'khor bsgrub //
NK027(sha)001:5753: 'khor ni lnga brgya sangs rgyas te //
NK027(sha)001:5754: de yi rgya gar bal po so mtshams su //
NK027(sha)001:5755: dge slong so skya de wa dang //
NK027(sha)001:5756: lha mo bkra shis dngos grub gnyis //
NK027(sha)001:5757: tshom bu bcu pa'i dkyil 'khor bsgrub //
NK027(sha)001:5758: de yi dngos rgya dang bal po yul gyi mtshams //
NK027(sha)001:5759: yang le shod kyi brag phug tu //
NK027(sha)001:5761: bal mo gza' yi sh+aakya gnyis //
NK027(sha)001:5762: tshom bu lnga yi dkyil 'khor bsgrub //
NK027(sha)001:5763: de yi rgya gar stag gzigs yul gyi mtshams //
NK027(sha)001:5764: yang le e ri'i brag phug tu //
NK027(sha)001:5765: slob dpon sti ra ma ti dang //
NK027(sha)001:5766: bu mo g+ha ga sid+d+hi gnyis ji ltar bsgrub cing rten pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:5767: de yi bod dang zhang zhung yul gyi mtshams //
NK027(sha)001:5768: gangs dkar ti se'i brag phug tu //
NK027(sha)001:5769: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:5770: lha mo dmar mo chos mtsho gnyis //
NK027(sha)001:5771: ji ltar bsgrub cing rten pa'i tshe //
NK027(sha)001:5772: de yi dngos mon bod gnyis kyi so mtshams su //
NK027(sha)001:5773: spa gro stag tshang seng ge phug /
NK027(sha)001:5774: slob dpon nam mkha'i snying po dang //
NK027(sha)001:5775: mkhar chen gaza'i mtsho rgyal gnyis //
NK027(sha)001:5776: ji ltar bsgrub de yi bod khams gtan ri'i brag phug tu //
NK027(sha)001:5777: slob dpon rgyal ba blo gros dang //
NK027(sha)001:5778: lha mo sum za ser mo gnyis //
NK027(sha)001:5779: ji ltar de'i bod yul gtsang gi g.yas ru'i phyogs //
NK027(sha)001:5780: nyug gi rdo rje sgrom bu ru //
NK027(sha)001:5781: gnub ban sangs rgyas ye shes kyi //
NK027(sha)001:5782: rang byung thig le nyag gcig don //
NK027(sha)001:5783: zla ba dgu pa'i sems nyid don //
NK027(sha)001:5784: dngos po'i gnas lugs gtan la phab //
NK027(sha)001:5785: ci ltar bsgrub cing de yi dngos grub deng 'dir stsol //
NK027(sha)001:5786: khung lung yon tan rgya mtsho ni //
NK027(sha)001:5787: thugs sras nang nas mchog tu gyur //
NK027(sha)001:5788: sprul pa mang po zhal gzigs pa //
NK027(sha)001:5789: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub brnyes //
NK027(sha)001:5790: de yi bsgrub gnas phyar sham dgon pa ru //
NK027(sha)001:5791: so ni ye shes dbang phyug gis //
NK027(sha)001:5792: chos nyid don dam thugs su chud //
NK027(sha)001:5793: rdzogs chen lta ba'i bka' yang phab //
NK027(sha)001:5794: de yi dngos shol yag gding gi gnas mchog tu //
NK027(sha)001:5795: dbang bzhi chu bo'i bka' bab pa //
NK027(sha)001:5796: sru ni legs pa'i sgron ma ni //
NK027(sha)001:5797: dge byed bco lnga'i slob bu smin //
NK027(sha)001:5798: de de dag nang nas zhu'i rus //
NK027(sha)001:5799: bsod nams sh+aakya zhes su grags //
NK027(sha)001:5800: de yi bod yul gtsang gi ru lags phyogs //
NK027(sha)001:5801: 'ug pa lung gi yang dben du //
NK027(sha)001:5803: bka' lung brgyud pa man ngag la //
NK027(sha)001:5804: phul byung shes bya ma lus mkhyen //
NK027(sha)001:5805: de yi g.yas ru rgya bo dge gnas su //
NK027(sha)001:5806: zur chung shes rab grags pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:5807: lta dgongs rtse mo phul du gyur //
NK027(sha)001:5808: snang brag sgyu mar mkhyen pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:5809: skal ldan gdul bya smin grol mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:5810: de'i g.yas ru chu bar li thung du //
NK027(sha)001:5811: glan ston sh+aakya bzang po ni //
NK027(sha)001:5812: snang srid lha 'dre bran du khol //
NK027(sha)001:5813: phrin las spyod pa thogs pa med //
NK027(sha)001:5814: de'i shang gi nya tshal khang stod du //
NK027(sha)001:5815: lha rje sh+aakya byang chub ni //
NK027(sha)001:5816: rdzogs chen lta ba phul du phyin //
NK027(sha)001:5817: shes bya thogs med ma lus mkhyen //
NK027(sha)001:5818: de'i 'og gdung lha rje 'gar zhes grags //
NK027(sha)001:5819: ye shes mkha' 'gro'i byin brlab pas //
NK027(sha)001:5820: zag med bde ba'i nyams dang ldan //
NK027(sha)001:5821: de'i 'chum gyi 'chad dgon gnas mchog tu //
NK027(sha)001:5822: sreg ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan ni //
NK027(sha)001:5823: yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab mnga' //
NK027(sha)001:5824: dbang gi chu bo'i bka' rnams rdzogs //
NK027(sha)001:5825: de'i sha ri rgya gar gling chung du //
NK027(sha)001:5826: mkhas pa klan ban rdo rje 'od //
NK027(sha)001:5827: gsang bdag zhal gzigs dus gsum mkhyen //
NK027(sha)001:5828: sham pa lar gshegs gdul bya 'dren //
NK027(sha)001:5829: de'i dam chos 'byung gnas sha ri mor //
NK027(sha)001:5830: glan ston brtson 'grus ye shes ni //
NK027(sha)001:5831: gdul bya yang dag sa la 'god //
NK027(sha)001:5833: de yi gung thang dpal gyi dgon pa ru //
NK027(sha)001:5834: mkhas pa bsod nams rgyal po yi //
NK027(sha)001:5835: dbang gi 'gro ba du ma smin //
NK027(sha)001:5836: de yi sprul sku lha rjes lha 'bum gyi //
NK027(sha)001:5837: drag po'i gdul bya mang po smin //
NK027(sha)001:5838: de yi glan ston chos kyi seng ge ni //
NK027(sha)001:5839: ting 'dzin dgongs pa drod dang ldan //
NK027(sha)001:5840: de yi rdza lung dpal gyi dgon pa ru //
NK027(sha)001:5841: dbang bzhi rdzogs pa sangs rgyas dpal //
NK027(sha)001:5843: de yi gnas mchog gung thang yang dben du //
NK027(sha)001:5844: glang chen bsod nams mgon po ni //
NK027(sha)001:5845: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyiis dbang bka' bab //
NK027(sha)001:5846: dbang mchog chu bo'i smin grol mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:5847: de yi dben gnas bye ma seng ge ru //
NK027(sha)001:5848: chos bdag 'bram ston rdo rje ni //
NK027(sha)001:5849: rgyud lung man ngag kun la mkhas //
NK027(sha)001:5850: de yi dngos grub deng 'dir stsol //
NK027(sha)001:5851: bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun yang dben du //
NK027(sha)001:5853: kun mkhyen 'jig rten gsum gyiis mgon //
NK027(sha)001:5854: de yi dngos grub deng 'dir stsol //
NK027(sha)001:5856: ye shes lha'i dngos grub blangs ba'i phyir /
NK027(sha)001:5857: gsal shing gi ri mo la /
NK027(sha)001:5858: spyan drang mchod dang bzlas pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:5859: bstod dang smon lam mjug bsdu drug /
NK027(sha)001:5861: dang po 'brang rgyas la gsal shing mtho dman rim pa bcu bzhi bya /
NK027(sha)001:5862: de nas pho brang dpal gyi mar me bkod pa de /
NK027(sha)001:5864: dbang bskur byin rlabs kyi snyan gsan dbab /
NK027(sha)001:5865: dal gyi lha tshogs nyid spyan drangs /
NK027(sha)001:5866: bstim bstan la spyan drangs pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:5868: a kra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:5869: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK027(sha)001:5870: sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:5871: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK027(sha)001:5872: badz+ra kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:5873: badz+ra am gu sha dzah ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK027(sha)001:5874: zhes pas gsal shing me sbar bas 'od dang sprul bar bcad nas se mor byon par bsam la /
NK027(sha)001:5881: bcom ldan 'das che mchog yab yum dang /
NK027(sha)001:5882: dbang mchog he ru ka yab yum dang /
NK027(sha)001:5883: badz+ra he ru ka yab yum dang /
NK027(sha)001:5884: gtso bo rnams kyi thugs ka nas zur brgyad dkyil 'khor nas 'bru brgyad shar /
NK027(sha)001:5885: snying po ru lu 'bru brgyad dang /
NK027(sha)001:5887: phar 'phros dpal chen thugs dam bskul //
NK027(sha)001:5888: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NK027(sha)001:5889: de nas badz+ra gong gi sngags rnams bzlas /
NK027(sha)001:5892: bcom ldan che mchog he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:5893: bla med yum chen khro mo'i rgyal //
NK027(sha)001:5894: mthing nag sku yi bdud bzhi 'dul //
NK027(sha)001:5895: nyi shu rtsa gcig sa rnams gnon //
NK027(sha)001:5896: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:5897: zhabs brgyad ting 'dzin dbyings su spor //
NK027(sha)001:5898: rgyan rnams ma lus sku la rdzogs //
NK027(sha)001:5899: khro rgyal sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:5900: bcom ldan dbang chen he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:5901: dbu dgu phyag ni bco brgyad yongs su rdzogs //
NK027(sha)001:5902: mthing nag dgyes pa chen po'i sku //
NK027(sha)001:5903: zhabs brgyad ru tra pho mo mnan //
NK027(sha)001:5906: rdo rje rigs mchog bdud 'dul rtsal //
NK027(sha)001:5907: gdug pa thabs kyi btul nas ni //
NK027(sha)001:5908: bdud rigs rdul du brlag mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:5909: dpal chen sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:5912: h'uh bcom ldan che mchog yab yum dang /
NK027(sha)001:5914: dpal chen yab yum la sogs pa rnams la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:5915: bdag cag rnal 'byor pa dkyil 'khor chen po'i 'dir tshogs pa rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:5916: shes bya la thogs pa med pa'i shes rab mi
NK027(sha)001:5917: brjed pa'i gzung rgyun gyi ting 'dzin mngon shes drug
NK027(sha)001:5920: snang ba dang mi snang ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:5922: dpal dang 'byor pa 'khor dang longs spyod la sogs
NK027(sha)001:5923: pa phun sum tshogs pa thams cad kyi dngos grub
NK027(sha)001:5924: stsal du gsol / myur du mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas par mdzad du gsol /
NK027(sha)001:5926: badz+ra am gu sha dzah gsum gyis dang po 'od dang sprul pa /
NK027(sha)001:5928: gsum pa lha 'od du zhu nas rang la thim pas /
NK027(sha)001:5929: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi gzi brjid dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK027(sha)001:5930: de nas rim pa gnyis la rgyud kyi he ru ka bzhi'i blangs pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:5931: pho brang gi mar me nas rigs bzhi'i lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas spyan drangs /
NK027(sha)001:5932: b+hud+d+ha kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:5936: am gu sha dzah ru lu zhes pas gnyis pa me spar bas rtser byon par /
NK027(sha)001:5952: karma yab yum la ru lu /
NK027(sha)001:5958: chos dbyings dag pa sangs rgyas yul nas bzhengs //
NK027(sha)001:5959: nyon mongs gnas pa'i sems can don kun mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:5960: thugs rjes byang chub gnas su 'god mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:5961: bcom ldan slob dpon b+hud+d+ha he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:5962: kro ti shwa ri bcas la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:5963: phun sum tshogs 'dzin yon tan mchog gi sku //
NK027(sha)001:5964: lha mo tshogs kyi kun nas rnam bstod cing //
NK027(sha)001:5965: rngam pa'i zhal du dug gsum 'dren mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:5966: bcom ldan 'das dpal dz+ny+aa na he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:5967: kro ti shwa rir bcas la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:5968: gsung mchog chos kyi sku ni kun khyab cing //
NK027(sha)001:5969: sa dang bar snang khams la gnas pa dag /
NK027(sha)001:5970: byang chub sems la rab tu 'god mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:5971: bcom ldan dpal chen pad+ma he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:5972: kro ti shwa rir bcas la nan tan drag shul spyod pa'i tshul 'dzin cing //
NK027(sha)001:5973: thabs mkhas thugs rjes chen po'i drag shul gyi //
NK027(sha)001:5974: rgyu drug sems can ma lus kun sgrol ba //
NK027(sha)001:5975: bcom ldan dpal chen karma he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:5976: kro ti shwa rir bcas la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:5978: hoh bcom ldan 'das rigs lnga he ru ka yab yum la dngos grub gsol ba /
NK027(sha)001:5980: drug pa bsdu ba ni gong bzhin no //
NK027(sha)001:5981: gsum pa lung gi he ru ka bzhi lcags kyu'i phyag rgya dang /
NK027(sha)001:5982: rak+sha he ru ka kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:5989: me sbar bas rtse mor byon /
NK027(sha)001:5990: gnyis pa mchod pa bdud rtsi gtor ma rak+ta 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:5992: lung gi he ru ka'i thugs zur brgyad /
NK027(sha)001:5997: gsum pa 'dzab ni gong gi snying po bzlas pa /
NK027(sha)001:6000: sbyor ba dam tshig dam tshig gsang ba sgrol ba'i
NK027(sha)001:6001: dbyings log lta 'joms byed skyabs gnas reg bya 'joms
NK027(sha)001:6002: // g+ha na nyams pa lta na mtshan ma sgrol //
NK027(sha)001:6003: lung gi khro rgyal tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:6005: hoh bcom ldan 'das lung gi he ru ka yab
NK027(sha)001:6006: yum tshogs la dngos grub stsal du gsol ba ni
NK027(sha)001:6008: drug pa bsdu ba gong bzhin /
NK027(sha)001:6011: koo'u ri brgyad kyi sngags dang /
NK027(sha)001:6012: badz+ra am ku sha dzah ru lu g+hu h+yas me sbar /
NK027(sha)001:6014: ko'u ri brgyad kyi thugs ka /
NK027(sha)001:6017: phar tshur bzlas pa bstod pa /
NK027(sha)001:6018: ko'u ri la sogs khro mo brgyad rnams ni /
NK027(sha)001:6019: gdug pa thabs kyi 'dul ba'i drag shul can //
NK027(sha)001:6020: sku mdog phyag cha sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK027(sha)001:6021: ye shes khro mo brgyad la khro mo brgyad la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:6023: lnga pa phra men brgyad dang sgo ma bzhi spyan drangs ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:6024: so so'i sngags dang phyag rgya /
NK027(sha)001:6025: badz+ra am gu sha dzah ru lu /
NK027(sha)001:6026: badz+ra te dza ste nga dzah mchod pa gsum 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:6027: sngags ru lu g+hu h+ya bzlas /
NK027(sha)001:6030: seng ha la sogs phra men brgyad rnams ni //
NK027(sha)001:6031: ye shes las la 'gyed pa'i phra men ma //
NK027(sha)001:6032: rnam 'phrul las kyi 'gro ba'i don mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:6033: seng ha phra men brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:6034: rta gdong la sogs sgo ma bzhi rnams ni //
NK027(sha)001:6035: tshad med bzhi yi 'gro ba'i don mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:6036: shar lho nub byang sgo bzhi thub par bsrungs //
NK027(sha)001:6037: sgo skyong khro mo bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:6039: phra men brgyad dang sgo ma bzhi la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:6042: drug pa spor ma brgyad dang /
NK027(sha)001:6043: gsang yum bzhi lcags kyu'i phyag rgya dang /
NK027(sha)001:6044: badz+ra a tra ti ar+ya tsa tud ta ra phata /
NK027(sha)001:6048: sh+r+ai sha ra ya na mah sh+r+ai badz+ra g+han+d+ha bu dza ya /
NK027(sha)001:6049: am gu sha dzah mchod pa gsum 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:6051: spor byed chen mo brgyad rnams dang //
NK027(sha)001:6052: gsang yum bzhi yi thugs ka nas //
NK027(sha)001:6063: chos dbyings rnam dag ngang las rang snang ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:6064: sna tshogs cir yang 'gyur ba'i sku mnga' zhing //
NK027(sha)001:6065: srid gsum zhing du sbyor ba'i g.yang gzhi gsol //
NK027(sha)001:6066: spor byed chen mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:6067: bar khyams de yi shar lho nub byang sgor //
NK027(sha)001:6068: dgyes pa bskyed pa gsang ba'i yum chen bzhi //
NK027(sha)001:6069: gnyis med rol ba'i byin rlabs sna tshogs 'phro //
NK027(sha)001:6070: shes rab yum chen bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:6072: hoh spor ma chen mo brgyad /
NK027(sha)001:6073: gsang ba'i yum chen bzhi la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:6076: bdun pa la dbang phyug ma nyer brgyad dang phyag rgya dang /
NK027(sha)001:6077: b+h+yo ma nu rak+sha so b+h+yo /
NK027(sha)001:6078: ru lu badz+ra am gu sha dzah mchod pa gsum pa 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:6080: dbang phyug nyer brgyad kyi thugs ka nas /
NK027(sha)001:6085: rtsa sngags nyer brgyad spel te bzlas /
NK027(sha)001:6088: ma sring la sogs dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad //
NK027(sha)001:6089: dreg pa lha chen rnams kyi chung ma ste //
NK027(sha)001:6090: dbang drag las la thog pa med pa ste //
NK027(sha)001:6091: nyi shu rtsa brgyad tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:6093: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad la dngos grub tu gsol ba sogs /
NK027(sha)001:6095: brgyad pa mkha' 'gro so gnyis phyag rgya dang /
NK027(sha)001:6098: badz+ra am gu sha dzah me sbar /
NK027(sha)001:6101: mkha' 'gro so gnyis thugs ka nas /
NK027(sha)001:6104: phar tshur e a ra li h'u /
NK027(sha)001:6109: nam mkha'i lus can gang yang thogs med cing //
NK027(sha)001:6110: 'dod dgur bsgyur ba'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK027(sha)001:6111: ma sring byams pa'i tshul du grogs mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:6112: mkha' 'gro sum cu gnyis la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:6114: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:6116: dgu pa ma bdun sring mo bzhi'i phyag rgya dang /
NK027(sha)001:6119: badz+ra am gu sha dzah me spar /
NK027(sha)001:6122: ma bdun sring bzhi'i thugs ka nas /
NK027(sha)001:6132: 'jig rten dreg pa 'dul ba ma mo'i tshogs //
NK027(sha)001:6133: phyi 'khor bsrung zhing nang skor skyong bar mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:6134: dur khrod ma bdun las kyi sring mo bzhi //
NK027(sha)001:6135: bgegs bsrung ma mo rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:6137: ma bdun sring mo bzhi la dngos grub tu gsol ba /
NK027(sha)001:6140: bcu pa la ging chen bco brgyad phyag rgya dang /
NK027(sha)001:6141: ging ka ra ha ha ru lu ru lu b+h+yo /
NK027(sha)001:6142: ru lu badz+ra am gu sha dzah me spar /
NK027(sha)001:6144: ging ka ra dang ru lu spel /
NK027(sha)001:6147: khams gsum sgrol ba'i ging chen bco brgyad ni //
NK027(sha)001:6148: srid gsum las la thogs med sgrol la brtson //
NK027(sha)001:6149: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu gtan nas brlag par byed //
NK027(sha)001:6150: ging chen ging lcam tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:6152: ging chen bco brgyad la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:6155: bcu gcig pa la steng gi khro bo khro mo drug cu phyag rgya dang /
NK027(sha)001:6158: badz+ra am gu sha dzah me sbar /
NK027(sha)001:6161: khro bo khro mo drug cu'i thugs snying po /
NK027(sha)001:6171: bcom ldan 'das h'u mdzad sa gsum brjid kyi gnon //
NK027(sha)001:6172: khams gsum 'dul mdzad ye shes lha yi lha //
NK027(sha)001:6173: 'jigs byed 'bar ba gdug pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms //
NK027(sha)001:6174: khro bo khro mo rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:6176: khro bo khro mo drug cu la dngos grub tu gsol ba sogs /
NK027(sha)001:6178: bcu gnyis pa phyogs bzhi'i pho na nyis brgya'i phyag rgya dang /
NK027(sha)001:6183: am gu sha dzah me sbar /
NK027(sha)001:6186: pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu'i thugs /
NK027(sha)001:6191: sngags de dag ru lu gyu h+ya spel lo //
NK027(sha)001:6194: ye shes thugs rjes phyogs bcur khyab pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6195: gdon bgegs 'dul ba'i las la thogs med pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:6196: ci bgyis bka' nyan las rnams myur mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:6197: phyogs bzhi pho nya'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:6199: phyogs bzhi pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu tshogs la dngos grub tu gsol ba sogs /
NK027(sha)001:6201: bcu gsum pa 'og gi ma mo drug cu phyag rgya dang /
NK027(sha)001:6203: badz+ra am gu sha dzah me spar /
NK027(sha)001:6206: ma mo drug cu'i thugs ka nas /
NK027(sha)001:6216: stong khams yongs su las la dbang ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:6217: ma chen rgyal mo srid pa gsum gyi bdag /
NK027(sha)001:6218: yum chen las la dbang ba'i ma mo che //
NK027(sha)001:6219: ma mo drug cu'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:6221: 'og phyogs kyi ma mo drug cu la dngos grub tu gsol ba sogs /
NK027(sha)001:6223: de nas rim pa bcu bzhi pa la /
NK027(sha)001:6224: khro bo khro mo rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang phyag rgya dang /
NK027(sha)001:6225: ma h+aa g+hu ru shwa ri ram gi li h'u /
NK027(sha)001:6226: badz+ra yo gi ni g+hu ru sa m+aa ya dzah me sbar /
NK027(sha)001:6227: 'od dang bcas te gsal shing gi rtse la byon par bsam /
NK027(sha)001:6234: man ngag mdo lung rgyud dang bcas pa'i rig 'dzin bla ma rnams kyis thugs ka nas //
NK027(sha)001:6235: snying po ru la 'bru brgyad g+hu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i 'od 'phros pa //
NK027(sha)001:6237: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NK027(sha)001:6238: ma h+aa g+hu ru sha ri ram shi ki ti li /
NK027(sha)001:6239: badz+ra yo ga gu ru sa m+aa ya dzah ru lu g+hu h+ya zhes bzlas so //
NK027(sha)001:6241: rig 'dzin bla ma'i byin rlabs ldan pa'i tshogs //
NK027(sha)001:6242: lhun grub phyag chen tshe dbang rnam smin gyi //
NK027(sha)001:6243: rgya gar bod kyi grub thob du ma'i tshogs //
NK027(sha)001:6244: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi dngos grub 'dir stsol cig /
NK027(sha)001:6247: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang gi bla ma rnams la dngos grub tu gsol ba sogs /
NK027(sha)001:6250: lan gsum gyi dang po 'od dang sprul pa /
NK027(sha)001:6251: gnyis pa yig 'bru gsum pa sku 'od du zhu nas bdag la thim /
NK027(sha)001:6252: bdag sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi gzi brjid dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK027(sha)001:6254: slob ma rnams phyir khrus byas /
NK027(sha)001:6258: dza gad re drangs te rol lo //
NK027(sha)001:6259: de nas dbang bskur bar byas te /
NK027(sha)001:6261: yo ga la sogs theg drug la /
NK027(sha)001:6262: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo bya /
NK027(sha)001:6263: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga la /
NK027(sha)001:6264: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bo bya //
NK027(sha)001:6265: rdzogs chen a nu yo ga la //
NK027(sha)001:6266: bsgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo bya //
NK027(sha)001:6267: rdzogs chen a ti yo ga ni //
NK027(sha)001:6268: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo bya //
NK027(sha)001:6270: yo ga la sogs pa drug gi dbang tshar nas /
NK027(sha)001:6271: da gsang sngags nang gi dbang bskur ba la /
NK027(sha)001:6272: cho ga sum cu rtsa drug ste /
NK027(sha)001:6274: phyi dang nang dang gsang bcu dang //
NK027(sha)001:6275: bcu gcig pa dang bcu gsum dang //
NK027(sha)001:6276: rnam pa gnyis kyi khyad par gyi //
NK027(sha)001:6277: dbang mchog sum cu rtsa drug rdzogs //
NK027(sha)001:6282: zab mo'i dbang gnyis su bstan pa la /
NK027(sha)001:6283: phyi dbang nang dbang ma h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:6284: bsgrub dbang gsang dbang a nu gtso che yang /
NK027(sha)001:6285: thun mong du dbang gang rung la bskur ba la /
NK027(sha)001:6286: slob dpon rnams gos bzang po dang /
NK027(sha)001:6288: thor gtsug dbu rgyan la sogs pa brjid bag dang ldan pas khri la 'dug ste /
NK027(sha)001:6289: kha g.yu kha gser la sogs pa thogs pas rgyal po lta bur dbang bskur ba'o //
NK027(sha)001:6290: yang thams cad khrus dang gtsang sbra byas te gos gtsang ma gon /
NK027(sha)001:6291: dpal rta mgrin snying khar dri bzang pos thig le dang bcas pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:6292: bram ze ltar dbang bskur ba'o //
NK027(sha)001:6293: yang na thams cad ye shes lnga'i ngang las nyams
NK027(sha)001:6294: nga bag tsha dang gtsang sme'i rtog pa med par
NK027(sha)001:6295: brtul zhugs chen po'i ngar dang ldan pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:6296: gdol ba ltar dbang bskur ba ste /
NK027(sha)001:6297: de dag kyang ldog pa tha dad du snang yang ngo bo gcig pas /
NK027(sha)001:6298: dbang stegs la yi dam che mchog gi nga rgyal gyi 'dug par bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:6299: de nas bla mas spyi bor nas rta'i mgur glu
NK027(sha)001:6300: phyogs bcur mtsher zhing bsgrag pas sangs rgyas byang chub
NK027(sha)001:6301: sems dpa' thams cad mdun gyi nam mkhar byon /
NK027(sha)001:6302: bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum la thim pas dbang bskur bas nus pa dang ldan par bya /
NK027(sha)001:6303: brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams kyang byon /
NK027(sha)001:6305: phung phung gi rnam pa'i 'od kyi phung po yi /
NK027(sha)001:6306: de'i 'od zer gyi slob ma rnams kyi bag chags dang snod ngan pa'i dri ma dag par bsam /
NK027(sha)001:6307: de nas sems can 'di dag 'khor ba las bsgral te bla na med pa'i /
NK027(sha)001:6308: byang chub la 'god snyams pa'i byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems ltar bsgom /
NK027(sha)001:6310: thugs ma yengs bar gsan mdzod /
NK027(sha)001:6311: de'ang dper na yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin chen dbang gi rgyal po /
NK027(sha)001:6312: de dgos 'dod thams cad kyi 'byung gnas yin te /
NK027(sha)001:6313: rang gi ci ltar gsol ba btab pa bzhin du 'dod pa'i don 'grub pa ltar /
NK027(sha)001:6314: bla ma 'di yang dgos 'dod thams cad kyi gnas yin pas /
NK027(sha)001:6315: mchog thun mong gi gsol ba gang btab 'grub pas
NK027(sha)001:6316: bla ma sangs rgyas bsgom la mos gus gdung sems
NK027(sha)001:6317: kyis la gsol ba thob bya /
NK027(sha)001:6318: slob ma thal mo sbyar la /
NK027(sha)001:6319: byang chub rdo rje sangs rgyas la //
NK027(sha)001:6320: sa mtha' sems dpa' chen po yi //
NK027(sha)001:6321: lci ltar mchod cing zhugs pa ltar //
NK027(sha)001:6322: de bzhin skal ldan bdag cag la //
NK027(sha)001:6323: rnal 'byor dbang phyug chen po yi //
NK027(sha)001:6324: dbang rnams rim par stsal du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:6327: sangs rgyas dag ni thams cad kyi //
NK027(sha)001:6328: gsang ba rdo rje gsum las byung //
NK027(sha)001:6329: khams gsum kun gyi phyag byas pas //
NK027(sha)001:6330: dbang bskur gnang ba chen po sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:6332: de nas dbyangs dang bcas pas /
NK027(sha)001:6335: slob bu rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:6336: sems can don la bdag brtson na //
NK027(sha)001:6337: bzod par mdzad de dgongs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:6338: badz+ra sa m+aa ya h'u dzah zhes lan gsum brjod pas /
NK027(sha)001:6339: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas mdun gyi nam
NK027(sha)001:6340: mkha' byon nas dbang bskur gcig par stsal bar bsam
NK027(sha)001:6341: la / rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad kun //
NK027(sha)001:6343: dang ba'i yid kyi bzhugs nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:6344: byin rlabs dbang mchog nod par mdzod //
NK027(sha)001:6345: ces brjod la dag bzhi yongs su rdzogs par bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:6346: thog mar phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu las /
NK027(sha)001:6347: dang po zhi ba'i phyag rgya'i dbang /
NK027(sha)001:6351: lnga pa bkra shis rdzas brgyad /
NK027(sha)001:6352: drug pa rin chen sna bdun /
NK027(sha)001:6353: bdun pa gdan khri brgyad pa rgyan rtags /
NK027(sha)001:6356: de la dang po zhi ba'i phyag rgya'i dbang sngar yo ga ltar spros na 'dir len /
NK027(sha)001:6359: rgyal po'i phyag rgya mchog gi rgya //
NK027(sha)001:6360: phyag rgya'i rtsa mchog mi 'dus pa //
NK027(sha)001:6361: ye shes lnga dang rigs lnga'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:6362: yi dam phyag rgya rdzogs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:6363: bden pa phyag rgya lnga yi dbang //
NK027(sha)001:6364: bskur bas rigs lnga ye shes lnga //
NK027(sha)001:6365: skal ldan rigs kyi bu rnams kyis //
NK027(sha)001:6366: dbang mchog dam pa thob par 'gyur //
NK027(sha)001:6367: h'u tram h+r+aih+aah a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)001:6369: dbang rin chen phreng ba las /
NK027(sha)001:6370: gnyis pa phyag mtshan gyi dbang rdzas rdo rje sogs rim pa bzhi'i thogs te 'di skad du /
NK027(sha)001:6372: me long lta bu'i ye shes rang bzhin rnyed //
NK027(sha)001:6373: 'joms byed rdo rje rang snang ste //
NK027(sha)001:6374: rdo rje sems dpa' dam tshig che //
NK027(sha)001:6375: mi phyed rdo rje'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6376: skal ldan rigs kyi bu khyod la rdo rje'i rigs //
NK027(sha)001:6377: rdo rje sems dpa'i phyag mtshan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:6378: me long lta bu'i ye shes rdo rje sems dpa'i
NK027(sha)001:6379: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK027(sha)001:6380: cig / ma h+aa shu da ri sha nya /
NK027(sha)001:6383: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi 'khor lo rin chen rang snang ba /
NK027(sha)001:6384: rnam par snang mdzad bdag nyid che //
NK027(sha)001:6385: chos kyi 'khor lo'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6386: skal ldan rigs kyi bu khyod la /
NK027(sha)001:6387: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs rnam par snang mdzad kyi phyag mtshan 'khor los dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:6388: stong nyid kyi ye shes rnam par snang mdzad kyi
NK027(sha)001:6389: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK027(sha)001:6390: cig / ma h+aa shu nya ta /
NK027(sha)001:6393: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes nyid //
NK027(sha)001:6394: yid bzhin nor bu rang snang bas //
NK027(sha)001:6395: rin chen 'byung ldan bdag nyid de //
NK027(sha)001:6397: rin po che'i rigs rin chen 'byung ldan gyi phyag mtshan rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:6398: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes rin chen 'byung ldan
NK027(sha)001:6399: gyi sku gsung thugs kyi dbang dam pa ma h+aa
NK027(sha)001:6400: sa man+ta dz+ny+aa na a b+hi pad+ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6401: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes nyid //
NK027(sha)001:6402: bag chags med par rang snang bas //
NK027(sha)001:6403: snang ba mtha' yas bdag nyid de //
NK027(sha)001:6404: spyod bzhi ma chags dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6405: pad+ma'i rigs snang ba mtha' yas kyi phyag mtshan pad+mas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:6406: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes snang ba mtha' yas
NK027(sha)001:6407: kyi sku gsung thugs kyi dbang dam pa ma h+aa
NK027(sha)001:6409: a b+hi ral gri thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6410: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes nyid //
NK027(sha)001:6411: ral gri'i dngos por rang snang bas //
NK027(sha)001:6412: don yod grub pa'i ngo bo ste //
NK027(sha)001:6413: sgrib pa gcod pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6414: las kyi rigs don yod grub pa'i phyag mtshan ral gris dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:6415: phrin las ye shes don yod grub pa'i sku gsung
NK027(sha)001:6416: thugs kyi dbang dam pa ma h+aa kri t+ya a
NK027(sha)001:6418: a b+hi gsum pa rigs ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6419: shes rab gzungs kyi dbang mchog ni //
NK027(sha)001:6420: rtogs dang ldan par gyur ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:6421: mtha' gnyis don du mi gtong ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:6422: rgyal yum shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK027(sha)001:6423: gzungs kyi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:6424: don dam rang bzhin spros dang bral //
NK027(sha)001:6425: dri med rnam dag byang chub sems //
NK027(sha)001:6426: cis kyang gso med rigs pa'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:6427: skal ldan rnal 'byor khyod la sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:6428: gnyis med yongs su rdzogs pas na //
NK027(sha)001:6429: thams cad bde ba chen po'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:6430: byang chub sems dang don du 'brel //
NK027(sha)001:6431: shes rab chen po'i rdzogs dbang sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:6432: ma h+aa mu tra a b+hi dril bu'am rigs ma'i gzugs gtad /
NK027(sha)001:6433: bzhi pa bum pa thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6434: bkra shis chen po'i bum dbang 'di //
NK027(sha)001:6435: bde gshegs bzhugs pa'i pho brang ste //
NK027(sha)001:6436: dkyil 'khor rdzogs par gyur pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6437: dbang mchog de yi sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:6438: badz+ra ka la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)001:6441: pad+ma ka h+r+aih pad+ma ka karma ka ya a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah bum pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:6442: nang gi sgrib pa ma lus pa dag nas /
NK027(sha)001:6443: dkyil 'khor yongs su rdzogs par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:6445: spros med spros bral chos kyi dbyings //
NK027(sha)001:6446: bum pa zlum po chos kyi gter //
NK027(sha)001:6447: phan byed smin pa'i mchog yin te //
NK027(sha)001:6448: 'gro ba'i nad sel bkra shis shog /
NK027(sha)001:6449: lnga pa bkra shis rdzas brgyad las /
NK027(sha)001:6450: dang po dur wa thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6451: gsang ba'i bstan pa rgyas nas ni //
NK027(sha)001:6452: yun ring gnas par gyur pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6453: bkra shis rdzas kyi dbang mchog kyang //
NK027(sha)001:6454: gnang ba chen po sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:6455: ting 'dzin dur was bsod nams kun tu 'phel //
NK027(sha)001:6456: ji ltar drang srong chen po a ta kas //
NK027(sha)001:6457: byin gyis brlabs pa'i rtsa mchog dur wa 'di //
NK027(sha)001:6458: reg pas nad rnams thams cad bsal gyur te //
NK027(sha)001:6459: nad kyi gdung ba kun las thar bar shog /
NK027(sha)001:6460: dur was dge ba'i rtsa ba 'gag med pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:6461: dbang thob nas ni kun tu bkra shis shog /
NK027(sha)001:6462: dur was tshe ni 'phel bar byed pa ste //
NK027(sha)001:6463: rdo rje sems dpa' tshe ni rab grub nas //
NK027(sha)001:6464: nyon mongs skye shi'i sdug bsngal rgyun bcad de //
NK027(sha)001:6465: bkra shis des kyang tshe ni rten gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:6467: gsang sngags las mtha' chags shing ral gri 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:6468: rdo rje dang ni rin chen chu skyes dang //
NK027(sha)001:6469: de bzhin las kyi rigs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:6470: kha dog bzang po mdog mdzes li khri 'dis //
NK027(sha)001:6471: lha ma'i 'dod don dbang du 'dul bar shog /
NK027(sha)001:6472: li khri dmar po dbang gi rang bzhin te //
NK027(sha)001:6473: chos rnams ma lus dbang du gyur pa ste //
NK027(sha)001:6474: chos kyis rgyal srid rab tu rten gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:6475: li khri'i bkra shis mchog tu brtan gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:6477: yang dag lta ba bden gnyis me long ston //
NK027(sha)001:6478: de grub der thob dam la 'da' mi mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:6479: chos rnams thams cad sgyu ma lta bu ste //
NK027(sha)001:6480: rang bzhin dag pa sgyu ma ltar shes nas //
NK027(sha)001:6481: gti mug mun sel bag chags bsreg sbyangs te //
NK027(sha)001:6482: me long lta bu'i ye shes thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:6483: me long ye shes chen po'i gzugs brnyan te //
NK027(sha)001:6484: ye shes rgyal po'i bdud rtsi mchog brnyes nas //
NK027(sha)001:6485: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pa //
NK027(sha)001:6486: bkra shis des kyang sgrib pa dag gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:6488: yang dag ngag gi sgra skad tshangs pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6489: ci ltar ma ra ya nar lha chen gyi //
NK027(sha)001:6490: dung sgra sgrogs nas rims nad bsal ba ltar //
NK027(sha)001:6491: dam chos bdud rtsi dung gi sgra grags pas //
NK027(sha)001:6492: nad kyi gdung ba kun las rgyal bar shog /
NK027(sha)001:6493: dung ni chos kyi sgra rnams sgrogs pa'i tshul //
NK027(sha)001:6494: yon tan rgya mtsho mchog tu bdag gyur nas //
NK027(sha)001:6495: rnam dag chos la thog med longs spyod pa //
NK027(sha)001:6496: bkra shis des ni tshe la longs spyod shog /
NK027(sha)001:6498: shes bcu srog gi dbang po thob nas ni //
NK027(sha)001:6499: yang dag dran pa g+hi wang nad gso mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:6500: ji ltar g+hi wang khyu mchog dbang po yi //
