NK027(sha)001:6501: srog gi dbang po gnyen du gyur nas ni //
NK027(sha)001:6502: rnam par dkar ba'i dam chos 'dzin pa ltar //
NK027(sha)001:6503: shes bcu srog gi dbang po thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:6504: g+hi wang dug gsum 'joms pa nad kyi sman //
NK027(sha)001:6505: sman mchog chos nyid rab tu rtog gyur te //
NK027(sha)001:6506: nyon mongs zug rngu med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:6507: bkra shis des kyang sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK027(sha)001:6509: yang dag don dam rtogs pa bil ba'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:6510: de thob de grub de las mi 'das mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:6511: ji ltar rgyu dang sa bon zug rngu las //
NK027(sha)001:6512: 'bras bu cher smin shes mchog bil ba ltar //
NK027(sha)001:6513: de bzhin dge ba'i rgyu mchog chung ngu las //
NK027(sha)001:6514: 'bras bu rgya che dpag med thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:6515: bil wa rgyu rkyen 'bras bu bcas pa'i chos //
NK027(sha)001:6516: 'jig rten 'jig rten 'das pa'i spyod pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6517: byang chub snying po mchog tu gyur pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6518: bkra shis des ni 'jig rten 'grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:6520: yang dag 'tsho ba rnams ni 'dod zho yi //
NK027(sha)001:6521: lha dbang brgya byin bdag nyid chen po yi //
NK027(sha)001:6522: byin gyis brlabs shing grub pa'i rdzas mchog gi //
NK027(sha)001:6523: nad rnams ma lus 'joms pa'i bdud rtsi ste //
NK027(sha)001:6524: rnam par rgyal ba'i ro mchog chen po 'dis //
NK027(sha)001:6525: bsam gtan ting 'dzin bcud dang ldan par shog /
NK027(sha)001:6526: zho ni kun gyi snying por gyur pa ste //
NK027(sha)001:6527: snying po rnam dag byang chub sems rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:6528: yon tan kun gyi snying por gyur pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6529: bkra shis des kyang nad rnams nyungs kar thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:6530: yang dag rtsol bas nyungs kar bdud bzhi 'joms //
NK027(sha)001:6531: bde bar gshegs pas byin gyis brlabs pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6532: bgegs rnams 'joms pa grub pa'i rgyal po 'di //
NK027(sha)001:6533: bar du gcod pa'i bgegs kyi tshogs bcom nas //
NK027(sha)001:6534: deng 'dir bkra shis mchog nyid thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:6535: nyungs kar rdo rje'i rigs te bgegs rnams 'joms //
NK027(sha)001:6536: yon tan mthu stobs chen por gyur pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6537: bdud bzhi bar du gcod pa kun bcom nas //
NK027(sha)001:6538: mi mthun phyogs las rab tu rgyal bar shog /
NK027(sha)001:6539: drug pa rgyal srid sna bdun las /
NK027(sha)001:6541: dam chos rnam par 'byed pa'i 'khor lo 'di //
NK027(sha)001:6542: de thob de grub de las mi 'da' mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:6543: 'khor lo rin chen rten pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:6544: sa bcu dag la dbang bskur zhing //
NK027(sha)001:6545: theg pa rnam gsum rtogs pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:6546: chos kyis rgyal po cher ston shog /
NK027(sha)001:6548: theg pa rnam gsum rtogs nas /
NK027(sha)001:6549: sa bcu dag la dbang bsgyur ba'i chos kyi rgyal po'i dbang dam pa glang po thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6550: ting 'dzin mi 'gyur stobs kyi glang po che //
NK027(sha)001:6551: de thob de grub de las mi 'da' mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:6552: glang po rin chen rten pa yin //
NK027(sha)001:6553: sa bcu dag la dbang bsgrub cing //
NK027(sha)001:6554: theg pa rnam gsum rtogs pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:6555: byang chub snying por gnas par shog /
NK027(sha)001:6557: theg pa rnam gsum rtogs nas /
NK027(sha)001:6558: stobs bcu la dbang bsgyur zhing /
NK027(sha)001:6559: dbang mchog dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:6561: rdzu 'phrul myur mgyogs shugs 'chang rdzu 'phrul rta //
NK027(sha)001:6562: de thob de grub de las mi 'da' mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:6563: rta mchog rin chen rten pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6564: rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhi'i dbang thob nas //
NK027(sha)001:6565: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho sgrol ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:6566: thar pa'i 'bras bu thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:6567: rta mchog gi dbang bskur nas /
NK027(sha)001:6568: rdzu 'phrul rkang pa bzhi yis 'khor ba'i sems can
NK027(sha)001:6569: thams cad thar ba la sgrol ba'i dbang dmag dpon
NK027(sha)001:6570: thogs / dran pa rang gi phyag mtshan gzhan 'joms dmag /
NK027(sha)001:6571: de thob de grub de las mi 'da' mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:6572: dmag dpon rin chen rten pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6573: mi 'jigs bzhi yi dbang thob nas //
NK027(sha)001:6574: phas kyi rgol ba tshar gcod de //
NK027(sha)001:6575: go cha chen po bgo bar shog /
NK027(sha)001:6577: mi 'jigs pa bzhis rgol ba thams cad tshar bcad nas /
NK027(sha)001:6578: go cha chen po bgos pa'i dbang dam pa btsun mo /
NK027(sha)001:6579: lus sems shin tu sbyangs pa btsun mo ste //
NK027(sha)001:6580: de thob de grub de las mi 'da' mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:6581: btsun mo rin chen rten pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6582: shes rab dbyings kyis mchog thob nas //
NK027(sha)001:6583: skye 'gag med pa'i don rtogs te //
NK027(sha)001:6584: byang chub snying por gnas par shog /
NK027(sha)001:6586: shes rab kyi dbyings kyi 'gag pa med pa'i don rtogs shing /
NK027(sha)001:6587: dbang dam pa blon po thogs /
NK027(sha)001:6588: gdul dka' 'dul mkhas khyim bdag dga' ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:6589: de thob de grub de la mi 'da' mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:6590: blon po rin chen rten pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6591: sum cu rtsa gsum dbang phyug rje //
NK027(sha)001:6592: rdzu 'phrul chen po brgya sbyin ltar //
NK027(sha)001:6593: lha yi rgyal po cher ston shog /
NK027(sha)001:6595: rdzu 'phrul chen po lha yi rgyal po'i dbang dam pa thob nor bu thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6596: btang snyoms yang dag don mdzad rin chen yin //
NK027(sha)001:6597: de thob de grub de las mi 'da' mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:6598: 'jig rten dbang phyug de bzhin gshegs //
NK027(sha)001:6599: dpe byad mtshan gyi brgyan pa steng //
NK027(sha)001:6600: gser gyi kha dog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:6602: mtshan dpe byad dang ldan zhing /
NK027(sha)001:6603: gser gyi kha dog sku'i sku thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:6604: rgyal srid sna bdun gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:6605: 'phags pa'i nor bdun gyi 'gro ba'i 'phong pa rgyun gcod /
NK027(sha)001:6606: mi gnas pa'i ye shes la spyod pa'i bdun pa gdan khri lnga las /
NK027(sha)001:6607: dang po seng khri thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6608: nyon mongs rang rig rtogs pas ye shes la //
NK027(sha)001:6609: zhes kyang ma gos thams cad 'joms //
NK027(sha)001:6610: so so'i gzugs kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:6611: mi 'jigs pa yi dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6613: sems nyid rtogs pa'i rigs pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6614: mtshan ma thams cad zil gyi gnon //
NK027(sha)001:6615: glang chen theg pa'i dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:6616: sangs rgyas stobs bcu'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6618: thams cad sems su rtogs gyur nas //
NK027(sha)001:6619: gar ma bsgrod par kun tu phyin //
NK027(sha)001:6620: myur mgyogs rta'i dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:6621: rdzu 'phrul rkang pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6623: nyon mongs sems su gang shes pa //
NK027(sha)001:6624: spyod bzhin mi gos dbang du byed //
NK027(sha)001:6625: mdzes byed rma bya'i dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:6626: rgyal ba'i dbang bcu thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:6627: lnga pa mkha' lding gi khri /
NK027(sha)001:6628: shes bya gang dang gang rtogs pa //
NK027(sha)001:6629: ltas pa med par thams cad gsal //
NK027(sha)001:6630: mkha' lding shang shang dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:6631: shes bya thogs med dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6632: sems can chen po lnga'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:6633: yon tan lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang thob par shog cig /
NK027(sha)001:6634: de nas rin po che khri ste /
NK027(sha)001:6635: sems nyid dgos 'dod lhun gyis grub pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6636: rtog pas ma btsal rang la snang //
NK027(sha)001:6637: rin chen khri yi dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:6638: yon tan rten pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6639: rin chen pad+ma seng ge'i khri //
NK027(sha)001:6640: bla mar gyur pa'i bdag mchog ste //
NK027(sha)001:6641: khyad par chen po gyur pa'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:6642: khri chen dag la bzhugs par bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:6643: rin po che'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:6644: 'gro ba lha dang bcas pa'i bla mar gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:6645: brgyad pa rgyan cha'i rtags las /
NK027(sha)001:6646: dang po cod pan thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6647: dar gyi cod pan phreng la sogs //
NK027(sha)001:6648: dbang mchog brjid pa'i rgyan gyi lhub //
NK027(sha)001:6649: 'gul rgyan do shal se mo do //
NK027(sha)001:6650: dpung rgyan lag gdub rkang gdub rnams //
NK027(sha)001:6651: dbang mchog rgyal po de la sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:6652: chos nyid cir yang snang ba longs spyod rgyan //
NK027(sha)001:6653: rigs lnga'i rin chen dbu rgyan 'di bcing pas //
NK027(sha)001:6654: ye shes lnga dang rigs lnga dbyer med pa //
NK027(sha)001:6655: rigs lnga'i dbu rgyan dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:6657: zhe sdang chen po rang gi sems //
NK027(sha)001:6659: byang chub phyogs rnams rtogs pa'i rgyan //
NK027(sha)001:6660: mtshan dang dpe byad la sogs pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:6661: 'bras bu'i chos la dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6662: sarba ta th+aa ga ta g+hu h+ya /
NK027(sha)001:6668: sat+wa swa b+h+aa wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK027(sha)001:6669: dgu pa ming ni rdo rje thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6670: dbang thob mdzes pa brjid pa'i rgyal po ste //
NK027(sha)001:6671: dbang phyug yin pas de la kun phyag 'tshal //
NK027(sha)001:6672: rdo rje dbang phyug zhes pa mtshan nas ni //
NK027(sha)001:6673: kun gyi sgra chen 'bod cing bsgrag par bya //
NK027(sha)001:6674: ston pa'i thugs rje nges par ming btags pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:6675: thugs rjes ngang nas nges pa'i sras su mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:6676: rdo rje ming gi dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:6677: rgyal ba'i zhing khams thams cad du //
NK027(sha)001:6678: dbang phyug grub pa'i snyan pas khyab par shog /
NK027(sha)001:6679: bcu pa ni 'khor lo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6680: gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs stong ldan pa zhig /
NK027(sha)001:6681: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la sbyin byas pas //
NK027(sha)001:6682: bzhi ni kun la kha lo bsgyur ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:6683: dbang mchog rgyal po 'di ni thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:6684: yongs la dbang bsgyur dbang gi mchog /
NK027(sha)001:6685: gang la'ang ma chags 'dod dgur bsgyur //
NK027(sha)001:6686: gnyis su med pa'i pho brang du //
NK027(sha)001:6687: spang len med par dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:6690: brjid pa'i don du 'bras bu bkod nas ni //
NK027(sha)001:6691: gzhan don 'di la phyin pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:6692: rgyal ba'i 'khor lo bskor bar mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:6694: 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal thabs kyi 'jig rten gyi
NK027(sha)001:6695: kha lo gyen du bsgyur ba'i dbang dam pa thob
NK027(sha)001:6696: par gyur cig / badz+ra tsakra a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)001:6698: de yan chad kyi phyi dbang bcu tshar ba'o //
NK027(sha)001:6699: de nas nang dbang bcu gcig las /
NK027(sha)001:6700: dang po gsang sngags gsang ba'i nyan pa'i dbang /
NK027(sha)001:6703: bzhi pa rdo rje rgyal po'i /
NK027(sha)001:6705: drug pa khyad par gyi rin chen bdun /
NK027(sha)001:6706: bdun pa khro bo'i phyag rgya chen po /
NK027(sha)001:6709: bcu pa bkra shis rtags kyi /
NK027(sha)001:6710: bcu gcig pa thig le ming gi dbang ngo //
NK027(sha)001:6711: de la dang po po ti thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6712: gsang ba'i sgo ru 'di zhugs nas //
NK027(sha)001:6713: glegs bam lag tu gtad pa yin //
NK027(sha)001:6714: dam chos mdzod chen theg pa gsum //
NK027(sha)001:6715: ma lus nyan pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6716: gsang ba gsang chen gsang ba rnams //
NK027(sha)001:6717: ston pas nges par gsung pa'i don //
NK027(sha)001:6718: nyan cing yid la 'dzin pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6720: chos thams cad nyan pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:6721: gsang bas bka' mtha' dag nyan pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:6722: slob ma'i lce la snang ba mtha' yas bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:6723: sarba ta th+aa ga ta d+harma sid+d+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)001:6724: gnyis pa las kyi dbang las /
NK027(sha)001:6725: sna tshogs rdo rje thugs te /
NK027(sha)001:6726: zhi rgyas dbang dang drag po yi //
NK027(sha)001:6727: rigs su gyur pa ma lus pa //
NK027(sha)001:6728: dgos pa thams cad byed par 'gyur //
NK027(sha)001:6729: las rnams rgya mtsho thams cad kun //
NK027(sha)001:6730: grub rtags rdo rje rgya gram rdzas //
NK027(sha)001:6731: thabs mchog dbang ni sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:6732: zhi rgyas dbang drag mngon spyod dang //
NK027(sha)001:6733: mnan bskrad rmong rngo 'gug pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:6734: gang byed las rnams 'grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:6735: bya ba phrin las kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:6736: 'gro don thogs pa med pa'i dbang dam pa gsum pa 'chad pa chos kyi 'khor lo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6737: gser gyi 'khor lo rtsib stong mu khyud ldan //
NK027(sha)001:6738: 'jig rten kun la kha lo bsgyur ba'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:6739: dbang bskur 'khor lo'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:6740: gzhan gyi re ba bskang ba'i bu mchog 'di //
NK027(sha)001:6741: rgyal po rgyal rigs rmad du byung ba bzhin //
NK027(sha)001:6742: rgyal tshab chos kyi rgyal bu byung bas na //
NK027(sha)001:6743: gsung rab dam pa'i mdzad gsum sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:6744: bdud rtsis slob ma'i tshogs kun skyong ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:6745: bstan pa sgrogs pa'i sa la gnas pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:6746: rdo rje rgyal por mnga' gsol dbang mchog 'di //
NK027(sha)001:6747: theg pa dgu yi rtags bcas sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:6748: chos 'chad pa'i bka' gsung rab mtha' dag bshad pa'i dbang dam pa d+har+m+aa tsakra a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)001:6749: bzhi pa rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang la /
NK027(sha)001:6750: po ti dang dril bu thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6751: bstan pa sgrogs pa'i sa la gnas byas nas //
NK027(sha)001:6752: rdo rje rgyal po dpal gyi dbang mchog 'di //
NK027(sha)001:6753: theg pa dgu yi rtags dang bcas pas sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:6754: glegs bam thogs te rdo rje rtse dagu'o //
NK027(sha)001:6755: rdo rje rgyal po 'gro ba 'dren pa'i dpal //
NK027(sha)001:6756: kun la bu bzhin brtse ba'i ngang tshul can //
NK027(sha)001:6757: rgyal ba'i gdung tshab bstan pa rin chen 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:6758: chos la dbang 'byor rgyal thabs thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:6759: rdo rje rgyal po thabs mkhas thugs rje yi //
NK027(sha)001:6760: brlabs kyi 'gro ba 'dren pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6762: dang po dom dred kyi gdan thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6763: dbang phyug la sogs dregs pa'i tshogs //
NK027(sha)001:6764: smon lam chen po brten byed pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:6765: dreg pa sgrol ba dbang gi gdan //
NK027(sha)001:6766: bstan pa zil gnon dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6767: gsum pa brtul zhugs dom gyi gdan /
NK027(sha)001:6768: mnyam rdzogs brtul zhugs chen po yi //
NK027(sha)001:6769: thams cad du ni thogs med phyir //
NK027(sha)001:6770: zil gnon dom gyi dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:6771: brtul zhugs gsum gyis dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6774: lha chen gdan gyi dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:6775: khams gsum dreg pa zil gnon pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:6776: dbang dam pa lnga pa khyu mchog gi gdan khri thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6777: rang snang yon tan mang po brjid //
NK027(sha)001:6778: rtsol ba zil gyi gnon byed phyir //
NK027(sha)001:6779: khyu mchog gzugs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:6780: thams cad zil gnon dbang thog shog /
NK027(sha)001:6781: drug pa ma h+aa'i gdan khri /
NK027(sha)001:6782: phung po khams sogs don rig pas //
NK027(sha)001:6783: yon tan mang po brjid snang phyir //
NK027(sha)001:6784: ma he gzugs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:6785: kun las mdzes pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6787: thabs la rol pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:6788: gdul bya kun la mthun 'jug phyir //
NK027(sha)001:6789: dad pa gzig gi dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:6790: thabs la mkhas pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6792: rgyu 'bras gnyis med sems nyid la //
NK027(sha)001:6793: sa lam dang po'i rims bral phyir //
NK027(sha)001:6794: mkhyen pa stag gi dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:6795: khyad par 'phags pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6797: sa rnams non pa'i rtags mchog gdan khri'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:6798: lha chen la sogs zhing chen nyi zla bcas //
NK027(sha)001:6799: che mchog ma he stag gzig dom gyi khri //
NK027(sha)001:6800: yon tan rdzogs pa'i gdan du sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:6801: drug pa khyad par gyi rin po che sna bdun las /
NK027(sha)001:6803: 'khor lo bskor zhing gcod pa'i rtags //
NK027(sha)001:6804: skye ba rnam bzhi rgyun chad pa //
NK027(sha)001:6805: de ring khyod la sbyin pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6806: skye bzhi bsgrod pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6807: 'khor lo'i dbang dam pa bskur bas skye ba rnam bzhi las sgrol ba'i dbang lha yum thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6808: dbang phyug la sogs bde ba'i yum //
NK027(sha)001:6809: thugs rjes gzungs kyi rig ma ste //
NK027(sha)001:6810: de ring khyod la sbyin pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6811: thabs la spyod pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6812: lha yum gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:6813: thabs kyi spyod pa 'jug pa'i rdo rje thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6814: chos rnams kun la thog med pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:6815: blon po kun ldan rdo rje sems //
NK027(sha)001:6816: de ring khyod la bskur ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:6817: shes bya mkhyen pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6819: rdo rje sems dpa'i blo gros phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang stobs po che thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6820: khams gsum bsdam pa kun 'dul ba //
NK027(sha)001:6821: stobs chen khro bo chen po ste //
NK027(sha)001:6822: de ring khyod la bskur ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:6823: bdud dpung 'dul ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6824: stobs po che'i dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:6825: bdud mchog mtha' dag 'dul zhing dbang dam pa glang po che thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6826: theg pa'i mtha' la gnas pa rnams //
NK027(sha)001:6827: zil gnon theg chen glang gi gzugs //
NK027(sha)001:6828: de ring khyod la sbyin pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6829: bsdam pa zil gnon dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:6830: byang chub sems dpa' spos kyi glang po che'i dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:6831: stobs bcu pha rol zil gyi gnon pa'i dbang dam pa rta mgrin thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6832: thams cad bdag nyid khyab pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6833: dbang phyug kun 'gro rta yi gzugs //
NK027(sha)001:6834: de ring khyod la sbyin pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6835: thogs med rdzu 'phrul thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:6836: khro bo rta mgrin gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:6837: gang la thogs med rdzu 'phrul gyi dbang dam pa ka mi spyod pa thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:6838: rnam shes phung po sangs rgyas pas //
NK027(sha)001:6839: rdo rje rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK027(sha)001:6840: 'byung ba nam mkha' rnam dag pa //
NK027(sha)001:6841: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK027(sha)001:6842: rtags kyi phyag rgya chen po 'di //
NK027(sha)001:6843: de ring khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:6845: mum da du shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)001:6846: a b+hi sems dpa' rdo rje /
NK027(sha)001:6847: sems dpa' rdo rje dbying la blta //
NK027(sha)001:6848: rten ma rdo rje'i 'gyur ba med //
NK027(sha)001:6849: rtags kyi phyag rgya chen po 'di //
NK027(sha)001:6850: de ring khyod la badz+ra sat+wa h'u /
NK027(sha)001:6851: badz+ra tish+tha h'u a b+hi rdo rje rin chen /
NK027(sha)001:6852: rdo rje rin chen chos don gsal //
NK027(sha)001:6853: rdo rje 'bar ba mtha' gnyis srog /
NK027(sha)001:6854: rtags kyi phyag rgya chen po 'di //
NK027(sha)001:6855: de ring khyod badz+ra rat+na h'u /
NK027(sha)001:6857: a b+hi chos kyi rdo rje /
NK027(sha)001:6858: chos kyi rdo rje chos don rigs //
NK027(sha)001:6859: rdo rje sdud ma dbyings su sbyor //
NK027(sha)001:6860: rtags kyi phyag rgya chen po 'di //
NK027(sha)001:6861: de ring khyod la d+harma badz+ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:6863: badz+ra h'u a b+hi las rigs rdo rje /
NK027(sha)001:6864: las rigs rdo rje dbyings su sbyor //
NK027(sha)001:6865: rdo rje bskyed ma cir mi gnas //
NK027(sha)001:6866: rtags kyi phyag rgya chen po 'di //
NK027(sha)001:6867: de ring khyod la badz+ra karma h'u /
NK027(sha)001:6868: tsan tra dz+wa la h'u a b+hi kha 'od rim las /
NK027(sha)001:6869: kun rdzogs sems dpa' rigs par ldan //
NK027(sha)001:6870: bsam pas 'byung ba'i rin po che //
NK027(sha)001:6871: de ring gdul bya ma lus re ba bskangs //
NK027(sha)001:6872: rdo rje rin chen gyi dbang gdul bya'i re ba bzhin bskangs ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:6873: skye la dbang bsgyur rgyal po mnyes pa'i thabs //
NK027(sha)001:6874: pha rol dpung 'joms srid thub 'dzin pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:6875: bdag gzhan don grub rdzu 'phrul rkang par ldan //
NK027(sha)001:6876: dgos 'dod yid bzhin bskang ba'i rin po che //
NK027(sha)001:6877: rgyal po de la thabs kyis sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:6878: ga bdun pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi dbang ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:6879: de ni rgyal ba'i yin pas na /
NK027(sha)001:6880: phyag rgya chen po'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:6881: ris sam 'bur ram lugs blugs pa /
NK027(sha)001:6882: phyag rgya gzugs brnyan de spyi bor bzhag /
NK027(sha)001:6885: gtso gzungs 'brel ba'i phyag rgya ste //
NK027(sha)001:6887: rdo rje rin chen pad+ma gri //
NK027(sha)001:6888: 'brel ba yum gyi yin pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:6889: 'bar ma nu me sdud chu lho //
NK027(sha)001:6890: rgyud dkrug chu na ma ki lho //
NK027(sha)001:6891: lung cus man nga ga de ltar gab //
NK027(sha)001:6892: me ni gdong dkar gso tsam nub //
NK027(sha)001:6895: gzugs kyis phung po sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:6896: sangs rgyas rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK027(sha)001:6897: 'byung ba sa ni sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:6898: de bzhin spyan dang lhun gyis grub //
NK027(sha)001:6901: a b+hi sems dpa' rdo rje /
NK027(sha)001:6902: sems dpa' rdo rje dbyings la blta //
NK027(sha)001:6903: rdo rje sgeg mo 'gyur ba med //
NK027(sha)001:6904: rtags kyi phyag rgya chen po 'di //
NK027(sha)001:6905: de ring khyed la sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:6907: ma le a b+h+ai rdo rje rgyal po /
NK027(sha)001:6908: rdo rje rgyal po mtha' bzhi 'joms //
NK027(sha)001:6909: bdug pa dbyings kyi tshim par byed //
NK027(sha)001:6910: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra ra dza /
NK027(sha)001:6912: a b+hi rdo rje chags pa /
NK027(sha)001:6913: rdo rje chags pa mtha' gnyis 'joms //
NK027(sha)001:6914: rdo rje lcags kyu de bzhin 'khyug /
NK027(sha)001:6915: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra hoh badz+ra am gu sha dzah a b+hi rdo rje lag pa /
NK027(sha)001:6916: rdo rje legs pa gsal bar bskul //
NK027(sha)001:6917: sgrol ma gnyis med tshul gyi gsal //
NK027(sha)001:6918: rtags kyi phyag de ring badz+ra sat+wa /
NK027(sha)001:6919: badz+ra de sha ra ti a b+hi 'od rim du /
NK027(sha)001:6920: rdo rje lcags kyu mda' gzhu'i rgya //
NK027(sha)001:6921: me long pog phur lcags kyu'i phreng //
NK027(sha)001:6922: rgyal mtshan se gol tog rgya gram //
NK027(sha)001:6923: rtags kyi de ring zhes gsungs pas /
NK027(sha)001:6925: tshor ba'i phung po sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:6926: rin chen rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK027(sha)001:6927: 'byung ba chu ni sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:6928: rin chen dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK027(sha)001:6929: rtags kyi phyag rgya de ring swa rat+na d+h+rig /
NK027(sha)001:6930: mum mo ha ra ti a b+hi rdo rje rin chen /
NK027(sha)001:6931: rdo rje rin chen mnyam nyid gsal //
NK027(sha)001:6932: phreng ba ma 'dres yongs rdzogs gsal //
NK027(sha)001:6933: rtags kyi de ring rat+na tram /
NK027(sha)001:6934: badz+ra ma le tram a rdo rje nyi ma /
NK027(sha)001:6935: rdo rje nyi ma gsal mtha' gnon //
NK027(sha)001:6936: me tog mtha' bral rang rig mdzes //
NK027(sha)001:6937: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra sur+ya gram /
NK027(sha)001:6939: a b+hi rdo rje rgyal mtshan /
NK027(sha)001:6940: rgyal mtshan mi gnon nga rgyal ldan //
NK027(sha)001:6941: zhags pas ma lus sems su sdud //
NK027(sha)001:6942: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra he ru tram /
NK027(sha)001:6943: badz+ra ba sha hri a b+hi rdo rje zhags pa /
NK027(sha)001:6944: zhags pa rang rig dgyes ldan pa //
NK027(sha)001:6945: rdo rje bde byed mtha' dang bral //
NK027(sha)001:6946: rtags kyi phyag rgya chen po 'di //
NK027(sha)001:6947: de badz+ra rat+na d+h+rig badz+ra ra tri tram /
NK027(sha)001:6949: rin chen gdugs kyi nyi ma dang //
NK027(sha)001:6950: rgyal mtshan po phreng rin chen dang //
NK027(sha)001:6951: me tog zhags pa bsil g.yab bo //
NK027(sha)001:6952: rtags kyi de ring zhes gsungs pa /
NK027(sha)001:6954: 'du shes phung po sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:6955: pad+ma'i rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK027(sha)001:6956: 'byung ba me ni sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:6957: pad+ma dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK027(sha)001:6958: rtags kyi de ring a ro lig /
NK027(sha)001:6959: pyam ra ga ra ti a b+hi rdo rje chos /
NK027(sha)001:6960: chos ni rang rig cir ma chags //
NK027(sha)001:6961: dbyings ni de don gsal bar byed //
NK027(sha)001:6962: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra d+harma h+r+aih g+hin+d+ha h+r+aih+aa b+hi rdo rje rnon po /
NK027(sha)001:6963: rdo rje rnon po mtha' rnams gcod //
NK027(sha)001:6964: sgron ma ma skyes don gsal byed //
NK027(sha)001:6965: rtags kyi de ring ta k+shi tri /
NK027(sha)001:6966: badz+ra a lo ke h+r+aih a b+hih rdo rje 'khor lo /
NK027(sha)001:6968: thams cad der 'bral lcags sgrog la //
NK027(sha)001:6969: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra tsakra h+r+aih badz+ra s+pho ta h+r+aiha b+hi rdo rje smras pa /
NK027(sha)001:6970: smra ba rig gsal brjod pa 'dra //
NK027(sha)001:6971: gsal bkra kun la gsal bshad byed //
NK027(sha)001:6972: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra p+aa sha h+r+aih badz+ra ra ga ra ti h+r+aiha 'od rim las /
NK027(sha)001:6975: pi wang mar me lcags sgrog dang //
NK027(sha)001:6976: rma bya'i mdangs rtags kyi de ring zhes pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:6978: 'du byed phung po sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:6979: las kyi rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK027(sha)001:6980: 'byung ba rlung ni sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:6981: las kyi dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK027(sha)001:6982: rtags kyis de ring ha pra dz+ny+aa d+h+rig /
NK027(sha)001:6983: tam badz+ra ra ti a rdo rje las rab /
NK027(sha)001:6984: las ni don bdun gcig par rigs //
NK027(sha)001:6985: gar ni gsal bar snang ba'i sgo //
NK027(sha)001:6986: rtags kyi phyag rgya chen po 'di //
NK027(sha)001:6988: badz+ra nir+ya a b+hi rdo rje srung ba /
NK027(sha)001:6989: rdo rje bsrung ba mtha' ma rigs //
NK027(sha)001:6990: byug pa de don blo rig pa //
NK027(sha)001:6991: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra rak+sha ha /
NK027(sha)001:6992: badz+ra g+han+d+he ha a b+he rdo rje gnod sbyin /
NK027(sha)001:6993: gnod sbyin mtha' gnyis za bar byed //
NK027(sha)001:6994: rdo rje dril bu dge gsal sgrogs pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:6995: rtags kyis de ring badz+ra yak+sha ha /
NK027(sha)001:6996: badz+ra g+hen+d+he hoh a b+hi rdo rje khur tshur /
NK027(sha)001:6997: khu tshur gnyis med don rig pa //
NK027(sha)001:6998: 'beb pa de nyid snang bar byed //
NK027(sha)001:6999: rtags kyi de ring badz+ra sin d+hi ha /
NK027(sha)001:7000: badz+ra a we sha ya ha /
NK027(sha)001:7002: ral gri rdo rje phreng ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:7003: mche ba khu tshur gang byug pa //
NK027(sha)001:7005: rtags kyis de ring lung a nu'i rigs bdag kun bzang thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7007: byang chub sems mchog ye shes rdo rje'i thugs //
NK027(sha)001:7008: srid gsum dbang bsgyur thams cad mkhyen pa'i dpal //
NK027(sha)001:7009: bsnyel ba mi mnga' 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:7010: kun bzang rdo rje yid la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)001:7011: e ma hoh kun bzang rdo rje yid la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)001:7012: rig pa tshur snang sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7013: sangs rgyas thams cad bskyed mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:7014: kun tu bzang po'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7015: h'u h'u h'u badz+ra tsit+ta h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7018: gdod nas ma byung ma skyes chos kyis dbyings //
NK027(sha)001:7019: ma skyes ma 'gag dngos por 'dzin dang bral //
NK027(sha)001:7020: 'byung byed thams cad bskyed pa yum gyi tshul //
NK027(sha)001:7021: bzang mo bya ba mo la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)001:7022: phyi yi yul ni sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7023: snang srid thams cad chos kyis dbyings //
NK027(sha)001:7024: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i yum //
NK027(sha)001:7025: kun tu bzang mo'i dbang mchog ni //
NK027(sha)001:7026: a a +aah badz+ra sa man+ta a b+hi rgyud ma hi'i gtso bo rdo rje sems dpa' thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7027: ma skyes rdo rje thabs la rol //
NK027(sha)001:7028: don dam dbyer med rol mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:7029: thabs dang shes rab byang chub sems //
NK027(sha)001:7030: rdo rje sems dpa' bdag la dgongs //
NK027(sha)001:7031: rnam shes phung po sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7032: rdo rje'i rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK027(sha)001:7033: sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs yin pas //
NK027(sha)001:7034: rdo rje sems dpa'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7035: 'byung ba nam mkha'i sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7036: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK027(sha)001:7037: rdo rje rigs kyi yum yin pas //
NK027(sha)001:7038: kun tu bzang mo'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7040: mum da du sh+aa ri a b+hi rnam snang thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7041: gzugs kyi phung po gnas dag pa //
NK027(sha)001:7042: de bzhin rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK027(sha)001:7043: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku yin pas //
NK027(sha)001:7044: rnam par snang mdzad dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7045: 'byung ba sa ni sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7046: rdo rje rigs kyis dbang phyug ma //
NK027(sha)001:7047: bder gshegs rigs kyis yum yin pas //
NK027(sha)001:7048: sangs rgyas spyan gyi dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7049: 'dzi na 'dzig lam te sha ra ti a b+hi rin 'byung thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7050: tshor ba'i phung po sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7051: rin chen rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK027(sha)001:7052: sangs rgyas kun gyi yon tan gyi //
NK027(sha)001:7053: rin chen 'byung ldan dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7054: 'byung ba chu yi sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7055: rin chen rigs kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK027(sha)001:7056: rin chen rigs kyi yum yin pas //
NK027(sha)001:7057: ma ma ki yi dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7059: mum mo ha ra ti a b+hi snang mtha' thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7060: 'du shes phung po sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7061: pad+ma'i rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK027(sha)001:7062: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung yin pas //
NK027(sha)001:7063: snang ba mtha' yas dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7064: 'byung ba me ni sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7065: pad+ma rigs kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK027(sha)001:7066: pad+ma rigs kyi yum yin pas //
NK027(sha)001:7067: gos dkar mo yi dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7068: a ro lig pyam ra ga ra ti a b+hi don grub thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7069: 'du byed phung po sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7070: las kyi rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK027(sha)001:7071: don yod grub pa'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7072: 'byung ba rlung ni sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7073: las kyi dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK027(sha)001:7074: sna tshogs 'dus pa'i yum yin pas //
NK027(sha)001:7075: dam tshig sgrol ma'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7077: tam badz+ra ra sti a b+hi sa snying thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7078: mig gi rnam shes sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7079: byang chub chen po mthong ba'i dpal //
NK027(sha)001:7080: bdag gis mig la bskyed byed pas //
NK027(sha)001:7081: sa yi snying po'i dbang gzugs su snang ba sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7082: byang chub lha mo dkar mo ste //
NK027(sha)001:7083: phyi yi gzugs la bskyed byas pas //
NK027(sha)001:7084: lha mo la s+ye'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7086: h'u la s+ye sa m+aa ya s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)001:7087: a b+hi nam mkha'i snying po thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7088: rna ba'i rnam shes sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7089: byang chub chen po thos pa'i dpal //
NK027(sha)001:7090: bdag gi rna bar bskyed byas pas //
NK027(sha)001:7091: nam mkha'i snying po'i sgra yi yul ni sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7093: yul gyi sgra la bskyed byas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7094: lha mo ma l+ye'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7096: tram ma le sa m+aa ya tram /
NK027(sha)001:7097: a b+hi spyan gzigs thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7098: sna'i rnam shes sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7099: byang chub chen po snam pa'i dpal //
NK027(sha)001:7100: bdag gi sna la bskyed byas pas //
NK027(sha)001:7101: spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7102: tshor zhing yul rnams sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7103: byang chub lha mo r+aa ga ti //
NK027(sha)001:7104: tshor ba'i yul la bskyed byas pas //
NK027(sha)001:7105: lha mo g+hirti dbang h+r+aihha h'u pad+ma b+ha ta ma /
NK027(sha)001:7106: hri g+hirti r+aa ga a mi tam a b+hi phyag na rdo rje thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7107: lce yi rnam shes sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7108: byang chub chen po myong ba'i dpal //
NK027(sha)001:7109: bdag gi lce la bskyed byas pas //
NK027(sha)001:7110: phyag na rdo rje'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7111: bro ba'i yul rnams sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7112: byang chub lha mo in+t+ra ni //
NK027(sha)001:7113: bro ba'i yul la bskyed byas pas //
NK027(sha)001:7114: lha mo dri yi dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7115: dzim ku ru pa ni h+r+aih a nirti r+aa ga ya mi s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)001:7116: a b+hi byams pa thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7117: mthong ba'i dbang po sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7118: byang chub chen po mthong bar byed //
NK027(sha)001:7119: de nyid las ni bskyed byas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7120: byams pa'i dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7121: dbyar dgun ston dpyid sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7122: dus bzhi'i yul rnams sems ma'i sku //
NK027(sha)001:7123: de nyid las ni bskyed byas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7124: d+hush+pe'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:7126: dzahd+hush+pe pra we sha ya s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)001:7127: a b+hi sgrib sel thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7128: thos pa'i dbang po sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7129: byang chub chen po thob par byed //
NK027(sha)001:7130: de nyid las ni bskyed byas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7131: sgrib pa rnams sel dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7132: de bzhin nyid las bskyed byas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7133: lha mo 'od mdzes ma yi sku //
NK027(sha)001:7134: de nyid badz+ra push+pe'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7135: thim ni sa ram pa ye /
NK027(sha)001:7136: h'u push+pe a we sha ya s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)001:7137: a b+hi kun bzang thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7138: tshor ba'i phung po sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7139: byang chub chen po tshor byed pa //
NK027(sha)001:7140: dbang po de las bskyed byas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7141: kun tu bzang mo'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7142: yul dus bzhi yang sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7143: lha mo mun sel 'od kyi mchog /
NK027(sha)001:7144: yul de nyid las bskyed byas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7145: a lo ke yi dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7147: bam d+he wa su ki ni /
NK027(sha)001:7149: myong ba'i dbang po sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7150: byang chub chen po myong byed pa //
NK027(sha)001:7151: dbang po de las 'jam dpal gzhon nu'i dbang mchog dus bzhi dus ni sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7152: dbang po de las bskyed lha mo 'joms byed bde ldan ma //
NK027(sha)001:7153: dus de'i yul la sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7154: badz+ra g+han+d+he'i dbang wa ki shwa ri mum sh+r+ai /
NK027(sha)001:7155: h+r+aihg+han+d+he tsit+ta hoh a b+hi gshin rje gshed thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7156: phyin ci log bzhi sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7157: 'joms byed khro bo'i rig shes te //
NK027(sha)001:7158: dreg shes nyid las bskur bskyed pa //
NK027(sha)001:7159: gshin rje gshed po'i dbang de yi yul bzhi rtag par ma yin khro mo ste //
NK027(sha)001:7160: de nyid las ni sku bskyed pa //
NK027(sha)001:7161: ro lang ma yi dbang stobs chen thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7162: phyin ci log bzhis sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7163: 'joms byed khro bo reg byed ste //
NK027(sha)001:7164: de nyid las ni gzhan gyi mi thub dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7165: de yi yul bzhi chad par ma yin khro mo nyid //
NK027(sha)001:7166: de nyid las ni sku bskyed pa //
NK027(sha)001:7167: mi pham ma yi dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7169: phyin ci log bzhi sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7170: 'joms byed khro bo reg byed sku //
NK027(sha)001:7171: de nyid rta mgrin dbang mchog khyed la sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7172: de'i yul bdag tu ma yin khro mo nyid //
NK027(sha)001:7173: yul de nyid la bskur bskyed pa //
NK027(sha)001:7174: khro gnyer ma yi dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7176: phyin ci log bzhi sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7177: 'joms byed khro bo reg byed de //
NK027(sha)001:7178: rig pa nyid las skur bskyed pa //
NK027(sha)001:7179: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7180: de'i yul bzhi sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7181: mtshan mar ma yin khro mo'i sku //
NK027(sha)001:7182: yul de nyid las skur bskyed pa //
NK027(sha)001:7183: ral gcig ma yi dbang kun bzang thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7184: yid kyi rnam shes sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7185: byed po kun tu bzang mo ste //
NK027(sha)001:7186: de nyid las ni kun tu bzang mo'i bzang mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7187: chos nyid skye med sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7188: bya ba kun tu bzang mo byung //
NK027(sha)001:7189: de nyid las ni skur bskyed pa //
NK027(sha)001:7190: kun tu bzang mo'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7192: nga rgyal thams cad sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7193: brgya byin lha yi dbang por byung //
NK027(sha)001:7194: de nyid las ni lha yi thub pa'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7195: mu ne krem a b+hi lha min thub pa thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7196: phrag dog thams cad sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7197: lha ma yin la thag bzang ris //
NK027(sha)001:7198: de nyid las ni skur bskyed pa //
NK027(sha)001:7199: lha min thub pa'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7200: mu ne brem a b+hi mi'i thub pa thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7201: 'dod chags thams cad sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7202: bcom ldan sh+aakya thub pa ste //
NK027(sha)001:7203: de nyid las ni sh+aakya thub pa'i dbang mu ne t+r+aum a byol song thub pa'i sku thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7204: gti mug thams cad sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7205: sangs rgyas seng ge rab brten byung //
NK027(sha)001:7206: de nyid las ni sprul sku byung //
NK027(sha)001:7207: byol song thub pa'i mu ne k+shem a yi dwags thub pa'i sku thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7208: ser sna thams cad sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7209: sangs rgyas kha 'bar sku byung ste //
NK027(sha)001:7210: ser sna nyid las sku bskyed pa //
NK027(sha)001:7211: yi dwags thub pa'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7212: mu ne ye +aah dmyal ba'i thub pa thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7213: zhe sdang ye nas sangs rgyas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7214: ston pa chos kyi rgyal po byung //
NK027(sha)001:7215: zhe sdang rgyu la sku bskyed pa //
NK027(sha)001:7216: dmyal ba'i thub pa'i dbang +aahmh'u h+r+aihhah gnas dang dbang por bkod la /
NK027(sha)001:7218: tshig btsan yul la dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:7219: rgyal ba'i bka' rtags phyag rgya'i dbang /
NK027(sha)001:7220: sku lnga yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur /
NK027(sha)001:7222: phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyi /
NK027(sha)001:7223: rigs kyi bu la phyag rgya bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:7224: sku lnga yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:7225: rigs kyis bu la rgyal po'i bka' rtags kyi phyag rgyas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:7226: rgyud ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK027(sha)001:7227: lung a nu yo ga'i lha tshogs zhi khro rab 'byams kyi sku lnga yongs su rdzogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7228: chos sku longs sku sprul sku rdo rje'i sku /
NK027(sha)001:7229: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:7231: de yan chad zhi ba'i dbang bzhi'o //
NK027(sha)001:7232: 'di khro bo'i dbang a nu la bsdus te bstan pa tsaka li nyung bas dbang thob /
NK027(sha)001:7233: don la ma h+aa la zhi khro gnyis yod /
NK027(sha)001:7234: de nas khro bo'i dbang la /
NK027(sha)001:7235: dang po dbang mchog gi sku thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7236: bcom ldan dbang chog he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:7238: dbu gsum dang por byung ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:7239: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK027(sha)001:7240: sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa'i dbu //
NK027(sha)001:7241: khams gsum mya ngan 'das pa'i zhal //
NK027(sha)001:7242: dbu gsum bar du rngams pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:7243: g.yas sngo g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK027(sha)001:7244: thabs dang shes rab sems kyi dbu //
NK027(sha)001:7245: srid gsum dbyings su rdzogs pa'i zhal //
NK027(sha)001:7246: dbu gsum tha mar rngams pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:7247: g.yas g.yon dbu gsum mthing ba'i zhal //
NK027(sha)001:7248: lung dang man ngag sems kyi dbu //
NK027(sha)001:7249: khams gsum re ba bskang ba'i zhal //
NK027(sha)001:7250: bco brgyad phyag rgya rol pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:7251: stong pa chos kyi dbyings su thim //
NK027(sha)001:7252: bco brgyad phyag na bsnams pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:7253: rdo rje glo snying zhing chung g.yas //
NK027(sha)001:7254: b+hud+d+ha zhing chung ti ra g.yon //
NK027(sha)001:7255: zhing zhags nyi ma khyung chen g.yas //
NK027(sha)001:7256: zhing chen zla ba 'ug pa g.yon //
NK027(sha)001:7257: me dang rgya mtsho ga bu g.yas //
NK027(sha)001:7258: rlung dang rin chen ri rab g.yon //
NK027(sha)001:7259: yon tan bco brgyad dbyings su rdzogs //
NK027(sha)001:7260: khro rgyal rgyan rnams sku la brjid //
NK027(sha)001:7261: kro ti mthing nag 'khril ba'i tshul //
NK027(sha)001:7263: rgyud rgyal che mchog he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:7264: dbang mchog sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:7267: ston pa kun bzang gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7268: khro rgyal kun gyi rje btsan yab //
NK027(sha)001:7269: sku dang phyag rgya mngon rdzogs pa //
NK027(sha)001:7270: che mchog he ru ka yi dbang sbyin no //
NK027(sha)001:7271: kun tu bzang mo'i chos nyid gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7272: khro mo kun gyi che btsun yum //
NK027(sha)001:7273: shes rab dbyings la skur bskyod pa //
NK027(sha)001:7274: kro ti shwa ri'i dbang sbyin no //
NK027(sha)001:7275: ka ta ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:7276: ka ta kro ti shwa ri h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:7277: a b+hi che mchog thog la /
NK027(sha)001:7279: ston pa kun bzang gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7280: khro rgyal kun gyi rje btsan yab //
NK027(sha)001:7281: sku dang phyag rgya mngon rdzogs pa //
NK027(sha)001:7282: che mchog he ru ka yi dbang sbyin no //
NK027(sha)001:7283: kun tu bzang mo gnas gyur pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:7284: khro mo kun gyi rje btsun yum //
NK027(sha)001:7285: shes rab dbyings las skur bskyed pa //
NK027(sha)001:7286: kro ti shwa ri'i dbang sbyin no //
NK027(sha)001:7287: seng ha ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:7288: seng ha ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:7289: a b+hi ston pa kun bzang yab yum gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7290: che mchog he ru ka yab yum dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7292: khro mo'i sku dang phyag rgya mngon rdzogs pa //
NK027(sha)001:7293: che mchog yab yum dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7294: kro ta kro ti shwa ri h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:7295: a b+hi e ma hoh chos kun sku la yongs rdzogs chos kyi sku //
NK027(sha)001:7296: rdo rje che mchog phyag 'tshal he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:7297: theg pa dgu dang 'khor ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK027(sha)001:7298: phyag rgya gcig tu bkod nas rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK027(sha)001:7299: 'khor ba dang ni mya ngan 'das pa'i chos //
NK027(sha)001:7300: dpa' bo chen po'i gdan du brjid cing rol //
NK027(sha)001:7301: 'dren gyi zla med che btsan gcig pu nyid //
NK027(sha)001:7302: gsang mchog 'bar ba'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:7305: dpal chen po'i sku la gtsug tor rgyal mtshan rtse mo la /
NK027(sha)001:7306: gser gyi tog stong ni rdzogs pa chen po dang /
NK027(sha)001:7307: sku dang sku'i rgyan la rdzogs pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:7308: bskyed pa'i rnal 'byor gyi gdan gyi 'og nor bu rin po che /
NK027(sha)001:7309: steng nas rdo rje rtse gsum gyi brag gtam pa la /
NK027(sha)001:7313: ri rab kyi kha mu tig gi cal dang /
NK027(sha)001:7314: karma gar+b+ha'i 'od khrig pa'i nor bu 'od 'bar brag la byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK027(sha)001:7317: lha mi yang 'khor ba gzugs med pas khams dang /
NK027(sha)001:7318: keng rus kyi ri rab dang /
NK027(sha)001:7319: gzugs khams zhing chen gyi sa dang /
NK027(sha)001:7320: 'dod khams kyi chags pa thams cad khrag gi rgya
NK027(sha)001:7321: mtsho'i mngon par mtho zhing phyag rgya rnam par spro
NK027(sha)001:7322: ba'i ting 'dzin dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK027(sha)001:7323: / de'ang che mchog mdo ltar na /
NK027(sha)001:7325: gnam zhal phyag gnyis sku la 'khril /
NK027(sha)001:7328: khro bo smug po yab yum /
NK027(sha)001:7330: cho ga bdud rtsi la dgos pa ltar na /
NK027(sha)001:7332: yum gyi zhal du bcug pa'i yum gyi mkha' nas /
NK027(sha)001:7333: badz+ra he ru ka phyed ma thon bdud rtsi bab pa'i sbyor ba gsungs so //
NK027(sha)001:7334: badz+ra he ru ka thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7335: rdo rje sems dpa' gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7338: mchod cing byin rlabs gsal bsgrub pas //
NK027(sha)001:7339: badz+ra he ru ka'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7340: nam mkha' kun bzang gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7341: khro mo dbang phyug sku gsal ba //
NK027(sha)001:7342: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med //
NK027(sha)001:7343: yab yum mchod cing gsal bsgrub pas //
NK027(sha)001:7344: badz+ra kro ta shwa ri'i dbang mchog sbyin /
NK027(sha)001:7345: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro ti shwa ri sa m+aa ya h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7346: a b+hi b+hud+d+ha he ru ka thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7347: rnam par snang mdzad gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7350: mchod cing bsgrub ste byin rlabs pas //
NK027(sha)001:7351: bud+d+ha he ru ka yi dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7352: sangs rgyas spyan ma gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7353: khro mo dbang phyug skur gsal ba //
NK027(sha)001:7354: thabs dang shes rab byang chub sems //
NK027(sha)001:7355: spyan drangs mchod cing bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:7356: kro ti shwa ri'i dbang b+hud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7357: b+hud+d+ha kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7358: ru lu ru lu a b+hi rat+na he ru ka thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7359: rin chen 'byung ldan gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7362: spyan bzang mchod cing bsgrub pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:7363: rat+na he ru ka yi ma m+aa ki ni gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7364: 'jigs byed khro mo'i sku gsal ba //
NK027(sha)001:7365: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK027(sha)001:7366: spyan drangs mchod cing bsnyen bsgrub pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:7367: kro ti shwa ri'i rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:7368: rat+na kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)001:7369: ru lu ru lu a b+hi pad+ma he ru ka thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7370: snang ba mtha' yas gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7372: dmar nag 'bar ba'i ral pa can //
NK027(sha)001:7373: bsgom zhing mchod cing bsgrub pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:7374: pad+ma he ru ka yi na bza' dkar mo 'jigs byed chen mo khro mo'i sku //
NK027(sha)001:7375: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK027(sha)001:7376: gnyis med byang chub bsgrub pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:7377: kro ti shwa ri'i pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:7378: pad+ma kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)001:7379: ru lu a g+hi karma he ru ka thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7380: don yod grub pa gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7383: gsal bar bskyed cing mchod bsgrub pa //
NK027(sha)001:7384: karma he ru ka yi dam tshig sgrol ma gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7385: 'jigs byed khro mo'i cha lugs bzhin //
NK027(sha)001:7386: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK027(sha)001:7387: lhag pa byang chub sems 'phros pas //
NK027(sha)001:7388: kro ti shwa ri'i karma sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:7389: karma kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)001:7390: ru lu a b+hi rak+sha he ru ka thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7391: mthu stobs mnga' bdag gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7392: sgrol byed chen po bdud rnams 'joms //
NK027(sha)001:7393: thod dbyug srin po sgrol la mkhas //
NK027(sha)001:7394: mthing nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK027(sha)001:7395: rak+sha he ru ka lha mo ral gcig gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7396: khro bo yab kyi cha lugs can //
NK027(sha)001:7397: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK027(sha)001:7398: rak+sha kro ti shwa ri'i ma h+aa rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:7399: ma h+aa tsan+d+ha sarba dush+tana ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:7400: ma h+aa rak+sha kro ti shwa ri h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:7401: ru lu a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:7402: e sha ra si ti na ma s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:7403: a b+hi sa nu he ru ka thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7404: mkhyen rab dbang po gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7406: ser nag mdog can 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK027(sha)001:7407: gang bsgrub mthu dang dbang brtson pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:7408: sa nu he ru ka yi 'jigs byed nag mo gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7409: khro mo dbang phyug kun gyi rje //
NK027(sha)001:7410: sprul pa yang sprul kun gyi rje //
NK027(sha)001:7411: sa nu kro ti'i ma h+aa sa na sh+r+ai he ru ka sa nu kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)001:7412: a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:7413: e sha ra si ti na mah ru lu a b+hi g+hu h+ya thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7414: thugs rje'i bdag po gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7415: gsang ba'i don la mnga' mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:7416: dmar nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK027(sha)001:7417: dus rnams rtag tu gsang ba'i lha //
NK027(sha)001:7418: g+hu h+ya he ru ka yi gsang ba'i lha mo gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7419: khro mo chen mo gsang ba'i lha //
NK027(sha)001:7420: gsang ba'i don la bskul byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:7421: g+hu h+ya kro ti'i g+hu h+ya sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan d+ha /
NK027(sha)001:7422: g+hu h+ya kro ti shwa ri /
NK027(sha)001:7423: ru lu a b+hi yak+sha thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7424: badz+ra ya k+sha gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7425: dpal ldan dam tshig mnga' mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:7426: ljang nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK027(sha)001:7427: bskal pa brgyar yang dam tshig lha //
NK027(sha)001:7428: rak+sha he ru ka yi khro mo dam tshig bya ra mkhan //
NK027(sha)001:7429: sangs rgyas sems can 'da' mi byed //
NK027(sha)001:7430: dam tshig dbyings su bskul byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:7431: yak+sha kro ti'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:7432: ma h+aa yak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:7433: ma h+aa tsan+da sarba dush+tan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:7434: ma h+aa yak+sha kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:7435: a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:7438: b+hi she tsa ni ma ga la ni /
NK027(sha)001:7440: ru lu a b+hi ko'u ri thog la /
NK027(sha)001:7441: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK027(sha)001:7442: 'khor lo brgyad kyi phyi rol na //
NK027(sha)001:7443: gru chad brgyad dang glo 'bur du //
NK027(sha)001:7444: khro mo brgyad kyi bskor ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:7445: sa yi snying po gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7446: srin mo chen mo ging rus brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7447: dkar mo mthu rtsal bskul byed pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:7448: badz+ra he ru ka yi badz+ra ke'u ri ha ha ha ru lu a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:7449: e sha ra pi ti na ma /
NK027(sha)001:7450: b+he sha tsa ni pi ti h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7451: a b+hi tsi ru thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7452: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK027(sha)001:7453: 'khor lo brgyad kyi phyi rol na //

NK027(sha)001:7465: gru chad brgyad dang glo 'bur du //

NK027(sha)001:7472: e sha ra sid+d+hi na ma b+hi sha ta ni si ti h'u /

NK027(sha)001:7487: srin mo nang grol 'dren ma brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7488: srin mo mthu rtsal 'ching byed ma //

NK027(sha)001:7491: ru lu a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:7492: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa na si ti h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7493: a b+hi kas ma ri thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7494: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK027(sha)001:7495: 'khor lo brgyad kyi phyi rol na //
NK027(sha)001:7496: gru chad khro mo brgyad kyi bskor ba ni //

NK027(sha)001:7499: sme sha'i mthu rtsal nyams byed pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:7500: kasma ri'i karma ri ha ha ha /
NK027(sha)001:7501: ru lu a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:7502: e sha ra si ti na mah b+hi sha tsa ni si ti h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7503: a b+hi sme sha ni thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7504: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK027(sha)001:7505: 'khor lo brgyad kyi phyi rol na //
NK027(sha)001:7506: gru chad brgyad dang khro mo kun tu bzang mo'i gnas gyur pas //
NK027(sha)001:7507: nub byang srin mo srog gcod brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7508: gtum mo'i mthu rtsal dbang byed pa //
NK027(sha)001:7509: sme sha na'i dbang badz+ra sme sha ne ha ha ha /
NK027(sha)001:7510: ru lu a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:7511: e sha ra sid+d+hi ti na mah b+hi sha tsa ni si ti h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7512: a b+hi tsan+d+ha li thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7513: dbang gi 'khor lo gru chad khro mo 'jam dpal gzhon nu gnas gyur pas //
NK027(sha)001:7514: byang shar srin mo smyon ma brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7515: ma tshogs mthu rtsal skyes byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:7516: tsan d+ha li yi dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7517: badz+ra tsan d+ha li ha ha ha /
NK027(sha)001:7518: ru lu a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:7519: e sha ra sid+d+hi na mah b+he sha tsa na si ti h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7520: a b+hi sing ha mu kha thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7521: dbang gi dkyil 'khor bar khyams phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du //
NK027(sha)001:7522: phra men brgyad kyi badz+ra la s+ye gnas gyur pas //
NK027(sha)001:7523: shar phyogs srin po seng gdong brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7524: phra men mthu rtsal gzi byin ma //
NK027(sha)001:7525: seng ha mu ka'i dbang badz+ra seng ha mu ka he he he /
NK027(sha)001:7526: ru lu a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:7527: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni si ti /
NK027(sha)001:7528: a b+hi bya kri thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7529: dbang gi bar khyams phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du //
NK027(sha)001:7530: phra men badz+ra ma le gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7531: lho phyogs srin po stag mgo brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7532: phra men mthu rtsal 'joms byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:7533: bya kri mu ka'i badz+ra bya kri mu ka he ha ha /
NK027(sha)001:7534: ru lu a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:7535: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni si ti h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7536: a b+hi sri la mu kha thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7537: dbang gi dkyil 'khor bar khyams phyogs phra men badz+ra girti gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7538: nub phyogs srin po srog len brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7539: phra men mthu rtsal 'dzin byed pa //
NK027(sha)001:7540: sri la mu ka'i badz+ra sri la mu ka he ha ha /
NK027(sha)001:7541: ru lu a b+hi shi e sha ra si ti na mah b+hi sha tsa ni si ti h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7542: a b+hi shwa na mu kha thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7543: dbang gi bar khyams phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du //
NK027(sha)001:7544: phra men badz+ra ni rti gnas gyur pas //
NK027(sha)001:7545: byang phyogs srin po spyang mgo brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7546: phra men mthu rtsal 'dri byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:7547: shwa na mu ka'i shwa na mu ka he ha ha /
NK027(sha)001:7548: ru lu a b+hi e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa na si d+d+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7549: a b+hi kri ta mu kha thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7551: phra men bzhi yi badz+ra d+hush+pe gnas shar lho'i srin po khrag 'thung brtul /
NK027(sha)001:7552: phra men mthu rtsal mgyogs byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:7553: kri ta mu ka'i badz+ra kri ta mu ka he ha ha /
NK027(sha)001:7554: ru lu a e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni sid+d+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7555: a b+hi kang ka mu ka thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7556: dbang gi bar khyams phra men badz+ra push+pe lho nub srin po gang zag brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7557: phra men mthu khyab byed pa /
NK027(sha)001:7558: kang ka mu ka'i badz+ra kang ka mu ka he ha ha /
NK027(sha)001:7559: ru lu a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:7560: e sha ra si ti na mah b+hi sha tsa nisid+d+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7561: a b+hi kha la mu ka thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7562: dbang gi bar khyams phra men badz+ra a lo ke ni gnas gyur pas //
NK027(sha)001:7563: nub byang srin po 'joms byed brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7564: phra men mthu rtsal za byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:7565: kha kha mu ka'i badz+ra kha kha mu kha he ha ha /
NK027(sha)001:7566: ru lu a b+hi a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:7567: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni si ti h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7568: a b+hi hu lu mu kha thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7569: dbang gi bar khyams phra men badz+ra gen+d+he gnas byang shar srin po bskul byed brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7570: phra men mthu rtsal myos byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:7571: hu lu mu ka'i badz+ra hu lu mu kha he ha ha /
NK027(sha)001:7572: ru lu a b+hi e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni si ti h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7573: a b+hi am gu sha thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7575: gru chad bar khyams phyi rim la //
NK027(sha)001:7576: rnam par thar pa'i sgo bzhi ru //
NK027(sha)001:7577: sgo ma bzhi yi bskor ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:7578: lha mo byams pa gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7579: shar gyi srin po rta mgo brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7580: byams chen rnal 'byor mgon mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:7581: am gu sha yi dbang badz+ra ar+ya te dza te nga dza phata /
NK027(sha)001:7582: ru lu ru lu a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:7583: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni si ti h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7584: a b+hi pa sha thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7585: dbang gi dkyil gru chad bar khyams phyi rim la //
NK027(sha)001:7586: rnal 'byor pa yi sgo bzhi ru //
NK027(sha)001:7587: sgo ma bzhi yi bskor ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:7588: lha mo snying rje gnas gyur pas //
NK027(sha)001:7589: lho yi srin po phag mgo brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7590: thugs rjes gzhan la phan 'dog ma //
NK027(sha)001:7591: badz+ra pa sha'i badz+ra a mo ka phata /
NK027(sha)001:7592: ru lu a b+hi she e sha ra si ti
NK027(sha)001:7593: na mah b+hi sha tsa ni si ti +aah lo
NK027(sha)001:7594: ka thogs te / dbang gi dkyil 'khor gru chad bar khyams phyi rim la //
NK027(sha)001:7595: rnal 'byor pa yi sgo bzhi ru //
NK027(sha)001:7596: dga' ba chen po gnas gyur pas //
NK027(sha)001:7597: nub kyi srin po dred mgo brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7598: dga' bas rnal 'byor srung mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:7599: lo ka ma'i badz+ra lo ki bam phata /
NK027(sha)001:7600: ru lu a b+hi she ka w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:7601: e sha ra pi ti na mah b+he sha ni si ti h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7602: a b+hi sa smi pa la thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7603: dbang gi gru chad rnal 'byor pa yi btang snyoms chen po gnas gyur pas //
NK027(sha)001:7604: byang gi srin po spyang mgo brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7605: btang snyoms chen mo'i don mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:7606: sa smi pa yi dbang sbyin no //
NK027(sha)001:7607: badz+ra sa smi pa la ya pa ta hoh ru lu a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:7608: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni si ti h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7609: a b+hi shar gyi spor ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7610: dbang gi rnam bzhi sgo bzhi'i sgo khyud ma //
NK027(sha)001:7611: snam bu phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi brgyad dag tu //
NK027(sha)001:7612: spor ma brgyad kyi bskor ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:7613: nang gi dbang mo gnas gyur pas //
NK027(sha)001:7614: srin mo 'bar ma nyi zhags brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7615: mi zad sna tshogs nyi zer zhags //
NK027(sha)001:7616: shar gyi spor ma'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7617: badz+ra a pra ti ar+ya ni /
NK027(sha)001:7619: a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:7620: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni pi ti h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7621: a b+hi shar lho'i spor ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7622: dbang gi snam bu phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du //
NK027(sha)001:7623: spor ma brgyad yi dwags ston pa gnas gyur pas //
NK027(sha)001:7624: 'bar ma srin mo me gtong brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7625: me khyer dmar nag glo phreng 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:7626: shar lho'i spor ma'i a badz+ra a pra ti /
NK027(sha)001:7627: a e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni pi ti h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7628: a b+hi lho'i spor ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7629: mi'i ston pa gnas gyur pas //
NK027(sha)001:7630: srin mo 'bar ma gtum mo brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7631: gti mug ser nag mdung thung 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:7632: lho yi spor ma'i badz+ra a mri tsa /
NK027(sha)001:7633: a b+hi sha e sha ra b+he sha a b+hi lho nub spor ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7634: dbang gi snam bzhi sgo bzhi sgo khyud la //
NK027(sha)001:7635: snam bu phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du //
NK027(sha)001:7636: spor ma dmyal ba'i ston pa gnas gyur pas //
NK027(sha)001:7637: srin po 'bar ma ral gri brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7638: gshin rje sngo nag ral gri'i sku //
NK027(sha)001:7639: lho nub spor ma'i badz+ra a mri ta ni /
NK027(sha)001:7640: a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:7641: e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni pi ti h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7642: a b+hi nub kyi spor ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7643: dbang gi rnam bzhi sgo bzhi sgo khyud ma //
NK027(sha)001:7644: snam bu phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du //
NK027(sha)001:7645: spor ma brgyad kyi phyi yi yul chos gnas gyur pas //
NK027(sha)001:7647: rdo rje dril bu 'khril byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:7648: nub kyi spor ma'i badz+ra a ra ti /
NK027(sha)001:7649: a b+hi she e sha b+he sha a b+hi nub byang spor ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7650: dbang gi rnam bzhi sgo bzhi sgo khyud ma //
NK027(sha)001:7651: snam bu phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du //
NK027(sha)001:7652: spor ma brgyad lha yi ston pa gnas gyur pas //
NK027(sha)001:7653: srin po 'bar ma gnod sbyin brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7654: gnod sbyin mthing nag khyung thog ma //
NK027(sha)001:7655: nub byang spor ma'i badz+ra a pra ti /
NK027(sha)001:7656: a b+hi e sha b+he sha a b+hi /
NK027(sha)001:7657: byang gi spor ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7658: dbang gi rnam bzhi snam bu spor ma lha mi'i ston pa srin mo 'bar ma thogs med brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7659: thog 'beb sngo nag skar mda' gtong //
NK027(sha)001:7660: byang gi badz+ra a b+hi a b+hi e sha ra b+he sha ra /
NK027(sha)001:7661: a b+hi byang shar gyi spor ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7662: dbang gi rnam bzhi snam bu spor ma byol song thub pa srin mo 'jig rten 'bar ma brtul //
NK027(sha)001:7663: 'jigs byed smug nag glog sha stobs //
NK027(sha)001:7664: byang shar spor ma'i badz+ra a pra ti ar+ya ni tsa du sh+tan phata /
NK027(sha)001:7665: a b+hi e sha ra si ti na mah b+he sha tsa ni si ti h'u /
NK027(sha)001:7666: a b+hi gsang yum gos dkar mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7667: dbang gi gru chad bar khyam phyi rim gsang yum bzhi yi dkar mo mig gcig rgyas 'debs ma //
NK027(sha)001:7668: dpal chen sku la sbyor mdzad ma /
NK027(sha)001:7669: mdun nas sangs rgyas gzungs mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:7670: sku dkar phyag na rdo rje bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:7671: gsang ba'i yum gyi dbang badz+ra sh+r+ai badz+ra ka sha
NK027(sha)001:7672: ra ya na mah a b+hi ser mo thogs te
NK027(sha)001:7673: / ser mo las mkhan tshe 'phel ma //
NK027(sha)001:7674: sku ser phyag na mda' gzhu 'geng //
NK027(sha)001:7675: dpal chen sku la sbyor mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:7676: g.yas na sangs rgyas gzungs mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:7677: gsang ba'i yum gyi dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7678: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga na sa ma ya na mah a b+hi dmar mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7679: dmar mo za byed dbang sdud ma //
NK027(sha)001:7680: sku dmar phyag na rgyal mtshan bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:7681: dpal chen sku la sbyor mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:7682: rgyab nas sangs rgyas gzungs mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:7683: gsang ba yum gyi dbang chog sh+r+ai badz+ra phata /
NK027(sha)001:7685: a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah nag mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7686: nag mo ral gcig rmongs byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:7687: ljang nag phyag na dril bu bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:7688: dpal chen sku la sbyor mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:7689: g.yon nas sangs rgyas gzungs mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:7690: gsang ba yum gyi dbang sh+r+ai badz+ra g+han d+ha ra
NK027(sha)001:7691: dza la na mah a b+hi dbang mo nyer brgyad
NK027(sha)001:7692: las / ma nu rak+sha thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7693: dbang gi dkyil phyi rim khrom gyi khrag mtsho la //
NK027(sha)001:7694: sgo bzhi snam bu'i ngos bzhi na //
NK027(sha)001:7695: dbang phyug tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:7696: srin po'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7697: dbang phyug chen po mi srin mo //
NK027(sha)001:7698: sku mdog dmar nag thod rlon 'chang //
NK027(sha)001:7699: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7700: dmar ser dril bu zhing chen g.yab //
NK027(sha)001:7701: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul byin rlabs kyi //
NK027(sha)001:7702: ma nu rak+sha'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:7703: a b+hi badz+ra bra ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7704: dbang gi phyi rim khrom gyi khrag mtsho la //
NK027(sha)001:7705: sgo bzhi snam bu'i ngos bzhi na //
NK027(sha)001:7706: dbang phyug tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:7707: tshangs pa'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7708: dbang phyug chen mo tshangs ma ste //
NK027(sha)001:7709: sku mdog dmar ser pad+ma bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:7710: de nyid dmar skya rtse lnga ban dmar sbrul //
NK027(sha)001:7711: mthu stobs dbang phyug bsam mi khyab //
NK027(sha)001:7712: badz+ra pra ma'i a b+hi ro'u tri thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7713: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi dbang phyug lha chen chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7714: dbang phyug chen mo 'khrug ma che //
NK027(sha)001:7715: sku mdog dkar mo tri shu la //
NK027(sha)001:7716: de nyid las ni dmar ser zhing dbyug snying 'byin gzig /
NK027(sha)001:7717: rol pa'i rdzu 'phrul byin rlabs kyi //
NK027(sha)001:7718: badz+ra re'u tri'i dbang a b+hi ke'u ri ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7719: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi dbyings phyug khyab 'jug chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7720: dbang phyug chen mo 'jug ser mo //
NK027(sha)001:7722: de nyid las ni rim pa 'khor lo pha wam ser //
NK027(sha)001:7723: reg pa'i mthu stobs bsam yas pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:7724: badz+ra ke'u ri'i a b+hi in tra thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7725: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi dbang phyug gzhon nu chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7726: dbang phyug chen mo dmar mo ste //
NK027(sha)001:7727: gzhon nu dmar mo mdung thung 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:7728: de nyid dmar mo dmar skya bam dbyug dred //
NK027(sha)001:7729: yon tan mthu rtsal bsam yas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7730: badz+ra in+t+ra'i dbang a b+hi besh+na be thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7731: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi dbang phyug brgya byin chung ma dbang phyug chen mo dbang mo che //
NK027(sha)001:7732: sku mdog dkar mo in tra'i gdong /
NK027(sha)001:7733: de nyid dkar dmar byi ba dung dmar bsring //
NK027(sha)001:7734: che ba'i yon tan bsam yas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7735: be sna ba yi dbang a b+hi badz+ra ping ga lam thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7736: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi sna bug dbang phyug lha mo khyo med gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7737: dbang phyug chen mo dmar mo ste //
NK027(sha)001:7738: zhi ba dmar mo tsan d+ha 'thung //
NK027(sha)001:7739: de nyid dmar mo dung dmar rgyu zhags 'thung //
NK027(sha)001:7740: yid kyi 'dod pa bsam yas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7741: sing ga la yi dbang a b+hi badz+ra a mri ta thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7742: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi sna bu'i dbang phyug nyi ma'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7743: dbang phyug chen mo bdud rtsi mo //
NK027(sha)001:7744: sku mdog dmar mo pad+ma bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:7745: de nyid bdud rtsi sngon mo chu srin bum //
NK027(sha)001:7746: sman gyi mthu stobs bsam mi khyab //
NK027(sha)001:7747: badz+ra a mri ta yi a b+hi badz+ra so'u mya ga thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7748: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi snam bu'i dbang phyug zla ba'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7749: dbang phyug chen mo zhi ba mo //
NK027(sha)001:7750: zhi ba dkar mo pu d+ha ri //
NK027(sha)001:7751: de nyid sngo skya bam ril khog smad sdig /
NK027(sha)001:7752: bdud rtsi byang chub sems kyi mthus //
NK027(sha)001:7753: badz+ra so'u myag dbang a b+hi badz+ra d+ha na thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7754: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi dbang phyug be con chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7755: dbang phyug chen mo be con mo //
NK027(sha)001:7756: sku mdog sngon po dbyug to thog /
NK027(sha)001:7757: de nyid las ni nag mo bam chen thod rlon khra //
NK027(sha)001:7758: drag shul 'joms pa'i mthu stobs kyis //
NK027(sha)001:7759: badz+ra na yi a b+hi badz+ra rak+sha si thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7760: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi dbang phyug srin mo
NK027(sha)001:7761: khyo med gnas dbang phyug chen mo'i srin mo ste
NK027(sha)001:7762: // sku mdog dmar ser thod khrag 'thung //
NK027(sha)001:7763: de nyid dmar nag zhing chen rgyu 'dren wa //
NK027(sha)001:7764: drag po'i mthu stobs bsam yas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7765: badz+ra rak+sha'i dbang a b+hi badz+ra yak+sha thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7766: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi dbang phyug nag chen
NK027(sha)001:7767: chung ma gnas dbang phyug chen mo za ba mo
NK027(sha)001:7768: // dmar nag sha dang khrag la rol //
NK027(sha)001:7769: de nyid las nag mo gam chen snyig 'byon stag /
NK027(sha)001:7770: mthu stobs gzhan gyi mi thub ste //
NK027(sha)001:7772: a b+hi badz+ra pra ti thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7773: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi dbang phyug b+h+ring gi chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7774: dbang phyug chen mo dga' mo ste //
NK027(sha)001:7776: de nyid las dmar mo 'khor lo thod par rgod //
NK027(sha)001:7777: mthu dang longs spyod bsam ra ti tam gi dbang a b+hi ru tri re ma ti thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7778: dbang gi phyi sgo bzhi dbang phyug stobs bzang chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7779: dbang phyug chen mo khrag 'thung myos //
NK027(sha)001:7780: sku mdog dkar mo gshol 'chang ma //
NK027(sha)001:7781: de nyid dmar nag rdor dbyug dung dmar rta //
NK027(sha)001:7782: mthu stobs rdzu 'phrul mtha' yas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7783: re ma ti'i dbang a b+hi badz+ra e ka tsa ra thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7784: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi dbang phyug rnam thos chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7785: dbang phyug chen mo gcig pu spyod //
NK027(sha)001:7786: rdo rje ser mo spu gris gcod //
NK027(sha)001:7787: de nyid dkar dmar rdo rje b+han+d+ha khyung //
NK027(sha)001:7788: 'byor ba'i longs spyod e ka tsa ri'i a b+hi ma nu ha ru thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7789: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi dbang phyug 'dod lha'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7790: dbang phyug chen mo yid 'phrog ma //
NK027(sha)001:7791: sku mdog dkar mo mda' gzhu thog /
NK027(sha)001:7792: de nyid dmar ser zhing bsdam byi za khyi //
NK027(sha)001:7793: 'dod pa'i yon tan kun rdzogs pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:7794: ma nu ha'i a b+hi badz+ra si ti kam thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7795: dbang gi phyi rim khrom gyi sgo bzhi dbang phyug
NK027(sha)001:7796: nor srung chung ma dbang phyug chen mo grub mor
NK027(sha)001:7797: byung // sku mdog dkar mo bum pa 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:7798: de nyid dkar dmar pad+ma pu shud mgo //
NK027(sha)001:7799: lhag par nor gyi longs spyod che //
NK027(sha)001:7800: si ti kam gi dbang a b+hi badz+ra ba ya b+he thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7801: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi dbang phyug rlung lha'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7802: dbang phyug chen mo rlung mo ste //
NK027(sha)001:7803: sku mdog sngon po ba dan phyar //
NK027(sha)001:7804: de nyid dmar skya ro za sha ba'i mgo //
NK027(sha)001:7806: ba ya b+he'i dbang sbyin a b+hi badz+ra ma h+aa ra na thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7807: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi dbang phyug skyong ma
NK027(sha)001:7808: khyo med gnas dbang phyug chen mo khyo med ma
NK027(sha)001:7809: // sku mdog dmar nag ral gris gcod //
NK027(sha)001:7810: de nyid ljang nag bam chen rnge'u chung g.yas //
NK027(sha)001:7811: sgrol byed mthu stobs bsam yas pa //
NK027(sha)001:7812: ma ra na'i a b+hi badz+ra a ga ni thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7813: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi dbang phyug tshogs me
NK027(sha)001:7814: lha'i chung ma gnas sku mdog dmar po gsal shing
NK027(sha)001:7815: 'dzin // dbang phyug chen mo me mor byung //
NK027(sha)001:7816: de las mi zad sku sprul pa //
NK027(sha)001:7817: ljang dmar mes bsreg rgyu 'dren skyin //
NK027(sha)001:7818: rnam rtog bag chags kun bsreg pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:7819: ag ne ma'i a b+hi shiny+tsa badz+ra b+ha ra hi thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7820: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi dbang phyug sa bdag chung ma dbang phyug chen mo phag mo byung //
NK027(sha)001:7821: sku mdog dmar nag mche ba bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:7822: de nyid las ljang ser rtse gsum byi ro phag /
NK027(sha)001:7823: 'jig rten khams kyi dbang mchog ma //
NK027(sha)001:7824: b+ha ra hi'i a b+hi badz+ra tsa mun ti thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7825: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi dbang phyug gshin rje'i
NK027(sha)001:7826: chung ma gnas dbang phyug chen mo rgan byed mo
NK027(sha)001:7827: // dmar smug byi ro rgyu ma za //
NK027(sha)001:7830: ma mo mthu dang kun rdzogs pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:7831: tsa mun ta'i a b+hi badz+ra pu ta na thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7832: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi dbang phyug tshogs bgegs kyi chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7833: dbang phyug chen mo sgo chen mo //
NK027(sha)001:7834: sku mdog dmar nag thod khrag 'thung //
NK027(sha)001:7835: de nyid 'jigs pa'i sku sprul pa //
NK027(sha)001:7836: ljang dmar bam chen longs spyod glang //
NK027(sha)001:7837: bgegs chen kun 'dul mthu stobs kyi //
NK027(sha)001:7838: su ta na'i a b+hi badz+ra ba tu na thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7839: dbang phyi rim sgo bzhi dbang phyug chu lha'i chung ma gnas dbang phyug chen mo chu lha mo //
NK027(sha)001:7840: sku mdog dkar sngo sbrul zhags 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:7842: ljang nag bdud rtsi dung dmar sbrul //
NK027(sha)001:7843: gter gyi longs spyod bsam yas pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:7844: ba ru na'i dbang a b+hi badz+ra ma h+aa ka li thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7845: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi dbang phyug nag mo'i
NK027(sha)001:7846: chung ma gnas dbang phyug nag mo chen mo ste
NK027(sha)001:7847: // sku mdog nag mo am gu sha /
NK027(sha)001:7849: nag mo lcags kyu khu byug mgo //
NK027(sha)001:7850: pu tra 'dzin byed thams cad rdzogs //
NK027(sha)001:7851: ma h+aa ka li'i a b+hi badz+ra tsa ka la thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7852: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi dbang phyug ra gdong
NK027(sha)001:7853: chung ma gnas dbang phyug chen mo ra mgo ma
NK027(sha)001:7854: // sku mdog dmar ser ra mgo ma //
NK027(sha)001:7855: sku mdog dmar ser zhags pa bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:7856: 'jigs byed sngon mo rgyu zhags 'dren pa'i ra //
NK027(sha)001:7857: 'khor bar mi gtong dbang mo che //
NK027(sha)001:7858: tsa ka la yi dbang a b+hi badz+ra bum pa ka thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7859: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi dbang phyug bum sna'i chung ma dbang phyug bum sna sngo nag ma //
NK027(sha)001:7860: sku mdog sngo nag lcags sgrog bsdoms //
NK027(sha)001:7861: 'jigs byed dmar mo be con lcags sgrog sing //
NK027(sha)001:7862: bgegs dpung srid bsdam dbang mo che //
NK027(sha)001:7863: bum pa sna ka'i a b+hi badz+ra lam po ta ra thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7864: dbang gi phyi rim sgo bzhi gsus chen chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7865: dbang phyug gsus 'dzin chen mo byung //
NK027(sha)001:7866: sku mdog sngo nag dril bu 'khrol //
NK027(sha)001:7867: 'jigs byed 'bar ljang nag dril chen dung dmar keg /
NK027(sha)001:7868: nga rgyal dreg pa bzhi bcur spor //
NK027(sha)001:7869: li po ta ri'i de nas mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis las /
NK027(sha)001:7870: ma h+aa badz+ra b+ha ra thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7871: dbang gi phyi rim lhag pa'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK027(sha)001:7872: phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad sgo bzhi ru //
NK027(sha)001:7873: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs kyis rdo rje sems dpa' gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7875: mkha' 'gro rdo rje rig dbang phyug /
NK027(sha)001:7876: badz+ra d+ha ra'i dbang a b+hi kro ti shwa r+ai thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7877: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gro'i tshogs rdo rje rgyal po gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7878: 'dren byed dkar skya lcags kyu ma //
NK027(sha)001:7880: kro ti shwa ri'i badz+ra ma h+aa he ma ti thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7881: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gros mtshams brgyad
NK027(sha)001:7882: rdo rje chags pa spyod byed thabs kyi mda' 'geng
NK027(sha)001:7883: ma // mkha' 'gro sgrol byed mthu dbang rdzogs //
NK027(sha)001:7884: ma h+aa ma ti'i dbang badz+ra ku ma r+ai thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7885: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gro mtshams rdo rje legs pa gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7886: spor byed dkar skya spu gri thogs //
NK027(sha)001:7887: ku ma hi'i dbang a b+hi ma h+aa tsi ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7888: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi rdo rje rin chen gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7891: badz+ra ma tsi dbang a b+hi badz+ra tri sh+r+ai sma ra ya thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7892: dbang gi phyi rim lhag ma'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK027(sha)001:7893: phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad sgo bzhi ru //
NK027(sha)001:7894: mkha' 'gro tshogs kyis rdo rje nyi ma gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7896: rnam rtog mun sel mthu dbang rdzogs //
NK027(sha)001:7897: tri sh+r+ai sma ra'i dbang a b+hi badz+ra tsag ne thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7898: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi sgo bzhi mkha' 'gro'i
NK027(sha)001:7899: tshogs kyis rdo rje rgyal mtshan gnas khro bo mthing
NK027(sha)001:7901: bdud bzhi 'dul byed dbang ldan pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:7902: badz+ra tsa ga'i dbang a b+hi ma h+aa kro ti thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7903: dbang gi dkyil phyi rim phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gro'i rdo
NK027(sha)001:7904: rje'i bzhad pa gnas 'joms byed zhing gi kha gdong
NK027(sha)001:7905: ma // dur khrod bgegs 'joms za byed pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:7906: ma h+aa kro ti a b+hi ma h+aa a mri ta thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7907: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gro'i rdo rje chos tshogs chags med dmar nag pad+ma bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:7908: nyes pa'i skyon bral legs dbang rdzogs //
NK027(sha)001:7909: a mri tot+ta'i dbang a b+hi ma h+aa soo ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7910: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gro'i tshogs rdo rje rnon po gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7911: chags bral dmar nag gri thod ma //
NK027(sha)001:7912: mkha' 'gro sgrol byed mthu dbang rdzogs //
NK027(sha)001:7913: ma h+aa so ma'i a b+hi ma h+aa badz+ra tan tri thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7914: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gro'i tshogs rdo
NK027(sha)001:7915: rje 'khor lo gnas 'khor lo dmar ser 'khor lo
NK027(sha)001:7916: 'phan // mkha' 'gro gcod byed mthu dbang rdzogs //
NK027(sha)001:7917: badz+ra dan ti'i dbang a b+hi ma h+aa ra mi ni thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7918: dbang gi phyi rim lhag ma'i dkyil phyogs bzhi mkha'
NK027(sha)001:7919: 'gro'i tshogs kyis rdo rje smra ba gnas gyur pa
NK027(sha)001:7921: thogs med lcags kyu dbang bsgyur ma //
NK027(sha)001:7922: ma h+aa ra mi na'i dbang a b+hi ma h+aa
NK027(sha)001:7923: smri ti ka pa la he ste ta ka thogs
NK027(sha)001:7924: te / dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gro'i
NK027(sha)001:7925: rdo rje phrin las sna tshogs lus 'tshams rgya gram
NK027(sha)001:7926: te / thogs // mkha' 'gro phrin las rdzogs pa'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:7927: hes te ta ka'i dbang a b+hi badz+ra so'u nya thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7928: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gro'i rdo rje
NK027(sha)001:7929: bsrung ba gnas bsrung ba sngo ljang go cha thogs
NK027(sha)001:7931: badz+ra soo ti'i dbang a b+hi a mri ta su ta na da ri thogs /
NK027(sha)001:7932: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gro rdo rje
NK027(sha)001:7933: gnod sbyin gnas gnod sbyin mo ljang mche ba 'dzin
NK027(sha)001:7934: // dam nyams gsod pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK027(sha)001:7935: su ta na da ra'i dbang a b+hi badz+ra bi la ki la thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7936: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi'i mkha' 'gro'i rdo rje
NK027(sha)001:7937: khu tshur gnas yan lag 'phrog ljang mu tig phyar
NK027(sha)001:7938: // rdul du brlag byed mkha' 'gro'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:7939: bi la ka li'i a b+hi bi shi ri ri thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7940: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi'i mkha' 'gro'i dpa' bar 'gro ba gnas 'gyur ba //
NK027(sha)001:7941: bya rog gdong la mi 'byin ma //
NK027(sha)001:7942: lag na gri dang mkhar gzhong thogs //
NK027(sha)001:7944: pe ri sha ri dbang a b+hi k+sha ni k+sha thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7945: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad sgo bzhi ru //
NK027(sha)001:7946: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs kyis kun tu bzang po gnas 'jigs byed dkar sngo mche gtsigs ma //
NK027(sha)001:7948: ka ni k+sha'i dbang a b+hi sha ni ta ga thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7949: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gro'i zla 'od
NK027(sha)001:7950: gzhon nu gnas bzhad mdog dkar mo snying 'byin ma
NK027(sha)001:7951: // thams cad sgrol ba'i mkha' 'gro ging //
NK027(sha)001:7952: sha na ta ka'i dbang a b+hi pa ta ki thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7953: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gro'i byang sems bzang skyong gnas gyur pa //
