NK027(sha)001:7954: 'u ga mgo dkar sngo keng rus 'chang //
NK027(sha)001:7955: las byed lhag sdud gzhi dbang kun //
NK027(sha)001:7956: be ta ka'i a b+hi badz+ra a na ya'i thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7957: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gro'i byang sems dra 'od gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7958: khyi mgo mthing nag keng rus 'chang //
NK027(sha)001:7959: dur khrod 'joms pa'i dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:7960: a na ya yi dbang a b+hi se ni ke thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7961: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gro'i rdo rje snying po gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7962: mthing nag rmong po phag gi mgo //
NK027(sha)001:7963: gtsang rme med par za byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:7964: pe ne ke'i a b+hi dza du la ya thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7965: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad mkha' 'gro'i nam mkha' mdzod kyi gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7966: sngo nag glog 'dren rnga mong mgo //
NK027(sha)001:7968: dza du la yi dbang a b+hi ka ti pi ki thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7969: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gro'i 'od dpag med pa gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7970: thod pa dgra s+t+wa bong bu mgo //
NK027(sha)001:7972: bi ti ki'i a b+hi badz+ra ta ra she thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:7973: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gro'i mya ngan kun 'joms gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7974: dmar nag spu gri ra yi mgo //
NK027(sha)001:7976: badz+ra tar shi'i a b+hi ka li pra we sha thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7977: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gro'i rgyal ba'i ye shes gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7978: dmar nag rus la byi la'i mgo //
NK027(sha)001:7979: ma lus sgrol byed mkha' 'gro'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:7980: pra we sha yi dbang a b+hi us ti ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7981: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi blo gros mi bzad gnas dmar ser keng rus dkar po 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:7983: us ting ma'i a b+hi ka trar na tsa thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7984: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi spobs pa brtsegs pa gnas dmar ser rus phreng lce spyang mgo //
NK027(sha)001:7986: ka ran tsa'i dbang a b+hi sarba ma tha ra thogs //
NK027(sha)001:7987: dbang gi phyi rim lhag ma'i phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gro'i ngan song kun 'dren gnas gyur pa /
NK027(sha)001:7988: mkha' 'gro srin mo bum sna ma //
NK027(sha)001:7989: rdo rje lcags kyu ka ta ri //
NK027(sha)001:7990: ma ta ra'i a b+hi sa ma ta ka thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7991: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gro'i byams pa brtsegs pa gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7993: zhags pa gri thogs 'dzin cing sgrol //
NK027(sha)001:7994: pa la ta ka'i a b+hi badz+ra sarba b+ha ga la thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7995: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gro'i spos kyi glang po gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:7997: lcags sgrog spu gri za byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:7998: b+han+d+ha la yi a b+hi badz+ra sa b+ha na a thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:7999: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mkha' 'gro'i sems dpa' don grub gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:8001: dril bu dgra s+t+wa sgrol zhing spor //
NK027(sha)001:8002: sa b+han a'i dbang a b+hi rdo rje kun trag mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8004: dbang gi phyi yi snam bu'i phyogs bzhi la //
NK027(sha)001:8005: ma bdun sring bzhi'i bskor ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:8006: ma mo bdun gyi dbang rgya mtsho chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)001:8007: dpal ldan shugs sgrol rtse mo ste //
NK027(sha)001:8008: ri rab bsnyil ma'i mthu mo che //
NK027(sha)001:8009: rdo rje kun grags dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:8010: ma ma d+hartu kro ti sha ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)001:8011: a b+hi kun tu bzang mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8012: dbang gi phyi yi snam bu'i phyogs bzhi la //
NK027(sha)001:8013: ma bdun sring bzhi'i bskor ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:8014: nam mkha' stong gi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)001:8015: thams cad kun la khyab mdzad cing //
NK027(sha)001:8016: ma lus yongs la dbang bskur ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:8017: kun tu bzang mo'i ma ma d+ha du kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)001:8018: a b+hi rdo rje kun gsal ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8019: dbang gi phyi yi ma bdun 'ja' tshon 'bar ba'i dkyil mdzes pa'i tshul gyi 'od 'phro zhing //
NK027(sha)001:8020: ma rig mun pa sel mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:8021: rdo rje kun gsal dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:8022: ma ma d+hartu kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)001:8023: a b+hi rdo rje ye shes thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8024: dbang gi phyi yi ma bdun dam tshig chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)001:8025: pho nya me ste drug cu'i gtso //
NK027(sha)001:8026: sha chen khrag la longs spyod pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:8027: rdo rje ye shes dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:8028: ma ma d+hartu kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8029: a b+hi rdo rje 'od chags ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8030: dbang gi phyi yi ma bdun khrag gi rgya mtsho'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)001:8031: rdo rje d+r+wa ba phreng togs shing //
NK027(sha)001:8033: rdo rje 'od chags dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:8034: ma na a b+hi rdo rje 'od 'phro thogs te //
NK027(sha)001:8035: dbang gi phyi yi ma bdun me dpung 'bar ba'i dkyil zhags pa stong gi bde ldan zhing //
NK027(sha)001:8037: rdo rje 'od 'phro'i ma ma a b+hi rdo rje g.yu sgron ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8038: dbang gi phyi yi ma bdun sring dbang phyug chen po'i dkyil dam tshig nyams pa gcod mdzad cing //
NK027(sha)001:8040: rdo rje g.yu sgron dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:8041: ma ma a b+hi lha'i sri mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8042: dbang gi phyi rim sring mo gling bzhi mgyogs ma lha yi sring //
NK027(sha)001:8043: sku la bya rgod thul ba gsol //
NK027(sha)001:8044: thugs dam rnal 'byor grogs la brtson //
NK027(sha)001:8045: lha yi sring mo'i dbang a b+hi gshin rje'i sring mo'i thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8046: dbang gi phyi'i sring mo mkha' la khyung lding gshin rje'i sring //
NK027(sha)001:8047: sku la stag gi thul ba gsol //
NK027(sha)001:8048: thugs dam rnal 'byor grogs la brtson //
NK027(sha)001:8049: gshin rje'i sring mo'i a b+hi klu'i sring mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8051: ma dmar mo g.yag thod klu yi sring //
NK027(sha)001:8052: na bza' chu srin lpags pa gsol //
NK027(sha)001:8053: dam tshig can la brtser dgongs la //
NK027(sha)001:8054: klu yi sring mo'i dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:8055: a b+hi gnod sbyin sring mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8056: dbang gi phyi rim ma bdun nag mo sder can gnod sbyin sring //
NK027(sha)001:8057: sku la rma bya'i thul ba gsol //
NK027(sha)001:8058: dam tshig can la brtser dgongs la //
NK027(sha)001:8059: gnod sbyin sring mo'i dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:8060: a b+hi dpa' bo chen po thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8061: dbang gi phyi rim snam bu'i sgo bzhi ru //
NK027(sha)001:8062: thugs kyi 'od zer sprul pa las //
NK027(sha)001:8063: mkha' 'gro ging gi bskor ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:8064: dpal chen las rnams kun byed pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:8065: mthing nag ral gri b+han+d+ha bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:8066: gang la dmigs pa sgrol ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:8067: rdo rje ging gi dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:8068: a b+hi khro mo chen mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8069: dbang gi phyi rim thugs kyis 'od zer sprul pa las //
NK027(sha)001:8070: mkha' 'gro'i khro mo khams gsum dbang bsdud ma //
NK027(sha)001:8071: sngo nag thod khrag 'joms pa thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8073: rdo rje ging mo'i dbang badz+ra ka ta ri badz+ra sh+aa shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8074: a b+hi dmar nag thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8075: dbang gi phyi rim thugs kyi mkha' 'gro ging gi rdo rje ging chen dmar nag ni //
NK027(sha)001:8076: dung dmar dang ni ka tar bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:8077: ma thogs myur du sgrol bar byed //
NK027(sha)001:8078: rdo rje ging gi dbang badz+ra ka ra ra badz+ra ging ka ra /
NK027(sha)001:8079: a b+hi gnod sbyin thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8080: dbang gi phyi rim thugs kyis mkha' 'gro ging chen rdo rje gnod sbyin ni //
NK027(sha)001:8081: ljang nag phyag gi sdig mdzub phyir //
NK027(sha)001:8082: dam tshig nyams chag sgrol byed pa //
NK027(sha)001:8083: rdo rje ging gi badz+ra ka da ra badz+ra ging ka ra /
NK027(sha)001:8084: a b+hi spyang mgo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8085: dbang gi phyi rim thugs kyis mkha' 'gro rdo rje ging chen spyang gi ni //
NK027(sha)001:8086: dmar nag lcags kyu spu gri thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8087: gsod pa'i las la shin tu dgyes //
NK027(sha)001:8088: rdo rje ging gi dbang badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8089: a b+hi gshin rje thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8090: dbang gi phyi rim thugs kyis mkha' 'gro rdo rje ging chen gshin rje ni //
NK027(sha)001:8091: mthing nag be con dgra s+t+wa 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:8092: ma lus sgrol ba'i ging chen te //
NK027(sha)001:8093: rdo rje ging gi badz+ra ka ta ri sh+aa shwa ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8094: a b+hi rol pa thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8095: dbang gi phyi rim thugs kyis /
NK027(sha)001:8096: mkha' 'gro rdo rje ging chen rol pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:8097: dmar nag b+han+d+ha phal tshab bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:8098: dgra bgegs ma lus dmyal thag chod //
NK027(sha)001:8099: rdo rje ging gi dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:8100: badz+ra ka ta ri shwa ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8102: dbang gi phyi rim thugs kyis mkha' 'gro ging gi rdo rje ging chen 'chi bdag ni //
NK027(sha)001:8103: ljang ser rdo rje gsor zhing bteg /
NK027(sha)001:8104: drag shul sbyor ba'i mthu stobs can //
NK027(sha)001:8105: rdo rje ging gi badz+ra ka ta ri sh+aa shwa ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8106: a b+hi dus mtshams thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8107: dbang gi phyi rim thugs kyi mkha' 'gro rdo rje ging chen dus mtshams ni //
NK027(sha)001:8108: ljang nag shag ti b+han+d+ha thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8110: rdo rje ging gi dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:8111: badz+ra ka ta ri sh+aa shwa ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8112: a b+hi ro lang thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8113: dbang gi phyi rim thugs kyis mkha' 'gro rdo rje ging chen ro lang ni //
NK027(sha)001:8114: ser nag zhing gi dbyug pa phyar //
NK027(sha)001:8115: gang la dmigs pa yud kyi 'joms //
NK027(sha)001:8116: rdo rje ging gi badz+ra ka ta ri sh+aa shwa ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8118: dbang gi phyi rim thugs kyis mkha' 'gro rdo rje ging chen 'joms pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:8119: smug nag rdo rje tho ba thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8120: bgegs kyi dpung yang yud kyi 'joms //
NK027(sha)001:8121: rdo rje ging gi dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:8122: badz+ra ka ta ri sh+aa shwa ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8123: a b+hi dbang sdud thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8124: dbang gi phyi rim thugs kyis mkha' 'gro ging lcam dbang sdud pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:8125: ljang nag rdo rje lcags kyu 'dren //
NK027(sha)001:8126: dmigs pa yud kyi dgra bgegs sgrol //
NK027(sha)001:8127: rdo rje ging lcam dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:8128: badz+ra ka ta ri sh+aa shwa ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8129: a b+hi dbang bsgyur ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8130: dbang gi phyi rim thugs kyis mkha' 'gro ging gi rdo rje ging lcam dbang bsgyur ma //
NK027(sha)001:8131: khams gsum zhing gi g.yab mo 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:8132: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul bsam mi khyab //
NK027(sha)001:8133: rdo rje ging chen badz+ra ka ta ri sh+aa shwa ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8134: a b+hi 'phrul mo che thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8135: dbang gi phyi rim thugs kyis mkha' 'gro rdo rje ging chen gzugs med rlung ltar rgyu byed cing //
NK027(sha)001:8136: gang la dmigs pa yud kyi khyab //
NK027(sha)001:8137: rdo rje ging lcam dbang badz+ra ka ta ra sh+aa shwa ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8138: a b+hi glog 'gyu ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8139: dbang gi phyi rim thugs kyis mkha' 'gro rdo rje ging lcam glog 'gyu ma /
NK027(sha)001:8141: cir yang bsgyur ba'i 'phrul mo che //
NK027(sha)001:8142: rdo rje ging mo'i dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:8143: badz+ra ka ta ri sh+aa shwa ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8144: a mthu mo che thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8145: dbang gi phyi rim thugs kyis mkha' 'gro rdo rje ging lcam mthu mo che //
NK027(sha)001:8146: ljang nag lcags kyi tho ba thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8147: rbod gtong bcol ba len byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8148: rdo rje ging gi badz+ra ka ta ri sh+aa shwa ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8149: a b+hi rtsal mo che thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8150: dbang gi phyi rim thugs kyis mkha' 'gro rdo rje ging mthing nag rdo rje dgra s+t+wa thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8151: phrin las rna nyan phra ma zer //
NK027(sha)001:8152: rdo rje ging mo'i dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:8153: badz+ra ka ta ri sh+aa shwa ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8154: a b+hi sgrol byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8155: dbang gi phyi rim thugs kyis mkha' 'gro rdo rje ging lcam sgrol byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8156: smug nag b+han+d+ha gri thogs ma //
NK027(sha)001:8157: phrin las srid gsum sgrol byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8158: rdo rje ging mo'i dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:8159: badz+ra ka ta ri sh+aa shwa ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8160: a b+hi za byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8161: dbang gi phyi rim thugs kyis mkha' 'gro rdo rje ging lcam myong byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8162: mthing nag phyag na longs spyod bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:8163: phrin las tshogs kyis phyag tshang byed //
NK027(sha)001:8164: rdo rje ging mo'i dbang badz+ra kro ta ka ta ri sh+aa shwa ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8165: a b+hi rnam rgyal yab yum thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8166: dbang gi phyi rim phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad steng 'og bcu //
NK027(sha)001:8167: dgra gdon ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:8168: sku yi kha dog mthing nag las //
NK027(sha)001:8169: khro bo khro mo drug cur sprul //
NK027(sha)001:8170: rnam rgyal mdog dkar rdo rje tho ba thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8171: snyems ma gtso 'khyud thod khrag yab la stob //
NK027(sha)001:8172: mthu rtsal yang che dri za'i gdon 'dul ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:8173: khro bo khro mo'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:8174: badz+ra kro ta ka ta ri sh+aa shwa ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8175: a b+hi dbyug sngon yab yum thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8176: dbang gi phyi rim thugs kyis mkha' 'gro sku yi kha dog mthing nag las //
NK027(sha)001:8177: khro bo khro mo drug cur sprul //
NK027(sha)001:8178: dbyug pa sngon po bsdig mdzub rin chen bsdom //
NK027(sha)001:8179: sder mo gtso 'khyud dung dmar yab la stob //
NK027(sha)001:8180: mthu rtsal che bas drang srong gdon 'dul ba //
NK027(sha)001:8181: khro bo khro mo'i dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:8182: badz+ra kro ta ka ta ri sh+aa shwa ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8183: a b+hi gshin rje gshed po thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8184: dbang gi phyogs bzhi dgra gdon sku yi khro bo khro mo drug cur sprul //
NK027(sha)001:8185: gshin rje gshed po mthing nag dbyug to phyar //
NK027(sha)001:8186: rdo rje dur khrod dung dmar yab la stob //
NK027(sha)001:8187: nga rgyal mthu chen gshin rje gdon 'dul ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:8188: khro bo khro mo'i dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:8189: badz+ra kro ta ka ta ri sh+aa shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8190: a b+hi mi g.yo ba thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8191: dbang gi phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad steng 'og bcu //
NK027(sha)001:8192: dgra gdon ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:8193: sku yi kha dog mthing nag las //
NK027(sha)001:8194: khro bo mi g.yo mgon po khu tshur ral gri thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8195: rdo rje gtun khung dung dmar gtso la stob //
NK027(sha)001:8196: rdzu 'phrul stobs chen srin po'i gdon rnams 'dul //
NK027(sha)001:8197: khro bo khro mo'i dbang badz+ra kro ta ka ta ri sh+aa shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8198: a b+hi rta mgrin thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8199: dbang gi phyogs bzhi dgra gdon sku yi khro bo khro rta mgrin mdog dmar pad+ma mda' gzhu bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:8200: rdo rje gtum mo dung dmar gtso la stob //
NK027(sha)001:8201: thugs rje mthu rtsal gti mug bdud 'dul ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:8202: khro bo badz+ra kro ta ka ta ra sh+aa shwa ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8203: a b+hi gzhan gyi mi thub pa thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8204: dbang gi phyogs bzhi dgra gdon sku yi khro bo gzhan gyi mi thub dgra s+t+wa gtun shing sngo //
NK027(sha)001:8205: rdo rje mda' snyems dung khrag gtso la stob //
NK027(sha)001:8206: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul klu gdon 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:8207: khro bo badz+ra a b+hi bdud rtsi 'khyil pa thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8208: dbang gi phyogs bzhi dgra gdon sku yi khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ljang nag rgya gram phyir //
NK027(sha)001:8209: rdo rje rlung 'byin dung dmar gtso la stob //
NK027(sha)001:8210: drag po mthu yi gnod sbyin 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:8211: khro bo khro mo yab yum dbang badz+ra kro ta
NK027(sha)001:8212: ka ri a b+hi khams gsum rnam rgyal yab yum
NK027(sha)001:8213: / dbang gi phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad steng 'og bcu //
NK027(sha)001:8214: dgra gdon sku ni kha dog mthing nag la //
NK027(sha)001:8215: khro bo khams gsum rnam rgyal rdo rje tho ba nag /
NK027(sha)001:8216: rdo rje gsod rkyen dmar gyi mchod pa 'dren //
NK027(sha)001:8217: drag shul mthu yi 'byung po 'dul ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:8218: khro bo yab yum rnams kyis badz+ra kro ta ka ta ri sh+aa shwa ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8219: a b+hi stobs chen yab yum /
NK027(sha)001:8220: dbang gi phyogs bzhi dgra gdon sku ni khro bo stobs chen dud ka 'bud dung rnga yab thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8221: rdo rje bskyod byed dung khrag yab la stob //
NK027(sha)001:8222: mthu stobs ldan pas sa bdag gdon 'dul ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:8223: khro bo badz+ra a b+hi h'u mdzad thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8224: dbang gi phyogs bzhi dgra gdon sku ni khro bo h'u mdzad dmar skya rdo rje mda' gzhu 'geng //
NK027(sha)001:8225: rdo rje sgra 'byin dung dmar zhal du stob //
NK027(sha)001:8226: nyi zla gza' skar yas gdon 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:8227: khro bo yab badz+ra kro ta a b+hi k+ai la ya thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8228: dbang gi sku yi 'od zer mthing nag las //
NK027(sha)001:8229: khro bo khro mo yab yum drug cu'i bskor //
NK027(sha)001:8230: dgra bgegs mang po 'dul slad du //
NK027(sha)001:8231: rdo rje phur pa mthing nag phur bu 'dril //
NK027(sha)001:8232: khro mo rgyas 'debs b+han+d+ha rak+ta bkang //
NK027(sha)001:8233: mthu dbang che bas lha dang dgra gdon 'dul //
NK027(sha)001:8234: khro bo yab yum gnyis kyi dbang badz+ra kro ta kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8235: a b+hi sme brtsegs thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8236: dbang gi sku yi khro bo dgra bgegs khro bo sme brtsegs mthing nag rdo rje thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8237: khro mo d+hi 'byin dung chen dam rdzas bkang //
NK027(sha)001:8238: mi gtsang rtogs 'joms bdud dang ru tra 'joms //
NK027(sha)001:8239: khro bo yab yum badz+ra kro ta kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8242: dbang gi sku yi khro bo yab yum drug dgra
NK027(sha)001:8243: bgegs ma lus yak+sha ljang nag phur pa bsdig mdzub
NK027(sha)001:8244: bsgrim // khro mo yag mo dung chen snying khrag bcas //
NK027(sha)001:8245: dam tshig nyams dang dam sri 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:8246: khro bo badz+ra kro ta a b+hi dmar nag yab yum /
NK027(sha)001:8247: dbang gi sku yi khro bo yab yum dgra bgegs 'byung po 'dul /
NK027(sha)001:8248: khro bo dmar nag rdo rje tho ba thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8249: khro mo dbang bsgyur mgo bcad rak+tasa bkangs //
NK027(sha)001:8250: mthu rtsal che bas mas gdon 'dul mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:8251: khro bo yab yum gnyis kyis badz+ra kro ta kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8253: dbang gi sku yi khro bo dgra bgegs 'byung khro bo za 'og thod sbrul sna tshogs mdog /
NK027(sha)001:8254: khro mo zab mo rdo rje thod khrag stob //
NK027(sha)001:8255: rdzu 'phrul mthu yi rmu gdon 'dul mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:8256: khro bo yab yum gnyis kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:8257: badz+ra a b+hi rab grub thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8258: dbang gi sku yi 'od zer khro bo yab yum
NK027(sha)001:8259: dgra bgegs 'byung po khro bo rab grub sngo nag
NK027(sha)001:8260: ral gri phyar // khro mo rab 'jigs thod khrag zhal du stob //
NK027(sha)001:8261: mthu rtsal che bas ya bdud 'dul mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:8262: khro bo yab yum badz+ra kro ta a b+hi ma h+aa ka la thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8263: dbang gi sku yi 'od khro bo dgra bgegs khro bo nag po chen po dmar nag zhags //
NK027(sha)001:8264: khro mo ral ba bsgreng pa thod khrag stob //
NK027(sha)001:8265: mthu rtsal che bas ya bdud 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:8266: khro bo badz+ra a b+hi pad rgyal yab yum thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8267: dbang gi sku yi khro bo yab yum dgra bgegs pad rgyal dmar nag de bzhin ral gri phyar //
NK027(sha)001:8268: ro lang de bzhin thod khrag zhal du stob //
NK027(sha)001:8269: mthu rtsal che bas nub kyi gdon rnams 'dul //
NK027(sha)001:8270: khro bo badz+ra a b+hi thal sbyor yab yum thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8271: dbang gi sku yi khro bo yab yum dgra bgegs mi 'chi thal sbyor sngo nag thal mo rdeb //
NK027(sha)001:8272: khro mo 'joms chen dung khrag zhal du stob //
NK027(sha)001:8273: mthu rtsal che bas srog chags 'dul mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:8274: khro bo yab yum badz+ra kro ta a b+hi gu lang yab yum thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8275: dbang gi sku yi khro bo dgra bgegs khro chen gu lang smug nag gtun shing rdeb //
NK027(sha)001:8276: khro mo las kun b+han+d+ha dmar gyi bskangs //
NK027(sha)001:8277: mthu rtsal che bas khams gsum bsad gsod mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:8278: khro bo badz+ra kro ta a b+hi rab rngam yab yum thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8279: dbang gi sku yi khro bo dgra bgegs rab rngam ljang nag rdo rje bskrug cing gsol //
NK027(sha)001:8280: gtun chen thod khrag tsit+ta gtso la stobs //
NK027(sha)001:8281: mthu rtsal che bas brjed byed gdon rnams 'dul //
NK027(sha)001:8282: khro bo yab yum badz+ra kro ta a b+hi gsum snang thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8283: dbang gi sku yi khro bo dgra bgegs 'jig rten gsum snang be con bsdig mdzub thog /
NK027(sha)001:8284: khro mo mi pham de bzhin dung chen thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8285: mthu rtsal che bas sgo bsrung shar gdon 'dul //
NK027(sha)001:8286: khro bo badz+ra kro ta kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8288: dbang gi sku yi yab yum dgra bgegs 'jig rten gsum 'dul dmar nag tho ba phyar //
NK027(sha)001:8289: khro mo lcags kyu de bzhin lcags kyu dang //
NK027(sha)001:8290: lho sgo bsrung zhing lha gdon 'dul ba'i bdag /
NK027(sha)001:8291: khro bo badz+ra a b+hi gsum 'ching yab yum thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8292: dbang gi sku yi khro bo dgra bgegs 'jig rten gsum 'ching sngo nag dbyug to phyar //
NK027(sha)001:8293: khro mo dung dmar dmar nag zhags pa thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8294: nub sgo bsrung zhing nub gdon 'dul ba'i bdag /
NK027(sha)001:8295: khro bo yab yum gnyis kyis badz+ra kro ta kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8296: a b+hi gsum 'jigs yab yum thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8297: dbang gi sku yi khro bo yab yum dgra bgegs 'jig rten gsum 'jigs dmar nag tho ba phyar //
NK027(sha)001:8298: khro gnyer thod khrag de bzhin zhal du stob //
NK027(sha)001:8299: mthu rtsal che bas sgo bsrung byang gdon 'dul //
NK027(sha)001:8300: khro bo badz+ra a b+hi be con yab yum thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:8301: dbang gi sku yi khro bo dgra bgegs be con sngon po rin chen be con phyar //
NK027(sha)001:8302: khro mo lcags sgrog de bzhin dung chen 'bud //
NK027(sha)001:8303: nub phyogs sgo srung nub gdon 'dul ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:8304: khro bo yab badz+ra kro ta kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8305: a b+hi ka ni yab yum thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8306: dbang gi sku yi 'od zer khro bo yab dgra bgegs ka ni badz+ra dmar nag ral gri mdzub //
NK027(sha)001:8307: ral gcig dung khrag gtso bo'i zhal du stob //
NK027(sha)001:8308: mthu rtsal che bas sgo srung byang gdon 'dul //
NK027(sha)001:8309: khro bo yab yum badz+ra kro ta a b+hi rdo rje go cha thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8310: dbang gi sku yi khro bo yab yum dgra bgegs khro bo go cha mthing nag go cha bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:8311: khro mo dril 'khrol thod khrag dril bu bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:8312: byang phyogs sgo srung byang gdon 'dul ba'i bdag /
NK027(sha)001:8313: khro bo yab yum gnyis mos dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:8314: badz+ra a b+hi rngam chen yab yum thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8315: dbang gi sku yi khro bo dgra bgegs khro bo rngams chen smug nag be con mdzub //
NK027(sha)001:8316: khro mo dbang sdud thod khrag zhal du stob /
NK027(sha)001:8317: mthu rtsal che bas bdud dang srin po 'dul //
NK027(sha)001:8318: khro bo badz+ra a b+hi tho ba yab yum thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8319: dbang gi sku yi khro bo dgra bgegs rdo rje tho ba dud ka tho ba bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:8320: khro mo za byed dung khrag yab la stob //
NK027(sha)001:8321: mthu rtsal che bas ma mo gshin rje 'dul //
NK027(sha)001:8322: khro bo yab yum badz+ra kro ta kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8323: a b+hi he ru ka'i rgyud las yang 'khor sum brgya drug cu'o //
NK027(sha)001:8324: shar gyi pho nya drug cu las /
NK027(sha)001:8325: dkar mo mgyogs byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8326: dbang gi sku yi 'od zer rnam 'phrul las //
NK027(sha)001:8327: sum brgya drug cur gdon sgrol phyir //
NK027(sha)001:8328: pho nya sum brgya drug cur sprul //
NK027(sha)001:8330: dri za'i dgra gdon 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:8331: shar phyogs 'od zer dkar po las //
NK027(sha)001:8332: dung gi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK027(sha)001:8333: rdo rje 'bar ba'i pho nya mo //
NK027(sha)001:8334: dmar mo mgyogs byed lcags kyu ma //
NK027(sha)001:8335: yid kyi phyin cing bsam pas 'grub //
NK027(sha)001:8336: dbang 'di bu la bskur bar bya //
NK027(sha)001:8337: b+ha na b+ha na am gu sha dzah a b+hi sder mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8338: rdo rje sder mo pho nya mo //
NK027(sha)001:8340: gar yang thog med glog 'gyu ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:8341: dbang 'di bu la bskur bar bya //
NK027(sha)001:8342: b+ha na b+ha na am gu sha dzah a b+hi k+ai la ya thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8343: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya drug cu'i gdon skrol phyir //
NK027(sha)001:8344: pho nya sum brgya drug cur sprul //
NK027(sha)001:8345: dri za'i dgra gdon 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:8346: shar phyogs 'od zer dkar po las //
NK027(sha)001:8347: dung gi mi mo pho nya rdo rje k+ai la ya //
NK027(sha)001:8348: dkar mo thogs med mig gsal ma //
NK027(sha)001:8350: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na b+ha na am gu sha dzah a b+hi 'big ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8351: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya dri za'i
NK027(sha)001:8352: shar phyogs dung gi mi pho nya rdo rje 'big
NK027(sha)001:8353: ma mo // dkar mo shel gyi mda' 'phen ma //
NK027(sha)001:8354: gang la dmigs pa grub byed pa //
NK027(sha)001:8355: dbang 'di b+ha na b+ha na ro lang ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8356: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya sum brgya
NK027(sha)001:8357: dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi pho nya rdo rje
NK027(sha)001:8358: ro lang ma // dkar mo lag na gri thog ma //
NK027(sha)001:8359: mgyogs byed dur khrod mkha' 'gro ma //
NK027(sha)001:8360: dbang 'di b+ha na b+ha na drag mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8361: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya dri za'i
NK027(sha)001:8362: shar phyogs dung gi mi mo drug rdo rje pho
NK027(sha)001:8364: dkar mo lag na mdung thog ma //
NK027(sha)001:8365: gang la sngags pa grub byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8366: dbang 'di bu la bskur bar bya //
NK027(sha)001:8367: b+ha na b+ha na a b+hi mgyogs byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8368: dbang gi sku yi 'od zer rnam 'phrul las //
NK027(sha)001:8369: sum brgya drug bcu'i pho nya 'jigs byed dri za'i
NK027(sha)001:8370: dgra gdon shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya
NK027(sha)001:8371: mgyogs pa mo // dkar mo ming sring g.yab mos 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:8372: ting 'dzin yid kyi pho nya mo //
NK027(sha)001:8373: dbang 'di b+h+ra na gtum mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8374: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs byed
NK027(sha)001:8375: dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi pho nya rdo rje
NK027(sha)001:8376: gtum mo ni // dkar mo snying 'byin cho nges 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:8377: sgrol byed pho nya tsit+ta yi //
NK027(sha)001:8378: dbang 'di b+ha na b+ha na a b+hi 'bebs ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8379: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs byed
NK027(sha)001:8380: dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya
NK027(sha)001:8381: 'debs ma ni // dkar mo gar byed glu len mkhan //
NK027(sha)001:8382: las la khrid pa'i pho nya yi //
NK027(sha)001:8383: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi gsal ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8384: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya sum 'jigs
NK027(sha)001:8385: byed dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi mi mo drug
NK027(sha)001:8386: cur sprul // rdo rje pho nya gsal ma ni //
NK027(sha)001:8387: dkar mo dung phreng glad la bskor //
NK027(sha)001:8388: sa ma ya yi phus 'debs ma //
NK027(sha)001:8389: dbang 'di bu la bskur bar bya //
NK027(sha)001:8390: b+ha na a b+hi sdod ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8391: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya sum brgya
NK027(sha)001:8392: drug cur 'jigs byed 'bar ba'i dri za'i shar phyogs
NK027(sha)001:8393: dung gi rdo rje pho nya dkar skya dar dkar
NK027(sha)001:8394: g.yab 'dor ma // rgyal ba'i yon tan cher ston ma //
NK027(sha)001:8395: rdo rje pho nya chen mo yi //
NK027(sha)001:8396: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi 'gugs ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8397: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs byed
NK027(sha)001:8398: dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya
NK027(sha)001:8399: 'gugs pa mo // dkar mo bdud kyi snying 'jug ma //
NK027(sha)001:8401: rdo rje pho nya sku dang bcas //
NK027(sha)001:8402: dbang 'di b+ha na a thog pa mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8403: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs byed
NK027(sha)001:8404: dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya
NK027(sha)001:8405: thogs pa mo // dkar dmar lag nas zangs gri 'chang //
NK027(sha)001:8406: dpa' bo chen po thogs pa med //
NK027(sha)001:8407: dbang 'di b+ha na a bskyed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8409: rdo rje pho nya bskyed ma ni //
NK027(sha)001:8410: dkar dmar rlung gi zhags thog ma //
NK027(sha)001:8411: rnal 'byor phrin las bskyed byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8412: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi 'chang bdag ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8413: dbang sku yi sum brgya drug cur pho nya 'jigs
NK027(sha)001:8414: byed dri za'i rdo rje pho nya 'chang bdag mo
NK027(sha)001:8415: // dkar dmar 'jigs byed zhags pa ma //
NK027(sha)001:8417: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi phra men ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8418: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs byed
NK027(sha)001:8419: dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi mi mo rdo rje
NK027(sha)001:8421: dkar dmar ma yi sgron ma khyed //
NK027(sha)001:8422: don dang rtags su bcas te 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:8423: dbang gi b+ha a myur byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8424: dbang gi sku yi 'od sum brgya pho nya 'jigs
NK027(sha)001:8425: byed dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho
NK027(sha)001:8427: dkar dmar glog gi zhags thogs ma //
NK027(sha)001:8428: gang bzang yid kyi 'debs par byed //
NK027(sha)001:8429: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi bskul byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8430: dbang gi sku yi 'od zer sum brgya pho nya
NK027(sha)001:8431: 'jigs byed dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje
NK027(sha)001:8432: pho nya dkar dmar skur mad'i 'od 'phen ma //
NK027(sha)001:8433: thugs dam bskul zhing phrin las byed //
NK027(sha)001:8434: dbang 'di b+ha na b+ha na a b+hi gsal bkra ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8435: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya sum 'jigs
NK027(sha)001:8436: byed dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi mi mo rdo
NK027(sha)001:8437: rje pho nya dkar mo rdo rje zhags 'phen ma
NK027(sha)001:8438: // sus kyang mi zlog thub pa dka' //
NK027(sha)001:8439: dbang 'di b+ha na b+ha na a b+hi yang dag mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8440: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs dri
NK027(sha)001:8441: za'i shar phyogs dung gi pho nya rdo rje yang
NK027(sha)001:8442: dag mo // dkar dang dmar gyi len phran 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:8443: khams gsum sa dgu yud kyi khyab //
NK027(sha)001:8444: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi chen po mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8445: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs dri
NK027(sha)001:8446: za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya chen
NK027(sha)001:8447: po ni // dkar ser rdo rje rtse gcig 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:8448: thugs dam dbang gi rtags ston ma //
NK027(sha)001:8449: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya mo //
NK027(sha)001:8450: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi gnon mdzad ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8451: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jig rten
NK027(sha)001:8452: dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya
NK027(sha)001:8453: gnon mdzad ma // dkar ser rdo rje brag 'phen ma //
NK027(sha)001:8454: ri rab rtse yang gnon byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8455: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi dbang phyug ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8456: dbang 'di sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs dri
NK027(sha)001:8457: za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya dbang
NK027(sha)001:8458: phyug ma // dkar ser dri shul gze mo 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:8459: dug gsum nad rnams 'joms byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8460: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi sred mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8461: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya sum brgya
NK027(sha)001:8462: 'jigs byed dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi mi mo
NK027(sha)001:8463: drug rdo rje pho nya sred mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:8464: dkar ser lcags kyu dmar po thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8465: btab pa tsam gyi gang yang khug /
NK027(sha)001:8466: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi kha 'bar ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8467: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs dri
NK027(sha)001:8468: za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya kha
NK027(sha)001:8469: 'bar ma // dkar ser sprin gyi go zu can //
NK027(sha)001:8470: kha la me 'bar rgya mtsho skam //
NK027(sha)001:8471: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi gsal byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8472: dbang 'di sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs dri
NK027(sha)001:8473: za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya gsal
NK027(sha)001:8474: byed ma // dkar ser dung gi 'khor lo 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:8475: gang la bya bas sa ler gsal //
NK027(sha)001:8476: dbang 'di bu b+ha na a b+hi khro bo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8477: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya 'jigs dri za'i shar dung gi rdo rje pho nya khro mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:8478: dkar ser khro mo'i gzugs 'chang ma //
NK027(sha)001:8479: de bzhin lag na g.yang gzhi rdeb //
NK027(sha)001:8480: dbang 'di b+ha na b+ha na a b+hi 'chang ba thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8481: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya drug cu'i gdon sgrol phyir //
NK027(sha)001:8482: dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya 'chang ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:8483: dkar ser rdo rje phur bu 'chang //
NK027(sha)001:8484: gang la bya ba'i snying la 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:8485: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi gtum mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8486: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs dri
NK027(sha)001:8487: za'i shar phyogs dung gi mi mo rdo rje pho
NK027(sha)001:8489: dmar ser rdo rje tho ba thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8490: gang la dmigs pa yud kyi 'joms //
NK027(sha)001:8491: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi khros ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8492: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs dri
NK027(sha)001:8493: za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya khros
NK027(sha)001:8494: ma ni // dmar ser rdo rje be con 'chang khro zhing //
NK027(sha)001:8495: gtum pa dpa' brtul cho dkar spyod //
NK027(sha)001:8496: dbang 'di las byed ma thogs te //
NK027(sha)001:8497: b+ha na a dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho
NK027(sha)001:8498: nya 'jigs dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje
NK027(sha)001:8500: dmar ser gcod pa'i ral gri 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:8501: sems can skye shi rtsad gcod ma //
NK027(sha)001:8502: dbang 'di b+ha na a dus mtshan ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8503: dbang sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs dri za'i
NK027(sha)001:8504: shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya dus mtshan
NK027(sha)001:8505: ma // dmar ser lag na shag ti thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8506: ma lus 'joms pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:8507: dbang 'di b+ha na b+ha na a b+hi thar pa mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8508: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya sum 'jigs
NK027(sha)001:8509: byed dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi mi mo rdo
NK027(sha)001:8510: rje pho nya thar pa mo //
NK027(sha)001:8511: dmar ser lag na gtun shing thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8512: rdul du brlag pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:8513: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi sku la ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8514: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs dri
NK027(sha)001:8515: za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya sku
NK027(sha)001:8516: la ma // dmar ser lag na lcags kyu 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:8517: ma lus 'dzin pa'i ging chen ma //
NK027(sha)001:8518: dbang 'di b+ha na dpal 'bar ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8519: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs dri
NK027(sha)001:8520: za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya dpal
NK027(sha)001:8521: 'bar ma // dmar ser ras kyi zhags pa 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:8522: dpal chen sku la sbyor mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:8523: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi bskyod chen ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8524: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs dri
NK027(sha)001:8525: za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya bskyod
NK027(sha)001:8526: chen ma // dmar ser rlangs kyi rkyal pa thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8527: bskul ba'i mi chen gtong ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:8528: dbang gi b+ha na a b+hi lus khros ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8529: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs byed
NK027(sha)001:8530: dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya
NK027(sha)001:8531: lus khros ma // dkar ser lcags kyi tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro //
NK027(sha)001:8532: ba spu skra 'khreg rdo rje'i sku //
NK027(sha)001:8533: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi ngag 'phrog ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8534: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs dri
NK027(sha)001:8535: za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya ngag
NK027(sha)001:8536: 'phrog ma // dmar ser 'gugs byed lcags kyu ma //
NK027(sha)001:8537: smra ba ngag gi lce 'phrog ma //
NK027(sha)001:8538: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi yid gtum ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8539: dbang gi sku yi sum rgya pho nya 'jigs dri
NK027(sha)001:8540: za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya yid
NK027(sha)001:8541: gtum ma // dkar ser sen mos snying 'byin ma //
NK027(sha)001:8542: thugs rjes bdud srin myos byed barlama //
NK027(sha)001:8543: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi sde chen mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8544: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs byed
NK027(sha)001:8545: dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya
NK027(sha)001:8546: sde chen ma // dmar ser ral gri'i g.yab mo 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:8547: thugs rjes bsgral ba'i zhing bcu sgrol //
NK027(sha)001:8548: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi gsod byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8549: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs byed
NK027(sha)001:8550: dri za'i shar dung gi rdo rje pho nya gsod
NK027(sha)001:8551: byed ma // dkar sngo dung gi zhags pa thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8552: thugs rjes bsgral ba'i zhing bcu sgrol //
NK027(sha)001:8553: dbang 'di bu la bskur b+ha na a b+hi zhags pa thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8554: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya sum 'jigs
NK027(sha)001:8555: byed dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho
NK027(sha)001:8556: dkar sngo dung gi zhags pa bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:8557: thugs rjes bdud dang srin po sgrol //
NK027(sha)001:8558: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi gsod ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8559: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya sum 'jigs
NK027(sha)001:8560: byed dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho
NK027(sha)001:8562: dkar sngo shel gyi gri thog ma //
NK027(sha)001:8563: gsod pa'i las la b+ha zhig dgyes //
NK027(sha)001:8564: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi za ba mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8565: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs dri
NK027(sha)001:8566: za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya za
NK027(sha)001:8567: ba mo // dkar sngo mam sa zas su za //
NK027(sha)001:8568: gti mug gtan nas zad mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:8569: dbang gi b+ha na a b+hi khrag 'thung ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8570: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs dri
NK027(sha)001:8571: za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya khrag
NK027(sha)001:8572: 'thung ma // dkar sngo b+han+d+ha thod khrag 'thung //
NK027(sha)001:8573: 'dod chags gtan nas zad mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:8574: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi mche ba mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8575: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs dri
NK027(sha)001:8576: za'i shar phyogs 'od zer dung gi rdo rje pho
NK027(sha)001:8578: dkar sngo keng rus khral khrol 'cha' //
NK027(sha)001:8579: zhe sdang gtan nas zad mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:8580: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi tshe len ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8581: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya sum brgya drug cur sprul //
NK027(sha)001:8582: 'jigs byed dri za'i shar phyogs 'od dung gi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK027(sha)001:8583: rdo rje pho nya tshe len ma //
NK027(sha)001:8584: rdo rje thugs kyis pho nya'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:8585: sdang ba dgra yi tshe 'phrog ma //
NK027(sha)001:8586: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi mdangs len ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8587: rdo rje pho nya mdangs len ma //
NK027(sha)001:8588: dkar mo dung gi ba ru bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:8589: gang la dmigs pa'i mdangs 'phrog ma //
NK027(sha)001:8590: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi srog 'phrog ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8591: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs byed
NK027(sha)001:8592: shar phyogs dung dung gi rdo rje pho nya srog
NK027(sha)001:8593: 'phrog ma // dkar mo lag g.yas tsit+ta 'byin //
NK027(sha)001:8594: skad cig yud la nyams pa len //
NK027(sha)001:8595: dbang 'di b+ha na b+ha na a b+hi snying 'byin ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8596: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs byed
NK027(sha)001:8597: shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya snying 'byin
NK027(sha)001:8598: ma // dkar sngo snying gi phreng ba bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:8599: rnam shes phung po gtan bcom ma //
NK027(sha)001:8600: dbang 'di b+ha a b+hi gcod byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8601: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya sum brgya
NK027(sha)001:8602: 'jigs byed 'bar ba'i dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi
NK027(sha)001:8604: rdo rje pho nya gcod byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8605: dkar ljang shel gyi dgra s+t+wa phyar //
NK027(sha)001:8606: rgyu drug 'khor ba rtsad nas gcod //
NK027(sha)001:8607: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi bskul byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8608: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs byed
NK027(sha)001:8609: dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya
NK027(sha)001:8610: bskul byed ma // dkar mo phyag na lcags kyu can //
NK027(sha)001:8611: zhing bcu bsgral nas thugs dam bskul //
NK027(sha)001:8612: dbang 'di b+ha na b+ha na a b+hi sna tshogs gzugs thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8613: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs byed
NK027(sha)001:8614: dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya
NK027(sha)001:8615: sna tshogs gzugs // bse yi len dkar na bza' gsol //
NK027(sha)001:8616: ma lus sgrol ba'i bya ra ma //
NK027(sha)001:8617: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi smyon ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8618: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs byed
NK027(sha)001:8619: dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya
NK027(sha)001:8620: smyon ma ni // dkar ljang shel gyi rdo rje 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:8621: gzhan gyi mi thub drag shul che //
NK027(sha)001:8622: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi 'jug byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8623: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs dri
NK027(sha)001:8624: za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya 'jug
NK027(sha)001:8625: byed ma // dkar ljang phyag na khrag thogs ma //
NK027(sha)001:8627: dbang 'di b+ha a b+hi yid 'phrog ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8628: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs byed
NK027(sha)001:8629: 'bar ba'i dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje
NK027(sha)001:8631: dkar ljang mtshon gyi gru gu thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8633: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi shiny+tsa ro rkun ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8634: dbang 'di sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs byed
NK027(sha)001:8635: dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya
NK027(sha)001:8636: ro rkun ma / dkar ljang zhing gi ro khur ma //
NK027(sha)001:8637: dur khrod bgegs kyi tshogs 'joms ma //
NK027(sha)001:8638: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi rdzus skyes ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8639: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs dri
NK027(sha)001:8640: za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya bsdu
NK027(sha)001:8641: byed ma // dkar ljang rlung gi zhags pa 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:8642: cir yang sprul pa'i sku gcig ma //
NK027(sha)001:8643: dbang 'di a b+hi 'jigs byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8644: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs byed
NK027(sha)001:8645: dri za'i shar phyogs dung gi rdo rje pho nya
NK027(sha)001:8646: 'jigs byed ma // dkar ljang dung gi mche ba 'dzin /
NK027(sha)001:8648: dbang 'di b+ha na a b+hi bcud len ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8649: dbang gi sku yi sum brgya pho nya 'jigs dri
NK027(sha)001:8650: za'i shar phyogs dung gi mi rdo rje pho nya
NK027(sha)001:8651: bcud len ma // dkar ljang g.yu yi za ma tog /
NK027(sha)001:8652: khams gsum tshe sdud pho nya mo //
NK027(sha)001:8653: dbang 'di bu la bskur bar bya //
NK027(sha)001:8654: b+ha na b+ha na a b+hi lho'i pho nya drug cu las /
NK027(sha)001:8656: dbang gi dkyil dgra dang gshin rje gdon 'dul phyir //
NK027(sha)001:8657: 'jigs byed pho nya'i lho phyogs 'od zer ser po las //
NK027(sha)001:8658: gser gyi mi mo drug cu byung //
NK027(sha)001:8659: yon tan pho nya dbyings phyug ma //
NK027(sha)001:8660: ser nag me yi zhags pa thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8661: ci bgyis zhes kyang thogs pa med //
NK027(sha)001:8663: ha la ha la pa sha h+aum /
NK027(sha)001:8665: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs byed lho phyogs gser yon tan pho nya mkha' 'gro ma //
NK027(sha)001:8666: ser nag sdig mdzub gyad 'dor ma //
NK027(sha)001:8667: lhag ma len cing bsgrub la mgon //
NK027(sha)001:8668: dbang 'di ha la ha la pa sha h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8669: a b+hi mthu 'beb ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8670: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs byed lho phyogs gser yon tan pho nya mthu 'beb ma //
NK027(sha)001:8671: dmar ser ba ngan g.yab dor ma //
NK027(sha)001:8672: bsgrub pa po la mthu byin 'beb //
NK027(sha)001:8673: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi pra ba ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8674: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs byed lho phyogs gser gyi yon tan pho nya pra ba mo //
NK027(sha)001:8675: ser nag rdo rje'i go gyon pas //
NK027(sha)001:8676: cis kyang mi tshugs rdo rje'i sku //
NK027(sha)001:8677: dbang 'di ha la ha la a b+hi mchongs mo che thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8678: dbang gi dkyil 'khor dgra dang gshin rje gdon 'dul phyir //
NK027(sha)001:8679: 'jigs byed pho nya'i skur sprul pa //
NK027(sha)001:8680: lho phyogs gser gyi yon tan pho nya'i mchong mo che //
NK027(sha)001:8681: ser nag 'chongs stabs byan lag thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8682: ri klungs kun sleb mchongs byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8683: dbang 'di ha la ha la pa sha h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8684: a b+hi khro gtum thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8685: dbang 'di dgra dang 'jigs byed lho phyogs gser gyi yon tan pho nya khro gtum can //
NK027(sha)001:8686: ser nag sdang mig dgra la zhon //
NK027(sha)001:8687: dgra bgegs ma lus 'joms byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8688: dbang ha la ha la a b+hi brtson byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8689: dbang gi dkyil dgra bgegs 'jigs byed lho phyogs gser yon tan pho nya brtson byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8690: ser nag rlung gi zhags pa 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:8691: gyen mthur med par rgyug cing 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:8693: a b+hi 'jigs gdon ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8694: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs byed lho phyogs gser yon tan pho nya 'jigs gdon ma //
NK027(sha)001:8695: kha bsgrad mche gtsigs lag gnyis gdon //
NK027(sha)001:8696: stobs che mthu yang 'joms byed pa //
NK027(sha)001:8697: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi sha za ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8698: yon tan pho nya sha za ma //
NK027(sha)001:8699: me khrag dbyug pa glad la bskor //
NK027(sha)001:8700: mang sa za zhing bdud kyi 'joms //
NK027(sha)001:8701: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi khrag 'thor ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8702: yon tan pho nya khrag 'thor ma //
NK027(sha)001:8703: mi mgo'i phur pa rlon pa ru //
NK027(sha)001:8704: mi snying khrag zhag blug cing 'thor //
NK027(sha)001:8705: dbang 'di ha la ha la a b+hi so gcig ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8706: dbang gi dgra dang gshin rje gdon 'dul phyir //
NK027(sha)001:8707: 'jigs byed pho nya'i sku sprul pa //
NK027(sha)001:8708: lho phyogs 'od zer ser po las //
NK027(sha)001:8709: gser gyi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK027(sha)001:8710: yon tan pho nya so gcig ma //
NK027(sha)001:8711: ser mo kha mig so gcig ma //
NK027(sha)001:8712: rdo rje rtse gcig mda' 'phen ma //
NK027(sha)001:8713: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi ral bsig ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8714: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs lho phyogs gser yon tan pho nya ral bsig ma //
NK027(sha)001:8715: ser nag ral bsig go zu can //
NK027(sha)001:8716: g.yon bsdig g.yas pa lcags kyu 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:8717: dbang 'di ha la ha la a b+hi 'khrel byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8718: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs lho phyogs gser yon tan pho nya 'khrel byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8719: ser mo sngon dmar zhags pa 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:8720: bardzu ni gnyan dang dung phor bardzu //
NK027(sha)001:8721: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi 'dzul byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8722: dbang gi dgra 'jigs byed lho phyogs gser yon na pho nya 'dzul byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8723: ser mo gser gyi zangs gri thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8724: sku ni sprul dang sre mong rdzu //
NK027(sha)001:8725: dbang 'di ha la ha la a b+hi myur byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8726: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs lho phyogs gser yon tan pho nya myur byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8727: ser mo mtshon gyi gru gu thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8728: sku ni 'ug srin bya ba bardzu //
NK027(sha)001:8729: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi mthu chen ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8730: dbang gi dgra 'jigs lho phyogs gser yon tan pho nya mthu chen ma //
NK027(sha)001:8731: ser mo thog gi char 'bebs ma //
NK027(sha)001:8732: gnas sa ri lung kun tu khyab //
NK027(sha)001:8733: dbang 'di ha la ha la a b+hi nag mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8734: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs byed lho phyogs gser gyi yon tan pho nya nag mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:8735: nag mo dril ba'i zhags pa 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:8736: khams gsum b+h+yo dang kus 'debs ma //
NK027(sha)001:8737: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi rtog med ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8738: dbang gi dgra dang bgegs 'jigs lho phyogs gser gyi yon tan pho nya rtog med ma //
NK027(sha)001:8739: ser mo b+han+d+ha rlon pa ru //
NK027(sha)001:8740: dam rdzas rnam lnga za zhing spyod //
NK027(sha)001:8741: dbang ha la ha la a b+hi rtogs 'joms ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8742: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs lho phyogs gser yon tan pho nya rtogs 'joms ma //
NK027(sha)001:8743: ser mo dung gi gzhung thog ma //
NK027(sha)001:8744: gang la bcol yang tshig cing khro //
NK027(sha)001:8745: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi spang ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8746: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs lho phyogs gser yon tan pho nya spang pa ma //
NK027(sha)001:8747: ser mo sprin gyi ga zha can //
NK027(sha)001:8748: glog gi phreng ba glad la bskor //
NK027(sha)001:8749: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi sna tshogs lus ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8751: yon tan pho nya sna tshogs lus //
NK027(sha)001:8752: dmar skya za 'og stod g.yog can //
NK027(sha)001:8753: rnga mong ga par bardzu byed pa //
NK027(sha)001:8754: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi gdong mig ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8755: dbang 'di dgra dang lho gser yon tan pho nya gdong mig ma //
NK027(sha)001:8756: dmar skya lcags kyi khra 'dzin ma //
NK027(sha)001:8757: dgra dang bgegs la glog ltar 'joms //
NK027(sha)001:8758: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi dur khrod ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8759: dbang gi dgra dang bgegs lho yon tan pho nya dur khrod ma //
NK027(sha)001:8760: dmar skya zhing gi g.yang gzhi 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:8761: mkhas pas dgra bgegs sgrol byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8762: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi mig 'gro ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8763: dbang gi dgra dang gshin rje gdon 'dul phyir //
NK027(sha)001:8764: 'jigs byed pho nya'i sku lho phyogs yon tan pho nya mig 'phrog ma //
NK027(sha)001:8765: khyung la zhon zhing glog 'debs ma //
NK027(sha)001:8766: gang la dmigs pa yud kyi 'grub //
NK027(sha)001:8767: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi shiny+tsa bde 'gro ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8768: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs lho phyogs yon tan pho nya bde 'gro ma //
NK027(sha)001:8769: mchong gi bya klag dmar mo zhon //
NK027(sha)001:8770: ser mo g.yu yi zor ba 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:8771: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi rgyal byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8772: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs lho phyogs yon tan pho nya rgyal byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8774: tshe dang phung po bcas pa 'joms //
NK027(sha)001:8775: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi 'dzum byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8776: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs byed lho phyogs yon tan pho nya 'dzum byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8777: ser skya mtshon gyi gru gu thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8778: bardzu ni bu chung spre'ura rdzus //
NK027(sha)001:8779: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi khrag myos ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8780: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs lho phyogs yon tan pho nya khrag myos ma //
NK027(sha)001:8781: dmar mo mchu ring dur bya'i gdong //
NK027(sha)001:8782: rtsa la rgyug cing snying khrag 'thung //
NK027(sha)001:8783: dbang 'di ha la ha la a b+hi rngams tshig ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8784: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs byed lho phyogs yon tan pho nya rngams tshig ma //
NK027(sha)001:8785: mngag cing bcol ba'i las bcol na //
NK027(sha)001:8786: rang la rang yang tshig cing khro //
NK027(sha)001:8787: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi mgyogs byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8788: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs lho phyogs yon tan pho nya mgyogs byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8789: ser skya mgyogs byed rlung la zhon //
NK027(sha)001:8790: gar yang mi btang mthu mo che //
NK027(sha)001:8791: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi gtum pa mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8792: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs byed lho phyogs gser gyi yon tan pho nya gtum pa mo //
NK027(sha)001:8793: dmar ser spu gri snying 'byin ma //
NK027(sha)001:8794: nyams pa'i dgra bgegs dmyal thag gcod //
NK027(sha)001:8795: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi mdung thung ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:8796: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs lho phyogs gser gyi yon tan pho nya mdung thung 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:8797: dkar ser g.yon sder g.yas mdung 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:8798: bdud dang srin po tshar gcod ma //
NK027(sha)001:8799: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi glog 'gyu ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8800: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs lho phyogs yon tan pho nya glog 'gyu ma //
NK027(sha)001:8801: dmar ser glog gi zhags pa 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:8802: nam mkha'i mtha' nas 'grim dbang ha la a b+hi thog 'beb ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:8803: dbang gi dgra 'jigs lho yon tan pho nya thog 'beb ma //
NK027(sha)001:8804: dmar ser thog gi tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro //
NK027(sha)001:8805: rgya mtsho gting yang skem par byed //
NK027(sha)001:8806: dbang ha la a b+hi spor byed ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:8807: dbang gi dgra 'jigs lho phyogs yon tan pho nya spor byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8808: dmar ser zhag chen zhal du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:8809: zhing chung gtan nas len par byed //
NK027(sha)001:8810: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi 'khrug byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8811: dbang gi dgra 'jigs lho phyogs yon tan pho nya 'khrug byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8812: ri rab rtse nas 'joms byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8814: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi shiny+tsa dbang phyug ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:8815: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs lho yon tan pho nya dbang phyug ma //
NK027(sha)001:8816: smug nag dur khrod khrag 'thung ma //
NK027(sha)001:8817: sgrol byed snying 'byin gri thogs ma //
NK027(sha)001:8818: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi ka ma la thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8819: dbang gi dgra dang gshin rje gdon 'jigs byed lho phyogs gser gyi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK027(sha)001:8820: yon tan pho nya ka ma la //
NK027(sha)001:8821: smug nag dur khrod khrag 'thung ma //
NK027(sha)001:8822: sgrol byed snying 'byin gri thog ma //
NK027(sha)001:8823: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi gsal bkra ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8824: dbang dgra 'jigs lho gser yon tan pho nya gsal bkra ma //
NK027(sha)001:8825: dmar ser nyi zla'i zhags pa 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:8826: gang ltar song yang mi gtong zhing //
NK027(sha)001:8827: dbang ha la a b+hi kha bsgyur ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:8828: dbang gi gra dang 'jigs lho yon tan pho nya kha bsgyur ma //
NK027(sha)001:8829: dmar ser dung gi sgo ba zhon //
NK027(sha)001:8830: ri lung med pa rjes kyi 'ging //
NK027(sha)001:8831: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi kun sgrol ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8832: dbang gi dgra 'jigs lho yon tan pho nya kun sgrol ma //
NK027(sha)001:8833: dmar ljang ral gri glad la bskor //
NK027(sha)001:8834: gso byed sram dang chu bya sprul //
NK027(sha)001:8835: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi myos byed ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:8836: dbang dgra 'jigs lho yon tan pho nya myos byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8837: dmar nag ra ro smyo bardzu can //
NK027(sha)001:8838: dkar dmar snying gi mtshams nas 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:8839: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi khrag 'thung ma /
NK027(sha)001:8840: dbang gi dgra 'jigs lho yon tan pho nya khrag 'thung ma //
NK027(sha)001:8841: dmar ljang thod khrag zhal du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:8843: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi 'bar ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:8844: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs lho yon tan pho nya 'bar ma ni //
NK027(sha)001:8845: dmar nag rin chen 'bar ba thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8847: dbang 'di bu la ha la ha la pa sha h'u /
NK027(sha)001:8848: a b+hi mi bzang ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8849: dbang gi dgra dang gshin rje gdon 'jigs byed pho
NK027(sha)001:8850: nya lho phyogs gser gyi yon tan pho nya mi
NK027(sha)001:8851: bzang ma // gnam sa gnyis kyang 'thags su 'thag /
NK027(sha)001:8852: skye 'gro gnyis kyang rtsa ba gcod //
NK027(sha)001:8853: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi shiny+tsa 'phrog byed ma /
NK027(sha)001:8854: dbang gi dgra dang 'jigs lho gser yon tan pho nya 'phrog byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8856: g.yon nas ga pus srog ma dbang //
NK027(sha)001:8857: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi sgrol byed ma /
NK027(sha)001:8858: dbang gi dgra 'jigs lho gser gyi rin chen pho nya sgrol byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8860: ma lus sgrol ba'i mthu mo che //
NK027(sha)001:8861: dbang 'di ha la ha la a b+hi sna tshogs stobs thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8862: dbang gi dgra 'jigs lho yon tan pho nya sna tshogs stobs //
NK027(sha)001:8863: ser skya zhing gi rkang lag 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:8864: dug gsum ma lus zhal du stobs //
NK027(sha)001:8865: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi yid 'phrog ma /
NK027(sha)001:8866: dbang gi dgra 'jigs lho yon tan pho nya yid 'phrog ma //
NK027(sha)001:8867: ser ljang na chung tshul du bardzu //
NK027(sha)001:8868: bsgrub par byed pa'i yid 'phrog ma //
NK027(sha)001:8869: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi srog len ma /
NK027(sha)001:8870: dbang gi dgra 'jigs lho gser yon tan pho nya srog len ma //
NK027(sha)001:8871: mi snying rus pa'i zhags pa 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:8872: zhing bcu gnas nas len par byed //
NK027(sha)001:8873: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi bcud len pas /
NK027(sha)001:8874: dbang dgra 'jigs lho yon tan pho nya bcud len ma //
NK027(sha)001:8875: ser smug zangs kyis mchu ring ma //
NK027(sha)001:8877: dbang 'di ha la ha la a b+hi tshe 'dzin ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8878: dbang gi dgra 'jigs lho yon tan pho nya tshe 'dzin ma //
NK027(sha)001:8879: bswe yi ga'u dmar po nas //
NK027(sha)001:8880: dza dmar pho nya tshe rkun ma //
NK027(sha)001:8881: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi dbang mo che /
NK027(sha)001:8882: dbang gi dgra 'jigs lho yon tan pho nya dbang mo che //
NK027(sha)001:8883: ser smug seng ge dkar mo zhon //
NK027(sha)001:8884: nyi zla rus pa'i zhags pa 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:8885: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi drag po 'joms pa ma /
NK027(sha)001:8886: dbang gi dgra 'jigs lho yon tan pho nya drag 'joms ma //
NK027(sha)001:8888: myur ba'i shugs 'chang thugs rje che //
NK027(sha)001:8889: dbang ha la a b+hi bdud byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8890: dbang gi dgra 'jigs lho yon tan pho nya bdud byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8891: dam tshig nyams pa'i bdud du 'bebs //
NK027(sha)001:8892: dge spyod rnams kyi dpal du che //
NK027(sha)001:8893: dbang 'di ha la ha la a b+hi bla 'dzin ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8894: dbang gi dgra 'jigs lho yon tan pho nya gla 'dzin ma //
NK027(sha)001:8896: ci ltar 'dul ba'i bzhin du sprul //
NK027(sha)001:8897: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi srog 'dzin ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8898: dbang gi dgra 'jigs lho yon tan pho nya srog 'dzin ma //
NK027(sha)001:8899: ser smug lcags kyu'i phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)001:8900: sems can kun gyi tshe srog 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:8901: dbang 'di ha la ha la a b+hi rtsa 'gro ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8902: dbang gi dgra 'jigs lho yon tan pho nya rtsa 'gro ma //
NK027(sha)001:8903: sum brgya drug cu'i rtsa la rgyu //
NK027(sha)001:8904: dam nyams dgra bgegs rtsa rgyus phrol //
NK027(sha)001:8905: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi gnas 'byin ma /
NK027(sha)001:8906: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK027(sha)001:8907: dgra dang gshin rje gdon 'dul phyir //
NK027(sha)001:8908: 'jigs byed pho nya sku sprul pa //
NK027(sha)001:8909: lho phyogs 'od zer ser po las //
NK027(sha)001:8910: gser gyi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK027(sha)001:8911: yon tan pho nya gnas 'byin ma //
NK027(sha)001:8913: sa dgu'i steng nas 'joms par byed //
NK027(sha)001:8914: dbang 'di ha la ha la a b+hi gnas stod ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8915: yon tan pho nya gnas bstod ma //
NK027(sha)001:8916: thugs rje chen po'i gang bsgral ba //
NK027(sha)001:8917: byang chub thar lam bde la bkod //
NK027(sha)001:8918: dbang 'di ha la a b+hi thog 'beb ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8919: dbang gi thugs rjes 'jigs byed skur sprul pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:8920: dgra dang klu gdon 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:8921: nub phyogs 'od zer dmar po las //
NK027(sha)001:8922: zangs kyi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK027(sha)001:8923: gsung gi pho nya thog 'bebs ma //
NK027(sha)001:8924: dmar nag lag na thogs 'beb ma //
NK027(sha)001:8925: gang la dmigs pa yud kyi bsreg /
NK027(sha)001:8926: dbang 'di gardza gardza s+pho ta bam /
NK027(sha)001:8927: a b+hi 'brug sgrogs ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8928: gsung gi pho nya 'brug sgrog ma //
NK027(sha)001:8929: dmar nag 'brug chen chibs su chibs //
NK027(sha)001:8930: stong gsum kun grags mthu mo che //
NK027(sha)001:8931: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi char 'beb ma thog sa te /
NK027(sha)001:8932: gsung gi pho nya char 'bebs ma //
NK027(sha)001:8933: dmar nag srin chen slag pa can //
NK027(sha)001:8934: dug dang bdud rtsi char 'beb ma //
NK027(sha)001:8935: dbang 'di a gardza a b+hi 'od 'gyed ma /
NK027(sha)001:8938: mun pa'i nang nas sgron gsal ma /
NK027(sha)001:8939: dbang 'di gardza gardza s+pho ta bam /
NK027(sha)001:8940: a b+hi bkrag gsal ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8941: thugs rjes 'jigs byed skur sprul pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:8942: dgra dang klu gdon 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:8943: nub phyogs 'od zer dmar po las //
NK027(sha)001:8944: gsung gi pho nya bkrag gsal ma //
NK027(sha)001:8945: dmar nag g.yu yi len phran can //
NK027(sha)001:8946: 'jig rten khams kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK027(sha)001:8947: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi 'ja' tshon ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8948: gsung gi pho nya 'ja' tshon ma //
NK027(sha)001:8949: dmar nag 'ja' tshon zhags pa thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8950: rdzu 'phrul cis kyang mi tshug pa //
NK027(sha)001:8951: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi 'od 'phro ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8954: phrin las myur mgyogs thogs pa med //
NK027(sha)001:8955: dbang 'di gardza a b+hi 'od gsal ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:8956: gsung gi pho nya 'od gsal ma //
NK027(sha)001:8957: dmar nag me 'od phyag na bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:8958: 'khor ba'i bag chags bsreg mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:8959: dbang 'di gardza a b+hi khrag 'thung ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:8960: gsung gi pho nya khrag 'thung ma //
NK027(sha)001:8961: dmar nag thod khrag skom du 'thung //
NK027(sha)001:8962: ma lus yongs kyi khrag 'thung ma //
NK027(sha)001:8963: dbang 'di gardza a b+hi dbang phyug dmar nag thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:8964: gsung gi pho nya dbang phyug ma //
NK027(sha)001:8965: dmar nag rdo rje pad+ma can //
NK027(sha)001:8966: srid pa gsum na mthu mo che //
NK027(sha)001:8967: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi sa bdag mo /
NK027(sha)001:8968: gsung gi pho nya sa bdag mo //
NK027(sha)001:8969: dmar sngo lcags kyi phag mgo thogs //
NK027(sha)001:8970: sa chen dgu yang 'khrug par byed //
NK027(sha)001:8971: dbang 'di gardza gardza s+pho ta bam /
NK027(sha)001:8972: a b+hi thugs rjes 'jigs byed skur sprul pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:8973: dgra dang klu gdon 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:8974: nub phyogs 'gugs byed ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:8975: gsung gi pho nya 'gugs byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:8976: dmar sngo rdo rje lcags kyu can //
NK027(sha)001:8978: dbang 'di gardza gardza ab+hi dkar sham mos /
NK027(sha)001:8979: gsung gi pho nya dkar sham mo //
NK027(sha)001:8980: dmar sngo bswe yi gdu gu can //
NK027(sha)001:8981: nyams pa'i khrag 'thung dbang mo che //
NK027(sha)001:8983: a lcags sgrog ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:8984: gsung gi pho nya lcags sgrog ma //
NK027(sha)001:8985: dmar sngo zhing gi rnge'u chung rdung //
NK027(sha)001:8986: dgra chen bdud bzhi zil gyi gnon //
NK027(sha)001:8988: gsung gi pho nya yid gzhung ma //
NK027(sha)001:8989: dmar sngo lag na khu tshur 'chang //
NK027(sha)001:8990: 'khor ba gnas nas spor mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:8991: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi lta na mdzes /
NK027(sha)001:8992: gsung gi pho nya lta na mdzes //
NK027(sha)001:8993: sngo dmar me tog chun 'phyang can //
NK027(sha)001:8994: yid 'ong phrin las kun mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:8995: dbang gardza gardza a b+hi sems 'phrog ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:8996: gsung gi pho nya sems 'phrog ma //
NK027(sha)001:8997: dmar sngo g.yu yi nyi ma bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:8998: ma lus kun gyi snying 'byin ma //
NK027(sha)001:8999: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi bdud 'beb ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9000: gsung gi pho nya bdud 'beb ma //
NK027(sha)001:9001: dmar sngo mi thod rta thod thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9003: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi mgyogs byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9004: gsung gi pho nya mgyogs byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9005: dmar sngo khyung chen chibs su bcib //
NK027(sha)001:9006: zil gyi gnon pa'i 'phrin las mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:9007: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi gsod byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9008: nub phyogs 'od zer dmar po las //
NK027(sha)001:9009: gsung gi pho nya gsod byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9010: dmar sngo sre zhon mdung thogs ma //
NK027(sha)001:9011: gang la dmigs pa yud kyi phyin //
NK027(sha)001:9013: a b+hi shiny+tsa snying 'dzin ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9014: gsung gi pho nya snying 'byin ma //
NK027(sha)001:9015: dmar ljang lag na tsit+ta thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9018: a dmar thung ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9019: gsung gi pho nya dmar thung ma //
NK027(sha)001:9020: dmar ljang dung chen khrag 'thung ma //
NK027(sha)001:9021: khams gsum yongs kyis snying khrag 'thung //
NK027(sha)001:9022: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi rkang 'jib ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9023: gsung gi dmar ljang dbyi yi mgo bo can //
NK027(sha)001:9024: zas su rkang dang bcud 'jib ma //
NK027(sha)001:9025: dbang 'di gardza gardza a las byed ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9026: gsung gi pho nya las byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9027: dmar ljang 'brug sngon chibs su bcib //
NK027(sha)001:9029: dbang 'di gardza gardza a zhags thogs ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9030: gsung gi pho nya zhags thogs ma //
NK027(sha)001:9031: sngon mo zhags thogs rlung la zhon //
NK027(sha)001:9032: khyod kyi mi gzigs gang yang med //
NK027(sha)001:9033: dbang gardza gardza a b+hi gla 'phrog ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9034: gsung gi pho nya gla 'phrog ma //
NK027(sha)001:9035: dmar skya skyi ser rlung la zhon //
NK027(sha)001:9036: sku la ri rgyal dkri mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:9037: dbang 'di gardza gardza a thogs med ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9038: gsung gi pho nya thogs med ma //
NK027(sha)001:9039: dmar ljang ral gri rnon po thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9040: dam las 'gal ba sgrol byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9041: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi za byed ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9042: gsung gi pho nya za byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9043: dmar ljang stag chen sder mang zhon //
NK027(sha)001:9044: gtsang sme med par za byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9045: dbang 'di gardza a myos byed ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9046: gsung gi pho nya myos byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9047: dmar nag lcags kyi tho ba thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9048: mgo dang glad pa 'gem byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9049: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi rmong byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9050: gsung gi pho nya rmong byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9051: dmar ljang lcags kyi d+r+wa ba thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9052: gang la bya ba 'dzin cing bsdom //
NK027(sha)001:9053: dbang gardza a bardzu byed ma /
NK027(sha)001:9054: gsung gi pho nya bardzu byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9055: dmar ser ra skyes kham pa bcib //
NK027(sha)001:9056: cir yang sprul cing bardzu byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9057: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi 'khrug byed ma /
NK027(sha)001:9058: gsung gi pho nya 'khrug byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9059: dmar ser rgya mtsho hub kyi 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:9060: klu yi gnas kyang 'joms par byed //
NK027(sha)001:9061: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi 'khrug byed ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9062: gsung gi pho nya 'khrug byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9063: dmar ser rgya mtsho hub kyi 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:9064: klu yi gnas kyang 'joms par byed //
NK027(sha)001:9065: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi drag mo /
NK027(sha)001:9066: gsung gi pho nya drag mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9067: dmar ser gtum pa dam pa zhon //
NK027(sha)001:9068: gti mug dreg pa 'joms byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9069: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi sgam ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9070: gsung gi pho nya sgam ma ni //
NK027(sha)001:9071: dmar ser khrag gi lan phran can //
NK027(sha)001:9072: ma lus 'joms pa'i mthu mo che //
NK027(sha)001:9073: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi 'joms ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9074: gsung gi pho nya 'joms ma ni //
NK027(sha)001:9075: dmar ser spang ti'i mgo bo can //
NK027(sha)001:9076: gti mug glang chen dred byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9077: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi rab dga' ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9078: gsung gi pho nya rab dga' ma //
NK027(sha)001:9079: dmar ser lag na zangs gri thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9081: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi 'dzin ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9082: gsung gi pho nya 'dzin ma ni //
NK027(sha)001:9083: dmar ser sprul nag zhags pa 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:9085: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi glog 'gyu ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9086: gsung gi pho nya glog 'gyu ma //
NK027(sha)001:9087: dmar ser rdzu 'phrul khra thog ma //
NK027(sha)001:9088: dam las log pa'i snying 'byin ma //
NK027(sha)001:9089: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi g.yul 'joms ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9090: gsung gi pho nya g.yul 'joms ma //
NK027(sha)001:9091: dmar ser lag na shag ti thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9092: dgra dang bdud kyi dpung 'joms ma //
NK027(sha)001:9093: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi lha 'brel ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9094: gsung gi pho nya lha 'brel ma //
NK027(sha)001:9095: dmar ser rdo rje thog 'phen ma //
NK027(sha)001:9096: srid pa gsum yang rtse nas 'joms //
NK027(sha)001:9097: dbang 'di gardza gardza a srog 'brel ma thog sa te /
NK027(sha)001:9098: gsung gi pho nya srog 'brel ma //
NK027(sha)001:9099: dmar smug 'joms pa'i a ra ti //
NK027(sha)001:9100: gsod cing 'joms pa'i pho nya mo //
NK027(sha)001:9101: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi myur byed ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9102: gsung gi pho nya myur byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9103: dmar smug glog gi ga zha can //
NK027(sha)001:9104: thugs rjes shugs 'chang pho nya mo //
NK027(sha)001:9105: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi ring byed ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9106: gsung gi pho nya ring byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9107: bud med lus la g.yang mo che //
NK027(sha)001:9108: ring lung med par rjes kyi 'geng //
NK027(sha)001:9109: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi bsreg byed ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9110: gsung gi pho nya bsreg byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9111: dmar smug lag na gri thog cing //
NK027(sha)001:9112: mtha' yas sems can sgrol la mkhas //
NK027(sha)001:9113: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi klong byed ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9114: gsung gi pho nya glog byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9115: dmar smug rdo rje be con gyi //
NK027(sha)001:9116: khams gsum rdul du brlag byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9117: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi tho ba ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9118: gsung gi pho nya tho ba ma //
NK027(sha)001:9119: dmar smug rdo rje tho ba phyar //
NK027(sha)001:9120: khams gsum bdud dang srin mo 'joms //
NK027(sha)001:9121: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi shiny+tsa gtun khung ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9122: gsung gi pho nya gtun khung ma //
NK027(sha)001:9123: dmar smug lag na gtun khung thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9124: che chung med par 'joms byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9125: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi zhags pa 'phen thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9126: gsung gi pho nya zhags pa 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:9127: dmar smug bdud kyi zhags pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:9128: gang la dmigs pa 'dzin byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9129: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi me khyer ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9130: gsung gi pho nya me khyer ma //
NK027(sha)001:9131: dmar smug dur khrod me chen gyi //
NK027(sha)001:9132: phyi nang med par bsreg byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9133: dbang 'di gardza a sdud byed ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9134: gsung gi pho nya sdud byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9135: dmar smug gser gyi phreng ba thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9136: dug gsum zhal du sdud byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9137: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi g.yang len ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9138: gsung gi pho nya g.yang len ma //
NK027(sha)001:9139: dmar skya rlung gi 'khor lo thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9140: ri rab gling bzhi g.yeng byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9141: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi bdud 'joms ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9142: gsung gi pho nya bdud 'joms ma //
NK027(sha)001:9143: dmar skya gtun dang tho ba thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9144: lnga phung rdul du brlag pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:9145: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi dpal mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9146: gsung gi pho nya dpal mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9147: dmar skya srid pa'i dpal 'phrog ma //
NK027(sha)001:9148: gser g.yu spel ma'i na bza' gsol //
NK027(sha)001:9149: dbang gardza a b+hi dbang phyug ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9150: gsung gi pho nya dbang phyug ma //
NK027(sha)001:9151: rdo rje rtse gsum thod khrag 'thung //
NK027(sha)001:9152: srid pa gsum na dbang chen khrag /
NK027(sha)001:9153: dbang gardza gardza a b+hi khrag pa mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9154: gsung gi pho nya grag pa mo //
NK027(sha)001:9155: dmar skya mi mgo dung du 'bud //
NK027(sha)001:9156: stong khams gdug pa rdul du barloga /
NK027(sha)001:9157: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi gtum pa can thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9158: gsung gi pho nya gtum bag can //
NK027(sha)001:9160: gang la bab kyang thog med pa //
NK027(sha)001:9161: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi k+ai la ya thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9162: ma lus 'joms pa'i mthu mo che //
NK027(sha)001:9163: dbang 'di gardza a b+hi sde tshogs mthogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9164: pad+ma'i pho nya'i sde tshogs ma //
NK027(sha)001:9166: ma mo 'bum sde bram du khol //
NK027(sha)001:9167: dbang 'di gardza a ha la'i gdong /
NK027(sha)001:9168: gsung gi pho nya rab brjid pa //
NK027(sha)001:9169: mi mgo rnam gsum phreng bar bsgrags //
NK027(sha)001:9170: glad la bskor bas dgra bo sgrol //
NK027(sha)001:9171: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi nub tshar /
NK027(sha)001:9172: byang gi pho nya drug cu las /
NK027(sha)001:9174: dgra dang gnod byin 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:9175: 'jigs byed pho nya skur sprul pa //
NK027(sha)001:9176: byang phyogs 'od zer ljang ku las //
NK027(sha)001:9177: g.yu yi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK027(sha)001:9178: phrin las pho nya rdo rje 'chang //
NK027(sha)001:9179: sngon po rdo rje rgya gram thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9180: phrin las rnam bzhi pho nya 'gyed //
NK027(sha)001:9181: dbang 'di gardza a b+hi 'joms chen ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9182: phrin las pho nya 'joms chen ma //
NK027(sha)001:9183: ljang sngon khyung gi khra thogs ma //
NK027(sha)001:9184: gti mug glu la dbang bsgyur ma //
NK027(sha)001:9185: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi 'dul mdzad ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9186: phrin las pho nya 'dul mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:9187: ljang sngon dred kyi g.yang gzhi 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:9189: dbang 'di gardza gardza a b+hi dbang phyug ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9190: phrin las pho nya dbang phyug ma //
NK027(sha)001:9191: ljang sngon thod rlon khrag gi bkang //
NK027(sha)001:9192: 'brug chen g.yar mo khal du zhon //
NK027(sha)001:9193: dbang 'di pa tsa pa tsa a b+hi grub byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9194: las kyi pho nya grub byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9195: ljang sngon mi mgo dung du 'bud //
NK027(sha)001:9196: khams gsum ma lus sgras phung ma //
NK027(sha)001:9197: dbang 'di pa tsa a b+hi bskul byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9198: phrin las pho nya bskul byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9199: ljang sngon snyan pa'i dbyug pa 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:9200: thugs dam gnyan po rgyud bskul bas //
NK027(sha)001:9201: dbang 'di pa tsa a b+hi grub pa mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9202: phrin las pho nya grub pa mo //
NK027(sha)001:9204: phrin las nan tan mthu mo che //
NK027(sha)001:9205: pho nya 'dis kyang dbang bskur cig /
NK027(sha)001:9206: pa tsa a b+hi mthar phyin ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9207: phrin las pho nya mthar phyin ma //
NK027(sha)001:9208: ljang smug g.yu yi thor gtsug can //
NK027(sha)001:9209: las su bcol na kun kyang grub //
NK027(sha)001:9210: dbang 'di pa tsa a b+hi mthar 'don ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9211: phrin las pho nya mthar 'don ma //
NK027(sha)001:9212: ljang smug rdo rje rgya gram thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9213: gang bcol las rnams mthar 'byin ma //
NK027(sha)001:9214: dbang 'di bu la bskur bar bya //
NK027(sha)001:9215: pa tsa pa tsa g+hen+d+he hoh a chud mi za thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9216: phrin las pho nya chud mi za //
NK027(sha)001:9217: ljang sngon dung gi mche ba can //
NK027(sha)001:9218: mgyogs pa'i las byed chud mi za //
NK027(sha)001:9219: dbang 'di pa tsa a dbang bskur ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9220: phrin las pho nya dbang bskur ma //
NK027(sha)001:9221: ljang dmar chu srin rgyal mtshan thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9223: dbang 'di pa tsa thogs med ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9224: phrin las pho nya thogs med ma //
NK027(sha)001:9225: 'dab chags bya yi rgyal po zhon //
NK027(sha)001:9226: 'jigs su rung ba'i mtshon cha phyar //
NK027(sha)001:9227: dbang 'di pa tsa a b+hi grub pa ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9228: phrin las pho nya grub pa ma //
NK027(sha)001:9229: dmar ljang shel gyi za ma tog /
NK027(sha)001:9230: dgra yi dbang dang dngos grub 'phrog /
NK027(sha)001:9231: dbang pa tsa a b+hi gsal byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9232: phrin las pho nya gsal byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9233: ljang dmar me yi zhags pa 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:9234: mun pa smag nas 'dren byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9235: dbang 'di pa tsa a b+hi dbang byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9236: phrin las pho nya dbang byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9237: dmar ljang rdo rje lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:9238: spra dang byi la sprul 'gyed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9239: dbang 'di pa tsa a dam tshig ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9240: phrin las pho nya dam tshig ma //
NK027(sha)001:9241: dmar ljang me zhags rtsub rtsi can //
NK027(sha)001:9242: dam nyams kun gyi rjes gcod ma //
NK027(sha)001:9243: dbang 'di pa tsa a bya ra ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9244: phrin las pho nya bya ra ma //
NK027(sha)001:9245: lcags kyi bya khra g.yu mig ma //
NK027(sha)001:9246: bltas pas mthong zhing mthong pa 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:9247: dbang 'di pa tsa a b+hi stang 'dzin ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9248: phrin las pho nya stang 'dzin ma //
NK027(sha)001:9249: dmar ljang rtsis kyi byang bu thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9250: legs nyes kun gyi stang 'dzin ma //
NK027(sha)001:9251: dbang 'di pa tsa a stang gcod ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9252: phrin las pho nya stang gcod ma //
NK027(sha)001:9253: dmar ljang rtsis kyi khram thog ma //
NK027(sha)001:9254: dge sdig gnyis kyi stang gcod ma //
NK027(sha)001:9255: dbang 'di pa tsa a b+hi gsal 'dzin ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9256: phrin las pho nya gsal 'dzin ma //
NK027(sha)001:9258: rgyal pham gnyis kyi gsal 'dzin ma //
NK027(sha)001:9259: dbang 'di pa tsa a b+hi bskul byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9260: phrin las pho nya bskul byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9261: ljang ser lcags kyi mda' 'phen ma //
NK027(sha)001:9262: rnam pa kun yang rung bar byed //
NK027(sha)001:9263: dbang pa tsa a b+hi dbang mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9264: phrin las pho nya dbang mo zhu //
NK027(sha)001:9265: ljang ser khrag gi phur pa thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9266: ma thog las la myur byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9267: dbang pa tsa phag mgo ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9268: phrin las pho nya phag mgo ma //
NK027(sha)001:9269: ljang ser phag mgo tho ba phyar //
NK027(sha)001:9270: che chung med par rdul du rlog /
NK027(sha)001:9271: dbang pa tsa a b+hi spyan brgya ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9272: phrin las pho nya spyan brgya ma //
NK027(sha)001:9273: mgo lus med pa mig gi gang //
NK027(sha)001:9274: khams gsum ma lus gsal zhing bkra /
NK027(sha)001:9275: dbang 'di pa tsa a b+hi mig stong ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9276: phrin las pho nya mig stong ma //
NK027(sha)001:9277: dbu stong phyag stong spyan yang stong //
