NK027(sha)001:9278: stong gsum stong la dbang chen grags //
NK027(sha)001:9279: dbang 'di pa tsa a b+hi 'od mgyogs ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9280: phrin las pho nya 'od mgyogs ma //
NK027(sha)001:9282: bltas pas mi mthong gang yang med //
NK027(sha)001:9283: dbang 'di bu pa tsa a b+hi rlung zhon ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9284: phrin las pho nya rlung zhon ma //
NK027(sha)001:9285: lag na lcags kyi dgra s+t+wa ljang //
NK027(sha)001:9286: rlung nag 'tshub ma chibs su bcib //
NK027(sha)001:9287: dbang 'di pa tsa rdzu 'phrul can thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9288: phrin las pho nya rdzu 'phrul can //
NK027(sha)001:9289: sbrul nag stong gi zhags pa 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:9290: ltas ngan rnga mong gwa pa zhon //
NK027(sha)001:9291: dbang 'di pa tsa rgyu ba ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9292: phrin las pho nya rgyu ba mo //
NK027(sha)001:9293: ci yang ma nges gzugs su ston //
NK027(sha)001:9294: chas g+hag chung sri sbrul gyi lus //
NK027(sha)001:9295: dbang pa tsa a dbang phyug rgyal thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9296: phrin las pho nya dbang phyug rgyal //
NK027(sha)001:9297: ljang ser mdung rtse gsum pa phyar //
NK027(sha)001:9298: dug gsum rtsad nas len byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9299: dbang pa tsa a khrag rgyal ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9300: phrin las pho nya khrag rgyal ma //
NK027(sha)001:9301: ljang nag stag zhon dred kyi mgo 'jig rten khams 'dir mthu cher grags //
NK027(sha)001:9302: dbang 'di pa tsa dpal sham ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9303: phrin las pho nya dpal sham ma //
NK027(sha)001:9304: dmar gyi gtor ma zhags par 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:9305: dbang pa tsa yak+sha ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9306: phrin las pho nya yak+sha mo //
NK027(sha)001:9307: ljang nag gnod byed mgo bo thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9308: gang la bya bar thod zor 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:9309: dbang pa tsa khro bag can ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9310: phrin las pho nya khro bag can //
NK027(sha)001:9311: bud med lus la skyes pa'i mgo //
NK027(sha)001:9313: dbang pa tsa a b+hi mche ba mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9314: phrin las pho nya mche ba mo //
NK027(sha)001:9315: lag gnyis rdo rje mche ba 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:9316: bzung pas mi zin gang yang med //
NK027(sha)001:9317: dbang 'di pa tsa dbang bskur ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9318: phrin las pho nya dbang bskur ma //
NK027(sha)001:9319: rdo rje go cha'i phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)001:9320: kun gyi mnga' bdag dbang mo che //
NK027(sha)001:9321: dbang 'di bu pa tsa dngos grub ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9322: phrin las pho nya dngos grub ma //
NK027(sha)001:9323: ljang nag 'dod yon lnga la rol //
NK027(sha)001:9324: dngos grub rnam gsum dus 'dir stsol //
NK027(sha)001:9325: dbang 'di pa tsa sgrol byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9326: phrin las pho nya sgrol byed che //
NK027(sha)001:9327: ljang nag thod pa'i phal tshab bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:9328: gang yang gsod par mi byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9329: dbang 'di pa tsa mnga' bdag mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9330: phrin las pho nya mnga' bdag mo //
NK027(sha)001:9331: srid gsum grags pa'i rnge'u chung brdungs //
NK027(sha)001:9332: ma lus gdug pa zil gyi gnon //
NK027(sha)001:9333: dbang 'di pa tsa a b+hi 'od 'phro ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9335: ljang nag cod pan shag ti thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9336: srid gsum gsal ba'i pho nya mo //
NK027(sha)001:9337: dbang pa tsa a grags pa mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9338: ljang nag gru gsum mthing nag thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9339: drag po las kyi pho nya mo //
NK027(sha)001:9340: dbang pa tsa a khro skyon ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9341: phrin las pho nya khro rkyen ma //
NK027(sha)001:9342: ljang smug ral pa sa la brdeb //
NK027(sha)001:9343: rang la rang gi tshig cing khro //
NK027(sha)001:9344: dbang 'di pa tsa myur grub ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9345: phrin las pho nya myur grub ma //
NK027(sha)001:9346: 'jam dpal rnon po lag na thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9347: ha ha ru lu'i sgra sgrog ma //
NK027(sha)001:9348: dbang a chud mi za thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9349: phrin las pho nya chud mi za //
NK027(sha)001:9350: ljang smug rin chen sgron ma thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9351: gdung bas brtse zhing phan 'dogs pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:9352: dbang 'di a b+hi gdul byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9353: phrin las pho nya gdul byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9354: ljang smug srin po'i thod pa thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9355: khyod kyi mi 'dul gang yang med //
NK027(sha)001:9356: dbang a rgya mtsho ma thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9357: phrin las pho nya rgya mtsho ma //
NK027(sha)001:9358: sna tshogs lus can rgya mtsho thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9359: 'dzam bu gling bzhi g.yo byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9360: dbang 'di pa a stang 'dzin ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9361: las kyi pho nya stang 'dzin ma //
NK027(sha)001:9362: sems can zhing bcu bsgral ba la //
NK027(sha)001:9363: dmyal bar ldang nges lcags kyus 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:9364: dbang 'di pa tsa sgrol byed ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9365: phrin las pho nya sgrol byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9367: rdul du brlag pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:9368: dbang pa tsa rang dbang mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9369: phrin las pho nya rang dbang mo //
NK027(sha)001:9370: ljang nag g.yu yi zhags pa 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:9371: 'jig rten las kyi gnyer gcig po //
NK027(sha)001:9372: dbang 'di pa tsa a b+hi 'dul can ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9373: phrin las pho nya 'dul can ma //
NK027(sha)001:9374: skyes bu na chung gzugs 'chang ma //
NK027(sha)001:9375: ci ltar dmigs pa bzhin du 'dul //
NK027(sha)001:9376: dbang pa tsa gom pa mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9377: phrin las pho nya gom pa mo //
NK027(sha)001:9378: ljang ku nyungs kar mda' 'phen ma //
NK027(sha)001:9379: dkar nag snying gi mtshams su bteg /
NK027(sha)001:9380: dbang pa tsa las mkhan ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9381: phrin las pho nya las mkhan ma //
NK027(sha)001:9382: ljang skya mtshe yi zor 'phen ma //
NK027(sha)001:9383: log pa'i phyogs rnams ldog byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9384: dbang pa tsa dbang bskur ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9385: phrin las pho nya dbang bskur ma //
NK027(sha)001:9386: nyi zla gza' skar klag par gnon //
NK027(sha)001:9387: 'dzam gling bzhi pa lag par thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9388: dbang 'di pa tsa a b+hi mchog sgrol ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9389: phrin las pho nya mchog sgrol ma //
NK027(sha)001:9391: skye shi gnyis kyi rtsad gcod ma //
NK027(sha)001:9392: dbang 'di pa tsa rgyug 'dzin ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9393: phrin las pho nya rgyug 'dzin ma //
NK027(sha)001:9394: thugs dam gnyen po rgyud bskul phyir //
NK027(sha)001:9395: shel dang lung tang phur bu bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:9396: dbang 'di pa tsa rngam pa mo thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9397: phrin las pho nya rngam pa mo //
NK027(sha)001:9398: ljang skya sha khrag rlon pa za //
NK027(sha)001:9399: gsod pa'i las la shin tu rngam //
NK027(sha)001:9400: dbang 'di pa tsa spro rkyen ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9401: phrin las pho nya spro rkyen ma //
NK027(sha)001:9402: ljang skya 'degs pa'i las la myur //
NK027(sha)001:9403: dza dza ho ho sgra 'debs pa //
NK027(sha)001:9404: dbang 'di pa tsa gtum chen ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9405: phrin las pho nya gtum chen ma //
NK027(sha)001:9407: gtum pa 'dod khams lha mi btsan //
NK027(sha)001:9408: dbang 'di pa tsa mig dmar ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9409: phrin las pho nya mig dmar ma //
NK027(sha)001:9410: khrag dang chang gi myos par byed //
NK027(sha)001:9411: mig rtsa dmar la ra gdang che //
NK027(sha)001:9412: dbang 'di pa tsa sen mo can thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9413: phrin las pho nya sen mo can //
NK027(sha)001:9414: dmar smug sems can lcags kyu bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:9415: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu 'dren byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9416: dbang 'di bu la bskur bar bya //
NK027(sha)001:9417: pa tsa pa tsa s+pho ta bam /
NK027(sha)001:9418: a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah khyam dgu pa'i 'og gi ma mo drug cu ni /
NK027(sha)001:9419: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK027(sha)001:9420: khams gsum srid gsum thams cad kyi //
NK027(sha)001:9421: dgra dang 'byung po bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:9422: sku yi 'od zer smug nag las //
NK027(sha)001:9423: las byed ma mo drug cur sprul //
NK027(sha)001:9424: ral pa gcig mthong 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK027(sha)001:9425: tri shul ral gri nad rkyal thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9426: ma mo 'di yi deng 'dir dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:9427: ma ma sha ri a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)001:9428: sbas pa'i ma mo thal mdog thod khrag 'thung //
NK027(sha)001:9429: g.yang gzhi dur khrod rgyan gyi mdzes par lhub //
NK027(sha)001:9430: ma mo 'di yi deng 'dir dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:9431: ma ma dur khrod tshogs kyi ma mo ral pa can //
NK027(sha)001:9432: mi thod phreng bas sku rgyan rab tu brjid //
NK027(sha)001:9433: khams gsum 'di na mthu chen 'gran zla med //
NK027(sha)001:9434: ma mo 'di'i ma ma srin po sgrol byed ma mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9435: smug nag phyag na b+han+d+ha thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9436: 'og gi phyogs nas las byed mthu mo che //
NK027(sha)001:9437: ma mo 'di yi ma ma za byed rngams pa'i ma mo chen mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9438: mthing skya khrag gi ral pa sa gsum gnon //
NK027(sha)001:9439: phyag gi skye 'gro yongs kyi tsit+ta bzung //
NK027(sha)001:9440: ma mo ma ma khams gsum sdud pa'i ma mo chen mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9441: dmar po thod khrag skam du 'thung byed pa //
NK027(sha)001:9442: nga rgyal dreg pa'i 'khor yang 'joms byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9443: ma mo 'di yi ma ma rgyu drug sgrol ba'i ma mo chen mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9444: smug nag me 'bar g.yang gzhi gos su gyon //
NK027(sha)001:9445: mi snying rus pa'i phreng ba glad la bskor //
NK027(sha)001:9446: ma mo ma ma srid gsum yongs la dbang bsgyur ma //
NK027(sha)001:9447: ser nag nyi zla thod du bcing //
NK027(sha)001:9448: gnam sa gnyis la dbang byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9449: ma mo ma ma mthu rtsal snyoms pa'i ma mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9450: ljang nag zhing gi go zu gon //
NK027(sha)001:9451: lag pa g.yas pa nag mkhar ldeg /
NK027(sha)001:9452: ma mo ma ma khros ma khrag 'thung gsur la dga' //
NK027(sha)001:9453: mi sha rta sha zas su za //
NK027(sha)001:9454: mi khrag rta khrag skam du 'thung //
NK027(sha)001:9455: ma mo ma ma sgrol byed ma mo chen mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9456: mthing nag nang rol glo snying 'dren //
NK027(sha)001:9457: phrin las dam nyams sgrol la brtson //
NK027(sha)001:9458: ma mo 'di ma mo za byed ma mo chen mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9459: sngo nag g.yu yi za ma tog /
NK027(sha)001:9460: nyams la len cing bsgrub la brtson //
NK027(sha)001:9461: ma mo ma ma a b+hi rngams byed nag mo tsit+ta bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:9462: nam mkha'i 'brug sngon chibs su bcib //
NK027(sha)001:9463: dgra dang nyams pa'i snying 'byin ma //
NK027(sha)001:9464: ma mo ma ma 'dzin byed ma mo chen mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9465: ser nag thod khrag lcags kyu thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9466: ma lus sgrol ba'i ging chen mo //
NK027(sha)001:9467: ma mo 'di yi ma ma bgegs chen 'joms pa'i ma mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9468: sngo nag spu gri tho ba thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9469: bgegs kyi rgyal po'i snying la 'debs //
NK027(sha)001:9470: ma mo 'di yi deng ma mo zhing bcu sgrol ba'i ma mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9471: ljang nag b+han+d+ha gri thogs ma //
NK027(sha)001:9472: 'jigs rten khams kyi dbang mo che //
NK027(sha)001:9473: ma mo ma ma chad pa gcod pa'i ma mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9474: sngo nag zhing gi g.yang gzhi rdeb /
NK027(sha)001:9475: dam tshig nyams pa'i snying 'byin ma //
NK027(sha)001:9476: ma mo 'di yi ma ma 'byung po sgrol byed ma mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9478: shar gyi phyogs kyi las byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9479: ma mo ma ma gshin rje sgrol byed ma mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9480: b+han+d+ha gri thogs gshin rje sgrol //
NK027(sha)001:9481: lho yi phyogs nas las byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9482: ma mo 'di ma ma nub phyogs klu sgrol chen mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9483: b+han+d+ha gri thog klu chen sgrol //
NK027(sha)001:9484: nub kyi phyogs na las byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9485: ma mo 'di yi ma ma a b+hi gnod sbyin sgrol byed chen mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9486: ljang nag b+han+d+ha gri thogs cing //
NK027(sha)001:9487: byang gi phyogs nas las byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9488: ma mo 'di yi ma ma a b+hi srin po sgrol byed ma mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9489: sngo nag b+han+d+ha gri thogs shing //
NK027(sha)001:9490: steng gi phyogs nas las byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9491: ma mo ma ma sha ri srin po sgrol byed ma mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9492: smug nag b+han+d+ha gri 'og gi phyogs nas las byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9493: ma mo 'di yi dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:9494: ma ma gzugs la mnga' mdzad dbang mo che //
NK027(sha)001:9495: dkar mo zhing gi dbyug pa bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:9496: dgra bo'i gzugs rnams 'phrog byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9497: ma mo ma ma sha ri khrag la dbang ba'i ma mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9498: sngon po thod khrag dkrug cing gsol //
NK027(sha)001:9499: dgra bo'i khrag rnams 'phrog byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9500: ma mo 'di yi ma ma drod la dbang ba'i ma mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9501: dmar mo lag na tsit+ta thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9502: sdang ba'i dgra bo'i drod 'phrog ma //
NK027(sha)001:9503: ma mo ma ma dbug la dbang ba'i ma mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9504: ljang nag thod khrag zhags pa thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9505: dgra yi dbug rnams 'phrog byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9506: ma mo ma ma sha ri srog la dbang ba'i ma mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9507: smug nag gri dang thod khrag 'thung //
NK027(sha)001:9508: dgra yi srog rnams myur du 'phrog /
NK027(sha)001:9509: ma mo 'di ma ma bkrag la dbang byed ma mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9510: ser nag ral gri thod khrag 'thung //
NK027(sha)001:9511: dgra yi gdong rnams 'jib byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9512: ma mo ma ma ma mo khrag 'thung bya rgod mgo //
NK027(sha)001:9513: ser nag ral gri thod khrag 'thung //
NK027(sha)001:9514: 'jig rten khyab pa 'i mthu bo che //
NK027(sha)001:9515: ma mo 'di yi ma ma ma mo za byed stag gi mgo //
NK027(sha)001:9516: dmar ser thod khrag zhal du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:9518: ma mo ma ma sha ri ma mo 'jig rten chu srin gdong //
NK027(sha)001:9519: sha khrag gsur la dga' byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9521: ma mo ma ma a b+hi ma mo chen mo dur khrod brgyan //
NK027(sha)001:9522: mi lpags rlon pa na bza' gsol //
NK027(sha)001:9523: dur khrod bgegs chen 'dul mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:9524: ma mo ma ma rdo rje gar gyi dbang mo che //
NK027(sha)001:9525: dbu brgya spyan stong kun la khyab //
NK027(sha)001:9526: ma lus sgrol ba'i ging chen ma //
NK027(sha)001:9527: ma mo ma ma pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug ma //
NK027(sha)001:9528: lag na mi mgo'i phor pa ru //
NK027(sha)001:9529: mi snying tshil bus bkang zhing gsol //
NK027(sha)001:9530: ma mo ma ma sa bdag chen mo pad+ma phreng //
NK027(sha)001:9531: dmar nag b+han+d+ha khrag gi bkang //
NK027(sha)001:9532: mig rtsa dmar zhing rngam pa mo //
NK027(sha)001:9533: ma mo ma ma srid pa gsum gyis mnga' bdag mo //
NK027(sha)001:9534: ri rab rtse nas bsnyil byed cing //
NK027(sha)001:9535: rgya mtsho gting nas snyog byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9536: ma mo ma ma a b+hi rgya mtsho gting gi dbang mo che //
NK027(sha)001:9537: na bza' chu srin lpags pa gsol //
NK027(sha)001:9538: sprul nag stong gi gdeng ka can //
NK027(sha)001:9539: ma mo ma ma ma mo rdo rje tho ba ma //
NK027(sha)001:9540: sngo nag mi srun tho ba thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9541: srin mo'i tshogs kyang 'dar zhing g.yo //
NK027(sha)001:9542: ma mo ma ma ma mo rdo rje gtun khung ma //
NK027(sha)001:9543: mthing nag dgra bo gtun du brdungs //
NK027(sha)001:9544: gang la bya ba rdul du rlog /
NK027(sha)001:9545: ma mo ma ma ma mo rdo rje dur khrod bdag /
NK027(sha)001:9546: sngo nag mi mgo rdo rje dbyug /
NK027(sha)001:9547: gdug pa'i tshogs kyis 'joms par byed //
NK027(sha)001:9548: ma mo 'di ma ma sha ri ma mo rdo rje gdeng pa mo //
NK027(sha)001:9549: sngo nag rdo rje rtse gsum bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:9550: gdul cing gtum pa'i drag shul che //
NK027(sha)001:9551: ma mo ma ma ma mo rdo rje gsal bkra ma //
NK027(sha)001:9552: dmar nag mi yi rgyu zhags 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:9554: ma mo ma ma ma mo rdo rje khrag 'thung ma //
NK027(sha)001:9557: ma mo ma ma ma mo nag mo dred zhon ma //
NK027(sha)001:9558: nad kyi rkyal ba gong du btab //
NK027(sha)001:9559: mtshon gyi gru gu klad la bskor //
NK027(sha)001:9560: ma mo ma ma dus bzhi'i rgyal mo mthu mo che //
NK027(sha)001:9561: srid pa gsum la dbang byed cing //
NK027(sha)001:9562: cir yang 'gyur ba'i sku mnga' ba //
NK027(sha)001:9563: ma mo ma ma ma mo gnas yul spyang gi'i mgo //
NK027(sha)001:9564: mi sha za zhing bdud khyim 'joms //
NK027(sha)001:9565: ltas pas bdud rnams brlag byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9566: ma mo ma ma ma mo bardzu byed stag dang dom //
NK027(sha)001:9567: gcan zan gdug pa'i tshogs su sprul //
NK027(sha)001:9568: ma lus 'joms pa'i mthu mo che //
NK027(sha)001:9569: ma mo ma ma ma mo 'dzum byed pho nya mo //
NK027(sha)001:9570: khra star 'dzum zhing khyi ltar zug /
NK027(sha)001:9571: gang la dmigs pa yud kyi len //
NK027(sha)001:9572: ma mo ma ma ma mo gnam sa phyed kyi bdag /
NK027(sha)001:9573: ri klung med par gzugs kyis kheb //
NK027(sha)001:9574: che chung med par 'joms par byed //
NK027(sha)001:9575: ma mo ma ma ma mo pho nya rgyug byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9576: bud med lus la 'ja' tshon gos //
NK027(sha)001:9577: bang ni ri lung med par rgyug /
NK027(sha)001:9578: ma mo ma ma sha ri a ma mo pho nya za byed ma //
NK027(sha)001:9579: bud med lus la stag gi mgo //
NK027(sha)001:9580: zas su gtsang sme med par bya //
NK027(sha)001:9581: ma ma ma rdo rje yang phyin pho nya mo //
NK027(sha)001:9582: dkar khra lcags kyu phur bu 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:9583: gang la bya ba grub par byed //
NK027(sha)001:9584: ma mo ma ma rdo rje bes phyin rtsal mo che //
NK027(sha)001:9585: sngo nag zhags pa phur bu thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9586: gang la bya ba grub par byed //
NK027(sha)001:9587: ma ma 'di yi ma ma rdo rje phag phyin thog pa med //
NK027(sha)001:9588: dmar nag thod khrag phur bu thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9589: gang la bya ba grub par byed //
NK027(sha)001:9590: ma mo ma ma rdo rje deng phyin dbang grub ma //
NK027(sha)001:9591: ljang nag dril bu phur bu 'phen //
NK027(sha)001:9592: gang la bya ba grub par byed //
NK027(sha)001:9593: ma mo ma ma sa bdag rgyal mo chen mo ni //
NK027(sha)001:9594: sa nag gser gyi ga bur bsnams //
NK027(sha)001:9595: tshe srog kun la dbang bsgyur ma //
NK027(sha)001:9596: ma mo 'di yi ma ma phyi 'khor skyong ba'i mnga' bdag mo //
NK027(sha)001:9597: rgyan dang cha lugs mdzes pa'i tshul //
NK027(sha)001:9598: gnas ni g.ya' ri gangs la gnas //
NK027(sha)001:9599: ma mo ma ma 'brog srin rnams kyi rje mo che //
NK027(sha)001:9600: bud med bzang bsdug 'od chags ma //
NK027(sha)001:9601: skra bshig ral pa gyen du bardzisa //
NK027(sha)001:9602: ma mo ma ma sha ri bud med khrag gi ral pa can //
NK027(sha)001:9603: ma mo 'di yi dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:9604: ma ma sha ri h'u dzaha b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)001:9606: h'u chen mthing skya rdo rje thod dbyug thogs //
NK027(sha)001:9607: sgra 'byin gtso 'khyud dung khrag yab la stobs //
NK027(sha)001:9608: phrin las nyi zla'i gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9609: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la bskur bar bya //
NK027(sha)001:9610: badz+ra kro ta h'u ka ra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:9612: kro ti sha li sha ya bya h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:9614: rnam rgyal dkar po rdo rje rtse lnga zhing dbyug phyar //
NK027(sha)001:9615: mda' snyems gtso 'khyud dung dmar yab la stobs //
NK027(sha)001:9616: phrin las dri za'i gdon rnams 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9617: skal ldan rigs kyi badz+ra kro ta b+hi dza h'u /
NK027(sha)001:9619: badz+ra la s+ye ke tu phata a b+hi dbyug pa sngo skya med dbal drang srong 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:9620: sder mo gtso 'khyud dung khrag yab la stobs //
NK027(sha)001:9621: phrin las drang srong gdon rnams 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:9622: skal ldan badz+ra kro ta ni tan tra h'u /
NK027(sha)001:9623: da ha da ha h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:9624: badz+ra kro ti sha ri pra ti dza h'u /
NK027(sha)001:9625: a b+hi gshed po ser nag be con gshin rje 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:9626: dur khrod gtso 'khyud thod khrag phrin las gshin rje gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9627: skal ldan badz+ra kro ta ya man ta ka h'u /
NK027(sha)001:9629: kro ti shwa ri ha na pa ti h'u /
NK027(sha)001:9630: a b+hi mi g.yo ljang sngon ral gri srin po 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:9631: gtun khung gtso 'khyud dung khrag yab la stobs //
NK027(sha)001:9632: phrin las srin po'i gdon rnams 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9633: skal ldan badz+ra kro ta ar+ya a tsa la h'u /
NK027(sha)001:9636: a b+hi rta mgrin dmar nag zhing dbyug khyung gshog 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:9637: gtum mo gtso 'khyud dung khrag yab la stobs //
NK027(sha)001:9638: phrin las klu yi gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9639: skal ldan badz+ra kro ta h+ya g+hi wa h'u /
NK027(sha)001:9641: tsan d+ha d+ha ri s+pha ti h'u /
NK027(sha)001:9642: a b+hi gzhan gyis mi thub dmar ljang ba dan rlung lha 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:9643: mda' snyems gtso 'khyud dung khrag yab la stobs //
NK027(sha)001:9644: phrin las rlung lha'i gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9645: skal ldan badz+ra kro ta a pa ra tsit+ta h'u /
NK027(sha)001:9648: a b+hi bdud rtsi ljang nag gnar mgo dbyug to phyar //
NK027(sha)001:9649: rlung 'byin gtso 'khyung dung khrag yab la stobs //
NK027(sha)001:9650: phrin las gnod sbyin gdon tshogs 'dul mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:9651: skal ldan rigs kyi badz+ra kro ta a mri ta kun d+ha li h'u /
NK027(sha)001:9654: a b+hi stobs chen dung ka thong gshol tir dbyug
NK027(sha)001:9655: thogs bskyed ma gtso 'khyud dung khrag yab phrin las
NK027(sha)001:9656: sa bdag gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9657: skal ldan badz+ra kro ta nas ha ha rnam rgyal dkar po rdo rje 'byung po 'dzin //
NK027(sha)001:9658: gsod ma gtso 'khyud dung phrin las 'byung po'i gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9659: skal ldan badz+ra kro ta tre lo kya bi dza ya h'u /
NK027(sha)001:9660: kro ta ma h+aa pa la h'u /
NK027(sha)001:9662: kro ti sha ri k+sho b+hi na h'u /
NK027(sha)001:9663: a b+hi na mo dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi byin rlabs kyi /
NK027(sha)001:9664: rigs kyi bu la phyag rgya chen po'i dbang mchog 'di bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:9665: rgyud ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK027(sha)001:9666: lung a nu yo ga dang /
NK027(sha)001:9667: man ngag a ti yo ga'i zhi khro rab 'byams
NK027(sha)001:9668: kyi sku lnga yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang dam pa
NK027(sha)001:9671: dbu rgyan mgo'i gnas la gtug /
NK027(sha)001:9672: bum chu dang shu nyee ta brjod cing /
NK027(sha)001:9673: ye shes lnga yi rta mchog phyag rgya yi //
NK027(sha)001:9674: gnas lngar gtug ste dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:9675: thugs kyi dbang mchog chen po ni //
NK027(sha)001:9676: rdo rje spyan la sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:9679: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)001:9680: rigs kyi bu la dbu rgyan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:9681: rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad gnas su dag nas /
NK027(sha)001:9682: ye shes lnga'i don rtogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:9683: dgu pa sku gsung thugs kyi dbang la /
NK027(sha)001:9686: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje yi //
NK027(sha)001:9687: rnal 'byor bde mchog de yin pas //
NK027(sha)001:9688: sku gsung thugs yon phrin las dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9689: rdo rje can la sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:9690: ka ya wa ka tsit+ta gu na /
NK027(sha)001:9692: a b+hi sku rdo rje thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9694: sku gsung thugs kyis rdo rje yi //
NK027(sha)001:9695: rnal 'byor bde mchog de yin pas //
NK027(sha)001:9696: bde gshegs rnams kyi sku yi dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9697: rdo rje can la sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:9698: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ka ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa ad+ma ko&a ha /
NK027(sha)001:9700: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa'i sku'i byin gyis brlab pa'i /
NK027(sha)001:9701: sku rdorje'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:9703: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje yi //
NK027(sha)001:9704: rnal 'byor bde mchog de yin pas //
NK027(sha)001:9705: bde gshegs rnams kyi gsung gi dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9706: rdo rje can la sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:9707: sarba ta th+aa ga ta wak+ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa ad+ma ko&a ha /
NK027(sha)001:9709: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa'i gsung gi byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)001:9710: gsung rdo rje'i dbang dam pa thob par +aahmh'u /
NK027(sha)001:9711: sku gsung thugs rnal 'byor bde mchog de yin pas //
NK027(sha)001:9712: bde gshegs rnams kyi thugs kyi dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9713: rdo rje can la sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:9714: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa ad+ma ko&a ha /
NK027(sha)001:9715: a b+hi na mo phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi bde
NK027(sha)001:9716: bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin gyi brlab kyis
NK027(sha)001:9717: // thugs rdo rje'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:9718: bcu pa bkra shis rtag brgyad kyi dbang ni /
NK027(sha)001:9719: dbang mchog thob pa'i bu de yi //
NK027(sha)001:9720: don rnams grub pa'i bkra shis phyir //
NK027(sha)001:9721: bdud 'dul bkra shis rdzas mchog rnams //
NK027(sha)001:9722: rtags kyi brgyan te sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:9723: dpal chen thugs kyis sa bon ni //
NK027(sha)001:9724: 'dren pa rnams kyi thugs lags pas //
NK027(sha)001:9725: bla med thar lam drang ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:9726: thugs de lta bur bkra shis shog /
NK027(sha)001:9727: ston pa bdud kyi bsdos pa'i tshe //
NK027(sha)001:9728: thugs kar dpal bar bkra shis gyur pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:9729: de ring khyod la byin pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:9730: thams cad mkhyen pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:9731: dpal gyi be'u thams cad mkhyen pa'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9732: gzhan gyi mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK027(sha)001:9733: bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK027(sha)001:9734: thugs nyid la yang mngon sum gsal bar ston //
NK027(sha)001:9735: 'khor lo bkra shis phyag zhabs mthil //
NK027(sha)001:9736: skyobs pa'i sangs rgyas 'dren pa'i lha //
NK027(sha)001:9737: nyon mongs sems can dman pa'i gsos //
NK027(sha)001:9738: phyag zhabs 'khor lo'i bkra shis shog /
NK027(sha)001:9739: ston la bdud dmag 'dren pa'i tshe //
NK027(sha)001:9740: phyag zhabs 'khor lo'i bkra shis gyur //
NK027(sha)001:9741: de ring khyod la sbyin pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:9742: chos 'khor bskor ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:9743: gzhan gyi mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK027(sha)001:9744: bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams phyag zhabs mthil la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK027(sha)001:9745: gsung mchog pad+ma chos kyi rgyal //
NK027(sha)001:9746: nyon mongs ma gos pad+ma'i sku //
NK027(sha)001:9747: thams cad sgrol ba'i gsal lag ste //
NK027(sha)001:9748: ljags mchog pad+ma'i bkra shis shog /
NK027(sha)001:9749: ston la bdud dmag ljags nyid pad+ma'i bkra shis gyur //
NK027(sha)001:9750: de ring khyod la sbyin pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:9751: cis kyang gos pa med pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:9752: ljags nyid pad+ma gos pa med pa'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9753: gzhan gyi mi thub che ba'i bsdo ba'i ljags kyi mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK027(sha)001:9755: mi nub rgyal mtshan 'dren pa'i sku //
NK027(sha)001:9756: thams cad bdud kyi sde brtul nas //
NK027(sha)001:9757: dpung bcom sangs rgyas sku ston te //
NK027(sha)001:9758: sku mchog rgya mtsho bkra shis shog /
NK027(sha)001:9759: ston la bdud kyi dmag drangs tshe //
NK027(sha)001:9760: sku ni rgyal mtshan bkra shis gyur //
NK027(sha)001:9761: de ring bdud las rgyal ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:9762: dbang mchog dam pa thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:9763: gzhan gyi mi thub che ba'i rtag dang ldan //
NK027(sha)001:9764: bsdo ba'i sku yi mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK027(sha)001:9766: bkra shis bum pa sems dpa'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9767: bcom ldan 'das kyi mgur lag ste //
NK027(sha)001:9768: mgur mchog bkra shis nyid byin pas //
NK027(sha)001:9769: bum pa'i bkra shis thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:9770: ston la bdud kyi dmag drangs tshe //
NK027(sha)001:9771: mgur nyid bum par bkra shis gyur //
NK027(sha)001:9772: de ring khyod la sbyin pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:9773: snying rjes 'dzin pa'i dbang mgur chu thugs rjes kun tu 'dzin pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:9774: gzhan gyi mi thub bsdo ba'i mgul gyi mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK027(sha)001:9775: gdug kyi tsha ba'i gdung ba kun bsal te //
NK027(sha)001:9776: nyon mongs ma lus kun las rgyal ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:9777: che ba'i yon tan ma lus rgyas pa ste //
NK027(sha)001:9778: logs pa'i phyogs rnams zil gnon bkra shis shog /
NK027(sha)001:9779: ston la bdud kyi dmag drangs tshe //
NK027(sha)001:9780: dbu skra gdugs su bkra shis gyur //
NK027(sha)001:9781: de ring khyod gdung ba sel ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:9782: dbu skra gdung sel bdugs kyi dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9783: gzhan gyi bsdo ba'i dbu skra'i mchog la snyan pa'i sgra rnams phyogs bcur sgrogs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:9784: mu stegs log pa'i phyogs rnams skrag pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:9785: sems can kun gyi shes pa'i rgyud gsal phyir //
NK027(sha)001:9786: gsung mchog dung gi rgyal po'i bkra shis shog /
NK027(sha)001:9787: ston la bdud kyi gsung gi dung du bkra shis gyur //
NK027(sha)001:9788: de ring khyod la sbyin pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:9789: rgol ba'i dpa' bskums dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:9790: dung gi rgol ba'i dpa' bskum skrog /
NK027(sha)001:9791: gzhan gyi mi thub bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams gsung gi mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK027(sha)001:9792: phyag zhabs nywa bzhi'i bkra shis te //
NK027(sha)001:9793: mdzes snyems yid 'ong kun gyi dpal //
NK027(sha)001:9794: nywa sha bkra shis gser nyar shog /
NK027(sha)001:9795: ston la bdud kyi dmag drangs tshe //
NK027(sha)001:9796: phyag zhabs nywa bzhi gser nyar gyur //
NK027(sha)001:9797: de ring khyod la 'khor ba'i nyams nga med par shog /
NK027(sha)001:9798: phyag zhabs nywa bzhi don mdzad dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9799: gzhan gyi mi thub bsdo ba'i nywa sha bzhi la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK027(sha)001:9800: 'di ni gser nywa dbang gi bkra shis shog /
NK027(sha)001:9801: bcu gcig pa ming gi dbang ni /
NK027(sha)001:9802: rnam snang gi sku thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9803: don rnams 'grub pa'i bu mchog ste /
NK027(sha)001:9804: rdo rje'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:9805: zhing khams kun du bsgrag pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:9806: rtsal gyi thig le'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:9807: thig le rtsal chen ming gdag go //
NK027(sha)001:9809: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin gyis brlab kyi /
NK027(sha)001:9810: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la /
NK027(sha)001:9813: thams cad 'dus pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:9815: des nang dbang bcu gcig rdzogs so //
NK027(sha)001:9816: de nas bsgrub dbang bcu gsum las /
NK027(sha)001:9817: dang po shes rab rig pa'i dbang /
NK027(sha)001:9818: gnyis pa khams gsum byang chub sems kyi dbang /
NK027(sha)001:9819: gsum pa yi ge 'khor lo'i dbang /
NK027(sha)001:9820: bzhi pa 'gro don rdzogs byed thong gshol gyi dbang /
NK027(sha)001:9821: lnga pa dug gsum steng gcod thod pa tshar gsum gyis dbang /
NK027(sha)001:9822: drug pa nyon mongs gcod pa mtshon cha'i dbang /
NK027(sha)001:9823: bdun pa spyod bzhi ma chags pad+ma'i dbang /
NK027(sha)001:9824: brgyad pa rnam pa bzhi la rdzogs pa'i ti ra'i dbyug pa'i dbang /
NK027(sha)001:9825: dgu pa don dam dbyer med sprul nag chun po'i dbang /
NK027(sha)001:9826: bcu pa gnyis med sbyor rtags lha mo yum gyi dbang /
NK027(sha)001:9827: bcu gcig pa bdag nyid chen mo longs spyod sna tshogs kyi dbang /
NK027(sha)001:9828: bcu gnyis pa mnga' bdag chen po bsgrub rdzas kyi dbang /
NK027(sha)001:9829: bcu gsum pa grags pa rdo rje ming gi dbang ngo //
NK027(sha)001:9830: de la dang po shes rab rig pa'i dbang ni /
NK027(sha)001:9832: skye med chos kyi dbyings nyid las //
NK027(sha)001:9833: blo yi dbang bskur thob pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:9834: shes rab chen po'i rig pa'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9835: sems lon don gyi ting 'dzin ni //
NK027(sha)001:9836: de ring khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:9837: prardza b+hir+ya a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)001:9839: bya ba'i bsam pa kun bral zhing //
NK027(sha)001:9840: brtsal ba med kyi byang chub sems //
NK027(sha)001:9841: snying rje chen po bde mchog gi //
NK027(sha)001:9842: khams gsum kun la dbang bskur ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:9843: dbang mchog khyed la sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:9844: ma na si tsa kra a b+hi gsum pa yig 'bru lnga thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9845: nyon mongs lnga po gnas gyur pa //
NK027(sha)001:9846: ye shes lnga yi dbang thob phyir //
NK027(sha)001:9847: yi ge 'khor lo'i dbang mchog ni //
NK027(sha)001:9848: dbang de bu yi lag tu sbyin /
NK027(sha)001:9849: purna tsakra +aah a b+hi bzhi pa thong gshol thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9850: srid gsum 'gro ba'i don rnams kun //
NK027(sha)001:9851: thams cad rdzogs par nus pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:9852: rtags kyi dbang mchog dam pa 'di //
NK027(sha)001:9853: thong gshol 'bar ba'i sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:9854: a mo g+ha sid+d+hi a b+hi lnga pa thod pa tshar gsum thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9855: dug gsum gting nas sprugs pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:9856: rtags chen ga'u rnam pa gsum //
NK027(sha)001:9857: dmar chen khrag gi bkang nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:9858: dbang thob de yi lag tu sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:9859: dug gsum gting bskrug thod pa'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9860: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:9861: dug gsum gtan nas zad byed pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:9862: ga'u gsum gyis dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:9863: sangs rgyas sku gsum thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:9865: a b+hi drug pa mtshon cha thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9866: thogs pa med pa'i shes rab kyi //
NK027(sha)001:9867: dug gsum rtsad nas bcad pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:9868: ral gri la sogs mtshon cha yi //
NK027(sha)001:9869: dbang mo dam pa khyod la sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:9870: khad rga a b+hi bdun pa pad ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9871: nyon mongs 'khor ba'i chos rnams la //
NK027(sha)001:9872: spyad kyang gos par mi 'gyur ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:9873: rtags kyi phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK027(sha)001:9874: pad+ma'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:9875: pad+ma a b+hi brgyad pa'i bam dbyug thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9876: las rnams rdzogs par byed pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:9877: dbang mchog dam pa'i rtags chen 'di //
NK027(sha)001:9878: sti ra'i dbyug to chen po dag /
NK027(sha)001:9879: dbang thob de yi lag tu sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:9880: zhing dbyug dgra s+t+wa tri shul la //
NK027(sha)001:9881: rnam bzhi las kyi 'dul ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:9882: phyag rgya chen por bstan pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:9883: sti ra chen po dbyug pa'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9884: skal ldan rnal 'byor khyod la sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:9886: a b+hi dgu pa sprul nag chun po thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9887: yum dang gnyis med 'khril ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:9888: chos nyid don dang gnyis med rtags //
NK027(sha)001:9890: skal ldan rnal 'byor khyod la sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:9891: dpal chen he ru ka la ni //
NK027(sha)001:9892: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK027(sha)001:9893: sbrul gyi chun po'i dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:9894: bdud dang srin po kun bcom nas //
NK027(sha)001:9895: 'jigs byed chen po mthu ldan shog /
NK027(sha)001:9896: tsakra a b+hi bcu pa gsang ba'i rig ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9897: gsang ba'i sbyor ba shes rab ma //
NK027(sha)001:9898: dri med rnam dag lha mo zhig /
NK027(sha)001:9899: mtshan ldan shin tu rgyas byas ma //
NK027(sha)001:9900: dbang thob de la sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:9901: don dam rang bzhin spros bral ba //
NK027(sha)001:9902: dri med rnam dag byang chub sems //
NK027(sha)001:9903: zhi byed gzungs ma gsal mo'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9904: skal ldan rnal 'byor khyod la sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:9905: d+ha ri a b+hi bcu gcig pa longs spyod sna tshogs pa thogs la /
NK027(sha)001:9906: bza' dang bca' dang btung dang sgo //
NK027(sha)001:9907: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad kun //
NK027(sha)001:9908: spyod bzhin ma chags rol pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:9909: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:9910: dza gad la sogs bdud rtsi yi //
NK027(sha)001:9911: 'khor ba'i rnam rtog gzhom pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:9912: dad ldan skyes bu tshim par gyis //
NK027(sha)001:9913: bdud rtsi rnam lnga'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:9914: bcu gnyis pa 'dod yon lnga thogs te /
NK027(sha)001:9915: dbang thog rgyal po chen po dang //
NK027(sha)001:9916: kun gyi bdag po yin pas na //
NK027(sha)001:9917: rol mo dri dang zhal zas dang //
NK027(sha)001:9918: 'dod yon lnga la sogs pa kun //
NK027(sha)001:9919: nye ba'i longs spyod rgyan rnams kun //
NK027(sha)001:9920: thams cad kun nas sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:9922: / bza' dang bca' dang gtung la sogs //
NK027(sha)001:9923: rang sems rnam dag rgyan gyi phyir //
NK027(sha)001:9924: gnyis med rol pa'i dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:9925: bdud rtsi yid bzhin sku 'grub shog /
NK027(sha)001:9926: tsa ru a b+hi na mo /
NK027(sha)001:9927: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)001:9928: zhal zas bza' btung gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:9929: 'dod yon lnga la longs spyod pa'i dbang dam pa
NK027(sha)001:9930: bcu gsum pa mnga' bdag chen po'i bsgrub rdzas thogs
NK027(sha)001:9931: la / sngon tshe dpal chen he ru kar //
NK027(sha)001:9932: phyogs bcur sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK027(sha)001:9933: stag gi sham thabs dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:9934: bdud dang srin po kun bsgral nas //
NK027(sha)001:9935: ma tshogs mkha' 'gro dbang du bsdus //
NK027(sha)001:9936: de bzhin skal ldan bu khyod la //
NK027(sha)001:9937: stag gi sham thabs gsol ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:9938: dpa' bo bdud las rgyal ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:9939: rnam dag 'joms pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:9940: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:9941: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK027(sha)001:9942: glang chen ko rlon dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:9943: gti mug gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:9944: khams gsum bdag por gyur pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:9945: de bzhin skal ldan bu khyod la //
NK027(sha)001:9946: glang chen ko rlon gsal ba ni //
NK027(sha)001:9947: gti mug gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:9948: bdud dpung chen po 'joms par shog /
NK027(sha)001:9949: sngon tshe dpal chen bdud dang srin po la sogs pa //
NK027(sha)001:9950: bcom ldan sku la bsdos pa'i tshe //
NK027(sha)001:9951: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK027(sha)001:9952: zhing gi g.yang gzhis dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:9953: bdud dang srin po brtul ba ltar //
NK027(sha)001:9954: 'khor ba rdul du brlag pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:9955: de bzhin skal ldan bu khyod la //
NK027(sha)001:9956: zhing gi g.yang gzhis dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:9957: thams cad 'joms pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:9958: sngon tshe dpal chen phyogs bcu thod phreng tshar gsum mnga' gsol bas //
NK027(sha)001:9959: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:9960: dug gsum gnas su dag nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:9961: thams cad 'dul ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:9962: sngon tshe phyogs bcu'i sbrul gyi chun po'i dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:9963: bdud dang srin po kun bcom nas //
NK027(sha)001:9964: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:9965: sngon tshe phyogs bcu'i khyung gi gshog pas dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:9966: bdud dang srin po zil gyi gnon //
NK027(sha)001:9967: de bzhin skal ldan bu khyod la //
NK027(sha)001:9968: khyung gi gshog pas rdo rje khyung ltar thog pa med pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:9969: mkha' ltar yongs la khyad par shog /
NK027(sha)001:9971: 'bar ba 'phro ba ye shes thugs rjer ldan //
NK027(sha)001:9972: ye shes gsal bas phyogs bcur mun nag sel //
NK027(sha)001:9973: bskal ba'i me dpung rab tu 'bar ba'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:9974: mtshan mar 'dzin rtog bsreg pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:9975: dz+wa la ram dz+ny+aa na h'u /
NK027(sha)001:9976: a b+hi khrag zhal thal ba'i mtshan ma bya zhing /
NK027(sha)001:9978: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK027(sha)001:9979: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK027(sha)001:9980: zhing chen gsar rnying ti ra bcas //
NK027(sha)001:9981: dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK027(sha)001:9982: khrag gi tshim bus mtshan pas ni //
NK027(sha)001:9983: 'di yang sngon gyi dam tshig lags //
NK027(sha)001:9984: 'di yang rtags kyi phyag rgya ste //
NK027(sha)001:9985: chos nyid zhag gi brgyan pas ni //
NK027(sha)001:9986: zhag gi tshim bu dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:9987: chos nyid dbyings kyi rgyal ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:9988: gdugs pa thabs kyi 'dul ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:9989: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:9990: chos nyid zhag gi dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:9993: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK027(sha)001:9994: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK027(sha)001:9995: zhing chen gsar rnying sti ra bcas //
NK027(sha)001:9996: dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK027(sha)001:9997: thal ba'i mtshan mas brgyan pas ni //
NK027(sha)001:9998: gdug pa ma lus rab 'dul ba //
NK027(sha)001:9999: che ba'i rgyal po kun gyi bdag /
NK027(sha)001:10000: thams cad kun du dpa' bo'i mtshan //
NK027(sha)001:10001: gdug pa zil gnon thal bas mtshan //
NK027(sha)001:10002: khams gsum gdug pa thal bar rlog /
NK027(sha)001:10003: de 'dra'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:10006: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK027(sha)001:10007: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK027(sha)001:10008: zhing chen gsar rnying sti rar bcas //
NK027(sha)001:10009: dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtsho bskyil //
NK027(sha)001:10010: khrag gis thig le'i mtshan pa 'di //
NK027(sha)001:10011: 'di yang sngon gyi dam tshig lags //
NK027(sha)001:10012: 'dod chags gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:10013: khrag gis thig le'i rtag mtshan nas //
NK027(sha)001:10014: khrag gi thig les dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)001:10015: gtum po drag po 'joms pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:10016: nga rgyal dreg pa 'joms mdzad cing //
NK027(sha)001:10017: dbang mchog dam pa thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:10019: a b+hi shiny+tsa bcu gnyis pa bsgrub rdzas kyi dbang la /
NK027(sha)001:10032: bsgrub pa'i rgyal po khyod la sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:10033: bsgrub pa'i las la dbang thob phyir //
NK027(sha)001:10034: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:10035: rgyal ba thams cad bsgrub pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:10036: tshe dang sman la sogs pa rnams //
NK027(sha)001:10037: bsgrub pa ma lus bsgrub par bgyis //
NK027(sha)001:10038: sarba sid+d+hi a wa d+hu ti a b+hi bcu gsum ming gi dbang ni /
NK027(sha)001:10040: rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK027(sha)001:10041: dbang thob de gnyis gcig pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:10042: rig 'dzin rdo rje rtsal gyi dbang //
NK027(sha)001:10043: rdo rje ming ni sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)001:10045: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi /
NK027(sha)001:10047: lha dang gnyis su med par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:10051: de yan chad kyi bsgrub dbang bcu gsum rdzogs so //
NK027(sha)001:10052: de nas rdzogs chen a ti yo ga las /
NK027(sha)001:10053: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:10055: bsgrub pa'i dbang mchog thob pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:10056: gsang ba'i bdag po yin pas /
NK027(sha)001:10057: gsang ba'i dbang mchog sbyin pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:10058: gru gsum mthing nag gi dbus su /
NK027(sha)001:10060: lte ba rdo rjes mtshan pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:10061: rdo rje dril bu yab yum gyi rten te lag tu byin te /
NK027(sha)001:10062: hoh gnyis med don dam byang chub sems //
NK027(sha)001:10063: bu mchog des snying la bzhag nas //
NK027(sha)001:10064: don dam kun rdzob la sogs pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:10065: rang byung ye shes chen po shog /
NK027(sha)001:10066: a ho ma h+aa su ka hoh rdo rje dril bu gtad do //
NK027(sha)001:10067: de nas ka p+aa la'i bdud rtsi sbyin la /
NK027(sha)001:10068: hoh dga' ba byang chub sems chen po //
NK027(sha)001:10069: kun du tshim par byed pa'i ro //
NK027(sha)001:10070: dkar dmar lhag pa'i byang chub sems //
NK027(sha)001:10071: dbang thob sems dpa' lce la bzhag /
NK027(sha)001:10072: don dam kun rdzob lhan gcig skyes //
NK027(sha)001:10073: rang byung ye shes chen po yi //
NK027(sha)001:10074: dbang mchog gsang ba thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:10075: a ho ma h+aa su ka hoh de nas rdo
NK027(sha)001:10076: rje'i sked pa dar dpyangs sngon po can byin te
NK027(sha)001:10078: gsang dang shes rab ye shes dang //
NK027(sha)001:10079: dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang //
NK027(sha)001:10080: rtsol med byang chub sems chen mo //
NK027(sha)001:10081: shes rab chen mo rtsal gyi dbang //
NK027(sha)001:10082: chos kun du mar dbang bskur nas //
NK027(sha)001:10083: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i dbang yin pas //
NK027(sha)001:10084: rdzas kyi tshig dang gang zag dang //
NK027(sha)001:10085: kun rdzob dbang de ma thob kyi //
NK027(sha)001:10086: chos la sems kyi dbang thob nas //
NK027(sha)001:10087: rgyal ba rig 'dzin thams cad dang //
NK027(sha)001:10088: srid gsum dbang chen thams cad kun //
NK027(sha)001:10089: de la dbang mchog bskur bar 'gyur //
NK027(sha)001:10090: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:10091: a ho ma h+aa su ka hoh de ni shin
NK027(sha)001:10092: tu bsdus pa'i lugs la zab pa'i dbang gsum dngos
NK027(sha)001:10093: su bskur ba logs na yod do //
NK027(sha)001:10094: gzhan du gsal ba man ngag ste /
NK027(sha)001:10095: shin tu gsal ba'i bka' rgya can gang rung la ma yin no //
NK027(sha)001:10098: // // mdo dbang gi zab pa'i dbang gsum mo //
NK027(sha)001:10099: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)001:10100: 'dir zab pa'i dbang gsum bstan par bya ste /
NK027(sha)001:10102: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i nges 'byed las //
NK027(sha)001:10103: snod dang dkyil 'khor bskur ba'i dus //
NK027(sha)001:10104: dbang gi ngo bo nges tshig dang //
NK027(sha)001:10105: bskur rdzas thabs dang rgyu rkyen dang //
NK027(sha)001:10106: gnas dang sgrib spangs thob pa'i tshad //
NK027(sha)001:10107: chos dang dgos ched skyon yon gyi //
NK027(sha)001:10108: mdor bsdus lung gi mtshan nyid bzhag /
NK027(sha)001:10109: ces gsungs la don bcu drug ste /
NK027(sha)001:10111: spyod pa'i brtul zhugs can la dam rdzas lnga la 'dzem bag med par longs spyod nus pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:10112: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor sor bzhi mdzub gang tsan dan
NK027(sha)001:10113: gser la gnas pa mkha' gsang gi tshad mtshan pa'o
NK027(sha)001:10115: lhag ma gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du phan nus
NK027(sha)001:10116: kyi dbang bco lnga thob cing bskyed rim la goms
NK027(sha)001:10117: nas rdzogs rim la 'jug pa'i dus so //
NK027(sha)001:10118: bzhi pa byang sems dkar dmar mkha' gsang du 'dres pa de'o //
NK027(sha)001:10120: sngar ma thob pa dang snod min la gab pas gsang dbang ngo //
NK027(sha)001:10121: de byin pas dam rdzas la longs spyod par dag zhing khams rgyas pa dbang zhes bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:10122: drug pa bskur rdzas thabs shes kyi ngo bo nyi
NK027(sha)001:10123: zla yin la de'i nus pa bskyed pa'i rdzas thod
NK027(sha)001:10124: pa'i dbu rgyan shun gyi cod pan no //
NK027(sha)001:10126: thog mar bla ma la zhu ba byas nas dal bzhed pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:10128: sor bzhi'i mdzub gang tshad ldan la //
NK027(sha)001:10129: nyi shu rtsa lngas rab mnyam ste //
NK027(sha)001:10130: gnas dang phyag rgya yi ge sogs //
NK027(sha)001:10131: rgyud bzhin tshad du mkhas pas bslab //
NK027(sha)001:10132: ces pa gong du bshad pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:10139: byang chub sems d+he gu snyoms par zug /
NK027(sha)001:10140: der lha zhe gnyis kyi mtshan ma zla gdan dang bcas pa byang sems rang byung gi bri /
NK027(sha)001:10141: de ltar ma grub na pad ma'i lte bar rdo rje bri'o //
NK027(sha)001:10144: bcu drug phyag rgya phyi nang gsang //
NK027(sha)001:10145: spyod lam lam gyi rgyu mthun nas //
NK027(sha)001:10146: bcud dang nges par ldan pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:10147: zhes pa lo bcu drug ma yon tan bcu gsum yod pa ste /
NK027(sha)001:10167: gang dang sbyar du btub pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:10168: dri bzang gi chu la sngags btab pa dang 'o mas phyi khrus /
NK027(sha)001:10169: chos bshad de 'du shes bsgyur la /
NK027(sha)001:10170: dam rdzas longs spyod par mos pa nang khrus so //
NK027(sha)001:10175: ga pur rnams sbyar ba'i phye ma sbrang rtsis ril bu byas la mur du bcug /
NK027(sha)001:10177: gos dang rgyan gyi ldub bo //
NK027(sha)001:10178: de nas rang rdor sems su sgoms pa'i gnas lnga rigs lnga /
NK027(sha)001:10179: yan lag bzhi la sgo ma bzhi /
NK027(sha)001:10180: gsang bar h'u las rdo rje rtse lnga /
NK027(sha)001:10182: yum dbyings phyug ma'i spyi bor sangs rgyas spyan ma /
NK027(sha)001:10184: snying kar kun tu bzang mo /
NK027(sha)001:10186: nang gi pad mor sgrol bzhi /
NK027(sha)001:10187: lag pa g.yas su mi pham ma /
NK027(sha)001:10190: phyi'i pad mar ral gcig ma bsam mo //
NK027(sha)001:10191: de nas phyi rol gyi dkyil 'khor dang yum gyi
NK027(sha)001:10192: mkha' nang gzhal yas khang du gsal ba'i nang du
NK027(sha)001:10193: zhi ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:10198: de nas slob ma 'jug pa la khrus bya /
NK027(sha)001:10200: slob mas rin po che'i snying khar bzung la gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:10202: rdo rje sems gtso khyod la 'dud //
NK027(sha)001:10203: thar lam chen po bdag 'dod de //
NK027(sha)001:10204: de nyid dbang dang dam tshig dang //
NK027(sha)001:10205: mgon po dpa' bos skyabs gsol zhing //
NK027(sha)001:10206: theg chen khang par gzhugs pa dang //
NK027(sha)001:10207: mkhyen rab ye shes bdag la stsol //
NK027(sha)001:10209: dkyil 'khor yab yub gang rung gi phyag tu me tog dor la /
NK027(sha)001:10210: hoh rang bzhin 'du 'bral med pa'i lha //
NK027(sha)001:10211: phyag rgya chen po'i tshogs mchog tu //
NK027(sha)001:10212: bdag kyang mnyam par sbyar ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:10213: byin rlabs rab tu bzhugs par gsol //
NK027(sha)001:10215: bla mas slob ma'i lag pa g.yon pa'i theb srin gyi bzung la /
NK027(sha)001:10216: bu 'dir shog cig ci bde ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:10217: las kyi rim pa 'gro ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:10218: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje bzung //
NK027(sha)001:10219: rdzogs pa'i ye shes bde chen la //
NK027(sha)001:10220: dmigs pa med pa'i gnas phyir du //
NK027(sha)001:10221: ser sna spangs ba'i dang yid kyi //
NK027(sha)001:10222: gtong zhing rang sems brtan por zungs //
NK027(sha)001:10223: ye shes rang gnas rdzogs dbang sbyin //
NK027(sha)001:10225: drangs ba de g.yas su bzhag la bsgrib pa dral /
NK027(sha)001:10229: phyag rgya bzhis snyoms par zhugs te /
NK027(sha)001:10230: yab yum gyi bde ba'i thig le yig 'bru'i tshogs
NK027(sha)001:10231: su gsal ba de dga' ba bcu drug gi rgyan
NK027(sha)001:10232: gyi rdo rje'i lam nas pad mor spros te /
NK027(sha)001:10233: ba gar 'khyil ba'i sa dal mchod /
NK027(sha)001:10234: slar drang ste rdo rje dang /
NK027(sha)001:10235: lha dang thig le ngo bo gcig tu gzhug pa de /
NK027(sha)001:10236: h'u dang phatahkyi slar spros te /
NK027(sha)001:10237: slob ma'i lce la bzhag cing /
NK027(sha)001:10238: gal po che dang sgyu 'phrul bla ma las /
NK027(sha)001:10240: nga ni rgyal ba kun gyi yum //
NK027(sha)001:10241: thig le byang chub sems chen po //
NK027(sha)001:10242: nga ni khro rgyal kun gyi rje //
NK027(sha)001:10243: ye shes rol pa'i 'byung gnas gter //
NK027(sha)001:10244: nga ni spyi dpal bla na med //
NK027(sha)001:10245: skyon bral thabs kyi rgyal po yin //
NK027(sha)001:10246: sems kyi dkyil nas drang ba'i chu //
NK027(sha)001:10247: khyod kyi lce la bab pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:10248: snying gi dkyil du bzung bar byos //
NK027(sha)001:10249: rigs kyi bu khyod ding phan chad //
NK027(sha)001:10250: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs mchog zung //
NK027(sha)001:10251: sangs rgyas kun gyi gtso bo yin //
NK027(sha)001:10252: byang chub sems dang mnyam pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:10253: sems dpa' kun gyi mchod gnas yin //
NK027(sha)001:10254: rigs kyi bu mchog 'di phyin chad //
NK027(sha)001:10255: phyi dang nang dang gsang ba yi //
NK027(sha)001:10256: bstan pa phyi nang zab mo kun //
NK027(sha)001:10257: sems kyi dkyil du bsdus nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:10258: rdo rje lce'i sgo phyes te //
NK027(sha)001:10259: bdud rtsi sman mchog dam pa 'di //
NK027(sha)001:10260: dad ldan skyes bu ngom par gyis //
NK027(sha)001:10261: sems kyi thig le'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK027(sha)001:10262: zhi khro 'bar ba'i gter sgoms la //
NK027(sha)001:10263: srid pa gsum la dbang bskur cig /
NK027(sha)001:10264: dbang chen thugs dam bskul bar byos //
NK027(sha)001:10265: skye 'gro kun la snying rje'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:10266: gdul ba'i phyag 'di cir yang spyod //
NK027(sha)001:10267: dug gsum rtsa ba bcad par byos //
NK027(sha)001:10268: phyi nang snod bcud rnam par dag /
NK027(sha)001:10269: rnam dag chen po nyid kyi lam //
NK027(sha)001:10270: byed spyod thams cad tshogs gnyis rdzogs //
NK027(sha)001:10271: 'gro don thams cad byang chub sems kyi dbyings //
NK027(sha)001:10272: sems kyi chu 'di btung bar byos //
NK027(sha)001:10273: rnal 'byor chen po don du zung //
NK027(sha)001:10274: h'u zhes brjod pas thig le lha'i ngo bo rdo
NK027(sha)001:10275: rje sems dpa' nyungs 'bru tsam lha zhig gi tshom
NK027(sha)001:10276: bu'i lce la bzhag pas snyig la thig le /
NK027(sha)001:10277: dus gsum sangs rgyas rang gi ye shes bde ba chen po'i sems su gsal ba /
NK027(sha)001:10278: rgyal thabs spyi blug gi dbang ngo //
NK027(sha)001:10279: bla ma de ltar bskur ba'i nus pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:10281: slob ma'ang rtog pa can tshul de ltar blor mi
NK027(sha)001:10282: shong ba la skyob dang sbyar nas gsang ste bskur
NK027(sha)001:10283: ba la'ang / dmigs pa yab yum gyi sbyor mtshams nas len par bsam dgos la /
NK027(sha)001:10288: dung dang nya phyis kyi tshul du bskur ba'ang nges pa yin gyi /
NK027(sha)001:10290: de ltar bskur bas slob ma'i las kyi rtsa nang
NK027(sha)001:10291: rigs drug gi sa bon zung gsum rnam shes tshogs
NK027(sha)001:10292: brgyad sgo gsum dug gsum gyi gnas ngan len sbyangs
NK027(sha)001:10293: dang dmigs med ye shes lnga pa'i gsal ba'o //
NK027(sha)001:10294: thig le snang la rang bzhin med pa skye 'gags
NK027(sha)001:10295: thams cad dang bral ba ni ye shes bla ma'i
NK027(sha)001:10297: de yang thabs dang byin rlabs kyi //
NK027(sha)001:10298: mi bskyod yab yum rol pa las //
NK027(sha)001:10299: bde ba gsal zhing mi dmigs pa //
NK027(sha)001:10300: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK027(sha)001:10301: rdo rje ye shes h'u tshogs kyi //
NK027(sha)001:10302: pad mo ye shes bsdus 'khyil ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:10303: nyungs dkar tshad tsam 'di yi sems //
NK027(sha)001:10304: rtse dang rtse ru byin pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:10305: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor chos khams kyi //
NK027(sha)001:10306: sa bon zur gsum gnyis dang bcas //
NK027(sha)001:10307: gnas ngan len pa gsum sbyangs te //
NK027(sha)001:10308: dmigs med sems kyi ye shes lnga //
NK027(sha)001:10309: gsal bas sa bon tshig pa bzhin //
NK027(sha)001:10310: mi skye thabs kyi dbug phyung pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:10312: de nas ye shes snying po'i thig le de h'u
NK027(sha)001:10313: ring po dkar la 'tsher ba gcig tu bsgom du
NK027(sha)001:10315: gal po che dang bla la /
NK027(sha)001:10317: thams cad bde ba chen po'i dbyings //
NK027(sha)001:10318: dge sdig las kyi bcos ma shing //
NK027(sha)001:10319: bsgom dang bsgrub pa mi 'gyang ba'i //
NK027(sha)001:10320: rnam dag sems nyid rin chen gter //
NK027(sha)001:10321: rdo rje snying po'i ye shes kyi //
NK027(sha)001:10322: khro rgyal kun gyi gtso gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:10323: sh+r+ai ma h+aa su ka badz+ra b+ho d+he h'u ho /
NK027(sha)001:10324: zhes pas bu'i sems nyid h'u ring por bsgom pa de /
NK027(sha)001:10325: che mchog tu gsal bar rdzogs pa'i thugs dkyil du gu h+ya he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:10326: de'i thugs dkyil du sa nu he ru ka ste /
NK027(sha)001:10327: lung gsum rgyud kyi he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:10328: rgyan thams cad rdzogs par bsgoms la /
NK027(sha)001:10329: des nus pa bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK027(sha)001:10331: shing shun gyi cod pan sngo dmar mgor bzhag la /
NK027(sha)001:10334: thabs dang thugs rje byin rlabs kyi //
NK027(sha)001:10335: rigs kyi bu mchog dbang bskur phyir //
NK027(sha)001:10336: gsang ba'i dbu rgyan 'di bcing bas //
NK027(sha)001:10337: rigs kyi bu mchog 'di yan chad //
NK027(sha)001:10338: 'jig rten che ba kun gyi bu //
NK027(sha)001:10339: che ba'i che ba'i zil gyi gnon //
NK027(sha)001:10340: sangs rgyas che ba'i mchod gnas ni //
NK027(sha)001:10341: rnal 'byor chen po khyod nyid yin //
NK027(sha)001:10342: sarba ta th+aa ga ta g+hu h+ya badz+ra /
NK027(sha)001:10343: rat+na mu ku ra tram tri badz+ra g+hu h+ya sid+d+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)001:10347: khyung gi gshog pa g.yas g.yon gding pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:10348: klu rnams ma lus zil gyi gnon pa ltar //
NK027(sha)001:10349: srid gsum yon tan mchog tu rdzogs pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:10350: sangs rgyas kun la mdzes pa'i yon tan mchog /
NK027(sha)001:10351: mchog tu che ba'i bdud bzhi zil gyi gnon //
NK027(sha)001:10352: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa g+hu h+ya badz+ra
NK027(sha)001:10353: ar+ya ma le a b+hi shiny+tsa hoh zhes pas dbang
NK027(sha)001:10354: bskur nas / dbang cig char 'jug pa las /
NK027(sha)001:10355: bu mchog mtshan ma rtog bral nyid //
NK027(sha)001:10356: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK027(sha)001:10357: kun la spyod par dbang thob nas //
NK027(sha)001:10358: slob ma bde la 'god byed pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:10359: byang chub chen po deng gyur to //
NK027(sha)001:10363: gsang ba'i don mchog 'di dag ni //
NK027(sha)001:10364: lta ba dman par bstan byas na //
NK027(sha)001:10365: dus min pa ni srog zad nas //
NK027(sha)001:10366: mgo gas snying yang tshig par 'gyur //
NK027(sha)001:10367: khab len gyi ni lcags sdud ltar //
NK027(sha)001:10368: mi 'dod bzhin du dbang med par //
NK027(sha)001:10369: bskal bar ngan song myong bar 'gyur //
NK027(sha)001:10370: des na shin tu gsang bar bya //
NK027(sha)001:10373: rang bzhin gnas don gsum pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:10374: tha snyad gnyis bsdus byang chub sems //
NK027(sha)001:10375: mtha'i tha snyad kun dben no //
NK027(sha)001:10376: yul yin ma mthong gsang ba'i mi //
NK027(sha)001:10378: lhag ma don gyi bden pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:10379: ye nas rang chas su ldan pas mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu /
NK027(sha)001:10380: bden pa'i ro dang ldan pa yi /
NK027(sha)001:10381: lhan gcig skyes pa'i rgyu ste /
NK027(sha)001:10384: spyod pa brtul zhugs dang sems dang ldan pa ni rgyu'i rkyen no //
NK027(sha)001:10385: cho ga yan lag lnga char ba'i nus pa bdag po'i rkyen /
NK027(sha)001:10386: sbyor ba nyams myong can gyi bla ma dbang blang ba'i yul dmigs pa'i rkyen /
NK027(sha)001:10387: skad cig ma'i rim pas go phye ba de ma thag pa'i rkyen no //
NK027(sha)001:10389: phyi rol pa gzhan gyi dben pa'i gnas /
NK027(sha)001:10395: bcu gcig pa sgrib pa spang tshul ni /
NK027(sha)001:10396: sgo gsum gyi sgrib pa dag tshul gang du bshad do //
NK027(sha)001:10397: bcu gnyis pa thob tshad ni /
NK027(sha)001:10398: lhag ma'i don dam bden pa rang la yong ba dbang gi nus pas /
NK027(sha)001:10399: rgyud la rnam par mi rtog pa skyes pa de'o //
NK027(sha)001:10400: bcu gsum pa chos ni rdzogs rim sgom par rung ngo //
NK027(sha)001:10402: dbang gsum pa'i rgyu byed cing /
NK027(sha)001:10403: thig le blang ste bstim pas tshe 'phel ba'o //
NK027(sha)001:10404: bco lnga pa ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK027(sha)001:10405: chos de dag bdag tu mi rung ba /
NK027(sha)001:10406: sgrib pa de rnams spang mi nus //
NK027(sha)001:10407: rim pas bsgrod pa'i go 'gag pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:10408: bcu drug pa yon tan skyon de dag bzlog pa'i yon tan no //
NK027(sha)001:10409: rgyal ba'i sras su gyur nas rigs kyi yum dang
NK027(sha)001:10410: sems mas byin gyis brlabs shing man ngag zab mo'i
NK027(sha)001:10412: gsang dbang gi man ngag zab mo rdzogs so //
NK027(sha)001:10414: // gsum pa shes rab ye shes kyi dbang ni /
NK027(sha)001:10415: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i dbang nges 'byed las /
NK027(sha)001:10416: snod dang dkyil 'khor bsgrub pa'i dus //
NK027(sha)001:10417: rang gi ngo bo nges tshig dang //
NK027(sha)001:10418: bskur ba'i thabs dang rgyu rkyen dang //
NK027(sha)001:10419: gnas dang sgrib spang thob pa'i tshad //
NK027(sha)001:10420: chos dang dgos ched skyon yon gyi //
NK027(sha)001:10421: mdor bsdus lus kyi mtshan nyid bzhag /
NK027(sha)001:10424: rig pa'i brtul zhugs can gsang bar man chad rdzogs shing /
NK027(sha)001:10429: gsum pa dbang bskur dus ni /
NK027(sha)001:10430: dbang bcu drug pa yan chad brtan pas gzhi lam
NK027(sha)001:10431: gyi ting nge 'dzin gsal bas rdzogs rim las su
NK027(sha)001:10432: rung ste / rlung stobs su gyur pa'i tshe'o //
NK027(sha)001:10434: mtshon bya rang bzhin gyi gnas pa la /
NK027(sha)001:10435: mtshon byed thabs kyi brlabs pas rang rig gsal la mi rtog pa'i nyams skye'o //
NK027(sha)001:10437: rig pa spros pa bral ba shes rab /
NK027(sha)001:10438: de nyid ma 'gag par gsal ba ye shes /
NK027(sha)001:10439: don de thabs kyis gsal bar byed pas shes rab ye shes kyi dbang ngo //
NK027(sha)001:10441: phyag rgya ma ga bur sid+ha ha dang ldan pa gtad pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:10443: las rim las yul gyi mtshan nyid //
NK027(sha)001:10444: thun mong rigs mthun rtog med rgya //
NK027(sha)001:10445: ud+pala dkar nag phyed skyil ldan //
NK027(sha)001:10447: dri chab dngos dang chu rlung brtag /
NK027(sha)001:10448: lto ba 'phra zhing rgyas pa yin //
NK027(sha)001:10449: zla ba mang ba'i myur bar 'gyur //
NK027(sha)001:10450: yan lag pad 'dra phyag mtshan can //
NK027(sha)001:10451: shin tu mnyes pa'i gzi brjid yod //
NK027(sha)001:10452: khang langs dal ba'i gus dang ldan //
NK027(sha)001:10453: skabs phyed bsnyen smra dang ba che //
NK027(sha)001:10454: sngon nas shin tu brtag par bya //
NK027(sha)001:10455: zhes pa'i mtshan nyid dang ldan pa la phyi nang
NK027(sha)001:10456: gi khrus byas rgyan gyi spras te bla ma la
NK027(sha)001:10457: 'bul / bla mas byin rlabs te thig le'i dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:10458: de nas slob ma ltar mos pa thal mo sbyar te /
NK027(sha)001:10460: kye kye bde mdzad phyag rgya che //
NK027(sha)001:10461: bdag la thugs brtser phan par dgongs //
NK027(sha)001:10462: mdzad dang sgra'i bde la stsol //
NK027(sha)001:10465: sangs rgyas mdzes pa'i zab brlab can //
NK027(sha)001:10466: thabs chen theg pa 'di las gsal //
NK027(sha)001:10467: rang zab mchog lnga za ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:10469: rlung srub 'chi ba'i spyod pa rnams //
NK027(sha)001:10470: khyod kyi bya bar nus sam smros //
NK027(sha)001:10472: e ma ngo mtshar rdo rje'i tshig /
NK027(sha)001:10473: bde ba chen po'i ye shes phyir //
NK027(sha)001:10474: rmad byung thams kyis spyod pa la //
NK027(sha)001:10475: bdag gi mi nus gcig kyang med //
NK027(sha)001:10477: de nas rig ma'i lag pa g.yas slob ma'i g.yon bar gtad la /
NK027(sha)001:10478: skyes bu 'di gzugs bzang ba yin //
NK027(sha)001:10479: de ring phan chad bu mchog khyod //
NK027(sha)001:10480: sgo gsum lha ru mnyam sbyor bas //
NK027(sha)001:10481: tha lam dben pa'i bya ba spang //
NK027(sha)001:10482: bde ba chen po nyams myong bas //
NK027(sha)001:10483: dka' thub theg pa'i lta ba spangs //
NK027(sha)001:10484: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:10485: bde ba'i nyams myong brten par byas so //
NK027(sha)001:10486: rten pa bar chad med sgom pas //
NK027(sha)001:10488: de bas skal ldan rigs bzang skyes //
NK027(sha)001:10489: gtan du 'bral bar ma byed cig /
NK027(sha)001:10493: bde ba chen po chos kyi sku //
NK027(sha)001:10494: shes rab thabs kyi rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK027(sha)001:10495: 'di dang skye ba thams cad du //
NK027(sha)001:10496: dngos grub gter 'di ma spang cig /
NK027(sha)001:10497: rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK027(sha)001:10498: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas khyod la byung //
NK027(sha)001:10499: yang na rdo rje dbang phyug rtsal //
NK027(sha)001:10500: dgug dang gdams pa ma shes na //
NK027(sha)001:10501: rdo rje'i bskal pa mtha' klas par //
NK027(sha)001:10502: chos sku thob par mi 'gyur ro //
NK027(sha)001:10504: slob ma'i snying dkar rdo rje dril bu gshib bzung la /
NK027(sha)001:10506: mi 'gyur rdo rje ye shes gnas //
NK027(sha)001:10507: ma brtsal byin pas bde ba'i mchog /
NK027(sha)001:10508: ma bltas gsal ba ye shes spyan //
NK027(sha)001:10509: gong na med pa kun gyi rje //
NK027(sha)001:10510: ye shes rang gnas brdal ba la //
NK027(sha)001:10511: mi 'gyur g.yung drung sa thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:10512: ma h+aa g+hu h+ya b+h+r+aum dz+ny+aa na ma dz+ny+aa na g+hu h+ya sid+d+hi swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ha /
NK027(sha)001:10513: de nas steng 'og gi sgo ye shes dgug pa'i
NK027(sha)001:10514: man ngag ni rang rig badz+ra he ru ka yab
NK027(sha)001:10515: yum gnas lngar rigs lnga yab yum bskyed la gnas
NK027(sha)001:10518: sgal tshig la dbang mo bkod la /
NK027(sha)001:10519: sa rlung gi dus su mig sna 'gram pa /
NK027(sha)001:10524: rim pa de 'dzin ma shes par bya /
NK027(sha)001:10525: thabs dang shes rab tshul gyis so //
NK027(sha)001:10528: barla dang khur tshos rked pa ru //
NK027(sha)001:10529: rtse ru chags pa skyes pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)001:10530: san thabs mkhas pas rig par bya //
NK027(sha)001:10531: zhes pa la sogs bde ba rgyas pa'i thabs mas byas te /
NK027(sha)001:10532: mkha' gsang byin gyis brlab nas phyag rgya bzhis snyoms par 'jug pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:10534: byin rlabs mnyes par gyur nas ni //
NK027(sha)001:10535: 'dod chags thig le rgyas byed pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:10536: bstan bcos bye brag brtsam par bya //
NK027(sha)001:10537: shes rab thabs kyis g.yas bzung ste //
NK027(sha)001:10538: stod smad bkug pa'i khyod ga ste //
NK027(sha)001:10539: dbang po yul bsdus 'khyud pa ni //
NK027(sha)001:10540: gsang ba chen po'i zhag pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:10541: stod smad shin tu bsdams byas te //
NK027(sha)001:10542: ma skyes mi gtong sgrog gi las //
NK027(sha)001:10543: bskyod pa ha sing bde sgra sogs //
NK027(sha)001:10544: kun tu grags shing bde myong hoh de ltar snyoms
NK027(sha)001:10545: par bzhag pas g.yon ldang la sogs pa'i sems lngas
NK027(sha)001:10547: sa bcu drug gi rim pa re re rlung bzung
NK027(sha)001:10548: nas thig le bzlog pa'i bde bas lam rdzogs tshul
NK027(sha)001:10549: ni / dga' ba bzhi re la bzhir phye ba bcu drug po yab la rim can du skye /
NK027(sha)001:10550: yab yum cig char du skyes /
NK027(sha)001:10551: de'ang dang po dga' ba'i dga' ba /
NK027(sha)001:10552: dga' ba'i dga' ba mchog dga' /
NK027(sha)001:10554: dga' ba lhan cig skyes dga' bzhi'i tshogs lam /
NK027(sha)001:10555: gnyis pa mchog dga' ba sbyor lam /
NK027(sha)001:10556: mchog dga' mchog dga' mthong lam /
NK027(sha)001:10557: mchog dga' dga' bral sa gnyis pa /
NK027(sha)001:10558: mchog dag'i lhan skyes sa gsum pa /
NK027(sha)001:10559: dga' bral gyi dga' ba sa bzhi pa /
NK027(sha)001:10560: dga' bral gyi mchog dga' sa lnga pa /
NK027(sha)001:10561: dga' bral gyi dga' bral sa drug pa /
NK027(sha)001:10562: dga' bral gyi lhan skyes sa bdun pa /
NK027(sha)001:10563: lhan skyes kyi dga' ba sa brgyad pa /
NK027(sha)001:10564: lhan skyes kyi mchog dga' sa dgu pa /
NK027(sha)001:10565: lhan skyes kyi dga' bral sa bcu pa /
NK027(sha)001:10566: lhan skyes kyi lhan skyes pa sa bcu gcig pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:10568: de'i rim 'byung dga' ba bzhi bcu drug ldan /
NK027(sha)001:10569: dang po'i bzhi rnams tshogs yin te //
NK027(sha)001:10570: gnyis gcig sbyor ba gnyis pa'i gnyis //
NK027(sha)001:10571: rab dga' tha ma'i cha dang po //
NK027(sha)001:10572: bcu dbang lnga gsum dbang dang ldan //
NK027(sha)001:10573: rdzogs rim nyi zla dus gcig bsnyen //
NK027(sha)001:10575: de'ang yab kyi thig le yum gyi bu gar spro ba /
NK027(sha)001:10576: yum gyi khams rdo rje'i drang ba /
NK027(sha)001:10577: yab kyi thig le gsal ba'i ngo bo /
NK027(sha)001:10578: yum gyi thig le stong pa'i rang bzhin /
NK027(sha)001:10579: rten thig le gnyis 'dres pa'i dus su /
NK027(sha)001:10580: rten chen gyi sems nyid gsal stong zung du 'char ba chos nyid yin /
NK027(sha)001:10581: de'i tshe yod med kyi mtha' ma bsgrib pa 'od gsal mngon du gyur pas /
NK027(sha)001:10582: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang zhes bya'o /
NK027(sha)001:10583: de'ang slob ma rlung sems la dbang ma thob pa thig le bzung /
NK027(sha)001:10584: 'gugs lcags pa'i nus pa med pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:10585: tshur 'di blor mi shong ba la /
NK027(sha)001:10586: ting nge 'dzin gyi rig ma la snyoms 'jug goms su bcug la /
NK027(sha)001:10587: ye shes gsal stong du ngo sprod do //
NK027(sha)001:10588: de'i bskul tshig bden pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:10590: che ba'i ye shes rnyed dka' ba //
NK027(sha)001:10591: shes rab thabs la brtan pas grub //
NK027(sha)001:10592: ming tsam gzhan la brten 'dra yang //
NK027(sha)001:10593: mngon gsum bde ba rang las byung //
NK027(sha)001:10594: dz+ny+aa na b+ho d+hi tsit+ta a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)001:10595: rigs kyi bu mchog khyod la ye shes rang gnas
NK027(sha)001:10596: kyi dbang gi chos nyid rang ngo sprad pas ye
NK027(sha)001:10597: shes rang gnas kyi dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:10600: de ring phyin chad bu khyod ni //
NK027(sha)001:10601: rang rig bde la gnas pas na //
NK027(sha)001:10602: rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya ste //
NK027(sha)001:10603: yum dang 'jam ma thams cad la //
NK027(sha)001:10605: rigs su gyur rnams thabs 'di zung //
NK027(sha)001:10607: dbang phyug rgyal po nyid du nges //
NK027(sha)001:10611: tha snyad gnyis bsdus kyi mtha' dang bral ba'i rang
NK027(sha)001:10612: rig rang gsal stong pa kun khyab tu gnas pa'o
NK027(sha)001:10613: // lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK027(sha)001:10614: zla ldan ma la sbyor ba gom pas thig le gnyis brten pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:10616: rig pa brtul zhugs can gyi dbang gsum pa la mos pa'i bu dbang chags pa'i rgyu'i rkyen no //
NK027(sha)001:10617: byed pa bsdom pa'i brtan dang rlung sems las su rung ba /
NK027(sha)001:10618: phyag rgya ma'i rgyu rkyen 'dzom pa'i mthu ni bde ba bskyed pas bdag po'i rkyen no //
NK027(sha)001:10619: nyams su len pa'i bla ma byin rlabs can ni /
NK027(sha)001:10620: dbang blang ba'i yul yin pas dmigs pa'i rkyen no //
NK027(sha)001:10621: thig le 'pho ba bcu drug gi cha'i rgyu 'bras
NK027(sha)001:10622: rim bzlog gi dus su phyi ma phyi ma'i go
NK027(sha)001:10623: 'byed pas de ma thag pa'i rkyen no //
NK027(sha)001:10625: sbyor ba'i gnas gsang ba yum gyi mkha' /
NK027(sha)001:10626: bde ba rtag pa'i gnas mar byung yar bzlog gi
NK027(sha)001:10627: lhan cig skyes dag'i dus thig le brtan pa'i gnas
NK027(sha)001:10629: 'dug cing bskyal ba'i gnas pa'i spar gyi bstan /
NK027(sha)001:10630: rang gi ngo bo gnas rig pa'i 'phrang ngo //
NK027(sha)001:10631: bcu gcig pa sgrib pa spong tshul ni /
NK027(sha)001:10632: rang rig gsal bas shes bsgrib srab cing nyon sgrib ka nas dag ste /
NK027(sha)001:10633: kun du 'od du gnas gyur pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:10634: bcu gnyis pa thob tshad ni /
NK027(sha)001:10635: mkha' gsang gi 'phrad pa la brten nas rig pa gsal la rtog med nyams su myong ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:10636: nyams myong de dang mi 'bral bas brten med thob pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:10638: gsang spyod thabs lam khyad par gyi chos rnams dang 'od gsal rdzogs pa ma lus bstan no //
NK027(sha)001:10639: bcu bzhi pa dgos ched ni /
NK027(sha)001:10640: dbang bzhi'i lam la brten po chags pas chags pa sbyang ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:10641: lam gong nas gong du bogs 'byung ba'o //
NK027(sha)001:10642: bac+wo lnga pa ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK027(sha)001:10643: thabs 'di min gzhan gyi dbang mi thob /
NK027(sha)001:10646: bcu drug pa yon tan ni /
NK027(sha)001:10648: skyon de dag las grol te /
NK027(sha)001:10649: yon tan dpag med thob pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:10650: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang gi man ngag zab mo rdzogs so //
NK027(sha)001:10651: bzhi pa bde ba chen po'i dbang ni /
NK027(sha)001:10653: snod dang dkyil 'khor bskur ba'i dus //
NK027(sha)001:10654: rang gi ngo bo nges tshig dang //
NK027(sha)001:10655: bskur rdzas thabs dang rgyu rkyen dang //
NK027(sha)001:10656: gnas dang sgrib spang thob pa'i tshad //
NK027(sha)001:10657: mdor bsdus lus kyis mtshan nyid bzhag /
NK027(sha)001:10660: 'bras bu la ming du btags pa ste /
NK027(sha)001:10662: gsum pa dkyil 'khor dbang gsum pa ltar ro //
NK027(sha)001:10663: gsum pa dbang bskur ba'i dus ni /
NK027(sha)001:10664: dbang gsum pa'i nyams len goms pa mchog tu gyur pa'i tshe'o //
NK027(sha)001:10666: bden gnyis dbyer med bde ba chen po'i ye shes so //
NK027(sha)001:10667: grangs kyi tha mar gyur pas bzhi pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:10669: chos thams cad gnyis med rol par shar ba /
NK027(sha)001:10672: rgyu rkyen las 'das pas 'gyur ba med pa bden pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:10673: dpe'i mtshon du med pas blo las 'das pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:10674: 'bras bu ni lhag par byar med pas mthar thug pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:10675: de nyid nyi zla'i thig le kha bsgyur te drang po la brten nas bde ba skyes pa bsten /
NK027(sha)001:10676: mtshon byed dpe'i ye shes phyag rgya dang bral yang
NK027(sha)001:10677: bde ba mi nyams par gnyis med kyi ye shes
NK027(sha)001:10678: gsal ba brten med la byang chub pa'i rten med
NK027(sha)001:10679: sa bon gnyis 'dres pa las skyes pa rgyu 'bras
NK027(sha)001:10680: rim pa'i dbang / thig le bskyur bas mthar phyin skyes pa rim pa bzlog pa'i dbang /
NK027(sha)001:10681: de dag thabs la brten nas /
NK027(sha)001:10682: don gsal snang gi nus pa thob pas dbang zhes bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:10684: rig ma nyi ma can de ni //
NK027(sha)001:10685: bcu gnyis phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK027(sha)001:10686: shin tu bstan pa'i gzhi ru shes //
NK027(sha)001:10687: rdo rje zla 'od mdzes ldan ma //
NK027(sha)001:10688: dman dang rig ngan rnam par spangs //
NK027(sha)001:10689: rdo rje'i mnga' yi ma phog cing //
NK027(sha)001:10690: gzhan dbang logs spyod ma byas pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:10691: bcu gnyis bcu gzhi bac+wo lnga yang rung /
NK027(sha)001:10694: drug par nyi ldan rgyan dang ldan //
NK027(sha)001:10695: nam mkha'i ba gshos bsam gtan goms //
NK027(sha)001:10696: shes rab ye shes rang gnas brnyes /
NK027(sha)001:10698: zhes pa ltar bla mas sbyin pa gsum pa bzhin byas la bskur ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:10699: kye ma mkha' klong rnam dag ma //
NK027(sha)001:10700: nyi ma bye ba'i 'od zer gyi //
NK027(sha)001:10701: mya ngan 'das pa'i mtha' blangs shing //
NK027(sha)001:10702: mtshan mo'i mun pa gsal bar mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:10704: nyi zla shar thabs de nyid kyi //
NK027(sha)001:10705: bsam yas lhun grub dal snang ba //
NK027(sha)001:10709: rtogs sam nyams su blang pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:10710: rtogs pa'i klong du sus 'dris pa //
NK027(sha)001:10711: mi zhes bya ba sangs rgyas yin //
NK027(sha)001:10712: bde chen dbang 'di bstan par bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:10713: d+harma ka ya a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)001:10714: rigs kyi bu la bde ba chen po'i dbang bskur
NK027(sha)001:10715: bas nyams su myong nas phyir mi ldog pa'i dbang
NK027(sha)001:10716: dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:10718: de nas sbyor thabs gsum pa bzhin byas pas bzung
NK027(sha)001:10719: ba'i bde ba la thun mong gis lam 'bras bu
NK027(sha)001:10720: dang bcas pa las bzlog thabs kyi bzlog ste /
NK027(sha)001:10721: dga' ba bcu drug gi rim pa bzlog pa lam
NK027(sha)001:10722: lnga sa bcu thun mong ma yin pa'i sa rdzogs
NK027(sha)001:10723: nas gsang ba rdo rje'i rtsa bar sleb pa bcu
NK027(sha)001:10724: gcig kun tu 'od sprul pa'i 'khor lo drangs pa
NK027(sha)001:10725: pad+ma can / rtsa gnas phab par bkram pas rtogs
NK027(sha)001:10726: tshogs lha'i dal du gsal la 'dzin pa med pa
NK027(sha)001:10727: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen de dag las mngon
NK027(sha)001:10728: pad+ma can / shes drug / mtshan so gnyis dpe byed brgyad cu'o //
NK027(sha)001:10729: de ltar dbang bskur thabs kyi nus pa dang mi ldan yang /
NK027(sha)001:10730: ting nge 'dzin gyi de ltar bya /
NK027(sha)001:10731: spang blang yod med kyi mtha' las mi brtsal bar
NK027(sha)001:10732: gnyis med zung 'jug mnyam pa nyid du ngo sprad
NK027(sha)001:10734: de nas dben par phra men gyi yul sogs chang
NK027(sha)001:10735: dang mar gyi bkang ba sogs kyi bla ma mnyes
NK027(sha)001:10736: par byas te bla ma'i mdun du mgo bzhag pa'i
NK027(sha)001:10737: rna bar gser gyi sbub mchu gtsug la /
NK027(sha)001:10739: dngos kun sems phyir spang blang bral //
NK027(sha)001:10740: skye mched mi 'gog cing mi sems //
NK027(sha)001:10741: gang yin bde chen rtsis ma bsgrim //
NK027(sha)001:10742: zhes byar med ka dag lhun grub tu ngo sprad do //
NK027(sha)001:10744: bden gnyis dbyer med ye nas rang la gnas pa'i sangs rgyas mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu /
NK027(sha)001:10745: de nyid thabs kyis gsal bar byas pas /
NK027(sha)001:10748: mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs can dbang 'di la dad pa na rgyu'i rkyen /
NK027(sha)001:10749: bzlog pa'i las man ngag 'dzom pa gzhi'i phyir bdag po'i rkyen /
NK027(sha)001:10750: bzhi pa nyams myong can gyi bla ma blang ba'i yul yin pas dmigs pa'i rkyen /
NK027(sha)001:10751: bzlog pa'i dga' ba bcu drug pa gsum gyis rim
NK027(sha)001:10752: pas rgyu 'bras kyis tshul du 'pho ba go 'byed
NK027(sha)001:10753: pas de ma thag rkyen no //
NK027(sha)001:10754: bcu pa gnas gsum pa dang mthun /
NK027(sha)001:10755: bcu gcig pa sgrib pa spangs tshul ni /
NK027(sha)001:10756: thun mong gis mthar phyin pas shes sgrib phra mo dang lta ba'i sgrib pa ma bsal bar dgos /
NK027(sha)001:10757: bcu gnyis pa thob tshad ni /
NK027(sha)001:10758: skad cig ma thun phyed slob thun mthar thug gi
NK027(sha)001:10759: rgyun gyi dbang du zung 'jug gi bde ba thob
NK027(sha)001:10760: bo // bcu gsum pa chos ni /
NK027(sha)001:10761: mthar thug gi chos ma lus pa'i skal bar ldan no //
NK027(sha)001:10762: bcu bzhi pa dgos ched ni /
NK027(sha)001:10763: rang gzhan gyi don du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de thob par 'dod pa'i phyir ro //
NK027(sha)001:10764: bac+wo lnga pa ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK027(sha)001:10765: thabs 'di dang bral nas bskal pa du mar lam gzhan gyi bsgrod cing mthar mi phyin pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:10766: bcu drug pa yon tan ni /
NK027(sha)001:10767: yon tan ma lus lhun gyis grub pas /
NK027(sha)001:10768: stong gsum lces brjod kyang rdzogs par mi 'gyur ro //
NK027(sha)001:10769: dbang bzhi pa'i man ngag zab mo thun mong ma yin pa rdzogs so //
NK027(sha)001:10770: de nas tshe'i dal gyi bum pa b+h+r+au gyi 'phro
NK027(sha)001:10771: 'du las gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa'i dbus
NK027(sha)001:10772: su / bam las tshe dpag med yab yum tshe rten /
NK027(sha)001:10773: shar du rnam snang bsgrang phreng can /
NK027(sha)001:10774: lhor rin chen 'byung gnas rgyal bu /
NK027(sha)001:10775: nub tu mi bskyod pa rin chen /
NK027(sha)001:10777: 'bru ma 'bum zla tshes kyi kha brgyan pa /
NK027(sha)001:10778: g.yas rang rtag 'dzin cing thams cad dkar po'o //
NK027(sha)001:10779: sems dpa' man chad g.yon rin po che'i snod 'dzin pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:10780: de nas sa ma ya dzahs snyan gsan dbab /
NK027(sha)001:10784: shunya t+ya sogs kyi dbang bskur /
NK027(sha)001:10785: byin rlabs kyi bde bar gshegs sogs kyi mchod /
NK027(sha)001:10786: bdud rtsi gtor ma rak+tasa mchod /
NK027(sha)001:10787: sbyor sgrol dang ting nge 'dzin dang phyogs bcu dus bzhis bstod la /
NK027(sha)001:10788: hoh bcom ldan 'das mgon po tshe dpag tu med pa 'khor dang bcas pa la /
NK027(sha)001:10789: dngos grub tu gsol ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:10790: khyed kyi sku gsung thugs kyi yon tan skye shi
NK027(sha)001:10791: med pa tshe'i dngos grub sngon gyi thugs dam las
NK027(sha)001:10792: ma 'da' bar da lta nyid du stsal du gsol
NK027(sha)001:10793: / de nas snying khar tshe rten bskyed la a yus mnan /
NK027(sha)001:10794: sor mo phyes pas badz+ra muhka hos dkyil 'khor gyi lha mang po 'phros /
NK027(sha)001:10798: b+h+r+aum badz+ra a yu she h'u dzah dzahmh'u bam hoh
NK027(sha)001:10799: brgya stong bzlas nas tshe dpag med yab yum mang
NK027(sha)001:10800: po spros / khams gsum gyi tshe bsdus pas gtso
NK027(sha)001:10801: bo'i zhal nas brgyud tshe rten la thim par bsam
NK027(sha)001:10802: po spros / / a yu h'u dzas bsrung bstim byas /
NK027(sha)001:10803: rigs bzhi la'ang spro bsdu dang bzlas par bya ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:10808: de nas rang gi snying kar tshe rten bskyed la /
NK027(sha)001:10809: +aa yu h'u dzah bzlas pas bum pa'i lha 'od du zhu /
NK027(sha)001:10810: tshe rten la thim pas lus 'od phung las /
NK027(sha)001:10813: h'u yang mi dmigs par bsam ste /
NK027(sha)001:10815: cis kyang mi 'gyur mi shig pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:10816: ston pa'i go cha bla na med //
NK027(sha)001:10817: mtshan ma'i spyod yul kun bcom nas //
NK027(sha)001:10818: thams cad kun las rgyal bar gnas //
NK027(sha)001:10819: ma byung mi gnas 'dus ma byas //
NK027(sha)001:10820: chos kyi dbyings su tshe sbas pas //
NK027(sha)001:10821: sangs rgyas kyis kyang gzigs mi 'gyur //
NK027(sha)001:10822: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a ta tish+tsa /
NK027(sha)001:10823: h'u gsum gyis tshe brtan pa'o //
