NK027(sha)001:10824: de nas yang rang rdo rje sems dpar bskyed la go bsgo /
NK027(sha)001:10826: pad+ma ka la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih b+hud+ha ka la sha sogs //
NK027(sha)001:10833: de nas bum par khro bo'i lha /
NK027(sha)001:10834: dbus su pad+ma he ru ka sogs dmar po bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:10838: hoh bcom ldan pad+ma he ru kah sogs /
NK027(sha)001:10843: ni b+h+r+aum badz+ra a yu she dzahmh'u +aah zhes pas lha mo tsan d+ha li dkar mo phyogs bzhi /
NK027(sha)001:10845: rin chen zhags pa can 'phros pas /
NK027(sha)001:10846: tshe bsdus gtso bo dang tshe rten la thim pa bstim /
NK027(sha)001:10855: gyi khams gsum gyi tshe bsdus bstim pas bum pa'i lha rnams 'od du zhu /
NK027(sha)001:10856: bdud rtsi yi ge lnga gyur /
NK027(sha)001:10857: a yu dz+ny+aa na brjod pas /
NK027(sha)001:10862: ha dpral bar thim pas lus yig 'brur gyur /
NK027(sha)001:10863: de dag kyang mi dmigs par bsam mo //
NK027(sha)001:10866: zhag tu byed kyang de ltar bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:10868: tshe nas la 'brang rgyas zla gam byas la /
NK027(sha)001:10872: bum pa'i g.yas su mar me bzhag /
NK027(sha)001:10873: 'brang rgyas la dbus su tshe dpag med yab yum
NK027(sha)001:10874: h'u bzhi las shar du rgyal mtshan mchog dkar mo
NK027(sha)001:10876: nub tu dbang bsgyur dpal ldan ma /
NK027(sha)001:10877: dmar mo pad+ma lcags sgrog can /
NK027(sha)001:10878: byang du mi bzang mdzes ldan ma ljang ku za ma tog dril bu can bsam mo //
NK027(sha)001:10879: tsan+da d+ha li 'dzab kyi spros bsdus tshe bsrung bya /
NK027(sha)001:10882: 'gro ba yongs kyi tshe la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:10883: dkar mo mgyog ma zhi byed 'od 'phro'i tshogs //
NK027(sha)001:10884: tshe dang gzi brjid 'gugs pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)001:10885: rdo rje tshe mchog 'gugs pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK027(sha)001:10886: mgyogs ma rnams kyi tshe khug la //
NK027(sha)001:10887: byin chen rnams kyi byin phob cig /
NK027(sha)001:10888: sa ma ya de bi am gu sha dza dzahmh'u /
NK027(sha)001:10890: lho phyogs dpal dang ldan pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)001:10891: sngon mo drag shul 'od zer stong 'phro'i tshogs //
NK027(sha)001:10892: tshe dang gzi brjid rin chen tshe mchog mgyogs ma
NK027(sha)001:10893: byin chen sa ma ya d+he wi pa sha h'u
NK027(sha)001:10895: nub phyogs pad+ma r+aa ga'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)001:10896: dmar mo dbang bsgyur 'od zer 'phro'i tshogs //
NK027(sha)001:10897: tshe dang gzi brjid pad+ma tshe mchog mgyogs ma byin
NK027(sha)001:10898: chen rnams kyis sa ma ya de wi s+pho ta
NK027(sha)001:10899: bam bam / byang phyogs rnam par dag pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)001:10900: ljang ku phrin las 'od zer 'phros pa'i tshogs //
NK027(sha)001:10901: tshe dang las rab mgyogs ma rnams byin chen sa ma ya d+he wa gan+d+he ho ho /
NK027(sha)001:10902: zhes brjod cing re re zhing sngags brgya rtsa dang bstim /
NK027(sha)001:10905: pad+ma ta krid badz+ra kro ta h+ya g+h+r+ai wa hu lu hu lu dz+ny+aa na ni h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:10906: ces pas rta mgrin dmar mo g.yas ral gri g.yon zhags pa can du ma spros /
NK027(sha)001:10907: tshe bkug par bsam zhing sngags bzlos /
NK027(sha)001:10908: de nas pad+ma he ru ka'i lte ba man chad khrag mtshor nub pa zhal gsum phyag drug pa'i /
NK027(sha)001:10909: dang po gnyis na b+hud+d+ha he ru ka yab yum /
NK027(sha)001:10910: bar ma gnyis na rat+na he ru ka yab yum /
NK027(sha)001:10911: mtha' ma gnyis na karma he ru ka yab yum mo //
NK027(sha)001:10912: de nas thal mo brdab cing /
NK027(sha)001:10913: b+hud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u phatah b+hud+ha kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:10915: lha dang lha ma yin gyi tshogs bkral nas tshe bsdus /
NK027(sha)001:10916: de bzhin du rat+na li dang /
NK027(sha)001:10920: a yu dzas 'od nag por bdag gi mdun du bsdus la /
NK027(sha)001:10921: mchog phur pad+ma 'dus par bskyed la sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs /
NK027(sha)001:10922: bo d+hi tsit+ta su ka h'u /
NK027(sha)001:10924: mang du dril mas he ru ka drag po sbyor ba'i byang sems phur pa la thim /
NK027(sha)001:10925: phur pa byang sems kyi rang bzhin du dkar ltem
NK027(sha)001:10926: ltem 'dug pa btab pa 'od nag nag po de
NK027(sha)001:10927: bdud rtsir dkar ltem gyi gyur te /
NK027(sha)001:10928: a yu h'u dzas 'brang rgyas kyi tshe dpag med la bsdu'o //
NK027(sha)001:10929: de nas mtshams bshags byin dbang bya /
NK027(sha)001:10931: mi gsum gyi tshe rdzas re re btegs la /
NK027(sha)001:10933: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK027(sha)001:10934: sgrib pa'i dri ma ma lus sel //
NK027(sha)001:10935: mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sku mnga' ba //
NK027(sha)001:10936: mnyam nyid sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:10938: bum pa'i lha rnams kyis sku la /
NK027(sha)001:10941: glad pa sku rdo rje gyur par bsam zhing ka la dang /
NK027(sha)001:10942: bum pa'i mar spyi bor blug /
NK027(sha)001:10945: mchog tu rnam par dag pa'i gsung //
NK027(sha)001:10946: gsung rab dam pa yi ge med //
NK027(sha)001:10947: brjod du med cing spros bral ba //
NK027(sha)001:10948: rdo rje'i gsung la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:10953: shin tu rnam par dag pa'i thugs //
NK027(sha)001:10954: chags med ye shes gnyis mkhyen pa //
NK027(sha)001:10955: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi //
NK027(sha)001:10956: rdo rje thugs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)001:10960: thugs kyi sid+d+hi thob par bsam /
NK027(sha)001:10962: nub phyogs byams ldan dbang gi zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)001:10963: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK027(sha)001:10964: thugs kyi dpal ber zla gsang ga'u nas //
NK027(sha)001:10965: rnal 'byor byang sems a yu dmar po de //
NK027(sha)001:10966: tshe gcig dbang gi bsgrub pa'i tshe lags kyi //
NK027(sha)001:10967: byin gyis brlab cing stsal du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:10968: a yu'i sngags dang chos rdzas gsum po snying khar brten cing bstim pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:10969: smon lam zhi ba ltar bya /
NK027(sha)001:10970: de nas dbang rdzas rnams rim par thogs /
NK027(sha)001:10971: mgrin pa snying khar bcug cing /
NK027(sha)001:10972: a yu dmar po rdo rje dbang gi tshe //
NK027(sha)001:10973: gzhan gyi mi 'phrog khams gsum kun las rgyal //
NK027(sha)001:10974: rang gi byang sems gdod nas skye shi med //
NK027(sha)001:10975: mi 'gyur tshe yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)001:10976: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa gu h+ye a yu dz+ny+aa na bin du b+h+r+au /
NK027(sha)001:10977: badz+ra a yu she dz+ny+aa na swa b+h+aa wa ad+ma ko&a ha /
NK027(sha)001:10978: na mo tshe dbang du gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:10979: dbang dngos grub tu gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:10980: skye med kyi ye shes su gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:10981: 'chi rkyen bsal bas zhi khro sprul pa'i tshogs la mnga' brnyes par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:10982: ces brjod la dngos grub kyi zhal zas rnams rim par rol bar bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:10983: de'ang dngos grub kyi lhag ma gsum ya dam gyi /
NK027(sha)001:10984: skal pa bla ma dkyil 'khor lha'i /
NK027(sha)001:10985: skal pa rgyal thabs rig 'dzin rnams kyi skal pa slob ma thams cad dagye'o //
NK027(sha)001:10986: de nas dngos grub brten par bya ba'i phyir sems can don phyir nan tan mchog bskyed de /
NK027(sha)001:10987: ye shes thugs rjes bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:10988: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub dam pa rnams //
NK027(sha)001:10989: bdag la stsal zhing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:10990: ka ya waka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra zhes brjod de /
NK027(sha)001:10991: kun gyi me tog gtor ro //
NK027(sha)001:10992: de nas mar me smon lam ni /
NK027(sha)001:10993: kun gyi srin lag sbrel la /
NK027(sha)001:10994: bla mas phyag g.yon gyi mar me bzung la //
NK027(sha)001:10995: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK027(sha)001:10996: snying po byang chub lam du zhugs pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:10997: 'khor ba'i g.yang sa chen po mi lhung zhing //
NK027(sha)001:10998: chags sdang gcong rong gnas su mi skye dang //
NK027(sha)001:10999: log lta dmyal ba'i zang khar sbab mi 'dril //
NK027(sha)001:11000: 'pho 'dzin gcan gzan gdug pa'i skad mi thos //
NK027(sha)001:11001: nyon mongs mtshon rtse gdug pa'i zer mi phog /
NK027(sha)001:11002: dge ba'i bshes gnyen bka' drin che ba dang //
NK027(sha)001:11003: srog gi sbrel ba'i mched dang lcam dral dang //
NK027(sha)001:11004: gsum pa'i dbang gi 'brel ba'i rig ma gsum //
NK027(sha)001:11005: skye ba 'di dang tshe rabs thams cad du //
NK027(sha)001:11006: mi 'bral rtse gcig 'grogs pa'i ting 'dzin gyi //
NK027(sha)001:11007: sa bcu khyad par rim gyi bsgrod par shog /
NK027(sha)001:11008: nam zhig tshe 'phos lus barjesa byung dus na //
NK027(sha)001:11009: 'khor ba'i g.yang sar lan gcig gtong srid kyang //
NK027(sha)001:11010: snang ba'i go 'byed zhun mar mdang ldan 'di //
NK027(sha)001:11011: rig 'dzin bsgrub pa po yi shul mtshon cing //
NK027(sha)001:11012: kun tu 'od kyi sa la rgyud sbyangs nas //
NK027(sha)001:11013: pad+ma chen po'i sa la lhun gyis grub //
NK027(sha)001:11014: 'khor lo tshogs chen sa la gshegs pa'i tshe //
NK027(sha)001:11015: sngon gyi rgyal ba rnams kyis mdun bsus shig /
NK027(sha)001:11016: yi dam lha yi rgyab nas srog rten cig /
NK027(sha)001:11017: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi mtha' bskyor cig /
NK027(sha)001:11018: mchod pa'i lha mo rnams kyis sna drongs shig /
NK027(sha)001:11019: ma tshogs dbang mo rnams kyi rjes skyongs shig /
NK027(sha)001:11020: lcang lo can gyi sa la phyin pa'i tshe //
NK027(sha)001:11021: phyi mi ldog pa'i sa la gnas nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:11022: rdo rje khro rgyal khyod kyi zhal mthong nas //
NK027(sha)001:11023: rig 'dzin rnams dang dbyer med gyur nas ni //
NK027(sha)001:11024: bla med sku gsung thugs su 'grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:11025: de nas bla mas shar sgo nas /
NK027(sha)001:11026: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dal ru /
NK027(sha)001:11027: zla gam zhal gyi gzhal yas bzhi /
NK027(sha)001:11028: dur khrod gsang ba'i rdzas rnams bkram /
NK027(sha)001:11029: mar me ye shes kyi 'od phung /
NK027(sha)001:11031: rang bzhin lhun grub kyi sna tshogs spyan drangs /
NK027(sha)001:11032: dngos grub rnam gsum blang ba'i byin rlabs kyi /
NK027(sha)001:11033: bdag cag dpon slob mched dang lcam dral rnams /
NK027(sha)001:11034: tshe 'dir yang dag gsang ba'i longs spyod dang ldan zhing /
NK027(sha)001:11035: rdo rje tshe'i yon tan phun sum tshogs shing /
NK027(sha)001:11036: 'gro ba ma lus pa'i don byed pa'i mthu phun sum tshogs par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:11037: tshe 'phos lus barjesa kyang ting nge 'dzin gyi rgyun
NK027(sha)001:11038: dang mi bral bar 'dren pas lung ston par gyur
NK027(sha)001:11039: cig / rig 'dzin gyi go 'phang thob ste /
NK027(sha)001:11040: he ru kas srog brtan nas /
NK027(sha)001:11041: sems dpa' brgyad kyi rgyab skyor /
NK027(sha)001:11042: sems ma brgyad kyi mdun bsus /
NK027(sha)001:11047: gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes chen
NK027(sha)001:11048: pos bdag gzhan gyi don ma lus pa lhun gyis
NK027(sha)001:11050: ces brjod la snum gyis kyang snying kar byug go //
NK027(sha)001:11051: de nas zhag bcu gcig 'gro ba'i snga dro /
NK027(sha)001:11052: gong du gsang mtshan dbang de'i rting par /
NK027(sha)001:11053: a ti yo ga'i lta ba rab 'byams kyi dbang gi sngon 'gro bya ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:11054: de yang thog mar khung ni /
NK027(sha)001:11056: rnam snang dbang gi thig le dang /
NK027(sha)001:11057: g.yu thang las rgyas par gsungs shing kun 'dus che mchog sku la chos kun yongs rdzogs so //
NK027(sha)001:11058: gdan zla ba nas spyi gtsug gi sangs rgyas nyer
NK027(sha)001:11059: gcig gi rgyal mtshan tog las mtshon te ston no
NK027(sha)001:11061: des rdul tshon phyi rtag rang lus nang /
NK027(sha)001:11062: don sems nyid gsang ba gsum mo //
NK027(sha)001:11063: tha ma don ni rig pa rang byung nyid de
NK027(sha)001:11064: ltar du shar ba'i yod pas rnal 'byor bas myong
NK027(sha)001:11065: ba'o // de'i phyir slob bu rnam snang chos bdun byas la /
NK027(sha)001:11067: ngal sor gzhug lhod dkyin bzhag go //
NK027(sha)001:11069: phyi nang 'dres pa'i lus kyi snying la mngon par shes ldan gyi mthong ba'i /
NK027(sha)001:11070: sngags 'char bas bsgom du rung ba'o //
NK027(sha)001:11072: dkyil 'khor byang shar na pad+ma bcu drug 'dab ma can nam /
NK027(sha)001:11073: 'khor lo rtsib brgyad pa dkar po'i steng du nyi ma dmar po la /
NK027(sha)001:11074: lte ba a dkar po kha sbyor /
NK027(sha)001:11075: mthar a dkar bcu drug kun bzang yab yum bac+wo brgyad dang /
NK027(sha)001:11076: bla mas lung las gsung pa'i gzugs der byon pa /
NK027(sha)001:11077: bac+wo brgyad ni ngo bor dgod /
NK027(sha)001:11080: sprul sku dga' rab sdud pa po 'jam dpal bshes
NK027(sha)001:11081: gnyen dang bzhi spyi khyab bla ma sku bzhi'i ngo
NK027(sha)001:11082: bo ste / sh+r+ai sing ha dang /
NK027(sha)001:11083: bod kyi bla ma dang bcas pa la brgyud pa
NK027(sha)001:11084: kun gyi ngo bo bum pa dkar po as mtshan
NK027(sha)001:11085: pa gcig bzhugs gnas su bya /
NK027(sha)001:11086: sku 'dra tsakli dang thugs kyis gsang mtshan gdung ras dbu skra na bza' la sogs 'god /
NK027(sha)001:11087: bum rdzas blug la kun bzang yab yum sbyor ba'i byang sems su bsam /
NK027(sha)001:11089: pad bskor gyi tha mar snying dkar mar gyi shun
NK027(sha)001:11090: la rtsa ba shar gyi rtse mo nub tu bstan
NK027(sha)001:11091: pa dang / steng du rtsa rig dang rtse mo pad gdan nyi ma dang a la reg pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:11095: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum thub drug sgo ba dang bcas pas /
NK027(sha)001:11096: mu khyud nang 'ja' ris phyi 'od skor /
NK027(sha)001:11102: de nas yi dam gang byed kyang zhi ba bya /
NK027(sha)001:11103: de nas las gzhung kun bzang don gyi phrin las kyi gsal gdab la /
NK027(sha)001:11104: chos skyong rig 'dzin mkha' 'gro gzhi bdag bskangs /
NK027(sha)001:11105: dad brtson gus btud bskyed la bla ma la gsol ba drag tu gdab /
NK027(sha)001:11106: rtogs pa skye ba'i slad du sgrib sbyangs yig brgya tshogs sogs man+dala bya /
NK027(sha)001:11107: sta gon rab gnas 'jug chog byas kyang bzang /
NK027(sha)001:11108: ma byas kyang chog ste sngon 'agro'o //
NK027(sha)001:11109: dngos gzhi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:11113: dang po lta ba rab 'byams kyi dbang ni /
NK027(sha)001:11114: de la rnal 'byor man ngag nges pa'i don la
NK027(sha)001:11115: mkhas shing ye shes lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin
NK027(sha)001:11116: du gyur cing / rigs pa'i rgyal po rang dbang du gyur pa la /
NK027(sha)001:11121: gser du ma btags kyang gser du snang yang gser
NK027(sha)001:11122: srang gcig gi zangs srang brgyad gser du 'gyur ba
NK027(sha)001:11123: bzhin / bdag nyid chen mo byang chub kyi dbang
NK027(sha)001:11124: du 'gyur na dbang ma bskur yang thams cad ye
NK027(sha)001:11125: nas byang chub kyi sangs rgyas su dbang bskur zhing
NK027(sha)001:11126: bzhin / / chos thams cad ye nas lhun gyis
NK027(sha)001:11127: grub par rgyu 'bras kyi chos thams cad dbyer med
NK027(sha)001:11128: la sangs rgyas sems can gnyis su med pa ni
NK027(sha)001:11129: dbang bskur na yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin chen
NK027(sha)001:11130: la ci ltar 'dod pa 'byung ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:11131: 'dra bas ye nas yangs pa chen po'i klong las gang yang mi rtog cing /
NK027(sha)001:11132: kun tu bzang mo la cir yang mi rtogs pas lta ba ye 'byams kyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:11133: chos rnams thams cad nam mkha'i khams //
NK027(sha)001:11134: dngos po mtshan ma kun las 'das //
NK027(sha)001:11135: de la mkhas pas bcos su med //
NK027(sha)001:11136: de bzhin sems kyi rnam pa kun //
NK027(sha)001:11137: de bzhin nyid du bcos las 'das //
NK027(sha)001:11138: 'di ltar ye nas yin rtogs na //
NK027(sha)001:11139: dbang rnams bskur yang ga la dgos //
NK027(sha)001:11140: stong gsum ma bcos chos nyid klong //
NK027(sha)001:11141: srid gsum ye nas rnam par dag /
NK027(sha)001:11142: khams gsum phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs //
NK027(sha)001:11143: dug gsum bdud rtsi byang chub sems //
NK027(sha)001:11144: lus ngag yid gsum ye shes lha //
NK027(sha)001:11145: thams cad skyon med yon tan snang //
NK027(sha)001:11146: bde ba che las gzhan med pas //
NK027(sha)001:11147: chos rnams thams cad ma bskur rdzogs //
NK027(sha)001:11148: sangs rgyas sems can thams cad kyang //
NK027(sha)001:11149: rgyu dang 'bras bu la sogs pa //
NK027(sha)001:11150: gnyis su med par ye shes las //
NK027(sha)001:11151: byang chub sems su dbang bskur yin //
NK027(sha)001:11152: ming dang tshig dang yi ge dang //
NK027(sha)001:11153: theg pa'i bye brag thams cad dang //
NK027(sha)001:11154: don dam gcig pu sus shes pas //
NK027(sha)001:11155: byang chub sems kyi dbang thob yin //
NK027(sha)001:11156: bskal pa grangs dang grangs med par //
NK027(sha)001:11157: de snyed bye ba ci 'das kyang //
NK027(sha)001:11158: dus gsum 'gyur ba med shes na //
NK027(sha)001:11159: byang chub sems kyi dbang thob yin //
NK027(sha)001:11160: las dang las can la sogs pa'i //
NK027(sha)001:11161: rtsol phong bya ba ci byas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:11162: byang chub don la rtsol med pas //
NK027(sha)001:11163: sangs rgyas rnams kyi ma brtsal bshad //
NK027(sha)001:11164: nyon mongs las dang sdug bsngal dang //
NK027(sha)001:11165: dngos 'dzin rtog tshogs thams cad kyang //
NK027(sha)001:11166: pad+ma chus ni ma gos bzhin //
NK027(sha)001:11167: byang chub sems la dgos pa med //
NK027(sha)001:11168: dbang dang dam tshig de dag kyang //
NK027(sha)001:11169: de bzhin phrin las bya ba kun //
NK027(sha)001:11170: byas pa skyon med legs pa yi //
NK027(sha)001:11171: ma byas na yang byang chub sems //
NK027(sha)001:11172: phyi nyid la'ang nang nyid phyi //
NK027(sha)001:11173: snang ba thams cad rang rig shar //
NK027(sha)001:11174: brjod pa'i tshig dang yi ge med //
NK027(sha)001:11176: de bzhin ma bcos byang chub sems //
NK027(sha)001:11177: ma brtsal bzhag pas gdod nas dag /
NK027(sha)001:11178: 'gyur ba med par lhun gyis grub //
NK027(sha)001:11181: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi spyi dbang rnam par snang mdzad thig le dbang gi le'u las /
NK027(sha)001:11182: de nas dam tshig nyams pa med pa'i dbang ni /
NK027(sha)001:11183: thams cad rang gi sems yin par shes shing ye nas kun tu bzang mo sangs rgyas pa las /
NK027(sha)001:11184: phyogs ris dang che chung sgro bskur med par lung
NK027(sha)001:11185: bstan par rtogs pas dam tshig la nyams pa med
NK027(sha)001:11186: pas dbang yang ma thob pa med /
NK027(sha)001:11187: spyod pa ma spangs lhun grub kyi dbang ni /
NK027(sha)001:11188: zhes byas ci spyod 'dre log spyi tshig gang byas kyang /
NK027(sha)001:11189: snying po byang chub sems las ma gtogs pa gang du yang 'gyur ba med pas /
NK027(sha)001:11190: nam mkha' tshon gyi mi zhan bzhin du /
NK027(sha)001:11191: spyod pa ci spyod bzhin thams cad kyi mdzad spyod lhun gyis grub pa la dbang yang thob pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:11192: grub pa mthar phyin pa'i dbang ni skyon dang yon tan /
NK027(sha)001:11193: bde ba dang sdug bsngal gnyis med gcig gi rgyan du gyur te /
NK027(sha)001:11194: ci byas chud mi za bar 'khor ba nyid mya
NK027(sha)001:11195: ngan las 'das par lhun gyis grub par the tshom
NK027(sha)001:11196: med / yid ches par grub pa mthar phyin /
NK027(sha)001:11197: dbang yongs su rdzogs par thob pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:11198: phrin las bya ba rtsal med pa'i dbang ni /
NK027(sha)001:11199: ye gdod ma nas sangs rgyas min na /
NK027(sha)001:11201: ye nas sangs rgyas yin pas gser dang 'dra la /
NK027(sha)001:11202: yin pa'i don ma yengs nas sems nyid sangs rgyas yin pas /
NK027(sha)001:11203: gnas lug de'i ngang las ma g.yos na /
NK027(sha)001:11206: 'pho 'gyur med pas de'i ngang las ma yengs ba de la /
NK027(sha)001:11207: 'dzin rtogs thams cad kyang skye med klong du shes pas 'khor ba yang ma grub /
NK027(sha)001:11210: gshis thog las ma yengs shig /
NK027(sha)001:11211: des na phrin las brtsal du yang med pas dbang yang thob bo //
NK027(sha)001:11214: yod ni rang gi sems la yod /
NK027(sha)001:11215: thob ni bla ma la thob /
NK027(sha)001:11216: mthar ni ma yang nas phyin /
NK027(sha)001:11217: grub ni ma bcos na grub /
NK027(sha)001:11218: dgongs pa nyag gcig tu 'dus so //
NK027(sha)001:11219: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi spyi dbang ngo //
NK027(sha)001:11220: de nas dbang de chags pa'i rten du a ti
NK027(sha)001:11221: yo ga dang sgom chen po gsal gdab pa'i phyir
NK027(sha)001:11222: / gnyis pa sems bzung ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:11223: de'ang snying gi dkyil du thig le dkar po sgo
NK027(sha)001:11224: nga tsam zhig bsgom bzhir re re de nas 'od
NK027(sha)001:11225: zer spyi gtsug tshangs pa'i bu ga na yar skar
NK027(sha)001:11226: mda' ltar thon / thig le gcig des thig phran
NK027(sha)001:11227: bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'phro je che je che
NK027(sha)001:11228: mang la stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten
NK027(sha)001:11230: thig phran thams cad tshur 'dus thig le bzhi po la thim /
NK027(sha)001:11231: thig phran dang bzhi po gnyis su med pa sras bde ba chen po'i ngang la bzhag /
NK027(sha)001:11232: de'ang yid kyi ma bslad pa /
NK027(sha)001:11233: gsal la rtog pa med pa de ye shes chen po yin no //
NK027(sha)001:11234: de rgyun du skyong ba'i phyir /
NK027(sha)001:11236: khong klong ma yengs ba tsam gsal 'debs pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:11237: de'ang des sgeg mos me long ma bltas pa bzhin yang blta yang blta sems la blta /
NK027(sha)001:11238: spang la g.yang mo skyong ba bzhin //
NK027(sha)001:11239: yang skyong yang skyong sems la skyongs //
NK027(sha)001:11240: byis sbas skong tsha nyul ba bzhin //
NK027(sha)001:11241: yang nyul yang nyul sems la nyul //
NK027(sha)001:11243: gdams ngag g.yu thang las kyang /
NK027(sha)001:11244: rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bskur man ngag rin po che /
NK027(sha)001:11245: gser gling du phyin pa lta bu /
NK027(sha)001:11246: snang srid chos skur mthong ba ste /
NK027(sha)001:11247: nyon mongs pa blang gi blta /
NK027(sha)001:11251: 'gal rkyen thams cad las sems yongs su bcug kyin blta'o //
NK027(sha)001:11252: de yang gnyis med ye shes rang shar de lta ba /
NK027(sha)001:11253: de'ang ngang la gnas pa de sgoms pa /
NK027(sha)001:11254: de dang mi 'bral de skyong ba /
NK027(sha)001:11255: de la mi 'da' ba dam tshig gi //
NK027(sha)001:11257: tur tur dran bar bya mi dgos pa de gnang /
NK027(sha)001:11258: mtshan 'dzin 'bad rtsol rang sar grol ba srog go //
NK027(sha)001:11259: de'ang snang ba nyid na ngo bo med /
NK027(sha)001:11263: don rang gi mtshan nyid ma rtog par tshig phyir 'brang na phyi'i mtshan du shor nas /
NK027(sha)001:11264: rtog chos go yul du lus nyan yod /
NK027(sha)001:11265: gsum pa ngo sprad pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:11266: dpe don phyi nang gi dal la /
NK027(sha)001:11267: rang gi sems bla ma kun bzang yab yum /
NK027(sha)001:11272: pan chen nyi shu rtsa gcig dang rtsa rgyud bla ma'i bar du gnas /
NK027(sha)001:11273: 'khor lo longs spyod bcas pa'i rtsal du shar ba yin no //
NK027(sha)001:11274: de yang gzhi don gyi kun gzhi dang yul chos
NK027(sha)001:11275: kyi dbyings ni kun bzang rdor sems yab yum yin
NK027(sha)001:11276: no // stong pa nyid kyi ye shes so //
NK027(sha)001:11277: de yang theg dman la gsang ste dkon mchog ces pa ste /
NK027(sha)001:11278: theg chen du gzhi la sangs rgyas yod /
NK027(sha)001:11280: sngags su da lta sangs rgyas yin /
NK027(sha)001:11283: sbyor ba don gyi kun gzhi dang /
NK027(sha)001:11284: yul snod bcud rnam par snang mdzad ni me long
NK027(sha)001:11285: lta bu'i ye shes ni yid kyi rnam shes dang
NK027(sha)001:11286: / yul chos rin chen 'byung ldan mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes /
NK027(sha)001:11287: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid dang yul lnga bdag /
NK027(sha)001:11288: 'od dpag med ni so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes sgo lnga'i rnam shes dang /
NK027(sha)001:11289: yul gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya don grub ni bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK027(sha)001:11294: lus sgo bzhi dbyings su sgrol ba'i ye shes kun gzhi 'da' ka thugs kyi ye shes /
NK027(sha)001:11295: yid stong pa nyid mi gnas khyab pa'i ye shes /
NK027(sha)001:11296: nyon yid klong du gyur pa'i ye shes te /
NK027(sha)001:11298: snang ba chos nyid ye shes dang /
NK027(sha)001:11299: rig pa rang byung ye shes gnyis dbus kyi rtsa mdud /
NK027(sha)001:11300: de las ye shes bzhi'i rtsa /
NK027(sha)001:11302: mdun rgyab la re re brgyad la /
NK027(sha)001:11303: phyogs bzhir bzhi ldan gyi dga' ba /
NK027(sha)001:11304: bcu drug rtsa 'dab phyi rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK027(sha)001:11305: nang lus kyis snying rtsa dang /
NK027(sha)001:11306: gsang ba sems kyi de kho na nyid bla ma'i thugs kyi dkyil 'khor las bstan pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:11307: bzhi pa la bzla pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:11308: dmar thag bcad pa rdo rje sems dpa'i gter bshags bya ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:11310: chos nyid ma bcos don nyid ma shes na //
NK027(sha)001:11311: ji ltar brtag pas sdug bsngal nyid du 'gyur //
NK027(sha)001:11312: lta ba kun tu bzang la mthol bshags na //
NK027(sha)001:11313: rnam dag gtor ma'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:11314: sems nyid ma yeng don nyid ma shes na //
NK027(sha)001:11315: ci ltar sgom kyang sdug bsngal nyid du 'gyur //
NK027(sha)001:11316: ting 'dzin kun tu bzang la mthol bshags na //
NK027(sha)001:11317: rnam shes gtor ma'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:11318: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub par ma shes na //
NK027(sha)001:11319: ci ltar bsgrub kyang sdug bsngal nyid du 'gyur //
NK027(sha)001:11320: phrin las kun tu bzang la mthol bshags na //
NK027(sha)001:11321: srog dbug gtor ma'i mchod pa phung po rgyal ba'i sku ru ma shes na //
NK027(sha)001:11322: ci ltar bskyed pas sdug bsngal nyid du 'gyur //
NK027(sha)001:11323: rang bzhin kun tu bzang la mthol bshags na //
NK027(sha)001:11324: 'byung ba gtor ma'i gzung ma shes rab nyid du ma shes na //
NK027(sha)001:11325: ci ltar spyad kyang sdug bsngal dam tshig kun tu bzang la mthol bshags na //
NK027(sha)001:11326: thig le gtor ma'i mchod pa rang byung gdod nas dag par ma shes na //
NK027(sha)001:11327: ci ltar brtsal yang sdug bsngal nyid du 'gyur //
NK027(sha)001:11328: rnam dag kun tu bzang la mthol bshags na //
NK027(sha)001:11329: sha khrag gtor ma'i longs spyod sgyu ma yin par ma shes na //
NK027(sha)001:11330: ji ltar bsags kyang sdug bsngal spyod pa kun tu bzang la mthol bshags na //
NK027(sha)001:11331: yo byad gtor ma'i phyi nang snod bcud gtor ma rab bsdus nas //
NK027(sha)001:11332: thugs rje sprul pa'i gtor mar rab sprul te //
NK027(sha)001:11333: ye shes rol pa'i gtor mar 'bul lags kyi //
NK027(sha)001:11334: chos nyid dbyings kyi gtor mar bzhes su gsol //
NK027(sha)001:11336: rig 'dzin gyi dgongs nyams bskur ba'i glur blang /
NK027(sha)001:11338: bla mas gtso bum bzung la /
NK027(sha)001:11340: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i dbang yin pas //
NK027(sha)001:11341: rdzas dang tshig dang gdam ngag dang //
NK027(sha)001:11342: kun rdzob rang la rag ma lus //
NK027(sha)001:11343: chos la sems kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:11345: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas rnams kyi byin gyis brlabs kyi /
NK027(sha)001:11346: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bos dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:11347: don dam rtsol med rtsal rdzogs kyi dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:11348: chos nyid dngos po med pa'i ye stong 'di //
NK027(sha)001:11349: lta ba 'di dang mi 'bral 'grogs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:11350: chos nyid nyams myong med pa'i bde stong 'di //
NK027(sha)001:11351: bsgom pa 'di dang mi 'bral 'grogs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:11352: sems nyid bcos pa med pa'i rang stong 'di //
NK027(sha)001:11353: spyod pa 'di dang mi 'bral 'grogs par shog /
NK027(sha)001:11354: chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa'i blo 'das 'di //
NK027(sha)001:11355: 'bras bu 'di dang mi ci ltar smon pa'i 'bras bu 'grub par shog /
NK027(sha)001:11356: smon lam gyi mthu btsan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:11357: de kho na nyid kyi don la gnas par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:11359: mgo bo nyid kar rig pa bstim /
NK027(sha)001:11360: bum chus khrus bya btud do //
NK027(sha)001:11361: de nas slob ma rnams mos gus dang ba chen po rtse gcig pas /
NK027(sha)001:11362: rje chos kyi sku la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK027(sha)001:11363: rje longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK027(sha)001:11364: rje sprul pa'i sku la skyabs bla ma sangs rgyas rin po che la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK027(sha)001:11366: phatah byas la sa le hrig ge rang sar bzhag go //
NK027(sha)001:11368: gdon ma zhugs pa'i smyon pa lta bu shes bya cig chos nyid kyi nyams 'char ro //
NK027(sha)001:11370: gang gi gang la gang 'du gang bsten pa /
NK027(sha)001:11371: cis phyir dgos pa mchog tu ye gnas pa //
NK027(sha)001:11372: 'dis ni nang gi 'gag drug bstan pa yin //
NK027(sha)001:11374: gang gi bskur ba'i slob dpon ni /
NK027(sha)001:11375: chos sku kun tu bzang mo nas rtsa ba'i bla ma'i bar /
NK027(sha)001:11376: dbang byin rlabs kyi brgyud pa dngos grub dang ldan pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:11377: gang gi bskur ba'i slob ma ni /
NK027(sha)001:11378: skal ldan dad brtson brtul bzhugs pa dang ldan pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:11379: gang bsten pa'i chos rnams ni rig pa rtsal gyi dbang ngo //
NK027(sha)001:11380: gang du bskur ba'i gnas ni /
NK027(sha)001:11383: rang la yod pa'i chos nyid kyi don de ngo shes gsal gdab pa'i ched du'o //
NK027(sha)001:11386: yi ge 'khor lo ye shes bla ma'i bar gyur gyis thams bcad dus gcig tu bsgrod do //
NK027(sha)001:11387: gcig shes kun grol lta ba'i klong zhes bya ba'o //
NK027(sha)001:11388: de nas nam lang pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:11389: dal bsdu las bzhi'i bro bya ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:11392: b+hud+d+ha kro ti shwa ri h'u ha he phata /
NK027(sha)001:11395: gti mug rdo rje 'khor bcas kyi //
NK027(sha)001:11397: yud tsam gyi ni zhi mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)001:11398: zhi ba'i las rnams grub par mdzad //
NK027(sha)001:11401: a na ya ho b+ha ga wan b+hi ya ra tsa h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:11402: hoh bcom ldan 'das b+hud+d+ha he ru ka 'khor dang
NK027(sha)001:11403: bcas pa'i lha tshogs la phrin las su snyan du
NK027(sha)001:11404: gsol ba ni / bdag cag rnams kyi sdang ba'i dgra dang /
NK027(sha)001:11405: gnod pa'i bgegs dang ya ma dam sri la sogs
NK027(sha)001:11406: pa las dang nyon mongs pa thams cad zhi bar
NK027(sha)001:11407: mdzad du gsol / shin+tanga ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:11408: ma b+h+r+aum b+hi sha b+hi shud+d+he rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK027(sha)001:11409: rat+na kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK027(sha)001:11413: nga rgyal rdo rje 'khor bcas kyi //
NK027(sha)001:11415: dpal dang gzi brjid chen po rnams //
NK027(sha)001:11416: yud tsam gyi ni rgyas par mdzod //
NK027(sha)001:11418: hoh bcom ldan 'das rat+na he ru ka 'khor dang
NK027(sha)001:11419: bcas pa'i lha tshogs rnams la phrin las snyan du
NK027(sha)001:11420: gsol ba ni / rnal 'byor pa bdag cag rnams
NK027(sha)001:11421: kyi tshe dang bsod nams dpal dang gzi brjid chen
NK027(sha)001:11422: po rnams zla ba yar gyi ngo bzhin du 'phel
NK027(sha)001:11423: zhing rgyas pa'i phrin las mdzad du gsol /
NK027(sha)001:11424: push+tinga ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:11425: bam b+h+r+au bi sha bi shud+d+he pad+ma he ru ka pad+ma kro ti shwa ri h'u ha he phata /
NK027(sha)001:11428: 'jig rten thams cad dbang du bsdus nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:11429: dbang du ma gyur gang yang med //
NK027(sha)001:11430: sum b+ha hoh bcom ldan 'das pad+ma he ru ka
NK027(sha)001:11431: 'khor dang bcas pa'i lha tshogs rnams la phrin las
NK027(sha)001:11433: bdag cag rnams la mi phan pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:11434: mi mdza' ba la sogs thams cad 'du bar mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:11435: pa shang ma na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)001:11436: e b+h+r+au bi sha b+hi shud+d+he badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru
NK027(sha)001:11437: ka badz+ra kro ti shwa ri h'u ha he phata
NK027(sha)001:11440: zhe sdang rdo rje 'khor bcas kyi //
NK027(sha)001:11441: 'jig rten thal ba rdul du brlag nas kyang //
NK027(sha)001:11442: drag po'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK027(sha)001:11444: hoh bcom ldan 'das badz+ra he ru ka 'khor dang
NK027(sha)001:11445: bcas pa rnams la phrin las su bcol ba ni
NK027(sha)001:11446: / bdag cag rnams la sdang ba'i dgra /
NK027(sha)001:11448: bsam sbyor ngan pa byed pa rnams thal ba bzhin du brlag pa'i phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)001:11449: sum b+ha ni 'gres so ra sha ma ra ya h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:11453: badz+ra ma h+aa kro ta sh+r+ai he ru ka a a +aa h'u phata /
NK027(sha)001:11454: hoh bcom ldan 'das dpal he ru ka'i 'khor nag
NK027(sha)001:11455: mo chen mo bzhin mi sdug pa'i bu mo chen
NK027(sha)001:11456: mo bzhi zhing bcu rdul du rlog /
NK027(sha)001:11459: dngos grub ma lus stsal du gsol /
NK027(sha)001:11461: rgyal ba mchod pas mnyes gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:11462: dam can thugs dam bskang gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:11463: pha ma la sogs 'gro drug la //
NK027(sha)001:11464: tshad med gtor ma 'di bsngosa pas //
NK027(sha)001:11465: longs spyod ldan zhing tshogs rdzogs nas //
NK027(sha)001:11466: thams cad sangs rgyas myur thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:11467: de nas nang du 'ong la dug gsum sbyin sreg bya /
NK027(sha)001:11468: dngos grub gter sba ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:11469: dal rtsar dang po zlums brus la dmar ser byug /
NK027(sha)001:11470: sman raka gi chag chag gdab /
NK027(sha)001:11471: b+h+r+au las gzhan yas su dmigs la /
NK027(sha)001:11473: sa yi lha mo'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK027(sha)001:11474: khrag 'thung rigs lnga'i gter sbed do //
NK027(sha)001:11475: bdud rtsi lnga yi gter sbas pas //
NK027(sha)001:11476: he ru ka yi mdun bsus nas //
NK027(sha)001:11477: ye shes lnga yi don rtogs shog /
NK027(sha)001:11478: ye shes lnga'i rgyas gdab bo //
NK027(sha)001:11480: sa yi lha mo'i dbyings phyug lnga'i gter sbed do //
NK027(sha)001:11481: sha khrag rus pa'i gter sbas pas //
NK027(sha)001:11482: yum chen lnga yi mdun bsus nas //
NK027(sha)001:11483: gsang ba'i mdzod dang 'phrod par shog /
NK027(sha)001:11484: skye med dbyings kyi rgyas gdab bo //
NK027(sha)001:11485: sa'i lha mo'i khro mo brgyad kyi gter sbed do //
NK027(sha)001:11486: rnam shes brgyad kyi gter sbas pas //
NK027(sha)001:11487: ma mo brgyad kyi mdun bsus nas //
NK027(sha)001:11488: gsang ba'i rdzas dang 'phrad par shog /
NK027(sha)001:11489: sa yi lha mo'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK027(sha)001:11490: phra men brgyad kyi gter sbed do //
NK027(sha)001:11491: gsang ba'i dam rdzas gter sbas pas //
NK027(sha)001:11492: mgo brnyan brgyad kyi mdun bsus nas //
NK027(sha)001:11494: rang rig ye shes rgyas gdab bo //
NK027(sha)001:11495: sa'i lha mo sgo ma bzhi yi gter sbed do //
NK027(sha)001:11496: rnam pa bzhi'i gter sbas pas //
NK027(sha)001:11497: khro mo bzhi'i mdun bsus nas //
NK027(sha)001:11498: bdud bzhi 'jigs las thar bar shog /
NK027(sha)001:11499: rig pa ye shes rgyas gdab bo //
NK027(sha)001:11500: sa'i lha mo'i dbang phyug chen po'i gter sbed do //
NK027(sha)001:11501: dam tshig bdud rtsi'i gter sbas pas //
NK027(sha)001:11502: dam can rnams kyi mdun bsus nas //
NK027(sha)001:11503: bdud rtsi zas dang 'phrad par shog /
NK027(sha)001:11504: rang rig ye shes rgyas gdab bo //
NK027(sha)001:11505: sa'i lha mo'i khro bo bcu'i gter sbed do //
NK027(sha)001:11506: dam rdzas rus pa'i gter sbas pas //
NK027(sha)001:11507: khrag 'thung rnams kyis mdun bsus nas //
NK027(sha)001:11508: rdo rje'i gral dang 'phrad par shog /
NK027(sha)001:11509: rang rig ye shes rgyas rdo rje slob dpon mched lcam gyi //
NK027(sha)001:11510: dam rdzas gtor ma gter sbas pas //
NK027(sha)001:11511: zag med gter la longs spyod cing //
NK027(sha)001:11512: gsang ba'i dal dang dngos grub rnams //
NK027(sha)001:11513: 'dod yon lnga yi longs spyod kyi //
NK027(sha)001:11516: de nas phyi rol tho'i rtsar /
NK027(sha)001:11517: dkar gtor cha bzhi bshams la /
NK027(sha)001:11519: gtor ma dang mchod pa lnga sngags kyi 'bul la /
NK027(sha)001:11520: ri rgyal lhun po'i tshan bzhis bstod cing /
NK027(sha)001:11521: a hi gats+tshasa gshegs su gsol /
NK027(sha)001:11523: mtshams phur dang ye shes lnga'i sgo byang la sku khrus gsol la /
NK027(sha)001:11524: dben par bzhugs su gsol bar chad bgegs kyi sgo byang /
NK027(sha)001:11526: dar gyi cod pan gcig tu bdud rtsi 'khyil bar bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:11527: sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs la dkyil 'khor gyi 'og tu bcug la phur pa de btag /
NK027(sha)001:11528: bdud rtsi thig gcig blug nas byang chub kyi sems
NK027(sha)001:11529: ma skyes kyi bar du mi thar bar bsam mo
NK027(sha)001:11530: // de las rjes bkra shis par 'gyur ro //
NK027(sha)001:11534: mdo dbang rgyal chen rgyal mtsho lta bu las /
NK027(sha)001:11535: bdag blo'i rnam dpyod dang mchu lta bu'i blo sa 'thor zhing du mar snang ba'i las khrig rnams /
NK027(sha)001:11536: gcig tu sdeb pa'i dbang mchog rin chen phreng //
NK027(sha)001:11537: dgyes pa'i dge ba gang thob bsod nams kyi //
NK027(sha)001:11538: khams gsum 'gro kun rdo rje 'dzin thob shog /
NK027(sha)001:11539: ces pa mdo'i dbang chog rgya che zhing du mar snang yang /
NK027(sha)001:11540: phyag len cung zhig mi 'dra ba 'dug na yang /
NK027(sha)001:11541: 'di ni zur ham shakya 'byung gnas kyi de rnams
NK027(sha)001:11542: kyi nang nas cho ga dbang bskur gyi phyag len
NK027(sha)001:11543: mang du mdzad pa mthong ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:11544: yang de nyid kyi khyod kyi mdo dbang chog khrid bde ka 'di ltar gyis gsungs pa'i bka' dang /
NK027(sha)001:11545: bdag blos rnam dpyod kyi kyu ru lugs su bstas
NK027(sha)001:11546: pas chog pa'i dbang chog rin chen phreng ba ces
NK027(sha)001:11547: bya ba 'di / chos smra ba'i dge sbyongs /
NK027(sha)001:11548: dmyal ba bde legs pa zhes bya bas /
NK027(sha)001:11549: zur thams cad mkhyen pa'i phyag len ci lta ba bzhin du /
NK027(sha)001:11550: g.yas ru yang dben du grub pa rdzogs so //
NK027(sha)001:11553: mdo rgyud man ngag chu gter chen po las //
NK027(sha)001:11554: bde legs rnam dpyod dri bzhom gyi bsrub pas //
NK027(sha)001:11555: dbang chog don gsal rin chen phreng mdzes 'khrungs //
NK027(sha)001:11556: rang gzhan bsgrub mchog skyes bu 'gul rgyan mdzod //
NK027(sha)001:11557: ces kyang byas te g.yas ru tsha la sgong gi
NK027(sha)001:11558: dgong du sprang 'khyam dkon 'bum gyi zhal bshos su
NK027(sha)001:11559: bsgrub pa yin / smin drug zla ba'o //
NK027(sha)001:11562: // // mdo dbang sa bcad bdun yod /
NK027(sha)001:11565: mdo'i theg pa yangs rdzogs kyi dbang 'di la /
NK027(sha)001:11568: phreng ba'i lugs su bskur ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:11569: yongs rdzogs lugs su bskur ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:11570: khyad par lugs su bskur ba'o //
NK027(sha)001:11571: dang po phreng ba'i lugs su bskur ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:11573: lha mi mi 'khrugs kun rig gi /
NK027(sha)001:11576: shwakya thub kyi gtso byas pa'i dkyil 'khor lnga /
NK027(sha)001:11577: nyan thos la thub pa la 'khor rnam bzhis bskur ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:11578: zung bzhi ya brgyad kyi bskur ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:11579: gnas brtan bcu drug gis bskur ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:11580: mchog bcu drug gis bskur ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:11581: mchog gnyis kyis bskur ba ste dkyil 'khor lnga /
NK027(sha)001:11583: thub pa la rang rgyal bcu gnyis kyis bskur ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:11584: gcig pa bswe ru lta bu dang /
NK027(sha)001:11585: khyung ldeng ne tso lta bu tshogs spyod che chung
NK027(sha)001:11586: gnyis bar ma gsum du byed pa'i 'dod tshul te
NK027(sha)001:11588: gtso bo la 'khor bse ru ne tso gnyis su bskur ba'i lugs dang lnga /
NK027(sha)001:11594: lha brgya ma ste lnga las /
NK027(sha)001:11595: sems tsam lugs thub pa gtsor byed pa lnga /
NK027(sha)001:11596: dbu ma lugs yum chen mo gtso byed pa dang lnga ste bcu /
NK027(sha)001:11597: mtshan nyid sde gsum lha mi dang bcas pa la nyer lnga /
NK027(sha)001:11600: spyir bsdus lnga gsum bco lnga ma /
NK027(sha)001:11601: de bzhin gshegs pa la drug gi gtso bo byas pa la dkyil 'khor bcu gcig /
NK027(sha)001:11603: yo ga rdo rje dbyings la gcig ste /
NK027(sha)001:11605: ma h+aa la zhi ba zhal gcig ma lha zhe gnyis ma dang /
NK027(sha)001:11607: lha gya gnyis ma rgyas pa'i lugs dang /
NK027(sha)001:11608: khro bo tshogs chen yongs rdzogs su bskor ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:11610: a nu la zhi ba rigs lnga kun bzang zhal gsum yum dang /
NK027(sha)001:11612: lha zhe gnyis bskur ba'i lugs dang /
NK027(sha)001:11614: rigs lnga yab yum zhal gsum ma las mi bskur ba'i lugs dang /
NK027(sha)001:11615: kun bzang zhal gsum yab yum dang /
NK027(sha)001:11616: rigs lnga zhal gsum yab yum la /
NK027(sha)001:11617: rigs lnga chung bzhi bcus bskor ba'i lugs dang /
NK027(sha)001:11618: khro bo tshogs chen rgyud lung gi khro bo yab yum nyi shu rtsa gnyis kyi bskur nas /
NK027(sha)001:11620: ma mo drug cu yan chad /
NK027(sha)001:11621: dam can rgya mtsho lhag sdud du bskur ba'i lugs dang /
NK027(sha)001:11622: rigs ni kun bzang nas jo bo sangs rgyas yan la brgya rtsa brgyad /
NK027(sha)001:11624: rang gi rtsa ba'i bla ma'i bar dang bcas pa dus gcig bskur ba'i lugs dang /
NK027(sha)001:11627: rig 'dzin slob dpon dang dgu'i gtso bo yab yum re re dang /
NK027(sha)001:11628: rin chen gyi slob dpon re bsgrub pa'i dam rdzas res dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:11629: bka' brgyad spyi dbang thams cad mdo'i thog nas thob pa'i lugs dang /
NK027(sha)001:11630: rgyud lung man ngag so so dbang gi rjes su /
NK027(sha)001:11631: so so'i rig 'dzin bskur ba'i lugs dang /
NK027(sha)001:11632: tshe'i dkyil 'khor du tshe dpag med la yum lha mo nyi shus bskur ba'i lugs dang /
NK027(sha)001:11634: gsang dbang gsum du phye ba'i lha zhi khro mdo lugs la /
NK027(sha)001:11635: cho ga dbang chog sgyu 'phrul kho na ltar bskur ba'i lugs dang /
NK027(sha)001:11637: rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bskur ba'i lugs dang /
NK027(sha)001:11639: mtshams bcad nas rgyun ma chad par zhag re re'i
NK027(sha)001:11640: bar bya ste long dang ldan pa la bskur ba
NK027(sha)001:11641: ni / rkyang pa'i lugs zhes bya ste /
NK027(sha)001:11642: dbang skas rang ma yeng zer /
NK027(sha)001:11643: phreng ba'i dbang gi bskur lugs zer ba yin no //
NK027(sha)001:11644: 'di ni bla ma bsam 'grub rdo rje ba /
NK027(sha)001:11647: gro yon tan sangs rgyas grags dang /
NK027(sha)001:11649: lha'i bka' lung thob phyag len mthong dbang ljag gtad
NK027(sha)001:11650: brgya thob cing theg dgu'i tshig don la mkhas pa'i
NK027(sha)001:11651: zur dbang sh+aakya 'byung gnas kyi phyag len rgyas pa
NK027(sha)001:11652: gcig yin la / gnyis pa yongs rdzogs su bskur ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:11653: sde tshan du bskur ba zhes bya ste /
NK027(sha)001:11656: lha mi dang mtshan nyid sde gsum zhag gcig la bskur /
NK027(sha)001:11657: kri ya yo ga zhag gcig la bskur /
NK027(sha)001:11660: bsgub pa gsum la zhag re re /
NK027(sha)001:11661: nang dbang bsgrub dbang gnyis la zhag re re ste /
NK027(sha)001:11663: de rjes dbang bsdus pa ru phab bdud rtsi la brten te bskur nas /
NK027(sha)001:11664: a ti glu bco brgyad kyi bum dbang bskur ba la zhag gcig ste /
NK027(sha)001:11665: zhag nges pa can bcu gcig la rdzogs par byed pa 'di ni /
NK027(sha)001:11666: glan bsod nams mgon po'i dbang bya ji bzhin pa ste /
NK027(sha)001:11667: bla ma bsam 'grub rdo rje'i phyag len rgyas par bskur ba kho na'i lugs yin la /
NK027(sha)001:11668: 'di ni zur pa'i lugs zhes bya'o //
NK027(sha)001:11669: gsum pa mdo khyad par du bskur ba'i lugs ni /
NK027(sha)001:11670: bdag don du gsal nas bsgrub pa dngos grub tu blang ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:11671: gzhan don du slob ma la a nu gcig chod bsgrag ste /
NK027(sha)001:11673: dang po ni rgyud kun 'dus la brten te /
NK027(sha)001:11674: khog yang dag bsgrub pas byas nas /
NK027(sha)001:11675: lha gtso bo che mchog yab yum la dam tshig
NK027(sha)001:11676: yab yum la sogs he ru ka yab yum drug
NK027(sha)001:11680: dam can rgyal mtsho'i bskor ba cig char du bsgom na /
NK027(sha)001:11681: dgu gzhugs dbang brlabs la sogs mi byed /
NK027(sha)001:11684: dam rdzas nang mchod gsum dang /
NK027(sha)001:11685: ma mer thod sku tshe rdzas la sogs gang 'byor la /
NK027(sha)001:11686: 'khor bcas kyi bcud bsdus par bsam la /
NK027(sha)001:11687: yang dag bzhin dngos blang rol /
NK027(sha)001:11688: bsdu bstims brtan por byas pas ye yin gyi don mngon du gyur bsam pa ni /
NK027(sha)001:11689: bla ma'i snyan rgyud zab don /
NK027(sha)001:11692: mdo lung rgyud pa'i gsol 'debs re yi dam byed dgos gsungs /
NK027(sha)001:11694: lha snying po'i gsal byed bla mas mdzad pa'i dbang gi rgyab yig gi bshams na /
NK027(sha)001:11695: gsang dbang skabs kyi dkyil 'khor lus rdzogs pa'i skabs nas gsal bar bdag go //
NK027(sha)001:11696: 'di ni 'chi ba dga' rab rdo rje'i lugs /
NK027(sha)001:11697: zur hang rin chen la gnang pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:11698: gnyis pa slob ma dbang du bskur ba ni /
NK027(sha)001:11699: sa chog sta gon zhag re re /
NK027(sha)001:11700: dkyil 'khor tshogs chen zhi khro brtsegs ma /
NK027(sha)001:11701: bsgrub brgyad theg brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor mtshon byed dang bcas pa des bskor ba bzhengs la /
NK027(sha)001:11711: las bzhi sbyin bsreg skabs bzhin 'bul /
NK027(sha)001:11712: phrin las rgyud lung brdeb pa zhi khro la gtsor byas /
NK027(sha)001:11713: dril 'adz+raba a li ka li dang /
NK027(sha)001:11714: g+hu h+ya dz+wa na chang mi chag pa bya /
NK027(sha)001:11715: bsgrub khrid rnams gong gi zhag bcu gcig mi tshogs chen dang khyad med /
NK027(sha)001:11716: dbang la nang dbang gi skabs su phyag rgya'i dbang la /
NK027(sha)001:11717: rigs lnga yab yum zhag gcig mas bskor /
NK027(sha)001:11718: 'khor mi bskur bsgrub dbang skabs kyi phyag rgya'i dbang la /
NK027(sha)001:11719: kun bzang rigs lnga yab yum zhal gsum pa la /
NK027(sha)001:11720: 'khor zhal gcig zhe gnyis ma'i tshul du bskur /
NK027(sha)001:11721: khro bo ni gtso bor thams cad rgyab yig bzhin du thams cad so sor tshang bar bskur /
NK027(sha)001:11722: rig 'dzin thams cad kyang dus gcig bskur /
NK027(sha)001:11723: bka' brgyad kyi bsgrub pa'i gtso bo dang dam rdzas sbyin pa 'dra /
NK027(sha)001:11724: zhor la theg brgyad kyi gtso bo'i tsakli rang sa'i rtsa sngags kyis bskur nas /
NK027(sha)001:11725: theg pa 'di zhes bya ba'i dbang yongs su rdzogs par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)001:11727: gsang dbang dang a ti gong dang khyad med /
NK027(sha)001:11729: gyang khang ba'i zhal gdams dang /
NK027(sha)001:11730: gro ston pa'i yig cha snying ma las byung ste gong ma gnyis kyi lung dang mi ldan pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:11731: theg pa so so ma mos pas 'brel 'jig 'dod kyang /
NK027(sha)001:11733: a nu rang la mos pa rnams kyang ched du bre khog nas phul 'don pa'am /
NK027(sha)001:11734: nam mkha'i klong nas 'byung ba tshang bar dbang bskur ba lta bu yin gsungs te /
NK027(sha)001:11735: sbrag ma'i lugs su dbang bskur ba rin chen sh+aakya 'byung gnas pa'i lugs so //
NK027(sha)001:11737: sngon 'gro bsod nams kyi dpung bskyed nas /
NK027(sha)001:11738: sa spyang ba yan zhag gcig /
NK027(sha)001:11739: spyi'i sta gon la zhag gcig /
NK027(sha)001:11740: de rjes phyag rdor sgo 'byed zhag gcig /
NK027(sha)001:11741: lha mi dbus su pad 'dab bzhi ster ba dang bcas pa la /
NK027(sha)001:11742: gtso bo lngar 'khor gcig tu dril ba'i dbang zhag gcig /
NK027(sha)001:11744: dbus su gtso bo pad 'dab bzhi /
NK027(sha)001:11746: pad 'dab bcu drug mgyogs dang gnas brten cag sa
NK027(sha)001:11747: mar bkod pa'i dbang la zhag gcig rang rgyal gtso
NK027(sha)001:11749: 'khor bse ru khyung lding gnyis dang nas 'dra bcu
NK027(sha)001:11750: gnyis la rang rgyal bcu gnyis dgod pa'i dbang dang
NK027(sha)001:11759: mgrin gyi lha dang bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor du dbang
NK027(sha)001:11760: bskur ba la zhag gcig kri ya lnga gsum bco
NK027(sha)001:11762: u pa ya thun mong bskur ba zhig dbang dang zhag gcig /
NK027(sha)001:11763: yo ga rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang
NK027(sha)001:11764: bskur ba zhag gcig ma h+aa a nu dril ba'i
NK027(sha)001:11765: zhag lnga gong dang 'dra ba las /
NK027(sha)001:11766: nang dbang gi lha dbang skabs su /
NK027(sha)001:11767: zhi lha zhe gnyis zhag gcig ma rgyab yig ltar bskur ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:11768: khro bo tshogs chen yongs rdzogs su bskur ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:11769: bsgrub dbang skabs su lha dbang la /
NK027(sha)001:11771: rigs lnga zhal gsum ma yum dang bcas pa bskur nas /
NK027(sha)001:11773: rgyud lung gi khro bo yab yum so sor bskur /
NK027(sha)001:11774: 'khor rnams spam ste lhag sdud du dbang bskur /
NK027(sha)001:11775: rig 'dzin rnams kyi sbam la bskur /
NK027(sha)001:11776: zhag gcig bsgrub pa'i gtso bo dang /
NK027(sha)001:11777: bsgrub rdzas rnams mdor khyar dang 'dra /
NK027(sha)001:11778: gsang dbang lag gnyis su yod pa'i /
NK027(sha)001:11779: gsang ram la gnas skabs phan bde bsgrub pa'i tshe dbang dang /
NK027(sha)001:11780: mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi sras su bsgrub pa'i gsung
NK027(sha)001:11781: shed dang gnyis rtsag ste bskur ba 'dir gnyis gcig
NK027(sha)001:11782: tu bsgrangs / gnyis pa bde ba chen po'i dbang la a ti bum dbang glu /
NK027(sha)001:11783: bco brgyad dang bcas pa bskur bas /
NK027(sha)001:11784: theg dgu'i 'dod gzhung thams cad rdzogs chen du la bzla bas mdzad /
NK027(sha)001:11785: gtad rgya dang bsgrog nas zhag gcig /
NK027(sha)001:11786: gnas bsrung gtang rag mchod pa dang bcas pa zhag gcig gtad rgya mi byed na zhag bcu gnyis /
NK027(sha)001:11787: byed na bac+wo brgyad du nges pa can /
NK027(sha)001:11788: 'di ni rin po sh+aaka 'byung bas lugs thams cad mdzad na'ang mdo'i dbang phud mdzad dus /
NK027(sha)001:11789: bla ma yi dam zhal gzigs kyis dus kyis gshis lam yin pas /
NK027(sha)001:11790: phyi'i bstan pa'i rim gro la phan cing 'phrod par byung gsungs /
NK027(sha)001:11791: 'di la zhi lha zhe gnyis pa nang dbang du bskur nas /
NK027(sha)001:11792: bsgrub dbang du khro bo gtso bsdus su 'di ma spros /
NK027(sha)001:11794: a ti ltar spros bral du ngo sprod pa'i bskur lug yin gsungs /
NK027(sha)001:11796: zhi khro rigs lnga gtso bsdu las ma'i bskur bar /
NK027(sha)001:11797: bsgrub dbang zhi khro lnga brgya brgyad cu gya gsum du bskor ba 'di /
NK027(sha)001:11802: rtog pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa /
NK027(sha)001:11803: lha grangs mdog ma nges pa /
NK027(sha)001:11804: 'khor lo tshogs chen du mngon du gyur par byed pa /
NK027(sha)001:11805: mdog lung gi dgong bzhed yin pas gcig tu shes
NK027(sha)001:11806: nas du mar nyams su blang bya ba yin gsung
NK027(sha)001:11807: / gsum pa bsdus pa zab don bka' rgya ma'i nyams len ni /
NK027(sha)001:11808: bdag don shin tu spros med du nyams su len pa'am /
NK027(sha)001:11809: gang zag spros med theg pa don ril du nyams su len pa la bskur nas /
NK027(sha)001:11811: a h'u ma'i rgyud nas 'byung ba bzhin /
NK027(sha)001:11814: 'bru gsum zhag nyer gcig bsnyen bsgrub bya /
NK027(sha)001:11817: zhag gnyis la b+hi ma lu'i bsnyen pa byas pa gcig gis slob ma la dbang bskur na /
NK027(sha)001:11820: mar me dgu dgu pa dang rnams lnga bshams /
NK027(sha)001:11821: yig 'bru dgu la theg dgu'i gtso bo rig par snang las bskyed /
NK027(sha)001:11825: slob bu rdor sems su bskyed pa'am /
NK027(sha)001:11826: rgyab yig nas 'thung ba'i gnas so sor /
NK027(sha)001:11828: de dag la 'od 'phros dkyil 'khor dang bum pa la phog /
NK027(sha)001:11830: yig 'bru dang dbyer med du gyur pas /
NK027(sha)001:11831: theg pa so so'i 'bras bu rim pa thob nas /
NK027(sha)001:11832: mthar thug rigs kyi bdag por gro bar bsam la /
NK027(sha)001:11833: lha zhu ba'i nus ldan gyi bum pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:11834: byin gyis brlab pa'i rdzas dbang tsaka li dgus rim sbyor bar bskur ro //
NK027(sha)001:11836: dmigs pa rang sa'i gnas su gtad /
NK027(sha)001:11839: theg dgu'i ched 'dzin rang sar grol ba'i /
NK027(sha)001:11841: a 'a ha sha sa ma ya /
NK027(sha)001:11847: des zhal zur ham sh+aakya 'byung gnas kyi 'ug pa lung lo sgrub skabs su gzigs dus /
NK027(sha)001:11848: rdo rje sems dpa' snying gi me long gi /
NK027(sha)001:11849: rgyud bzhin theg dgu gdon 'grel du nyams su long gsungs pa la brten nas /
NK027(sha)001:11850: blo spros pa can lam ston pa'i bka' rgya /
NK027(sha)001:11851: spros chung la ston pa'i spel rgya /
NK027(sha)001:11852: the tshom la gsung rgya dam rgya gsum dang ldan pa 'di /
NK027(sha)001:11853: thugs sras bsod nams rgyal mtshan la gnang /
NK027(sha)001:11854: kun la grags pa med gsungs dang /
NK027(sha)001:11855: de ltar lugs rnam pa lnga ru grags pa'i mdo dbang 'di /
NK027(sha)001:11856: rdul tshon gyi dkyil zhal phyes nas /
NK027(sha)001:11857: phyi dbang rgyud gyi chu bo la /
NK027(sha)001:11858: lha dbang bum gcig pa ma theb pa'i dbang brgya dang brgyad /
NK027(sha)001:11859: nang dbang la zhi bar phye ba /
NK027(sha)001:11861: bsgrub dbang la brgya dang bco lnga /
NK027(sha)001:11862: gsang dbang la gnyis su byas pa'i rnam grangs brgyad brgya dang so gcig /
NK027(sha)001:11863: lung brgyar gtad rgya dang bcas pa //
NK027(sha)001:11864: dpal 'ug pa lung du chos grwa'i zur po'i bsgrub gnas su /
NK027(sha)001:11865: gsang sngags snying 'gyur gyi mnga' bdag /
NK027(sha)001:11868: zur sh+aakya cha la sh+r+ai dang /
NK027(sha)001:11869: sh+aakya mi gnyis gnyis kyi drung du thob cing /
NK027(sha)001:11870: phyag len rgyas them dpal ldan bzang pos mdzad /
NK027(sha)001:11871: bka' drin thob pa lugs lnga'i snyan rgyud thugs gtad rjes gnang bcas pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:11872: zhal gdams yi ge bris phra thig dang bcas la /
NK027(sha)001:11873: bdag cog ro bsod nams rgyal mtshan dapalabazanga pos /
NK027(sha)001:11874: dang po bla ma bsam 'grub rdo rje drung du thob pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:11875: rjes su rin po che sh+aakya 'byung gnas kyis phyag len lnga mthong zhing /
NK027(sha)001:11876: bka' rdzogs gtad rgya dang bcas pa lan lnga thob pa bzhin /
NK027(sha)001:11877: dmigs dus kyi bstan pa'i skabs thog dang bla ma'i dgongs pa rdzogs thabs la dmigs te /
NK027(sha)001:11878: bka' bsrung mdo mgon po dbang por bzhag nas /
NK027(sha)001:11882: mi'i lu dbang du bzhin yod pa'i chos 'chad rnams dang /
NK027(sha)001:11883: dpon po rdo rje blo gros pa gnyis la gsal bzhin /
NK027(sha)001:11884: chos kyi spyan dang ldan pa /
NK027(sha)001:11885: bla ma tshul khrims bzang po /
NK027(sha)001:11886: bstan pa mi nub par bka' nyan pa yin pa /
NK027(sha)001:11887: gang zag rgyud tshod dang sbyar ba'i dbang po rab 'bring tha gsum la /
NK027(sha)001:11889: gang la gang 'dul du ston cing /
NK027(sha)001:11890: theg pa so so ba rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:11891: dbang skal so so dum bu bar byin pas rung la /
NK027(sha)001:11892: rdo rje'i blo can bka' bdag nus pa rnams la /
NK027(sha)001:11893: dbang gnyis thob kyis dus na /
NK027(sha)001:11894: mnyes pa gsum gyi bka' rgya grol te /
NK027(sha)001:11896: mdor na bka' sde zur tshos phyag len bzhin /
NK027(sha)001:11897: kahthoga pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen dam pa rnams kyi zhal thogs dang /
NK027(sha)001:11898: kham dbus gtsang gsum gyi gdul bya gang yin la mdo yongs rdzogs pa 'di /
NK027(sha)001:11906: shar phyogs kyi rgyal tshab mnga' gsol ba'i yi ge la ra rtags kyi thil gyis mnan pa'o //
NK027(sha)001:11907: bstan pa rab rgyas 'gro don mthar phyin nas /
NK027(sha)001:11908: bar chad kun bral srid zhi mnyam grol shog /
NK027(sha)001:11909: yo ga la gtso bo dkar dang ser dang 'khor tshom bu dang /
NK027(sha)001:11910: gral thab gang byas rung rgyang /
NK027(sha)001:11915: yo ga'i rdzas dbang dgos kyi drug cu rtsa gnyis /
NK027(sha)001:11916: spyir du phyi dbang brgya rtsi'i skang dang /
NK027(sha)001:11917: dbang grang dbang don rgyas pa na gsal /
NK027(sha)001:11918: phyi nang dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa lnga ni /
NK027(sha)001:11919: mchog dbang gcig tshogs ma bu gnyis /
NK027(sha)001:11930: phyi cha gsum rdo rje sems dpa' 'khor dang mgron
NK027(sha)001:11931: thams cad la gcig bsod nams gter sbyin gyi dkyil
NK027(sha)001:11932: 'khor dang / tshogs las 'bar ba tshom bu /
NK027(sha)001:11933: phrin las mtshams sbyor zhi khro dang /
NK027(sha)001:11934: rtsa ba zhi khro phrin las dang /
NK027(sha)001:11936: longs spyod tshogs dang lha mi 'jug sdud de gnyis /
NK027(sha)001:11937: lha mi la rnam snang gi ngan 'gro sbyong ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:11939: sman lha nad zhi ba dang /
NK027(sha)001:11940: snang mtha' mtshon 'khrugs zhing bam dang /
NK027(sha)001:11941: sh+aakya thub mu ge dang zhi ba lnga'o //
NK027(sha)001:11942: nyan thos la 'khor gnyis rang byung khyim pa ste /
NK027(sha)001:11944: so so skye bos mtshon pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:11948: dge bsnyen pho mo dang 'khor brgyad dang /
NK027(sha)001:11950: mchog ye shes bcu drug dang /
NK027(sha)001:11952: nang mchod gnas brten sbrul ba'am /
NK027(sha)001:11954: rang rgyal la 'khor gnyis bse ru ne tso phyi nang dang /
NK027(sha)001:11955: 'khor gnyis bse ru ne tso la gsum /
NK027(sha)001:11964: lha brgya gnas gtso bo thub pa dang /
NK027(sha)001:11973: cha gsum gtso bo phye bas dagu'o //
NK027(sha)001:11974: u pa sku mdog ye shes gtso bo'o //
NK027(sha)001:11975: yo ga rdo rje dbyings rdzogs so //
